44027027	Ma hune ko 14 hamo hamo kyo wai dawara Meditereinyen hokan mosnam pako hwore wai takurina mosore ko saku , saku hamite . Ma hun dure tei ku dunuku mosore tikminkrai ka hine hrodi kyo di kuryakedi hariti .
44027028	Hamo ko auri pyenkin rop dwaen me ho , hoe sa wainam hatomga di , wai ya gau ko 40 mites haku dyeti . Mate hatomgadi , wai ya gau ko 30 mites haku dyeti .
44027029	Ma ka hina tempwa priti , mosore ko ta ike tkmau di diti . Hamo ko anka itkoesin hamo , rop me draekin ho , mosore sigite hokan taera tombreti . Ma ka guriguri tyeti ko , kwoe kaeknada .
44027030	Ma kru mosore tmoe hominkrai ko krya hwarwerakiti . Ko mosore dingi rope krwawa , mosore hoko gwema dimoru sya wai ti aete . Ma ko anka mosore kugiten hatomgwera kraekraema homiti .
44027031	Ma Por yo ami me ka yomkra dima tyete kru mosornam hominkrai ko mosornam kwehenaemkroko , gyo dei sen braema wirin .
44027032	Hamo ami ka rope ko titigu dingi ko waia sa tete .
44027033	Ukan kae kira ku diroko , Por ya butmin ko dima prite , gyo aku 14 hamo paewi ko kudmaepu .
44027034	Hamo gyo kudin deka aikinina . Gyo butmin ko bryoko sa dei sireiki . Kru trua ya binwoe tru a gwemki dite .
44027035	Hara yo kudin sa God dima ehya dasu kudin ko tkuwa dite .
44027036	Hamo ka totokin ko wirinkusu ka tyonam kukuma hine saekusu ko kesu kudin diti .
44027037	Ma wike mosornam syeti butmin ko tu handred end sebenty siks ( 276 ) hamo .
44027038	Ma ko butmin kudua di bryokae diku , ko nasi wit ko taera wai hatyeti hamo mosore ko hukwaema tnada .
44027039	Ma kwoe kaeku ukan ko , kru mosorenam hominkrai ko to tru dyeti , ma to hoko ko braemkmaen . Ma ko to hmyenaete mate drni ko wamo ae dyeti . Hamo ka hine bra priti , kyo drni tonae wako ten tmaekina kroko kyo kuta bryoko diwe .
44027040	Harano ko mosore anka rope draekin ho titigu , wainam syamite . Hamake tari diminin sure haepki rope me draekin ho duma hreti . Sata duma hre , huhurina bai hokan tori idimo , mosore ko kugite di dima teti . Hamo sa takadi di dimiti .
44027041	Ma mosore ko taka drni tkiwa pete . Hamo kugite drni tkiwa tkoeku a tmaekite . Ma sigite ko wai takurina tkwya kira domsorite .
44027042	Hamako ami ka hine bra priti , ko wogitmin wike butmin kuwyera diti , tenam ko wai susunka taka hwarmeda .
44027043	Ma ami yomkra yo Por yen ko yo a dite . Hamo yo ka homwerakrai hosa ten dwete . Ma ya tyete , kru dika ko susunkin braema , hamroko , gyo guatumki tutura susunka di taenyai .
44027044	Ma gwin gyo mare , deipkyon o nakoe mosorenin diwa taera ho me susunknai dite . Hamo kyo butmin hamike susunka tama , di taera aikiti .
44028001	Ma kyo butmin di taerasu aikiti . Ma tonai ho ka kyo dima priti , dupi hi ya hi ko Morota du daeriti .
44028002	Ma ko kyo dima proeka dei bi gyori ka aewe dima hateti , tenam wai suru kyokinku .
44028003	Por yo dei taera drua kumta dei binae hokan hreko , sine kyomkin bangi mta , ya krite timgite .
44028004	Ya hamo timga ae , wike gwin ka diwa priti , kru hiko wike yenin kru , ma yo waia myaepu , ma Tona Hweke Dware Hoe Daenkra ya aku gawema hen ko yo a de .
44028005	Ma Por yo krite wawarmo sine ko kwasiri taka deia dura hokan syete . Ma Por yo sina yete tren ko dimaen .
44028006	Ma ko pa dyeskiti . Ka hina ya bute rwimaudi da o ma katma pwa kiritmaudi da pa dyeti . Hamo ko tmaeki pa dyetikroko di , kronam ate yo dima pkinaemku diku , ka hine ate bra diku priti yo ko tona tru diti .
44028007	Ma kua peti kuri deigwenam tru hokan homina . Ma deigwenam hoko wike dupinam hokan penkrai ka yomkra , ya hi ko Pubria , ya homina . Hamo ya kumta kyo dima kire da kyo gyori kuta ya aewe aku haepki trumo hamo hwyeti .
44028008	Ma Pubria yai ko kmin wya , gen pora kapoe me sua ai dumka aete . Hamo Por yo ta ya ri aera hokan haka , God dima twya ya krite ya ku ti hre gaikite .
44028009	Ya hamo homo gaiku dyakano , wike tren mena dupi hokan penkrai butmin pko ya hohomo gagaikiti .
44028010	Ma ko kudin me gryogryo pya sumsa kyo dima daemiti . Ma kyo hote mosore nam bra tweraku diroko , kua hodrai butmin ko mosornam breti .
44028011	Ma dwarin haepki trumo wirinku diroko kyo hote mosore tru to Areksaenda hwya kumta po kyo sya hokan bra teti . Mosore ho ya hi ko Tona Haepki Ta Tikmo Hamten . Ma swi kwoe hokeko yo dupi nam kno tonam hokan sa pamite . Hamo kyo hokan bra teti .
44028012	Ma kyo keta to Sairakrusa hokan sa hokan aku haepki trumo peti .
44028013	Hokan hwya keta to Regiam seti . Aentryo ukan hwore ko kua pkewi hoke mtete . Hamo kyo hokan hwya taka dure aentryo mate hokan hwya takasu , to Putiori seti .
44028014	Ma kyo Keriso ko drinu dinkrai wike gwin hokan po diwa , ka kyo dima hariti , gyo pura trusa kyominki hikan hunai diti . Hamo kyo hokan hwya hote Rom dima teti .
44028015	Ma Keriso ya wike Rom hokan penkrai ko kua pkrai hupe daera kumta twa taerin tonae to Apia hokan ko kyo tupmiti . Ma hote taka aenin aewe haepkitrumo tina , hokan kesu kyo ko tupmiti . Hamo Por yo ka pkrai diwa God dima tyete , gu ko waenukina da ya hin ko yomekite .
44028016	Ma kyo Rom hokan taenku diroko , Por yo aewe tru ya kumasa pen ko bryoko dite . Ma ami woda trua yo tikminina , pako yo krya tmenda .
44028017	Ma aku haepki trumo wirinku diroko , Por yo Ju yomkra ko uru pko , swa kutwyera swa hre tete . Hamo ko kumta gaemo diroko , ya ko dima tyete , no kire gyoke , no kua wike me kua koma kua kigwam ka tyo daerinkra . Hoko no hro naedmaepu . Kua wike Jerusraem hokan penkrai ka no sa Rom wike ko dima dae no wogitmiti .
44028018	Hamo ma ka no dima tondaermiti . Ma tenam no pumaekin hweke tru hre ko dimaepu hamo ko no hma hre tnada .
44028019	Ma Ju wike ko a diti . Hamo no Rom yomkra ya no begemna de , ma no wike ko dima kyom swa tru aemaepu .
44028020	Tenam hakina kren nokwa ureko , gyo pko diwa , swa twyera .
44028021	Ka yo dima tyeti , kyo kwo tru Judia hokan kima hre pko simaepu . Ma kua wike hokan hwya pkewi ko swa tru hakin sapkmaepu . Ma gwa swa swokin tru tmyaepun .
44028022	Hamo kyo gwa hine bren ho tyo daerwera , tenam wike guminki gaema swa tyenkrai , wike gwin ka harinkrai ko ko duwa virin dinkrai .
44028023	Hamo ko aku tru hya hreti . Hamo aku hoko pko diroko wike pya kumta Por ya aewe hokan gaemiti . Hamo diroko Por yo God ya wike tikmin swa ko ukan komdwa naegimi tete troko hun kusu naedite . Ma Yesu ko drinu God ya pru msyen swa ho naegimaka mate koma Moses ya kimite ho naegimaka , mate God ya tyo tyen wike ka kimiti swa ho ko dima naegimaka hamite .
44028024	Hamo wike gwin ko daera drinu diti . Ma gwin ko daera hiko drinu swa dmaepu .
44028025	Hamo ko asi tamaka gwin ko swa ate tyo , ma gwin ko swa ate tyo , hamike tamiti . Ka hro teti , tenam ko Por yo swa trusa hirike tyenku . Ya tyete ko God ya Durea kru Aisaia ya mgatram gite gua kigwam ko dima dumasa tyena .
44028026	Aisaia ya tyete , gu kuta wike ko dima tnya gyo daerinsu daeryeiki ma drike a sireiki . Ma gyo drurinsu druryeiki ma a direiki .
44028027	Tenam tonesu ho ka hine ko nononkina kren . Ka kehenam a daermeda ka kehenam ko tutuminkrai , ka krona me dimeda ka krona ko pupukinkrai . Pako no dima pko nokwa homo ko gagaikmeda dina .
44028028	Por ya hara naede tyete , bryoko , gyo hamosu braemknai , God ya warmin swa ko swa ate wike ko dima pru tena . Hamo ko daeryeiki .
44028030	Ma ambum haepki hamo Por yo aewe tru , ya henin hoe ko yaesa dae yo hokan hete . Ma wike dika yo diwera pko diroko , kyo paka swa kutwye demite .
44028031	Ma kru trua to ya naegimin ten dumaepu . Hamo yo God ya wike tikminkra swa me mate Yesu Keriso ya swa ko yo ai mesa naegimamite .
45001001	No hi ko Por . No ko Yesu Keriso ya tmoe homnada hro sen kru . Ya no diwa urite . Yo hoda no ya hupe waenukin naegimnano dite .
45001002	Uminki , God ya tyo tyenin wike ko God ya tyo kimiti . Ko hamosu hupe waenukin pko daerwekraiha diti .
45001003	Hupe waenukin hiko God ya kya Yesu Keriso , kua Yomkra ya swa . Ma yo ko wikma hamteti . Ma yo ko King Debid ya kyankya .
45001004	Ma yo ko God . Tenam ya ware ko God ya ware ho bryoko . Ma yo pwako , yo hote warmo durkyo asite .
45001005	Ma God ya yo dima tyo , yo no ko ya swa tyenin kruknada no sa hrete . Tmoe hiko waenukina . No Keriso ya swa , wike to hoe hoe butmin hamo ko dima naegimo , ko daera drinu da homnaida .
45001006	Hamo Rom wike swa hiko gyo dima kesu aera . God ya gyo urite . Yo gyo Yesu Keriso ya wikemnaida .
45001007	Hamo nokwa kwo hi kimrako wike dika Rom hokan penkrai ko God ya wike diko dima proeka hine pya braka ya wikeknaida urite , gyo dima hi kimraha .
45001008	Ma no yatumki swa hi tyerakra . No gua dware no Yesu Keriso yo dima tyo ya God dima tye , God gu ko duwa dra . No hirya , tenam wike to hoe hoe butmin ko gua God ko drinu dinkrai ko du daerinkrai .
45001009	God yo braema nokwa trya ko drinu , no aku butmin gua hi me gua kronam ko God dima tyenkra . Ma God ya kya hupe waenukin ko no proenam ae butmin naegiminkra . Ma God yo braema nokwa yo dima gua swa tyenkra ko .
45001010	No tyaka hirike kentinkra , hamo ya hoda droko no kurisu kuta gyominki swa tyera .
45001011	No hine pya brenkra , no gyo dyerada . Tenam ko gyo me paka God ya swa naegimo , gua hine bren ko aiknaida .
45001012	Nokwa trya drike ko nokwa gyo naegimo gua hine bren taetaepmo , no hine bren gua taetaepmo haminina .
45001013	Kire gyoke , gyo braemknaida , aku pya no gyo dima pkirada hine pya brenkra , ma kronam ate nokwa pkin ko ten dwenkra . No wike gwin ko naegimo ko waenuma penkrai , hote ho bryoko gyo kesu hamira da hine brenkra .
45001014	Nokwa sumsa sen hoko , no hote wike gwin ko dima daemira . Wike to hyenu penkrai da mate wike dei dure penkrai da mate braemkin wike da mate braemkin dumkin wike ko dima daemira .
45001015	Hakina krenku , no hoda wike Rom hokan penkrai gyo dima kesu Yesu ya hupe waenukin hoko tyadaemirada .
45001016	No braema God ya hupe waenukin ko aiya . Hamo kru ara dika ka hina hupe hoko drinu droko , God ya ai ko warmin braema . Ma Ju wike ko swa hi ko katumki daeriti . Ma wike gwin ko marensu daeriti .
45001017	Hupe waenukin ya tyen ko hiwa . God ya wike ko ya swa ko drinu dinkrai ko , ya ko duminkra dina . Hamo Kwonam kima tyen ko harina , kru ara dika ka God ya swa ko dumahaki du , God ya ko dumra droko ko warka hureiki .
45001018	Ma God yo hwekmin wike ko dima kyomkinkra . Tenam ko ya swa ko duma tyen ko ko a dinkrai .
45001019	Ko braema God ya kronam ko , tenam God yo hoko ko dima naegite . Hamo yo ko dima dore dae .
45001020	Songmena gryo butmin ko God ya homa hrenaha ma ko ho dyaka ya ai ko tei atka yae yosa hakina aepesu aenkra ho diwa braemkinkrai . Hamo ko God ko diwake du , ka drinu dinaemkin ya hoe tigin braema wirin .
45001021	Ko braema God ko , ma ko yo dima drinu gu ko God harinkmaepu . Hamaka ko yo dima duwa , gu kyo waenuma tikminkra dinkmaepu . Hamo ko yo dima hine hamasa brenkrai howa , ma ka hine ko nononka hunam pena dinaekina .
45001022	Ka tyenkrai , ko ko braemnain wike da no , ko nononkiti .
45001023	Hamake ko God Kwoe kom penkra ya kine tei atka waenuka yae yo sa hakina aepesu henin yo dima hine brumaepu . Ko ike me dei sa wikma homa ware gryogryo , smire da sine da , tosura domkmaekin ho dinaeka hohoma ko dima hine pya brenkrai .
45001024	Hamo diku , God yo ko hro naedu , kae ka buta hodra hosa swoswoma hominkrai .
45001025	Ko God ya swa duma tyen ho tyenkmaepu . Ko swa ho sa krwyo atma kraekraema tyenkrai . Hamo ko gryogryo God ya homin , ho dima tyaka , yanai yae yosa hakina yo dima swa tmyaepu . Hi ko drinu .
45001026	Tenam ko kronam swokin hamike homo diku , God yo pa dyeskinkra . Ara ko ka kru me kwenkmaepu , ko kronam ate hominkrai .
45001027	Ma kru ko kesu ara me kwenkmaepu , ko hoda kru kaesa kronam swokin hominkrai . Hakina krenku ka kronam swokin ho hominkrai hoe ko kaesa dore dyenkrai .
45001028	Ma ko God dima hine bren ko a du , God yo ko kworu ko hine ate bra kronam swokinsa homiskinkrai .
45001029	Ka hin ko kronam swokin ate ate homwera dinkrai . Ko grimka , gwoegwoeka , wike tuma yaka , kraekraemaka swa bukramgite kutyaka , su tyaka , God ko ko a deka , ikaremaka , irenka , kai kaem ka swa prikmaka , hine yoma brenaemka , swagumin tyen kyaka , proekinaemka , hamike hominkrai .
45001030	
45001031	
45001032	Ma ko braema God ya tyen ko , wike dika himike homroko hoe ko pwensa . Ma ko kronam swoka hakin hominsku wike gwin ko kesu diwano ko hoko duwa dinkrai .
45002001	Kire gyoke , gyo wike gwin begemraike . Gyo swa tru rwyo tyen braema wirin . Ma gyo kesu haminkroko , guae gyo kesu ho begemraiha .
45002002	Wike ko kronam ho hominkrai ko ma God ya ko begemroko hoko duwa .
45002003	Kire gue , gu wike gwin begeminkraha . Ma gu kesu kronam ho bryoko hominkra . Gu hine hrodi God yo gu a begemike .
45002004	Ma God yo gwa hweke dore katma a daemaekra . Yo gu dima proeka pa dyeskra . Hoko gu braema wirinne . Ma gu braema di , ma gu ho dima hine brumaepuha . Yo gu dima proeka pa dyenkra ko tenam yo hoda gu gwa kronam swokin dima a da hro naedrnada .
45002005	Ma gwa proe ko tukinsa . Gwa hweke hro naedin ko gu a da , hweke ya hoe hoko a se dinkra . Hakina kren , God ya begemin aku hoko pko diroko , yo gu begemo dore hyena dye .
45002006	Hokeko God yo wike butmin ko tmoe naekin homiti hoe ho bryoko daemi .
45002007	Ma wike gwin ko waenuma paka tmoe waenua homaka , ware dyaen dyaen sen ho hine brenkrai . Hamo God yo ware dyaendyaen ho ko dima dae .
45002008	Ma wike gwin ko kae ka hodrai ho sa hine bra homakano , God ya tyo daera a da no , kronam swokin sa hine bra hominkrai . God yo ko dima kyomkikraha .
45002009	Kru ara dika ko hweke turoko , ko tren me pyenkin direiki . Ju wike ko katumki dore hakin ko dyaewi , ma swa ate wike ko maresu direiki .
45002010	Ma wike dika kronam waenuma hominkrai ko God yo ka hi hyenmaka waenuma pen daeka hami .
45002011	Tenam God yo wike butmin bryoko begeminkra .
45002012	Swa ate wike ko Moses ya koma ko ko braemkmaepu . Ma ka hweke turoko dore kesu direiki . Ma Ju wike ka koma ko aera . Ma hweke turoko koma swa hoa begemi .
45002013	Tenam wike ko God ya koma swa daeriskroko , God ya ko dima dumnaiha dinkmaepu . Daera homin wikesa ko God ya ko duminkra .
45002014	Ma swa ate ate wike ko God ya Koma kimin ko ko braema wirin . Ma ko kaesa koma ya tyen homroko ka naegiminkrai hi ko ka koma .
45002015	Ka hominkrai kyo dima naegiminkra koma ya tyen ko ka proe ti kimina . Ka kunam kesu kimina . Ma ka hina tyen ko aku tru ko duma hominkrai ma aku tru ko swoma hominkra dinkrai .
45002016	Ma aku tru ko pki . Aku hoko pko diroko , God ya pru Yesu Keriso ya wike butmin ka hine gwegwemin ho begemi . Hamo God ya hi homikra swa ho no tyadaeminkra .
45002017	Ma gyo harinkrai , kyo ko Ju wike dinkrai . Ma koma ko kyo braema , ma hoa kyo begemin braema wirin , ma kyo ko God ya wike dinkrai .
45002018	Gyo braema God ya hoda dinkra ko , hamake gyo koma tyen ko hyaeka kronam di ko duwa , ma di ko swokina , hoko gyo braema .
45002019	Ma gua hin ko wike kron dworokina dinaekina ko gyo ka gyori ten wike . Ma wike hunam pena dinaekin ka kae ko gyoha dinkrai .
45002020	Gua hin ko gyo ko nononkin wike ka naegimin wike ko gyoha . Gua hin ko koma ko gyo braema ma hoato braemkin butmin ko aeraha .
45002021	Ma gyo wike gwin naegiminkrai , ma guae gyo ko naegiminkmaepune . Gyo wike gwin naegimaka , uma siromoe dinkrai , ma gyo kesu uma taerinkraike .
45002022	Ma gyo aeng tirome dinkrai . Ma gyo kesu aeng tyenkraike . Gyo tona wike ka kriteme homin ho dima swa tyenina wirin dinkrai . Ma gyo gryo kritme homin aewe hokan gryo twen ko gua kuta uma taerinkraike .
45002023	Ma gyo irinme tyaka , God ya koma ko kyo dima aera dinkrai . Ma gyo God ya koma kyenkraike . Hamroko God dima hukwae daen braema .
45002024	God ya Kwonam kima tyen ko harina , Ju wike gua hamike hominkrai kren , swa ate wike ko God dima swa swokin tyenkrai .
45002025	Ma gyo koma swa daera homroko , gua kate tigin kronam ko drikmena , ma gyo koma daera hominaemkroko , gyo ko kate tiginaemkin ho bryoko .
45002026	Ma swa ate wike ka kate ko tiginkmaepu . Ma kudi ko koma swa daera homroko , hamroko , God ya hin ko ko kate tigin wike bryoko wirinne .
45002027	Ma koma ko gyo dima kimina aera , ma gua kate ko tigina , ma gyo koma ho kyenkrai . Hamo swa ate wike ko gyo dima keidikeidima tryeiki .
45002028	Ma di ko Ju krunune . Kru di ko kate tigin kronam nu senane . Kru di ya kate graegitensa ko tigina hoa wirin .
45002029	Ma Ju nu ko hiwa , kru diya ya tyonam ko Ju yo ko howa . Ya proe ko tigin kru ho . Ma tmoe hi ko God ya Dure ya tmoe . Hoko koma ya tmoe wirin . Kru hakemin ko God ya ko dima gyo ko bryoko dinkra , wike ka wirin .
45003001	Hakina krenku , wike gwin ka hine brumaudi , hamo Ju wike ko kronam tru aerake , hamo ko wike gwin dimkinane . Ma kate tiginkrai hoko taetaepminane .
45003002	Heno , Ju din ko drike mena , ma drike tru ko hiwa . Uminki God ya swa ko Ju wike ko dima tyo , ka daera sa tikmnaida .
45003003	Ma drinu din wike gwin hoa , swa hiko daera drinu dinaemka duma homaepu . Hakina kren , God yo kesu ya tyen hoko yae kimaudi .
45003004	Wirinsa . Wike butmin ko kraekraemin wike dini , ma God yasa ko kraekraema tyen braema wirin . Kwonam kima tyen ko hirina , Gu swa naekin tryoko , gu dumasa tyenkra . Ma wike ka gu begemroko , gu dumasa tyaka ko dimki .
45003005	Ma kudi kua kronam swokin hominkrai hoa God ya kronam waenukin hoko naegimroko God yo kua dore daeroko hoko bryoko wirin din braemane . ( Ma to hyenu wike gwin ka hin harike bra tyenkrai . )
45003006	Wirin wirinsa . Kutadi God yo ko waenuma begeminaemkin kru hamroko , yo naemike kru ara butmin ko begemin braemane .
45003007	Ma kudi no swa duma a tmyaekin ho tryoko , ma God ya duma tyen ho naegimroko , ma naemo diwa ya no ko hwekmin kru dmawe .
45003008	Hakina kren kyo harike twye , kyo kronam swokin homroko , kronam dukin pkin braema dwe . Ma wike gwin ka no dima harewi , swa hiko gwa tyereke da no keidimaewi . Ma ko marensu dumasa ka hoe sireiki .
45003009	Ma Ju wike kuasa ko duwane , ma swa ate wike ko duwa wirinsane . Wirin . No sem gyo dima naegima naede , Ju wike da mate wike ate kyo butmin ko hwekea dmyaena .
45003010	Kwonam kima tyen ko harina , kru trua waenukiskina hmaepu .
45003011	Ma God ya braemkin sen kru tru ko hmaepu . God gu ko hya din kru ko hmaepu .
45003012	Wike butmin ko God ko hro krwyo tena , hamakano , butmin ko hwekesa twenkrai . Kru trua kronam dukin hominkmaepu .
45003013	Ma ka swa ko pwen pom dinaekina , swoswokina . Kraekraemin swa da mate kyomkin swa da ma ka ti twomnam tyenkrai , sina timga wai dripminkrai ho bryoko .
45003014	Ko gu puna harike tyenkrai .
45003015	Ko wike ko katmasa yaka tuma yenkrai .
45003016	Ko dike troko wike ko domsora hro tenkrai .
45003017	Waenuma pen kronam ko ko braema wirin .
45003018	Ma ko God dima tempwen braema wirin .
45003019	Kyo braema wike dika koma trya ho daera homwera dinkrai ko koma ya tyen hoe butmin ko dima ko aera . Hamo kru truato no koma kyenkmaepu din braema wirin . Hakina kren , wike butmin ko koma kyenkrai kren , God yo ko begemi .
45003020	Ma kru trua koma ya tyen homroko , hamroko , God ya kru ho dumin braema wirin . Koma ya tmoe ko , wike ko dima naegiminkra ko , ko koma kyen wikeha dinkra .
45003021	Ma aekwa ko God ya kronam wike ka yo dima duminkra ho naegiminina . Hoko koma ya tyenkra ho wirin . Hi ko Moses ya koma swa kimin ho ma God ya tyo tyadaemin wike ko kesu swa hi naegimamiti .
45003022	Hamo wike dika Yesu Keriso yo dima dumahaki droko , God yo ko dumi . Hamo kru ara dika ko haryoko , no hina drinu God ya pru pken kru ya no hweke dware hoe ko ya pwete droko , God ya kru ara ho dima tye , gu ko dumnaha dikraha . Tenam wike butmin ko bryokosa .
45003023	Butmin kyo ko hwekmena krenku , kyo God ya po pen kronam kwori wenema penkrai .
45003024	Ma God yo ya proeki hamaha din ko wike ko dima sumsa daen ho me yo Yesu Keriso pru ya wike ko hma hro ko dima dumnaiha dinkra .
45003025	God ya Yesu daete . Hamo ya pwen ho me wike dika ya pwete dima dumahaki droko kua hweke ko hamaha din braema . God ya homina homite , tenam ya naegimira hweke ko yo a da hoko begema hoe ho daete . Semina yo pa dyeskite , yo wike ka dore katma daemaen . Ma aekwa yo ka hweke naegima begiminkra tenam ya naegimira hweke ko yo a . Ma ya kronam ko hweke dumka , hweke begema hoe dae dumira ho naegimo , kru ara dika ko Yesu ko no hweke hoe sete du , God yo ka hweke hoe a dae , ma ko ko kwasu dukra harinkra .
45003026	
45003027	Hamo kyo naekin homaka kua hi hyenmawe . Kronam tru wirin . Naemo diwa kyo kua hi ko hyenmin braema wirinne . Tenam ko kyo kua koma swa sa daera hominkrai hoane . Wirin , tenam kyo Yesu ya homite swasa daera kua hina drinu diti kren .
45003028	Hamo kua hine brenkrai ko hiwa , kru ara dika ko Yesu ya homite ho dima dumahaki du diroko , God ya tyenkra , no ko dumina dinkra . Ma ko koma swa sa daera hominkrai kroko , hoato God yo diwa , gyo dumraiha dmaepu .
45003029	Ma God yo ko Ju wike ka God sa ne . Ma yo ko swa ate ate wike ka God wirinne . Wirin . Yo ko wike butmin ka God .
45003030	Hamo God ko trusa . Yo Ju wike dika ya swa ko drinu du diroko , ya ko dumi , ma swa ate wike ko kesu ya swa ko drinu du diroko , ya ko kesu dumi .
45003031	Ma haminkrai kren ya drike ko kyo koma Kwonam kimin ko hro naedraike , Wirin . Kyo Koma ho ko drik mina dinkrai .
45004001	Ma kua kigwam Abraham ko . Hamo kyo yo dima naerike tmyawe . Ma God ya yo dima nakoe homiteke .
45004002	Kutadi ya tmoe tru homite kroko , God ya yo dumite , hamroko yae yo rwyo irin ko bryoko . Ma God ya kinaetegite irin ko drike wirin .
45004003	Tenam Kwonam kima ya tyen ko Abraham ya hine God ko ya swa ko dumraha du God ya yo dima dumraha dite .
45004004	Ma kru ara diya yo to hyenu tmoe homa ya hoe siroko , hoko proekin daera harinkmaepu . Ya hoe sira ko ya tmoe homin dware .
45004005	Ma kru trua harikraha , nokwa hina no God dumahaki dite hoasa no taetaepmi , ma no tmoe homin hoa wirin dinkra . Hamaka ya hina God ya wike hwek min ko dima gyo ko hweke dumkina dinkra . Hamo God ya hina kru ho ya dumahaki din hoa yo kru ho ko duwa dinkra .
45004006	Ma Debid yo kesu uminki tyena ya drike ko howa . Ya tyete ko wike diko God ya ko dima gyo ko duwa dinkra , ma ko sem kronam tru dukin homaewidi ma homaepudi , wike hoko yoyomki penkrai .
45004007	Debid ya tyete ko , wike diko God ya ka , hweke hamaha dina ma ka hweke swa ko yo kwonam a kimi , wike hoko yoyomkinkrai .
45004008	
45004009	Ma yoyomkin dra Debid ya tyete hoko wike ka kate tigina God yo ko dimasa daemike . Wirin . Kate tiginaemkin ko dima kesu . Tenam Kwonam kima tyo nokwa trya , Abraham ya God ya tyena ko yo homikraha du , God ya yo ko kru duwa , bryoko dite .
45004010	God yo dikroke hirike tyeteke . Abraham yo kate ko tigina hokene ma tiginaemkina , hokene . Tiginaemkia hoke .
45004011	Ya kate ko marensu tigite . Ma ya kate tigin ho naeginkra ko , God ya yo ko duwa , bryoko dinkra , tenam ya yo dima tyen ko drinu dinku . God ya hi hirite , Abraham ya kate ko tiginaemkin hoke . Hamo wike dika kate tiginaemka God dima drinu da dumahaki din wike ka hya tenin kru ko Abrahamha .
45004012	Ma yo ko kate tigin wike ka hya ten kru kesu . Hoko wike dika ka kate tigina ma ko God ya tyen ko yo homikraha harike da penkrai ko ko Abraham ho bryoko , ya kate tiginaemkin aku hoke .
45004013	God ya Abraham ya kya me ka kya me ko dima tyete to hyenu ko yana kikraha harite . Yo harite tenam Abraham yo Koma tyo ho daera homite kren hoa wirin . Yo harite tenam Abraham ya hina God ya tyen ko homikraha du , God ya yo , ko duwa dite .
45004014	Ma kudi God ya swagumin ko koma daera hominkrai ko dima daeroko , wike ko God ya swa ko drinu tyen ko drike dumkina , ma God ya swagumin kesu ko drike dumkina .
45004015	Ma koma ho ko God ya kyoma sapkinkra . Ma koma ko aenaemkroko , wike ko koma ho kyen braema wirin .
45004016	Ma God ya swagumite ko Abraham yo dumahakite kren yo dima aete . Hamo Abraham ya kyankya butmin ko God ya swagumite ko , ko sumsa sireiki . Koma daera homin wike ko dimasa daena wirin , God ya swa ko drinu dinkrai ko dima kesu dae .
45004017	Kwonam tru kima tyen ko harina , Abraham yo ko wike pya tei ate ate kai ko gu . God ya swagumin hoe ko yo . God yo wike tosurin dinaekin ko uru ko hote hwyen braema . Ma penaemkin ko pen braema .
45004018	Abraham yo God ya swa dumahaki da sekraha dite . Ma hokeko ya sekra ko dimaepu . Hamo yo wike butmin kai kite . Kwonam kima tyen ko harina , gwa kyankya ko pute bryoko kwari hyaekin ko bryoko wirin .
45004019	Hokeko , ya ambum hyaekin ko 100 simaekite . Ma yo ya bute ko sem pwena dinaekina ho hine braka mate Sera yo kesu kya bra imae ko sem arikina ho hine bra ko , ya dumahaki din ko dropkmaepu .
45004020	Ya dumahaki din ko kworinaemka , God ya swagumite ko bubutkinaemka hamite . Ma dumahaki hoa yo ai dae , God dima ehya dite .
45004021	Yo hine bra braemki naede tyete , God ya swagumite ko homin braema dite .
45004022	Ya harike tyenku God yo Abraham ko duwa dite .
45004023	Ma Kwonam kima tyena yo ko duwa dra , hoko Abraham ya swasa wirin .
45004024	Swa hoko dikua kua hine ko Komin kru yo kua Yomkra Yesu yo pwo durkyo asite du , ma God ya kyo ko dumraiha dikraha , wike kyo , swa hoko kyo dima ko aera .
45004025	God ya tyo , Yesu yo pwete , kua hweke dware . Hamo yo durkyo asite tenam God ya kyo diwa kyo ko hweke dumka dumasa pen ho bryoko dinkra .
45005001	Tenam kyo God ya tyen dima duma haki dinku God ya kyo diwa duwa dinkra . Hamo kwasu kyo God yo dima ganeswama waenuma penkrai . Ma hi ko Yomkra Yesu Keriso yo dima dae ya kyo dima daete .
45005002	Kyo ya swa ko drinu dinkrai kren , God ya proekin kronam kyo dima naegimo kyo kwasu hi daeri hurai .
45005003	Hamo kyo irin me yoyomkin me huma hwyaka , God ya kronam waenukin hureiki dinkrai . Hamake pyenkin kyo dima pko diroko irinkwe . Tenam kyo braema , pyen ko kyo dima pkrai ko kua hine bren ko aikinkrai .
45005004	Ma kua hin bren ko aikiskroko , God ya ho diwa duwa dinkra . Ma ya kyo dima duwa dinku , kyo huma paka hoe direiki .
45005005	Ma kyo ya hoe siwera huma proko , kyo pyenema penkmaepu . Tenam God ya proekin ya Dure dima dae kua proenam twenkra . God ya Dure hoko kyo dima sumsa daena .
45005006	Ma kyo ko kya dinaekina hwyeti , hamo aku diko God ya tyete , hokeko , Keriso yo wike swoswokemin ko dima pwete .
45005007	Ma kru trua yo kru waenukin yo dima pwen ko tukina . Ma dikani kru trua yo kru dukin yo dima pumaudi .
45005008	Ma God ya proekin kronam kyo dima naegimite . Hamo kyo ko hwekmesa kwo diwa , Keriso ya kyo dima pwete .
45005009	Ma ya pwete kren , God ya kyo diwa bryoko dinkra . Hamo God ya kyo dima kyomkmeda yo hote hata ten ho dwe .
45005010	Ma uminki kyo God dima totetyamiti . Hamo ya kya pwenku kwasu kyo ko ya kire dinkra . Hamo tenam kyo ko God ya kire dinkra kren , Keriso warme henkra ya kyo waenuma tikmin braema .
45005011	Ma hosa wirin .
45005012	Ma hwekeko , kru trusa yo gitma to hyenu dima pkina . Hamo ya hweke hrete kren , pwen kesu pkite . Ma aekwa to hyenu wike butmin ko tosurinkrai . Tenam kyo butmin hwek mina kren .
45005013	Ma hweke ko to hyenu hikan aete hokeko koma ko daemaepu . Ma koma daenaemkin hokeko , hweke ko hyaekmaepu .
45005014	Ma Adam ya he kumta Moses yo taenku dure hokan wike ko tosuriti . Hamo Adam ya hweke ko God ya swa daera hominaemkin hweke hakin ho hrimaepu ko hweke ate tweti hoa ko tosuriti .
45005015	Ma kru haepki ho ti ta drike ko trusa wirin . Tenam God ya proeki daen ko Adam ya hweke hren ho bryoko , wirin . Drinu , wike pya ko tosuriti , tenam kru truasa hweke hrete kren . Ma God ya proekin ko hata . Hamo ya sumsa daen ko wike pya ko dima daete ma ho kesu ko hata . Ma ya proekin kronam ko kru trusa , Yesu Keriso yo dima dae , ya kyo dima daete .
45005016	Ma God ya daen me mate kru tru ya hweke hoa ti ko atkina . Hweke trua hrae , God ya diwa begema tyete hoko hwekeha dite . Ma marensu wike ko hweke pya two , God ya diwa proeka tyete , hweke dware gronka dore a dae dite .
45005017	Drinu kru trua hweke hrete hoa pwen ko pkite . Ma kru tru , Yesu Keriso ya homite , hoe ko hyena pkite . Hamo kru ara butmin , dika God ya proekin hyenu ho siroko , God ya ko sumsa dudumo ko Keriso yo sena kren ko ware hi sireiki .
45005018	Hamo hweke trusa hreti krenku , ya hoe ko wike butmin ko dore dyen direiki . Hote ho bryoko , kronam dukin trusa homite kren , ya hoe ko wike butmin ka hweke dore a direiki . Ko ware dyaen dyaen hamo hureiki .
45005019	Ma wike butmin ko hweke min kiti , tenam kru trua yo God ya swa daera homaepu kren , hote ho bryoko ko butmin ko God dima bryokaereiki , tenam kru trua yo God ya swa daera homite kren .
45005020	Ma koma ko pkite . Hamo ko koma ho braemki kiya ko , hweke ko hote hyenkite . Ma hweke ko hyenku diroko , God yo huma pa dyaka , dore katma daemaepu .
45005021	Ma hweke , ya wike tikmamo ko tosurinkrai . Ma aekwa ko God ya proekin hoa kyo tikmo kyo kronam dukin hominkrai . Ma God ya kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso pru yo kyo gyori kuta yominki to waenukin hokan preiki .
45006001	Hamo kyo naerike tmyawe . Kyo kua hweke me hamo penkmawe , ma hamroko , God ya proekin kronam ko hyenkin braemane . Hamawe .
45006002	Wirin wirinsa . Kyo ko hweke dima pwen dinaekina . Hamo kyo naemike hwek me hamo hwyen braemane .
45006003	Gyo braema , kyo baeptais dite ko , Yesu Keriso ya hinam yo me pkori , pwena dinaekiti .
45006004	Ma kyo wai bra yetiko , kyo yome pkori giwa brena dinaekiti . Hamo Yai ya aia Keriso ko warmo durkyo asite , hote ho bryoko , kyo kesu warka asi ninka hwyenina .
45006005	Ma kyo yominki pkorina kren , ya pwete , hamo kyo kesu yominki pwena dinaekite . Ma yo warmo asite , hamo hote ho bryoko kyo kesu warmo asryeiki .
45006006	Ma kyo braema kua kronam brunai ko Keriso yominki dei pwenin hokan hro tuma yeti . Hamo hweke , kua tyonam gite aera hoko wirinmirada . Hamo kyo Hweke ya tyo daera hominina wirin .
45006007	Tenam wike ko puroko hweke ya aia ko tikmin braema wirin .
45006008	Ma tenam kyo Keriso yominki pwenku , kyo braema kyo yominki hureiki .
45006009	Kyo braema Keriso ko durkyo asite . Yo hote a pwi . Pwen kato yo a tikmreiki .
45006010	Tenam yo aku trusa pwa hweke ya ai domsorite . Ma yo aekwa ko God yominki henkra .
45006011	Ma Hwekea gyo urioko guae rwyo gyo dima harike hine brenknai , no ko pwena dinaekina dinknai . Ma kyo God yominki ware aepesu hamo hwyenkrai , tenam Yesu Keriso yo ten yo dima homite kren .
45006012	Hweke ya gua bute tikminina wirin . Hamroko gyo tikmroko gua buta ka hodrai ko hominsa . Haminina wirin .
45006013	Gua bute braeke ko kronam swokin homnaida daeromoe . Gyo guasa God dima daenkra . Gyo ko pwen hokan warmo ae pkina . Hamo gua bute butmin kronam waenukin hominaete God dima daenina .
45006014	Hweke ko gua yomkra da hrenina wirin . Gyo koma ya tryasa daera hominina wirin . Gyo God ya proekin kronam hamike hominina .
45006015	Hamo kyo naemawe . Tenam koma ko kyo tikminaemka , God ya proekina kyo tikminkra kren , kyo hweke hrimawe . Wirinsa .
45006016	Gyo braema . Kudi gyo kru trua gyo hro sena kroko ya swasa daera hominina . Ma hweke ya tyo daera homroko , hoe ko pwensa . Ma God ya gyo tikmo ya swa daera homroko ya gyo ko duwa di .
45006017	Ma no God dima gu ko waenukina dra . Tenam uminki gyo ko hweke ya tmoesa homamiti . Ma drinu swa gyo dima naegimo gyo daera hoko drinuda gua proe me hominkrai .
45006018	Ma hweke ya aia gyo wogitmina kren gyo ya tmoe homamiti . Hamo God ya gyo hma hre , gyo yomkra waenukin ya tmoe hominkrai .
45006019	( No aku butmin swa gua braem hosa handruri tyenkra , tenam gyo hosa braema kren . ) Sem uminki gyo hweke ya tmoesa homamiti . Ma gyo kronam swokin ate ate pya homamiti . Hote ho bryoko aekwa God ya kronam waenukinsa hominknai .
45006020	Ma gyo hweke ya tmoe homi hwyetiko , gyo kronam dukin me homaepu .
45006021	Hamo gyo kronam ho homamiti ko aekwa gyo ho hine bradi hukwaekinkraiha . Ma ya hoe ko nakoene . Hoe ko pwensa .
45006022	Ma aekwako , hweke gyo tikminko hmuri two , God ya gyo tikminkra . Haminku guane butmin ko God yana . Hamo hoe ko , God yominki ware dyaen dyaen hyenina .
45006023	Hweke turoko , hoe ko pwen . Ma God ya sumsa daen ko , kyo Yomkra Yesu Keriso yominki dyaen dyaen hamo hwyenina .
45007001	No kire gyoke , no swa hi tyerakra ko gyo braemkrai , tenam koma swa ko gyo braema . Wike ware me hurai ko , koma ya tryasa daera hominkrai .
45007002	Hamo hoko hikina . Ma ara ya kru siroko , ara ya kru yo heskroko , koma ya tyena kren , ya kru mesa kwehwyenina . Ma yo puroko , koma ya tyen , yominki kwenina din ko wirinkra .
45007003	Ma kudi ara ho , ya kru ko po , ma yo kru truminki kwehroko , yo ko kore tyen ara dinkrai .
45007004	Gyo kesu ko hikina . Koma ho dima , gyo kesu ko tosurin ho bryoko , tenam gyo kesu ko Keriso ya bute . Hamo yo pwa durkyaete . Ma aekwa gyo ko yana . Hamo kyo God ya tmoe waenuma homnada .
45007005	Ma kuae kua hodrai hamike homiti ko , Koma ya tyen ho hyaeka braemki kronam swokin homamiti . Hamo hoko kyo pwen tmoe homiti .
45007006	Ma uminki koma ko ya kyo wogitmite . Ma kyo koma ho dima hine brenkra ko kyo ko tosurin dinaekina . Ma aekwa kyo hmuri twena hurai . Ma kronam brunai , Koma kima tyen hamike hominkmaepu . Kyo kronam nin , Dure ya kronam , hamike hominkrai .
45007007	Hamo kyo hirike tmyawe . Koma ko swokina dmawe . Wirin . Ma kudi koma wirin hamroko hweke ya drike no braemkin braema wirin . Ma kudi Koma ya tyen ko wike gwin ka gryo tru gua siwera da hine brenkromoe harinaemkroko , no hine hamike a bre .
45007008	Ma Koma ho pkina , hamo hoa hweke ko no tyonam gite homo , hamo no gwoegwoeka gryogryo ate ate hoda dite .
45007009	No uminki koma braemkinaekin hokeko no waenuma hete . Ma koma ya pkite ko , hweke kesu pkite .
45007010	Hamo no pwete . Ma koma ya drike ko waenuma peninada . Ma no dima ko pwensa sapkite .
45007011	Ma hweke ko ya ten diwa , koma ho me no dima kraekraema pwene yete .
45007012	Ma God ya Koma ko waenukin yaeyosa hakina . Ma God ya homnaida din swa kesu ko waenukina .
45007013	Hamo drike ko naekinane , kronam waenukin hoa no pwen yeteke . Wirin . Hweke ya no yete . Hwekea kronam waenukin sa kumta ho me no pwene yete . Hamo hweke ya drikenu naegu dyen braema Hamo koma hoa hweke ya kronam swoswokin ho naegimu braemkin braema .
45007014	Kyo braema Koma ko dure yana God ya daena . Ma no ko to hyenu wikesa . Hamo hweke ya ya tmoe homnada no hro sete .
45007015	No braema wirin nokwa homra ko . Ma nokwa homira dinkra ko no hominkmaepu . Ma nokwa a homi dra ko hoko nokwa hominkra .
45007016	Tenam nokwa hominkra ko no a dinkra , hoa haeginkra ko , no hine Koma ko duwa .
45007017	Himike ko nokwa hominkmaepu , hweke no tyonam henkra , ya hominkra .
45007018	No braema kronam waenukin ko no tyonam aemaepu . Ma hoko no hinam hokan aemaepu . Ma no kronam dukin homiradi , ma no a homaekinkra .
45007019	Ma no kronam waenukin homira dinkra ma no hoko hominkmaepu . Ma no kronam swokin ko no a dinkra ma no hoko hominkra .
45007020	Hamo nokwa no a dasu hominkra hoko nokwa hominkmaepu . Hweke no tyonamgite aenkra ya hominkra .
45007021	Ma no kronam hikin dyenkra . No kronam dukin homira kwerma , no kronam swokinsa dyenkra .
45007022	Ma no tyonam ko God ya koma dima yoyomkin hyena .
45007023	Ma tru no butena aeka tmoe homo dyenkra . Ma koma hia me koma tru no hina trya koma ko duwa dra hamo ti ko grwine brenkrai . Hamo hweke ya koma no butnam aenkra hoa no wogitminkra .
45007024	Hamo no yoyomkinkmaepu . Bute hia no pwene dima satra . Hamo kru dia no taetaepmike .
45007025	God gu ko duwa , gu Yomkra Yesu Keriso pru ya sete .
45008001	Ma aekwa ko , wike dika Yesu Keriso yominki huroko , God ya ko begema ko ko hwekmina a harike tye .
45008002	Tenam Dure ya koma ko , kyo Yesu Keriso yominki henkra . Hamo pwen me hweke ka koma , no wogitmiti , hamo ya no hma hrete .
45008003	Ma Koma yo kronam naekin homin braema wirin , tenam kua bute ko aia wirin kren God ya homite . Yo hweke , kua tyonam aenkra , ho begema prite , gu puna dite . Ma ya himike homite , ya kya pru kru hwekmin yo dinaekina pkite . Yo hweke hoe sera pkite .
45008004	God ya hamite , tenam ko Koma dukin ya tyen ko hweke kua tyonam aera ko hoe daenina . Tenam kyo Dure ya tyo hominkrai . Bute ya tyo , hominkmaepu .
45008005	Ma wike dika kae ka hodrai hosa hominkrai ko , ka hin ko , ka hodrai hoa tikminkra . Ma wike dika dura ya tyo daera hominkrai , Dura ka hine tikminkra .
45008006	Ma wike dika kae ka hin ko bute ya hodrai hosa homroko , hoe ko pwensa . Ma wike dika ka hine ko Dura ya ko tikmroko ko ware waenuma pen ho sireiki .
45008007	Ma kru dia yae ya bute ya hodra homroko , yo God dima totetyenkra , tenam yo God ya koma swa daerinkmaepu howa . Yae yo homin braema wirin .
45008008	Wike dika kae ka hodrai sa hominkrai wike ho kato God dima yoyomkin daen braema wirin .
45008009	Ma gyo guae gua bute ka hodrai hamike hwyenkmaepu . Gyo Dure ya naemike hominknai du hamike hominkrai . Kutadi God ya Dure gyominki hroko gyo homin braema . Ma kru dia Keriso ya Dure yominki henaemkroko , yo ko Keriso yana wirin .
45008010	Ma Keriso ya gyominki gua tyonam hroko , ya gyo duma hre , God yo duwa dite , hamo gua bute ko domkin braema tenam hwek hoa , ma gua dure ko ware dyaen dyaen hureiki .
45008011	Ma God ya Dure , ya Yesu warmo asite Dure hoa , yo gyominki hroko hamroko , ya gua bute warmo asryeiki .
45008012	Hakina kren , kua bute ya hodrai , hamike homina wirin .
45008013	Kudi gua bute ya hoda hamike homroko gyo tosuryeiki . Ma gua bute ya hodrai ko , Dure ya kuryoko , gyo warkreiki .
45008014	Wike dika God ya Dure ya tyo daera hominkrai ko ko God ya kya .
45008015	Tenam God ya Dure gyo dima daen hoa , gyo dima pkite ko gyo hro sena dinaeka a tempureiki . Dure ya , gyo God ya kya kuku minkra , hamo kua urin ko ai , nai harinkrai .
45008016	God ya dure ya kua dureminki hake tyenkra , kyo ko God ya kya dinkrai .
45008017	Tenam hakina krenku , tenam kyo ko ya kya kren , kuai ya wike kana gaemin kyo kesu taeryeiki . Ma God ya Keriso yo dima daena , ho kesu kyo taeryeiki . Ma kyo pyenkin Keriso ya sete hakin kyoke siroko , kyo kae waenukin sen hakin kyo kesu sireiki .
45008018	No braema pyenkin aekwa kua hi dirai ko kukina . Tenam hamosu God ya kae waenukin kyo dima taenku direiki .
45008019	God ya homite butmin ko huma paka , God ya kya ko dima taenknada .
45008020	God ya homina ko hoe ye . Ma hiko ka hodra wirin . Tenam God ya hodra kren .
45008021	Ma God ya hodra ko hamosu ya homin domkmaekin ko hro naedreiki , ma God ya kya ka a domkmaekin hoko ka taeryeiki .
45008022	Ma kyo braema aekwa , God ya homin ko tren diwa pyaerinkrai . Ma tren hoko ara ka kya hamtwera keka dyenkrai hakina .
45008023	Ma God ya homin ka sa pyaerinkmaepu . Wike dikua God ya Dure mena kroko , Dure hoko yatumki kyo dima sumsa daete , kyo kesu pyaerinkrai . Tenam kyo huma penkrai , hamo God ya kyo homo kyo , ya kyanu kreiki . Hamo hokeko kua bute nin homa hre waenuma preiki .
45008024	Ma kyo huma penkrai kren , kyo ai mena . Ma kudi kyo hamosu diwekrai hoko diwasu , kyo hote huma paka hine brenkmaepu .
45008025	Ma kua dyenaemkrai hoko kyo totokinaemka huma penkrai .
45008026	Hakina kren , kyo aikinaemkrai ko , Dure ya kumta kyo taetaepmikraha . Tenam kyo braema wirin , kyo naerike God dima tyenkmawe . Hamo Dure ya kyo taetaepmira God dima idima tyenkra . Ya tyenkra ko no swa me tyen braema wirin .
45008027	Ma God ya wike ka proe nam dyenkra ko , dure ya hin kesu yo braemkinkra . Tenam Dure ya God ya wike ka swa God dima idima tyenkra , ma God ya hodra ko yo braema kren ho bryoko tyenkra .
45008028	Kyo braema , wike diko God ya ura taeri two ko yo dima hine pya bruroko , kronam naekin butmin ko dima pkroko , God ya homo waenuki .
45008029	Hamo wike diko God ya diwa braem wike hoko ya kya dinaeknaida . Ma ya kya Keriso ya andu kusu , yagmore ko pya pnaida .
45008030	Hamo wike diko God ya sem hyaeka hro ura gyo ko duwa dite . Hamo yo kru ho ko dima kae yae yane hoko ko dima daete .
45008031	Ma God ya kronam himike homako , kyo swa naerike tmyawe . Kudi God yo kyominki hroko , kru dika kyo domsorin braemane .
45008032	God yo kyo a domsori . Ma ya kya ko yae tuma simaepu , yo hamahada butmin hamo kyo dima daete . Hakina kren , ya kyo dima gryo kesu , butrain kyo dima sumsa daen braemane .
45008033	Ma kru dika God ya wike ko hwek mina dike . God yaesa harike tyenkra ko ko hweke wirin .
45008034	Hamo kru dia ko begemin braemane . Yesu Keriso ya wirin . Yo pwa , mate durkyo asi ta , God ya krite dunaetegite paka kua swa idima tyenkra .
45008035	Hakina kren , kru dika Keriso ya hine pya brenkra kyo dima tigi ridwen braemane . Pyenkin hoane , ma domsorin hoane , ma gehmenka sere dumka hakin hoane . Ma pwen hoane . Ma kronam naekin hoane .
45008036	Ma Kwonam kimin ko harina .
45008037	Kronam ka hominkrai hi butmin ko kyo dmyaena , tenam kru kyo hine pya brenkra yo me kren .
45008038	Drinu no braema kronam truato ya kyo dima hine pya brenkra hoko tigi ridwen braema wirin . Pwen me ware me , mate God ya po penkrai wike me kwoe kom penkrai gwin da mate aekwate da mate hamo kesu .
45008039	Ma togite da mate komegite da mate to tukramgite da God ya kronam butmin hominkra tru ko , God ya kyo dima hine pya brenkra , kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya kyo dima naegimite hoko , tigi ridwen kru tru ko hmaepu .
45009001	No drinu trya , no ko Keriso yana , hamo no gyo dima kraekraema tmaepu . Ma no hinnam God ya Durea tikminkra , yo kesu no dima harike trya no kraemaepu dra .
45009002	No kraenaemka trya ko no wike ko no kapoe , me no saio , ko ko dima hine bruroko no pyen hyena dyenkra . Hamo ko me kren , no proe pyenkra hakin no ko naesa God ya a din diwa , mate no kwasu Keriso dyenaemkroko bryoko .
45009003	
45009004	Ma tenam ko ko God ya wike , hamo ko ko ya kya mite , ma ya ai , me waenuma pen ko ko dima naegite . Hamo ya swagumin ko dima naegimite , ma koma ko dima dae mate God nu yo dima swa tyenkrai kronam hoko ko braema . Hamo ya ko dima swa dumasa swa tyete .
45009005	Ma ka kigwam kahwoe ko Hibru wike , hamo wike pya ko kronam pya ka homamiti ko ko braema . Ma Keriso , yo ko to hyenu wikma hete ko ka kyankya dinaekite . Ma God ya ko butmin tikminkra ko ko aepesu yo dima gu ko duwa , dinina . Hamna .
45009006	Ma nokwa harmaepu , God ya swagumin ko a hoe ye harmaepu , tenam Isrwaeo wike butmin ko God ya wike wirin .
45009007	Ma Abraham ya kyankya butmin ko ko God ya kya wirin . God ya Abraham dima tyete , kya pya bra iwekraiko , nokwa gyo dima swagumiteko , Aisaek ya kyankya dreiki .
45009008	Hakina kren , kya diko kua hamtenkrai hi bryoko hamtroko ko ko God ya kya din braema wirin . Ma kya diko God ya swagumin hokan hamtroko , ko ko God ya kyankyanu .
45009009	Tenam God ya swagumite aku hoko pkosu nokwa rwyo pkikra hokeko Sera yo sem kru kya hamtena dye .
45009010	Ma hosa wirin . Rebeka yo kesu . Ya kru kya ko haepki ma kai ko trusa , yo ko kua kigwam Aisaek hoa .
45009011	Ma tenam kya tru ko God yae hoda , hamo kru kya haepki ti hamtenaemkin hoke ti kronam swokin me dukin me homaepu , hokeko God ya ara ho dima tyete , kya rwa ko kya bi ya tmoe homi dite . Hakina kren , God ya kru tru sete ko , ya homra ho duku wirin , ya hodrasa .
45009012	
45009013	Kwo nam kimin ko no Jeikop dima hine pya brenkra . Ma Iso dima ko no a dite .
45009014	Hakina kren , kyo naerike tmyawe , God yo begemin ko bryokmaepune . Wirinsa .
45009015	Ya Moses dima prite , no wike di dima dore a dae droko a dae . Ma no di dima proekroko yo dima proeki .
45009016	Hakina kren , kronam hoko wike ka homaekina wirin , God ya proekin hoa . Dore katma a daemaekina .
45009017	Ma Kwonam kimin ko Ijep wike ka king dima harina , nokwa gu king sa hreteko , gwa no ai me no hi to hyenu wike butmin ko naegimnada .
45009018	Hakina kren , God yo di dima proekira kroko , proekinsa , ma kru di dima ka proe tukmira kroko , hamin braema .
45009019	Ma gyo kru trua no dima harmaudi , ma God yo naemike kru tru ko hweke mena din braemane . Tenam kru di ka God ya hoda du ko a din braemane .
45009020	Ma gu ko kru naekinane hamo gu God dima kyasiri tyen braemane . Ma to dronge brekema hominkrai yo kru ya hominkra dima gu naemike no homira harike tondaerinkmaepu .
45009021	Ma homin kru yo hoda to dronge tru ambutminsa breke urin haepki homa tru ko yaeyosa , ma tru ko aku butmin urinin homa hamire droko ya hami .
45009022	Ma God ya homite ko hote ho bryoko . Ma God ya kyom me ya ai naegite . Ma yo wike ko dima kyomkite , ka hominkrai ho aku butmin pa dyete . Hamo yo hine bra ka hominkrai hoe swokina ko dima daerakraha dite .
45009023	Ma ya ai waenukin ko dima naegimira . Ma ai hoko kyo dima pya daemite . Kyo ya proekin dyenkra . Yo sem kyo homina kren kyo hamosu ya ai diwekraiha .
45009024	Kyo ko wike ma kua hi ko ya hyete . Ma hoko Ju wike kasa wirin , swa ate wike ko kesu .
45009025	Ma hi ko God ya tyo , Hosia ya Kwonam kimina .
45009026	Ma to tru wakan ko ko dima tyete gyo ko no wike wirin da , hamosu gyo ko God waremen ya kya dikraha .
45009027	Ma Aisaia ya kesu Isrwaeo wike ka swa tyete ko , Isrwaeo wike ka tei ko hyenki wai dawara ya drni dinaeki , ma gwin , kasa dei sireiki .
45009028	Tenam Yomkra yo to hyenu wike katma begemi .
45009029	Aisaia ya sem tyena , kudi Yomkra , ai min , yo kua kyankya gwin kworinaemkina kroko kyo ko Sodom me Gomora ko dinaekina .
45009030	Hamo kyo haryai , swa ate wike ko kaesa God dima a dumaekiti , tenam ka drinuhaki dinku , God ya ko dumite .
45009031	Ma God ya wike ko koma tru homakano God dima dumweradi , a homaekiti .
45009032	Ma naemo diwane . Tenam ko God ya swa ko drinu dmaen kren , ka homnai hoasa ko taetaepmin braema demiti . Hakina kren , ko ike hyenu hokan totiti .
45009033	Kwonam kima tyen ko , gyo dinai no to Saion hokan ike trusa hre , hamo wike ko hokan totreiki . Ma kru ara dika yo ko drinu God ya kya dinkrai ko a totekreiki .
45010001	Nogmore gyoke no proeka hine pya brenkra ma no wike ko gwemkromeda . Hamo no ka swa God dima idima tyenkra .
45010002	Ma no braema , ko God dima proekinkrai . Ma ka yo dima proekrai hoko drinu hine bra hominkmaepu .
45010003	Tenam God ya wike ka ten duminkra ten hoko ko braema wirin . Hamo kaesa ten ate hominkrai . Hakina kren ko God ya ten ho tnai dinkra , ma ten hoko ko a dinkrai .
45010004	Tenam Koma ko Keriso ya hoe yete . Hamo ya swa drinu drai wike ka ten ko God ya duminkra .
45010005	Ma Moses yo , wike ko koma swa daera homo God dima dumin swa hi kimite . Ma wike dika koma ko daera homroko ko hureiki .
45010006	Ma Kwonam kimin ko harina , God dima dumahaki du , dumin swa ko hiwa , gyo guaesa rwyo tondaeryomoe , kru diko Hewen dima ten braemane dromoe . ( Hoko Keriso yo sa syenaete . )
45010007	Ma kesu gyo tondaeryomoe , kru dia , to kupram syeke dromoe . ( Hoko Keriso ya pwen ko samtenaete sye . )
45010008	Ya tyen ko hiwa . God ya swa ko gyo kuri aera . Gua titwomnam ae hote gua proenam ae hamrai . Swa daera dumahaki din hiko kyo naegiminkrai .
45010009	Gyo haryoko , Yesu ko Yomkra , God ya yo drinu warmo durkyo asi tina droko , gyo a gwemkreiki .
45010010	Ma God ya swa ko drinu droko hoa God ya kyo dumikraha . Ma kua titwome haryoko kyo a gwemkreiki .
45010011	Ma Kwonam kima harina , wike dika yo dima gu ko drinu God ya kya droko , ko a totokreiki .
45010012	Hamo swa hiko wike butmin kyo dima aenkra . Ju wike me swa ate wike ko ko drike trusa . God ko wike butmin kua yomkra . Ma dika yo dima uryoko , yo ko taetaepmo ko waenuma pen braema .
45010013	Kwonam kima tyen ko harina , wike dika God ya ko taetaepmnada kenti uryoko , yo ko taetaepmo , ko a gwemkreiki .
45010014	Ma kudi ko ya swa ko drinu dinaemkroko , ko naemike ko taetaepmnada urin braemane . Ma ko swa hoko daerinaemkroko naemike swa hoko drinu din braemane . Ma swa hoko aima yoma tyenaemkroko , ko naemike daerin braemane .
45010015	Ma swa tyen wike ko pru tenaemkroko , ko naemike yoma naegimin braemane . Kwonam kima tyen ko harina , wike dika swa waenukin hupe tryoko , wike gwin ka ko dima yoyomkinkrai .
45010016	Ma wike butmin hamo ko swa waenukin hupe hoko daera drinu dmaepu Aisaia ya prite , Yomkra , wike dika kua swa daera drinu dirike dite .
45010017	Hamo swa hoko daera drinu dinkrai . Ma swa kua daerinkrai ko Keriso ya tyete .
45010018	Ma nokwa tondaerira . Ko swa hiko sem daermaepune . Ko drinu daeriti . Kwonam kima tyen ko , ko kuta to hoe hoe butmin ko dima swa naegimiti .
45010019	Ma no hote tondaerira . Ma Isrwaeo wike ko drike braemkmaepune . Sem uminki Moses ya yatumki tyete , Maren no wike tonesu trusa wirin ho taera ko dima naegimo diroko , no tonesu tru nononkina ka nokwa waenuma naegimra ho diwa ko wakreiki .
45010020	Ma Aisaia ya tempwenaemka tyete , wike trua no drurinaemkin hoa no dyeti . Wike no dima kentinaemkin ko dima taenke .
45010021	Ma ya Isrwaeo wike ka swa tyete ko harite , no aku butmin no krite me wike daerinaemka a dinkrai ko taetaepmira harina .
45011001	Hakina kren , nokwa tondaerira , ma God yo ya wike ko a deka kworiteke . Wirinsa . No ko Isrwaeo kru . No kigwam yai yai ko Abraham . Ma no kigwam tru ko Bensamin .
45011002	Ma wike God ya sem taeri twen ko yo kwormaepu . Gyo braema Kwo tru hokan kimin ko Iraija ya Isrwaeo wike ka homiti swa God dima a da tyete ko .
45011003	Yomkra , ko gwa tyo tyen wike kuwya , gryo gu dima daerwera twenkrai ri hoko grura naedewi . Hamo nokwasa hra . Ma ko no kesu wyera drai .
45011004	Ma God ya tyete ko naerikene . Ya harina , wike nae tikmra ko 7000 hamo . Hamo ko kraekraemin god Bar dima gu ko hya harmaepu .
45011005	Ma aekwa kesu hote ho bryoko , God ya proeka wike kukumasa taerite .
45011006	Yo ka waenuma homo diwa taermaepu . Yo di dima proekra hosa taerite . Tenam kudi God ya proekin ko wike dika ko waenuma hominkrai ko dimasa aeroko , hamroko hoko proekin kronam nu wirin .
45011007	Hamake , ma Isrwaeo wike ka druriti ko dimaepu . Yae wike kukumasa God ya hoda din kasa dyeti . Ma gwin ko God ya swa a da kehenam tutumiti .
45011008	Kwonam kima tyen ko God ya ka hin me ka proe ko tukina homi , hamo ko aekwa kesu diwa daera hamin braema wirin .
45011009	Ma Debid ya tyete , no hoda ko ro gaema praiko totetyen wike ka kumta ko taentaema ka dore daenaida .
45011010	Ma no hoda ka kron ko , dudumnaida . Hamo ko pyenkin ko aku butmin dinaida .
45011011	Hamo nokwa tondaerira . Ma Ju wike ka totitiko , totinu totitike . Wirinsa . Tenam ko hweke tweti kren , hamo swa ate wike ko a gwemkikra swa daeriti . Hamo Ju wike ka ko dima waknaida .
45011012	Ju wike ka hweke kren , swa ate wike ko waenuma penkrai . Ma hamosu Ju wike butmin ko God ya kronam waenuma homroko , swa ate wike ko me waenuma penkreiki .
45011013	Ma no aekwa swa ate wike gyo dima tyera . God ya no pru swa ate gyominki tmoe hominkra ko irin me hominkra .
45011014	Dikani no wike , ko ko diwa wakmaudi , hamroko gwin ko gwemkin braema wirin .
45011015	God yo ko kukuma kwore hamo wike gwin God dima totiti , ko hote krwyo kumta , God dima kire diti . Ma ko aku tru yo dima krwyo pkroko , ko naemawe . Hoko tosurin wike ka durkyo asin aku .
45011016	Ma gyo da hya krwa hoko msa kukin ko God dima daera hoa drike ko ambutmin yo dima daena dinaekina . Ma kudi dei droke ko God yanakroko , dei seke ho kesu yansa .
45011017	Ma dei orib , wike ka tikminkrai , ya seke gwin ko pkura dei orib tru ko dei durena hamo ya seke ho pkura kumta dei orib wike ko tikminkrai ya buti hokan drima pupumina . Ma swa ate wike gyo ko dei orib dei durin ho dinaekina . Hamo Ju wike ko God ya swa daera dorekiti , ma aekwa gyo kesu God ya swa daera dore dyenkrai .
45011018	Hamo aekwa gyo ko wike seke pkurina dinaekin ko dima a dromoe . Ma gyo naemike irin me pen braemane . Gyo ko sekesa . Gyo dei droke taetaepmin kmaepu . Ka gyo taetaepminkrai .
45011019	Ma gyo harwekraiha , hene , ma seke hoko pkurinku ri nokwa hokan pnadaha .
45011020	Hoko drinu . Tenam ko God ya swa ko drinu dmaepu kren ko pkureiwi . Ma gyo ko hurai tenam gyo ya swa ko drinu dinkrai kren . Gyo tempwenmesa hunai , hamasa irinkromoe .
45011021	Ma God yo Ju wike ko dore daete , ma yo ko hro naedmaepu . Ma ko dei seke nu dinaekina . Hamo gyo hine hrodi ya gyo dima dore a daeke .
45011022	Hamo God ya proekin me God ya yoma begeminkra ko kyo hi dyenkraiha . Ma yo totin wike ko dima yo ko tukina . Ma kru dika ya proekin hakin hoda droke ko dima proekinkra . Ma gyo ya proekinkra haminaemkroko gyo kesu pkura wama hasiri .
45011023	Ma kudi Ju wike ka dumahaki dinaemkin hro naedroko God yo hote ka ri hokan hren braema . Ya hamin braema .
45011024	Ma swa ate wike gyo ko dei orib seke dei durina hakina hamo gua seke tru ko pkua dei tru wike ka tikminkrai hokan dima kwaepma purinina . Ma kronam hiko ya ate , hamo wike kato homaekina wirin . Ma Ju wike ko dei wike tikminkrai hakina . Ma seke sem pkurin hoko God ya ko sa dei trusa kwaekma purin ko tuwa wirin .
45011025	Ma swa tru hiko drinu , ma sem gwemkina hamo no hoda gyo braemknaida . Gyo braemkroko , kyo ko braemnain wike a haryeiki . Swa ko hiwa , Ju wike ka dumahaki dinaemkin ko aepesu hamo a ae . Ma swa ate wike naemo ko God dima pkosu ka a din ko naedreiki .
45011026	Hamroko , Isrwaeo wike butmin ko a gwemkreiki . Ma Kwonam kima tyen ko , kua taetaepmin kru yo Saion hokan hwya pki . Ya pkosu Jeikop ya kyankya ka hweke ko sora wirinmi .
45011027	No ka hweke sora wirinmroko , ko dima swagumin ko tye .
45011028	Tenam Ju wike ko hupe waenukin ko a dinku , ko God dima wasikra , tenam swa ate wike gyo me kren , tenam ka kigwam ko ya kire hakina kren wike ya taerin ko kesu ya kire .
45011029	Ma God yo di sera dra sensa . Ma yo di taetaepmira dra yo taetaepminsa . Yo hine ate brenkmaepu .
45011030	Ma sem uminki swa ate wike gyo God ya swa daera homaepu . Ma aekwa gyo God ya proekin kronam sirai , tenam Ju wike ko ya swa daera homaepu kren .
45011031	Hote ho bryoko , gyo God ya proekin senku , aekwa Ju wike ka God ya swa daera hominkmaepu kren ko hamosu God ya proekin direiki .
45011032	Tenam God ya wike butmin hamo wogitmina dinaeka two hreti . Tenam ko ya swa daera hominaemku diwa . Hamo yo ko dima proekin kronam naegimin braema .
45011033	God ya braemkin ko hyena . Ma ya hine bra tyenkra ko , hoe tyen braemane . Ya hominkra ko dia naegimin braemane . Dia yo dima swa naegimin braemane .
45011034	Kwonam kima tyen ko dia Yomkra ya hin braemane . Kru dia yo dima swa tong naegimin braemane .
45011035	Ma kru ara dia yokingai tru yo dima sumsa daesu , maren ya rwyo yo dima daen braemane .
45011036	Tenam gryo butmin ko ya homina , ya tikmo hwyenkraiko yo me kren . Ma kyo ya hi aepesu hyaeki kwenina . Haminina .
45012001	Hakina kren , nogmore gyoke , God ya kyo dima proekra kren , no gyo dima tyera , guae gyo osma God dima daen tmoe ya hodra hamike hominaete daenkrai . God dima swa waenuma tyen kronam ko hiwa .
45012002	Ma gyo to hyenu wike ka hominkrai ho diwa , gyoke hamasa hamike hominkromoe . Ma gyo God pru ya homo gua hin bren atkin braema . Hamo gyo God ya hodra me mate ya hin bren diko duwa hoko gyo braemkin braema .
45012003	Ma tenam God ya proekin no dima daenku , nokwa gyo dima trusa trusama tryaha guae gyo rwyo irinkromoe , God ya braemkin naekin gyo dima daena , ho me guaesa gyo rwyo begeminina .
45012004	Kuae kua bute ko trusasa ma seke ate ate pya aera . Hamo ko tmoe ate ate hominkrai .
45012005	Hote ho bryoko , wike kyo ko pya , ma kyo ko bute trusa , Keriso yominki pkworina . Ma kua bute butmin ko yae yae hakina , ma kyo bute ko trusa pkworina .
45012006	Hakina kren , God ya proekin naekin kyo dima daena kroko , ho me hohominina . Ma kudi God ya kyo dima ya swa naegiminina da ya braemkin daena kroko , braemkin ho me naegiminina .
45012007	Ma kudi wike gwin taetaepmin tmoe daena kroko , wike gwin taetaepminknai . Kudi naegiminina kroko naegiminina .
45012008	Ma kudi wike ka pyenku taetaepmin swa daena kroko haminina . Ma gryo pya daena kroko wike gwin ko dima pya daenknai . Ma dia yomkra tmoe homroko , aiki hominina . Ma kru dia proekin tmoe homroko , yoyomkinme hominina .
45012009	Ma gyo wike gwin ko dima hine pya brurai droko haminina . Kronam swokin ho dima a deka , dukin hosa tuma senina .
45012010	Krwistin goegmore ko dima hine pya braka , ka hi hyenmaka rwyo matum hine bro , matum hine bro , haminknai .
45012011	Ma gyo tmoe aiki hominknai kudropkin kromoe . Yomkra yo dima proeka hine pya braka ya tmoe hominknai .
45012012	Ma God ya gyo dima daemi , hamo gyo hine yoyomki me pyenkin pko diroko huma paka God dima tyenina .
45012013	Ma kudi Krwistin wike gwin gryo ka buten aenaemkroko , ma guane aeroko , kru ara ka buten aenaemkra ho ko dima daenina . Ma keisen ko dike pkoro no aewe dima mtna dinknai .
45012014	Ma wike dika gyo dima kronam swokin homina kroko , God dima harike tnyai ko dima kronam waenuma hominina dnai . Hene ko taetaepmna dnai , mate ko dima dore daenina wirin dnai .
45012015	Ma wike dika yoyomkroko , gyo kesu yoyomkinina . Ma wike dika byen drimroko , gyo kesu hamike byen drimnai .
45012016	Gyo kru tru di dima naemike proekroko wike butmin ko dima kesu hamike proekinina . Guae gyo irinkromoe . Ma tmoe kukin hokesu hominina . Gwae gu dima no ko braemnai drome .
45012017	Ma kudi kru trua gyo dima kronam swokin homroko , gua matum rwyo yo dima kronam swokin homromoe . Ma kronam diko wike butmin ka hina hoko duwa drai ho hominknai .
45012018	Ma ganeswamin ten aeroko wike butmin ko dima ganeswamnai .
45012019	Kire , gyoke wike gwin ko dima dore daeromoe . God ya kyomka ko dima dore dae . Kwonam kima tyen ko Yomkra ya tyen ko dore ko nokwa dae dina .
45012020	Hakina kren , Kwonam kima tyen ko harina kudi kru trua gu dima kyomkina ma yo gehmenkroko kudin daena . Ma yo wai garinkroko , wai daena . Gyo hamike homo ya kepro kiwekrako kworito yo hukwae dyen braema .
45012021	Hamo kronam swokin hoa gyo dmyaenina wirin . Ma kronam swokin hoko kronam dukin me ten dunai .
45013001	Gyo butmin Gaman ka swa daera hominknai . Ma God ya heno dinaemkroko , Gaman ko Gaman tmoe homin braema wirin . Ma Gaman aekwa hi prai ko God ya taeri twena .
45013002	Hakina kren , kru ara dika Gaman aekwa hi prai ko dima ko a droko , ko God ya taeri twen ko ko a drai . Hamo kru ara hamrai ko kaesa begema dore direiki .
45013003	Tenam wike dika kronam waenuma hominkrai ko Gaman dima tempwenkmaepu . Ma kronam swokin hominkrai ko Gaman dima tempwenkrai . Ma gyo hoda gua yomkra yo dima tempwenaemka pwerane . Ma gyo kronam waenukin homroko , ya gyo dima duwa dikraha .
45013004	Tenam Gaman ko God ya tmoe homin kru hamo ya tikmo gyo waenuma pnaida . Ma gyo swokin homroko , ya gyo dima dore daemeda tempwenknai . Yo ko God ya tmoe homin kru hakina kren diya ya kronam swokin hominkrai ko yo God ya dore ko dima daenkra .
45013005	Hakina kren , Gaman ka swa aika naekin tyo daera hominknai . God ya dore daemeda ho tempwen wirin . Tenam God ya Dure ya gua tyonam hine duminin ko howa .
45013006	Hakina kren , gyo takesi sere daeminkrai , tenam ko hiwa Gaman ko God ya tmoe hominkrai kren .
45013007	Hakina kren , gyo trusa trusama sere gua naemo sirai ho rwyo daen ko bryoko . Sere gua taerinkrai takesi mate to gua penkrai dware takesi daenina . Ma takesi taerin wike ko dima hine waenuma brunai . Ma kru dika ko yomkra tmoe homroko ko dima hine waenuma braka , ka hi hyenminina .
45013008	Ma wike gwin ka rwyo dima mgakwen daeroko , ka hina gua hoe ko dima rwyo daenina . Hamo ka gyo dima yomkrakinkrai , hamo ka hoe ko katma rwyo daenina . Ma gua seskiri ko aera . Ma kua seskiri ko wike gwin ko dima hine brenina . Ma gyo wike gwin ko dima hine pya bruroko koma butmin ko gyo ho homraiha .
45013009	Ma koma ko gyo braema hoa kore aeng tiromoe , wike pwene ryomoe mate uma siromoe mate mgokinkromoe , ma gwin kesu butmin ko drike trusa , guae gyo dima naemike hine brurai hote ho bryoko wike gyo kuri prai ko dima kesu hamike hine brenina .
45013010	Ma gyo kru trua yo dima hine pya braka ko dima kronam swokin a homreiki . Hakina kren , gyo wike dima hine pya bruroko , gyo koma homnain din butmin hominkrai .
45013011	Gyo himike hominknai , tenam gyo braema gua krogoe uma aen aku ko naedewi . Aekwa ko asi tmoe homin akusa . Tenam kua Yesu ko drinu diti hoke kua dei sen aku ko wena , ma aekwa ko kurya .
45013012	Hunam ko sem wirinkirakra . Ma ukan ko sem kaekmae kurya . Hakina kren kyo hunam ya tmoe hominkrai ko naedwe . Mate kyo kae ya totetyen gryogryo taera draekwe .
45013013	Kyo wike kaemin ka hurai ko bryoko huwe . Kyo wai pya dua mate kudin pya dua mate kore aeng tyaka , mate grwine braka , gwogwoekeka haminkromoe .
45013014	Hamo kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya totetyen gryogryo taera draeknai . Ma gua krona gua buta ya hodra diwa ho dima hine pya brenkromoe .
45014001	Ma kru ara dika ka hin bren ko aia wirin kroko , ko dima swa grwine brenkromoe . Ko dima kire dinknai .
45014002	Ma kru ara trua , God ya swa braemkrako , kudin butmin dinkra . Ma kru tru God ya swa yoma braemkinaemkrako , sanamin gryogryosa dinkra .
45014003	Hamo kru kudin butmin dinkra hoa kru butmin dinaemkinkra yo dima gu hina ko swokina drome . Mate sanam gryogryo hosa dinkra ya kudin butmin dinkra yo dima kesu gu hina ko swokina drome , tenam God ya yo dima gu ko kru waenukina dina .
45014004	Ma gu ko kru naekinane . Hamo gu kru tru ya tmoe homin kru begemrake . Yanai ya hin sa ya tmoe homin kru yo waenuma hna droko haminina , ma swoma hna droko haminina . Ma yo waenuma hi , tenam Yomkra ya hoda dinku , yo waenuma hen braema .
45014005	Ma kru trua ya hin ko aku tru ko hyena . Ma kru trua ya hin ko aku butmin ko bryokosa . Hamo guaesa hine bra braemkinina .
45014006	Kru dia aku diko yae atkina droko , Yomkra ya hi hinada . Ma kru dia kudin butmin dinkra yo kesu Yomkra ya hi hinada , tenam yo yomkra dima duwa drako , kudin ya dra dware . Ma dia kudin gwin yo a drako , Yomkra ya hi hinada , ma yo God dima gu ko duwa dinkra .
45014007	Ma kyo kuae kua kumasa hwyenkmaepu . Ma kuae kumasa tosurinkmaepu .
45014008	Ma kua hurai hiko Yomkra yo me kren kyo hi huraiha . Ma kua pwenkrai ko Yomkra dima pwenkrai . Ma kyo hwene , ma pwene , hamroko , Yomkra yana .
45014009	Ma Keriso ya pwa durkyo asiteko , tenam yo hoda wike ihyamin da mate tosurin wike ka Yomkrakrada .
45014010	Hamo sanamin gryogryo dinin gyoke , gyo naemo diwa gua goegmore begemraike . Ma kudin butmin dinkrai gyo naemo diwa gua goegmore ko dima swokina draike . Kyo butmin God ya kinaegite hwyo ya kyo begemi .
45014011	Tenam Kwonam kimina tyen ko harina , Yomkra ya tyete , no ko God ware me henkra , hamo wike butmin ko no kinaegite tama drima praka , no dima gu ko Godnu dreiki .
45014012	Hakina krenku , kua hominkrai ko , kuae trusa trusama God dima naegimreiki .
45014013	Hamo kyo kuaesa rwyo begemo rwyo begemo haminkrai ko naedwe . Ma gyo hirike hine brunai , no tmoe swokin a homi , pako na goegmore totmeda .
45014014	No Yomkra Yesu Keriso yominki henkra kren , no braema , kudin butmin ko , monkun wirin . Ma kudi kru trua ya hina kudin diko monkun droko , yo kudin ho din ko bryoko wirin .
45014015	Ma kudi gu kudin tru du , ma gwa gmore ya diwa proe pyenkroko , gu gwa gmore dima hine pya brumaepu hoa . Ma kudin gwa dinkra hoa , Keriso ya kru ho dima pwete ho domsorome .
45014016	Gua braeme , gua hina hrodi diko gua duwa drai ko wike gwin ko swokina dmeda .
45014017	God ya wike tikminkra kudin deka wai deka haminina wirin . God ya dure ya daenkra ko waenuma pen me yoyomkin me ganeswama pen kronam daenkra .
45014018	Ma kru trua Keriso ya tmoe hamike hominkroko , God ya yo dima yoyomku mate wike ka kesu yo ko duwa dinkrai .
45014019	Hamo kyo kronam naekin hine bra yoma homroko hoe ko , wike ko ganeswama waenuma pen braema , hamo kyo kronam hoko hominkwe . Hamo wike ko kesu aikin kronam ho diwa kronam hoko kyo hominkwe .
45014020	Ma gyo tmoe God ya homin ko domsoriomoe kudin dware . Ma kudin butmin dinina . Ma kudi kru trua kudin naekin du ma kru trua diwa yo toti hweke hren braema , hamroko kudin hoko dinina wirin .
45014021	Hakina kren , kronam dukin ko hiwa . Kudi saio tru deka wai wain deka mate kronam tru homo gua gmore yo diwa totmaekina kroko , kronam gua hominknai hoko naedinina .
45014022	Hamo gua hine brenkrai ko kudin din mate dinaemkin hoko gyo me God guaesa tyenina . Ma kudi kru ara trua dia yae ya kronam druradi , pyenkin tru dyenaemkroko , hamroko kru ara hoko yoyomkin braema .
45014023	Ma kudi ya hina kudin hi du ko dukmawe o swokmawe , hine hamike brasu , kudin ho droko , God ya homin ko duwa wirin dra , tenam kronam ya homrako , God ya swa ko tuma simaepu kren . Ma God ya tyo , ma wike ka hin ko ate droko , hoko hweke .
45015001	Ma wike dikua God ya swa yoma daera drinu dinkrai kua wike aikinaemkin ka pyenkin dirai ko taetaepminina . Kuae kua hodraisa hominina wirin .
45015002	Ma kyo kua gmore ko taetaepmo , aiki yoyomkin me pnaida . Hamroko ko God ya swa ko yoma braemkin braema .
45015003	Tenam Keriso yo yae ya hodra ho homaepu . Kwonam kima tyena ko ikaremin swa ka gyo dima tyenkrai ko no dima kesu tyenkrai .
45015004	Kwonam kimin butmin hoko , wike ka kikimiti kyo dima naegimnaida . Hamo kyo hyaeka kyo braemki huma po , God ya kumta kyo taernaida .
45015005	Ma God yo ko huma tmaeki paka mate swa waenuma tyen teinam nai ko yo . Ma ya hin trusa gyo dima dae , Yesu Keriso yai ta hine bren trusa gyo dyeti hakina .
45015006	Hamo gyo hine bren trusa mate swa trusa dinaeka kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso yai God ya hi waenuma hyenina .
45015007	Hakina kren , gyo wike gwin ko dima kire dinknai , Keriso ya gyo dima kire dite ho bryoko , hamo God ya hi waenuma hyenmin braema .
45015008	Nokwa gyo dima tyerakra , Keriso ya Ju wike ko dima naegimira , God ya swa ko drinu dnaida . Hamo ka kigwam ko dima ya swagumin ho dumira pkite .
45015009	Ma yo hoda swa ate wike ko kesu , God ya ko proekra kren ka yo dima duwa dnaida . Ma Kwonam kima tyen ko no swa ate wike kominki haka gu dima gu ko duwa dikraha dina .
45015010	Ma swa tru ko hiwa , swa ate wike gyoke , gyo God ya wike kominki yoyomkinknai .
45015011	Ma hote swa tru tyen ko hiwa , swa ate wike gyoke , Yomkra dima yo ko duwa dinina .
45015012	Mate Aisaia ya tyen ko hiwa , Jesi ya kyankya ko taenki ko dina . Hamo yo kumta swa ate wike ko ya tikmo ko yo dima hine bra yo huma pwekraiha .
45015013	Ma God yo ko hamosu siwekraiha huma pen yanai . Ma yo ko yoyomkin me waenuma pen gyo dima daemna , gyo ya swa ko drinu din krenku . Hamo gyo Dure ya ai me hamosu taenki ko drai ho huma aiki pen braema .
45015014	No goegmore gyoke , no braemki naedra gyo ko duwa dra . Ma gyo butmin braemkewi ma gyo guae gua kire ko rwyo matum naegimo rwyo matum naegimo hamin braema .
45015015	Ma nokwa swa aikin kwonam hi kimra ko , no tempwenaemka kimra .
45015016	No himike kimra tenam no ko Yesu Keriso ya tmoe homin kru , hamo no swa ate ko dima naegiminkra . Ma no ko prist dinaekina . No swa ate wike ko God dima satyoma daenkra . Ma ya dure ya sem tyete , ko ko God ya wike dina .
45015017	No Yesu Keriso yominki haka God ya tmoe hominkra kren tmoe nokwa hominkra ho dima irin braema .
45015018	No tempwenaemka tyera , Keriso ya pru no wike swa ate ko dima tyo , ko God ya swa daerinkrai .
45015019	Yo Dure ya ai me tei atma naegimite . Ma no Jerusraem din Irinikam din dure hokan Keriso ya hupe waenukin naegimi kwamite .
45015020	No hoda , hupe waenukin hiko to dika sem naegiminaemkin hokansu naegimira . No , wike gwin ka naegimina kroko no hote hokan a naegimi .
45015021	Kwonam kima tyen ko harina , wike dika sem ya swa daerinaemkin ko daera drike dyen braema .
45015022	Ma no aku pya gyo dima tera hine brenkra . Ma tmoea nokwa tmaeke ko ten dwemamiti .
45015023	Ma no tmoe aekwa to hikan hominkra ko sem wirinkra hamo no ambum pya kuta gyo dyera dinkra , hamo no hine ko aekwa gyo dyera dra .
45015024	Ma no to Spein dima taka ten dure hokan no gyo dyera . Hamo no gyominki aku naemo hmaudi , hamo gyo no taetaepmosu no hote ten hokesa ten braema .
45015025	Ma aekwako , no Jerusraem dima ti . Hamo God ya wike hokan prai ko taetaepmira .
45015026	Tenam Keriso ya wike to Masedonia me to Akaia hokan prai ko kaesa hine bra swa twya gaema God ya wike mgyore to Jerusraem hokan penkrai ko dima sere daewera .
45015027	Ma hoko kae ka hine bra yoyomkin me ko taetaepmwera , tenam Ju wike ko God ya kronam ka braem ho swa ate wike ko dima naegiminku . Hamo swa ate wike ka gryogryo pya aeroko , hoko hote Ju wike ko dima rwyo daenina .
45015028	Ma no tmoe hiko wirinku diroko , sere ka gaemiri butmin hamo Jerusraem dima daeno no to Spein ten hoke taka gyo dye .
45015029	Ma no braema nokwa gyo dima pkikrako , no Keriso ya haguma waenuma pen kronam no dima aenkra ho gyo dima sapki .
45015030	No kire gyoke , no hoda kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya hinam me dure ya proekin gyo dima trya , gyo no me , no hi God dima tyenknai .
45015031	Ma gua God dima hirike tyo , no Judia dima tako , God ya no taetaepmo Keriso dinaemkin wike ka no yenina wirin . Mate tyo , God ya wike hokan prai ko nokwa ko taetaepmin sapkra ko bryoko dreiki .
45015032	Hamo kudi God ya hoda droko , no yoyomkin me gyo dima ten braema . Ma no gyo dyakano hote yoyomkin dyen braema .
45015033	Ma God , yo ko kate druki waenuma pen yanai . Hamo yo aku butmin gyominki henkna . Haminina .
45016001	Ma kua uke Pibi , yo Keriso ya wike to Senseria hokan penkrai ko dima tmoe waenuma hominkra .
45016002	Hamo yo gyo dyera pko diroko , gyo Yomkra ya hinam kyominki pwe dnai . Hi ko God ya wike ka homin ho bryoko homnai . Ma ya hodra gua naemike taetaepmaekina kroko haminina . Tenam yo sem wike pya , taetaepmaka no kesu taetaepminkra .
45016003	Ma Prisira me Akwira , ti dima duwa dnai . Kyo trusa hmene Keriso ya tmoe hominkrai .
45016004	Ti no taetaepmwera ta ware dima hine brumaepu . Hamo no ti dima duwa dra . Ma nokwasa ti dima harmaepu swa ate wike Keriso ya wike butmin ko kesu ti dima duwa drai .
45016005	Ma wike ka aewe hokan gaeminkrai ko dima duwa drai .
45016006	Ma ara Meri , yo dima duwa dnai , tenam yo gyo dima tmoe hyena hominkra kren .
45016007	Ma Andronika me Juria , ti dima duwa dnai . Ti ko Ju wike . Hamo ti no me pkori wogitmiti . Hamo Keriso ya tmoe homnaida pru teti ko ti braema . Ti sem Keriso yo gitkiti . Ma no ko margite .
45016008	Ma Ampriata , no kire , yo dima duwa dnai . Ki Yomkra ya swa ku tyamamiti .
45016009	Ma Ebana yo kesu Keriso ya tmoe hominkra . Hamo Stasi , no kire , ti dima duwa dnai .
45016010	Ma Apera , ya Keriso ko drinu dinkra ko bryoko diwadi , bryokaete . Hamo yo dima duwa dnai . Ma Aristobura ya gire ko dima kesu duwa dnai .
45016011	Ma Herodia , yo kesu Ju kru , me Nasisa ya gire ko Keriso wike ko dima duwa dnai .
45016012	Ma Traipina , da mate Traiposa , ti Yomkra ya tmoe hominkrai , me no kire Pesia yo Yomkra ya tmoe waenuma hominkra , hamo ko dima gyo ko dima duwa dnai .
45016013	Mate gyo Rupa yo Yomkra ya tmoe waenuma hominkra . Ma yaeme yo kesu , no ko ya kya nu dinaekina . Hamo ti dima kesu duwa dnai .
45016014	Ma Asinekrita , me Prega da mate Aemis me Patroba da mate Hema da mate Keriso ya goegmore butmin kominki penkrai , ko dima duwa dnai .
45016015	Ma Piroroga me Juria , da mate Neria me yauke , da mate Orimpa da mate God ya wike butmin kominki penkrai , ko dima duwa dnai .
45016016	Ma gyo Keriso ya wike gua diwa knaiyaema kuaepe hokan pturinknai . Ma Keriso ya wike butmin ka gyo dima duwa din swa twya hre ho traha .
45016017	Kire , gyoke , nokwa tyerakra ko yoma daera braemknaida . Wike dika kae ka hinsa naegimo diroko , hamo wike gwin ko hine ate ate brakano Keriso ya kronam ko hro naede kae ka hodraisa wike hakin ko gyo ho hominkrai hamo wike hakemin ko gyo diwa garinkrai .
45016018	Tenam wike swa hakin tyenkrai ko Keriso kua Yomkra ya swa naegiminkmaepu ko kae ka gen tikmin swasa tyen-krai . Hamo ka swa ko pipesa tyaka aekwasa homin swa kraekraema tyo diroko nononkin wike kato swa hoko daera drinu dini dinkrai .
45016019	Ma Keriso ya swa gua daerinkrai hupe hoko wike butmin ko daerinkrai . Hakina kren no gyo dima yoyomkra . Ma no hoda gyo kronam waenukin homaka gyo ko braemknaida . Ma swokin naekin pko diroko gyo nononkina dinaeka pa dyeskinknai .
45016020	Hamo kua waenuma pen teinam nai ko Godsa . Hamo ya Saiten ya naede gua karike tkyo hre .
45016021	Timoti , yo kesu nominki tmoe trusa hominkra . Hamo ya duwa din swa gyo dima hre ho traha . Ma Rusia da mate Jason da mate Sosipata , ko butmin ko Ju wike . Hamo ko gyo dima duwa din swa ho hre traha .
45016022	Ma no hi ko Tetia , ma no kwo hi kimra ko Por ya mgatram swa kimra . Ma no kesu Keriso ya wike . Ma swa ho hre tra .
45016023	Ma kyo Gaia ya aewe hokan prai . Ma Keriso ya wike hikan gaeminkrai , yo kesu gyo dima duwa drai . Ma Irasia to hyenu hia sere tikmin kru , ma kua gmore Kwotasti ti gyo dima duwa din swa hre traha .
45016025	Ma kyo God ya hi hyenwe . Yo gyo taetaepmo , Yesu Keriso ya hupe nokwa gyo dima naegimu , sem gwemkin ho taenku drinu din braema .
45016026	Ma swa sem gwemkin hoko God ya tyo tyen wike ka Kwonam kimina kren , wike ko braemkin braema . Ma God ya aepesu hamo hekraha du , wike butmin ko ya swanu daera drinu da homin braema .
45016027	God braemnainu yasa butmin braema . Ma Yesu Keriso yo me kren ai waenukin gu dima aepesu yae hamo aekraha . Hamnada .
46001001	No ko Por , ma no ko Keriso ya tmoe homnada pru ten kru . God yaesa , no sa ya tmoe homin hrete .
46001002	Nokwa , no kire Sostenis , ki ko God me Keriso ta wike , to Korin hokan penkrai gyo dima kwo hi kimnai . Yesu Keriso ya gyo taetaepmo gyo waenuma pen kronam ho sinaida . Hamake ma gyo ko yana dira . Ma wike to hoe hoe butmin dika ko kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya hi hyenminkrai ko dima kesu hi kimraiha . Ma yo ko ka Yomkra ma kyo kesu kua yomkra .
46001003	Kuai God me Yomkra Yesu Keriso ti gyo tikmo , gua hine waenukrnaida .
46001004	No aku pya God dima gu ko duwa dinkra tenam God ya kya Yesu Keriso yo dima kronam waenukin daesu ya gyo dima daete .
46001005	Ma gyo Keriso yominki hwyenkrai ko gua braemkin me gua swa ko waenukina .
46001006	Gyo Keriso ya swa ko yoma daera gua hinam hreti .
46001007	Hamo gyo Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya pkikra ho humroko , God ya taetaepmin Dure ko gyo senaha .
46001008	Ma Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya gyo tikminkra ko , ya krwyo pkikra hokeko , gyo hweke dumkina dye .
46001009	Ma gyo ya kya Yesu Keriso yominki hunaida . Yo ko dumasa tyenin kru .
46001010	Kire gyoke , no Yesu Keriso ya hinam tyerakra , gyo grwin bren ko naedrnaida . Hamo gyo butmin hine bra swa trusa tyenkrnaida .
46001011	No gmore gyoke , Krowi ya wike ka no dima tyaewi ko , wike gwin gyo grwin bre praiko dewi .
46001012	Gyo grwin brenkrai tenam gyo harinkrai , no ko Por ya wike dinkrai , ma gwin gyo harinkrai , no ko Aporos ya wike dinkrai . Ma gwin gyo harinkrai no ko Pita ya wike dika , gwin gyo no ko Keriso ya wike dinkrai .
46001013	Ma Keriso ko ridwa yae yae hakinane . Ma Por , yo gua dware dei buti hre pweteke . Ma gyo Por ya hinam wai bra yetike .
46001014	Nokwa gyo kru tru ko wai mga myaepu , yae Krispas me Gaiasi ma hamo ti sa no wai mga ya . Ma kru trua me win .
46001015	Krwika gyo nokwa ko wai bra yere ko da no hi hime .
46001016	Drinu , no kwasu braemkra , no Stepanas ya gire ko kesu wai bra ya . Dikani no gwin kesu bra ya ke di .
46001017	Ma Keriso yo no wai sa bra nyada pru tmyaepu . Yo no pru kuta hupe waenukin tyadaemrnada . Hamo no braemkin wike ka tyenkrai harike a tye , tenam pako Keriso yo dei buti pwete swa ho ko ya drike kumeda .
46001018	Ma wike dika ko God ya ware ten dyenaemkroko , ko gwemkina dinaeka , ka hina harinkrai , Keriso ya dei buti pwen swa ko hmene yen swa no dinkrai . Ma God yo kyo gyori tenkra . Hamo kua hina harinkrai ho ko God ya tei atkin ho dinkrai .
46001019	Drinu , Kwonam kima tyen ko hirina , marensu no wike ka braemkin domsori ko dina aera . Ma hote hamo wike wa hine ate ate pya brenkrai ka braemkin ko hote kumi .
46001020	Hamo braemkin kru ka ri ko dikan praike . Ma swa kikimin wike ko dikan praike , ma to hyenu hikan swa kyokyo brenkrai ko dikan praike . Ma God yo kyo dima naegimite , to hyenu braemkin ko hmene yen kronam dinaekina .
46001021	Tenam God yo ko braemnain kru kren , ya haru diku , to hyenu wike kae ka braemkin hoa , God ko ko braemkin braema wirin . Ma swa kua tyenkrai ho ko hmene yen swa dinaekina dinkrai , hoko kru ara dika God ya swa ko drinu dinkrai ko sa ya tonae dima gyori tenkra .
46001022	Ma Ju wike ko hoda kronam tei atma homu diwera dinkrai . Ma Grwik wike ko daera braemkwera diskinkrai .
46001023	Ma kyo ko Keriso ya dei buti pwete swa hosa naegiminkrai . Ma Ju wike ka harinkrai , swa hakin ko , ko a dinkrai . Ma Grwik wike ka harinkrai , swa ho ko drike wirin dinkrai .
46001024	Hakina krenku , ekyake , sem God ya uru kyo daerewi , Ju wike da ma Grwik wike da kyo ho daerewiha . Kyo braema howa , Keriso ko God ya ai , hamo yo ya braemkin ho sena .
46001025	God ya hmeneyen swa hoa wike ka braemkin ko dmyaena . Ma God ya kudropkin hoa wike ka ai ko dmyaena .
46001026	Kire gyoke , God ya gyo uriteko , gyo ko braemkin hyenu da mate yo ko aiya no da ya hi hyenmin wike hakemin ko pya wirin .
46001027	Ma to hyenu wike ka hmenyen kronam dinkrai hoko God ya so braemkin wike ko hukwaeknaida . Ma ka harinkrai kronam hoko aikinaemkin howa , hamo God ya hoko so , diwa aikin wike ko hukwaeknaida .
46001028	Ma to hyenu wike ka harinkrai , hoko mon dinaekina no da ko a ditikrai , hoko God ya so , ka drike mina dinkrai , ho ko wirinkrnada .
46001029	Ma ya himike homu , kru trua God ya kron ti hokan ya hi ko hyena din braema wirin .
46001030	Ma God ya gyo sa , Yesu Keriso yome hrena . Ma Yesu yo ko kua braemnain kru . Ma yo kyo hweke dumka hro , God yo kyo diwa kyo ko duwa dra . Hamo yo kyo homo yae yo sa haka yo dinaeknada . Yo kyo hma hre trnai dite .
46001031	Ma God ya sem Kwonam kimin ko , kru tru diya ya hi hyenmira kroko , Yomkraa yo dima homite , hosa hyenminina dina .
46002001	Kire gyoke , nokwa gyo dima pkeko , no God ya swa sem gwemin hoko , no gyo dima swa gawema naegimaepu .
46002002	No gyominki hako , no kronam tru dima hine brumaepu . No dumasa Yesu Keriso ya dei buti pwere ho dima sa hine breha .
46002003	Ma uminki no gyo dima pkeko , no aia wirin . Ma no girma tempwa kaduen hyena tya .
46002004	Ma nokwa naegima tyako , braemkin wike ka swa hakin ho tmyaepu . Nokwa naegima ko , God ya Dure ya ai , ho naegima .
46002005	Gyo God ya swa ko drinu dinkraiha , tenam gyo wike ka braemkin saewi hakina wirin . Gyo God ya ai ho saewi krenku .
46002006	Drinu wike diko God ya kronam braemkin wike ko , ko ko aia , no ko dima swa braemkin naegiminkra . Ma nokwa braemki tyenkrako to hyenu ka braemkin hakina wirin . Ma ho ko wirinkin braema .
46002007	Nokwa tyadaeminkra ko God ya braemkin homesa . Swa ho ko gwemkina aete . Ma God yo to hyenu hominaemkin hoke yo kronam waenukiskin kyo dima dae ko da hoko yatumki homa hro naedite .
46002008	Ma to hyenu hikan penkrai yomkra truato swa hia drike handuma braemkin braema wirin . Ma kudi kru trua hoko braema hamraino , Yomkra waenukiskin ko dei buti hro a ryeiki .
46002009	Ma hoko sem swaguma Kwonam kimina kren . Ma kronam tru ko , wike kua knon me dyenkmaepu , ma kua kehenam me daerinkmaepu , ma kua hin ko braemkinkmaepu , hoko God yo wike yo dima hine pya brenkrai ko dima homina .
46002010	Ma kyo braema kronam hi ko , tenam God yo ya Dure waenukin pru psya kyo dima naegiminkra . Ma Dure waenukina , God ya kronam gwemin ho kesu ko drureka samta kyo dima naegiminkra .
46002011	Kru trua yo yoma braemkin braema wirin , ya kire ya hinebrura hoko . Ma Dure wa kru hoa tyonam hra hoa yae sa braema . Hamo hote ho bryoko , kru truato yo God ya hine brenkra ho braemkin braema wirin , God ya dure waenukin yaesa braemkin braema .
46002012	Ma kyo to hyenu dure simaepu , kyo God ya Dure kyo dima pru pkite ho seti .
46002013	Hakina krenku , braemkin kua sen ko wike ka braemki naegimrai ho naegimaepu , kyo Dure Waenukina kyo dima naegiminkra hosa naegiminkrai . Ma Dure ya naerike tryoko , ya swa hosa naegiminkrai .
46002014	Ma kru ara dika ko Dure Waenukin senaemkroko , Dure ya hwya daeminkra ko sen braema wirin . Tenam ho ko ko braemkmaepu , ma ho ko hmene yen kronamsa dinkrai . Tenam dure min wike kasa ko dure ya drike braemkin braema .
46002015	Hamo kru ara dika ko Dure mina kroko , kronam butmin ko yo begemin braema . Ma wike dure min ko , kru trua ko begemin braema wirin .
46002016	Ma Kwonam kimin ko Yomkra ya hin ko kru diya braema ne , ma kru diya yo Yomkra dima gu himike homna din braemane . Ma kyo Keriso ya hine brenkra hamike sa hine brenkrai .
