46003001	Kire gyoke , uminki no gyo dima tyete ko , wike Duremin ko dima tyenkra ho bryoko wirin . Ma no to hyenu wike ko dima tyenkra ho bryoko , gyo dima tyen braema . Hamo no aikinaemkin Krwistin wike ko dima tyenkra ho bryoko tyete .
46003002	Ma no tute dore dinaekin ho sa gyo dima dae dewi . Ma kudin tukin ko gyo dima daen braema wirin . Tenam gyo tuka hakin ko din braema wirin krenku . Ma aekwa kesu kudin tukin hoko gyo din braema wirin .
46003003	Tenam gyo to hyenu wike ka hwyenkrai gyo kesu hamike sa hwyenkrai . Ma gyo gua kire dima patka grwin bruroko gyo ko to hyenu wike saha .
46003004	Ma gyo hirike tryoko , kyo ko Por ya wike du , ma gwin gua to kyo ko Aporosi ya wike du , hamroko gyo ko to hyenu wike saha .
46003005	Ma Aporosi yo ko naekin krune . Ma Por yo ko naekin krune . Ki ko God ya tmoe homin krusa . Yomkra ya ki dima tmoe naekin daea ho ki homo , gyo God ko drinu dewi .
46003006	Ma no kudin ke hre , Aporosi yo wai dridripma , ma God ya ke hoko taetaepmu mtinkra .
46003007	Hakina krenku , kru trua yon hre , me kru trua wai dridripma hamroko tmoe hoko hyena wirin . God ya hominkra ko drike hyena . Tenam ya hominkra ko , yon ko deri mtenkra .
46003008	Ma wike wa ke hre , wai dridripmo haminkrai ti ko tmoe trusa . God yo kru trusa trusama ko dima ko tmoe naemike homroko , yo hoe bryokosa daemi .
46003009	Drinu kyo ko God ya tmoe homin krusa , ma gyo ko God ya deigwenam dinaekina .
46003010	Hamo God ya no dima tmoe tru homnada naegi ko , no ko aewe tin kru hyenu dinaeka no hrukesa wya hrea . Hamosu aewe nokwa hruke wya hrea hoko , kru trua yo hokan tinkra . Ma kru ara dika ko aewe twekraiko , pitmasa tinina .
46003011	Gyo braemaha , aewe hruke , sem hmyen ko Yesu Keriso . Ma kru trua hruke ho hma hruke ate saku hmyen braema wirin .
46003012	Ma kru trua hruke hokan aewe tira kroko , gor o siba o ike tukin ya sere min ho me aewe tira , ma wike gwin ko degan o kose ho me tryeiki .
46003013	Marensu ka tiwi drike ko Keriso ya aku hokesu braemkwekraiha . Ma ka tiwi ko dei me bryoko diwrkraiha .
46003014	Ma kudi kru tru , hruke wya aewe tu , deia duwenaemkroko , tmoe homin kru ko ya hoe sen braema .
46003015	Ma kudi wike ka tin ko deia duroko , ko ya hoe a sireiki . Ma ka tin ko deia duo tryorinina dinaekina .
46003016	Ma gyo braema wirinne . Gyo ko God ya Tempo aeweha . Ma God ya Dure Waenukin yo gua tyonam henkra .
46003017	Ma kudi wike dika God ya Tempo aewe domsoryoko , God ya kesu kru ho ko domsorin braema . Tenam God ya Tempo aewe domsoryoko , God ya kesu kru ho ko domsorin braema . Tenam God ya Tempo aewe ko yae yosa hakina krenku . Hamo gyosa ko ya Tempoha .
46003018	Kru tru yae yo rwyo kraen ko bryoko wirin . Ma kudi kru gyominki penkrai trua , yo to hyenu kronamsa homaka hirike tryoko , no ko braemnain kru droko , yo ko nononkin kru dinaekroko , yo braemknain kru kikraha .
46003019	Tenam to hyenu braemkin kronam hoko God yo diwa hoko nononkin kronam dinkra . Ma Kwonam kimin ko hirike tyena , ma wike ko braemnai no da ko kraekraema homroko , ka braemkin ko daia yenkrai ho bryoko .
46003020	Ma Kwonam kima tru tyena , Yomkra yo braema , braemkin wike ka hine brenkrai ko drike dumkina .
46003021	Hakina krenku , kru trua , wike ka homin ho , irin ko bryoko wirin . Tenam gryosa butmin ko guana .
46003022	Por da ma Aporosi da ma Pita da ma to hyenu da ma ware da ma pwene da ma aekwa da ma hamosu pkikra ho butmin hamo ko guana .
46003023	Ma gyo ko Keriso yana ma Keriso ko God yana .
46004001	Gyo kyo dima hine himike brenkrnai . Kyo ko Keriso ya tmoe homin wike , hamo kyo God ya swa sem gwemin ho tikminkrai .
46004002	Ma tmoe homin wike ko tmoe yanai ya swa sa daera pitmasa hominkrai .
46004003	Ma kudi gua ma wike gwin ka no kronam begemwera kroko , hoko no hine brumaepu . Drinu no kesu nae no kronam rwyo a begemi .
46004004	Drinu no hine hrodi , no hweke tru hrimaepu . Tenam hakina krenku naesa no ko kru duwa no dike tyen ko bryokmaepu . No begemin kru ko yomkra yasa .
46004005	Hakina krenku , ya aku ko pkenaemkinku , gyo katma begemromoe . Ya aku ho bryokae pkosu . Hamosu Yomkra ya kumtasu wike ko begemi . Yo ka hin ate ate bra gweminkrai , hoko hunam dinaekina , hoko sapta topkyen hro naegimikraha . Hamo wike ko braemkwekraiha . Hamo hokeko , God ya wike butmin trusa trusa tmoe waenuma homina kroko , ya hoe ko dima dae .
46004006	Ma no Aporos kia kronam swa hi trya , gyo swa hi drike braemknaida . Koma naerike kimina kroko hosa hyaeka diwa duma hominkrnai . Hamake ma gyo kru trua h'isa hyenmaka ma kru trua h'i hyeminaemka haminkromoe .
46004007	Sen , gyoke , kru diya tyo gyo tei atke wikene . Ma gyo mgakwen naekin tru God yo dima ko simaepune . Ma gyo God yo dima sa taerinkrai ho , ma guato gyo mgakwen tru yo dima senaemkina dinaeka , guae gua hi sa hyenminkraike . Ma gua sena aera hoko butmin ko God yo dima sa taerinkraiha . Hamo naemo diwa gyo guae gua hisa hyenminkraike . Ma guato sumsa daemaepu .
46004008	Ma gua hodrai butmin ko sena , bryoko aerake . Hamo gyo sem gryogryo namin kru kinane . Kyo gyo taetaepminaemku , guaesa king dinane . Ma kudi gyo sem king dina kroko , kyo hmene king da pkori pwe .
46004009	Ma no hine hrodi ko God ya pru ten wike sa mangite hrea . Ma ko harike tyenkrai , gyo tosurnyai diskinkrai . Hamo God ya po penkrai da ma to hyenu wike da ka kron ti kuwyera dinkrai .
46004010	Yesu ya dware kyo ko nononkina dinaekrai . Ma gyo ko Yesu me kren , gua braemkin ko hyena . Ma kyo ko aia wirin . Ma gyo ko aia . Ma gua hi ko hyena . Ma kua hi ko hyena wirin .
46004011	Sem uminki peti da ma aekwa kesu kyo gehmen sa hurai , ma wai garin tyaka kepro kakaika , ma bai kesu pya wirin , hamake wike ka krite me kuyo , kyo hamasa to ate ate kwenkrai .
46004012	Kyo tmoe ko idimasa hominkrai . Ma wike gwin ka kyo dima su tryoko , kyo swa waenukin ko dima tyenkrai . Ma ko kyo dima kronam swokin hamasa homroko , kyo kronasa diwa naedinkrai .
46004013	Ma ko kyo dima idima ikarema tryoko , kyo ko dima kwamga tyenkrai . Ma to hyenu wike ko kato kyo ko mon o tupe dinaekina dinkrai . Ko sem ma aekwa kesu harinkrai .
46004014	Nokwa hi kimra ko gyo dima hukwae daera kimaepu . No proekra gyo dima gyo ko no kyanu dinaekina kren .
46004015	Ma kudi wike Keriso ya kronam swa gyo dima naegimaka gyo tikminkrai ko ten tausen ( 10,000 ) hamo kroko , guai ko trusa . Gua Yesu Keriso saewi hokeko no ko guai dewi , tenam no swa ware nin hupe waenukin ho gyo dima naegimite krenku .
46004016	Nokwa homo gyo dyaewi hosa bryoko hominkrnai .
46004017	Hakina krenku , no Timoti pru kuta gyo taetaepmnada . Yo ko no kya dinaekina , ma no yo dima hine pya brenkra . Ma yo Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya tmoe ko waenuma homin braema . Maren yo nokwa Yesu Keriso ya ten tenkra kronam kesu naegimikraha . Ma no to dike takano , wike Keriso dinkrai ko dima Keriso ya kronam hoko naegiminkra .
46004018	Ma wike gwin gyo hine hrodi no gyo dima a pki ko da , guae gua hi sa hyenminkrai .
46004019	Ma dikani kudi God ya trna droko , no katma tikraha . Kutasu wike ho ka ai no braemkikraha , ma ka swa ko no a hine bre .
46004020	Tenam God ya po pen kronam ko swasa wirin , hoko ai hyena kren .
46004021	Gyo naekin hodane . Ma no tuke me sasu gyo dima pkmawe , ma no pitma pen kronam me prnoekin kronam hosa gyo dima sa pkmawe .
46005001	Swa hikina pko daerire . Gua wike ko aeng tya kronam swoswokin homra ko du daerya . Ma kronam hoko Krwistin dinaekin wike ko hominkmaepu . Kru trua yo yai ya runaen aeng tyenkra ko du daerya .
46005002	Ma gyo naemo diwa kronam hakinsa homaka iryaike . Ma gyo byen drimaka kru kronam ho homra ko pru trna .
46005003	Ma no bute ko wenema hra , ma no dure ko gyominki hra . Ma no gyominki hena dinaeka , kru kronam swokin homra ko no sem kua yomkra Yesu ya hinam begema naedire .
46005004	Ma no dure ko gyominki haka kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya ai kesu hekraha .
46005005	Hamo gyo God dima twya , kru hoko Saiten ya krite ti hrae , ya bute ko hweke dware hoe senina . Ma Yomkra ya aku hokeko , ya dure ko yo hamo henina .
46005006	Ma gyo guae rwyo irinkrai ko duwa wirin , gyo braema , yist kuma hrae diroko , bredi ko rwiwa hyenkin braema .
46005007	Hamo gua yist brunai ko wama hasiri bred nin hosa senina . Ma kua Guri Ten ro ko sem dmaekrai , tenam kua Guri Ten sipe bi , hoko Yesu Keriso hamo ko sem yeti .
46005008	Ma kyo kua ro ko yist brunai me dinina wirin . Tenam yist hoko hweke kronam dinaekina . Hamo bred yist me wirin hoko kronam waenukin ho bryoko , hamo ro din hokeko bredi hakinsa dwe .
46005009	Ma no kwo tru sem kima ko hirike kima , gyo kru dika ko ko aeng tyenkina kroko kominki kire da promoe .
46005010	Ma no to hyenu wike di ka kronam swokin hominkrai ko hro naedrnai dmaepu . Ma ko ko grimeka , uma taerika , tona swokina ka swa tyaka haminkrai . Hamroko gyo to hyenu hiko hro tenina .
46005011	Ma nokwa kwonam kima ya drike ko kru diya haryoko God ko kuai hamo kyo ko goegmore droko ma yo aeng tyenka grimaka , ma dure swokin dima hine braka , swa swokin tyaka , ma su tyaka wai swokin dua nononkina dinaeka , hamakeno yo kru trua gryo uma taereka haminkra yominki kire da penina wirin . Hote hamo kru hakina yominki paka kudin din kromoe .
46005012	Tenam wike Krwistin dinaemkin ko begemin ko no tmoe wirin . God ya ko begemi . Ma Krwistin wike gyo Keriso ya hinam hmene gaemroko gyo matum begema matum begema hamin ko bryoko wirinne .
46005013	Ma Kwonam tyen ko kru kronam swokin hominkrai gyominki penkra ko pru wamo trna .
46006001	Ma Krwistin wike gyo grwin swamano , gyo to , Krwistin wike ka gyo begeminkmaepune . Ma gyo kuta Krwistin dinaemkin wike ka gyo begeminkrnai dinko , gyo hukwaekinkmaepune .
46006002	Gyo braemkmaepune , hamosu God ya wike ka to hyenu wike ko begemreiki . Ma hamosu gyo to hyenu wike ko begemreiki kren , gyo swa kukukin ko gua begemin ko bryoko wirinne .
46006003	Ma gyo braema wirinne , ma gyo God ya hupe tyen wike kokesu begemreiki . Hakina kren , gyo to hyenu kronam begemin ko bryoko .
46006004	Swa gwin gyo dima aeroko , gyo to Krwistin dinaekin wike ka begemraidane .
46006005	Krwistin wike gyo begemin braemkin kru trua hmaepune .
46006006	Gyo himinkrai , Krwistin kru tru yo Krwistin kru tru ko Keriso ko drinu dinaemkin wike ka kron ti hro begeminkraike .
46006007	Tenam gyo gua kire ko begeminkrai hoa gyo naeginkrai ko gyo ko bryoko wirin . Hakina kren , ko gyo dima swa swokin tryoko , hamaha da , hro naedrnai . Ma gua gryo uma taerioko hamaha da , hamo sa aenina .
46006008	Ma gyo , guaesa kronam swokin gua kire dima hominkraiha .
46006009	Ma kronam swokin hominkrai wike ko God ya waenuma pen kronam ko , ko sen braema wirin . Ho ko gyo braema wirinne . Guae gua hine bren hoa gyo kraeme . Ma kru gwin ko aeng tyaka ma kraekraemin god krite me homin ko dima swa tye prai . Ma ara ko ka kru poro , ma kore ate tyenkrai . Ma wike gwin gyokru guaesa gua kire kominki tmoe tyenkrai .
46006010	Hamake ma gyo kru trua gryo uma gwoegwoeki taereka ma grimekano wai swokin dua nononkinkrai . Ma ya kum ikarema tyaka uma taereka haminkrai . Hamo wike kronam hakemin ko God ya waenuma pen kronam ko , ko sen braema wirin .
46006011	Sem uminki wike gwin gua kronam ko hakina . Ma gyo hoko hamaha da naediti . Hamo God ya gyo ko yana no da taeri twena . Hamo gyo ko waenukina dina . Ma kua God yaesa tyosu Yomkra Yesu Keriso me Dure Waenukin ta hamike homiti .
46006012	Ma kru trua harike tmyaudi , kronam butmin ko no homin braema , dmaudi . Drinu , ma kronam butmin gu dima ko duwa wirin . Ma no kesu harike tyen braema , kronam butmin nokwa homin braema . Ma gryo trua no yomkrako no ya tmoe hominkra ko no a heno di .
46006013	Ma kru trua harike tmyaudi , kudin ko genkinina ma gen ko kudin senina . Drinu , ma God yo haepki ho ta tmoe ko wirinmi . Ma bute ya aeng tyeninada homaepu . Kua bute ko Yomkra yana . Ma Yomkra yo kua bute tikminkra .
46006014	Ma Yomkra yo ditnam ae , God ya ai me warmo yo durkyo asite . Hamo God yo kyo kesu ya ai me warmo kyo durkyo asryeiki .
46006015	Hamo gyo hoko braemkmaepune . Ma gua bute ko Keriso yana . Hamo no naemawe , no bute braeke , Keriso yane ho me , aeng timawe . Wirin .
46006016	Ma kru diya yo ara kore tyenkin me pkorina kroko , ta bute ko trusa , hamo hoko gyo braema wirinne . Ma God yo sem tya , ta bute ko trusa kreiki .
46006017	Hakina krenku , kru diya Yomkra tike pkorina kroko , ti ko Dure trusa .
46006018	Hamo gyo kore aeng tyenkrai ko hro hwara trnai . Ma wike gwin ko hweke gwin twenkrai , ko wike gwin ka bute domsorinkrai . Ma kru trua yo aeng tiroko , yae yo ho domsoryaha .
46006019	Gua bute ko Dure Waenukin ya aewe . Ma hoko gyo braema wirinne .
46006020	Tenam God ya gyo hro sete , hoe ko hyena . Hakina krenku , gua bute me God ya hi hyenminkrnai .
46007001	Ma kwo gua kimaewi hoe ko kwasu rwyo hi kimraha . Gua kimewi ko kru trua ya ara senaemka hen ko duwa dewi .
46007002	Ho ko duwa , ma tenam wike pya ko kronam ate ate homaka hamasa kore aeng tyenkrai krenku , kru trusa trusama kae ka runaen tikminina . Ma hamaka ara ko kesu trusa trusama kae ka kru tikmu haminina .
46007003	Ma kru ko ya hodra droko hominina . Ma ara kesu ya kru ya hodra droko hominina . Ti ta hodrai ko matum rwyo dae , rwyo dae haminina .
46007004	Ma ara ya bute ko yaesa ko tikminina wirin , ya kru ya tikminina . Hote hamo kru kesu ya bute yaesa tikminina wirin , ya runaen ya tikminina .
46007005	Gi sema naedu diroko , trua no gu a drome . Ma kudi gi Godminki swa tmyaekroko , hamroko yae po yae po hamwera kroko hoko bryoko . Marensu gia hodrai hominina . Kwika gua bute guaesa tikmu , Saiten ya gi bryoko dimeda .
46007006	Ma nokwa swa hi tryako , gyo hominkrnai dmaepu , tenam gua tondaerinku no ho tryaha .
46007007	No hoda kru ara butmin ko no dinaeka hunaida . Ma God yo tmoe tei ate ate kru ara butmin , trusa trusama ko dima daeminkra . Trua to tei atkin so , ma trua to tei atkin so , haminkrai .
46007008	Ma no kwasu ara kru taerinaemkin da mate ara kwire gyo dima tyera , no hin ko gyo gua kuma hamo hwyenina . Nokwa henkra haminina .
46007009	Ma kudi yo gua bute mate gua hin bren me waenuma tikmin braema wirinkroko , hamroko , ara sermin ko bryoko . Ma gua hodrai sa hine pya bruroko , ho ko bryoko wirin .
46007010	Ma kru ara sem taerin gyo dima koma tru hrira , koma hiko nana wirin , yae Yomkra yana . Ma hoko himike , ara yo ya kru ko kworinina wirin .
46007011	Ma kudi ya kru ko kworyoko ya kumasa henina . Ma hoko yo a droko , yo hote krwyo kuta ya kru ti hin trusa bra penina . Ma kru kesu ya runaen kworin ko bryoko wirin .
46007012	Ma wike gwin gyo dima ko nokwasa tyerakra , ( ma hi ko Yomkra ya swa wirin . ) Ma kudi Krwistin kru trua yo ara Krwistin dinaemkina ara sena , ma ara hoko kru hominki pera droko , kru hoko ara hoko kworyome .
46007013	Ma Krwistin ara diya Krwistin dinaemkin kru sano , ma kru hoko yo ara hominki pera kuro , yo kru hoko kworyome .
46007014	Gyo braema hoa , drinu dinaekin kru yo ara , God ya bryoko dite ho siroko , yo kesu bryoko pen braema . Ma kudi ko haminaemkroko , gua kya ko waenuma a preiki . Ma aekwa God ya dira ko , ko ko bryoko prai .
46007015	Ma kudi , drinu dinaemkin yo ya sen kworira kroko , kworin ko bryoko . God yo hoda yo grwin brenaemka waenuma prnaida .
46007016	Ma hi kesu hine brunai , dikani Krwistin ara gyo ke gyo gua kru taetaepmo ko Krwistin dmaudi . Ma Krwistin kru gyoke , gua runaen taetaepmo ko Krwistin dmaudi .
46007017	Kronam naekin , God ya sem prnyen ho so , God ya gyo urioko , gyo kronam ho sa hwyenina . No swa hi ko Krwistin wike butmin ko dima naegimra .
46007018	Ma kru trua yo , God ya yo dima urite aku hoke , ya kate tigina kroko , hoko hote tiginaemkina dinaeka homrome . Ma kru trua God ya yo dima urite aku hoke , ya kate tiginaemkina kroko , yo ko tiginina wirin .
46007019	Tenam ko kate tigin da ma kate tiginaemkin da ho ko drike hyena wirin . Ma God yo tyo daera homin ko drike hyena .
46007020	Ma Yomkra ya gyo ura naekin tmoe gyo dima prnya hoko hamosa homitenina .
46007021	Ma gu ya hoe dumkin tmoe homo , God ya gu ure , hamo gu hokan dima proe pyenkrome . Hamo gu ho ko kwori , gwa hodra ho homra duro , tenina .
46007022	Ma kru diyayo yahoe dumkin tmoe homo , Yomkra yo uryoko , tenam yo ko Yomkra yana krenku , ya hodra ho homin braema . Hamo hote ho bryoko kru diko yae ya tmoe homo Keriso ya uryoko , yo ko Keriso ya hro sen kruha .
46007023	Ma God ya gyo hro sete ko , ya hoe hyena , hamo gyo wike gwin ka tmoe homnaida hro senina wirin .
46007024	Kire gyoke , tmoe naekin homo God ya gyo uryoko , gyo hokan sa hwyaka hominkrnai .
46007025	Ma swa tru gua kimaewi ko , kru ara serminaemkin swa hi ko Yomkra no dima tyo dmyaepu , ma nae sa hine bra trya . Ma God ya no taetaepminku , no swa hi ko daera hine brenina .
46007026	Ma kronam himike homin ko bryoko . Tenam aekwa dure hikan ko pyenkin dirai kren , hakina kren , no hin ko gyo guae ho prai hamo sa prnai .
46007027	Ma gyo ara ko sem taerina kroko , ho ko duwa , hamo gyo ko kwerwerada swa tryomoe . Ma gyo ara ko serminaemkina kroko , ara taerwera druryomoe .
46007028	Ma kudi gyo ara paku sermroko hoko hweke wirin . Ma kudi ara ka kwaten kru taerioko , ho kesu hweke wirin . Ma kru ara min ka pyen hoko gyo simeda .
46007029	Kire gyoke , swa nokwa trya ya drike ko hiwa , tenam ko teikron ko gawekinaemkra krenku , kru ara min gyo ara serminaemkina dinaekinkrnai .
46007030	Ma kru dika ko byen drima kurai ko , byen dumkina dinaeka kwenkrnai . Ma kru dika ko yoyomkrai ko yoyomkinaemkina dinaeka kwenkrnai . Ma dika ko gryo gryo twa taerinkrai ko ko gryogryo twa taerinaemkina dinaeka hunai .
46007031	
46007032	No gyo kronam ate ate hoa gua hin bren domsormeda . Ma kru dika ko ara taerinaemkroko , ko Yomkra dima hine pya brenkrai , tenam ko hoda Yomkra ya hodra ho homira kren .
46007033	Ma kru trua yo ara sano , yo to hyenu kronam sa hine pya brenkra , tenam ya runaen dima sa hine pya braka ya hodra ho homira .
46007034	Hamo ya hin bren ko haepki . Ma ara paku ko kru taerinaemkrai ko Yomkra dima hine pya braka , ka bute me ka dure ko God dima daenkrai . Ma ara sem kru min , ko to hyenu kronam hisa hine pya brenkraiha . Hamo ka kru ka ko dima hine waenuma brunaida .
46007035	Hamo nokwa swa hi trya ko gyo waenuma prnaida . Gua homrai ten a dwe . Gyo kronam ate ate brenkromoe . Ma kronam naekin ko duwa kroko ho homaka , ma Yomkra ya tmoe yoma homaka , hosa , haminina .
46007036	Ma kru trua ara paku yo dima hin daemina ma ya hin ko yo dima ko bryokaenaemku diroko , ma ya hodra droko ara ho sermina .
46007037	Ma kru trua ya heskira dra , ma wike gwin ka tmyaepu , ma ya ai kroko , yae hamo heskinina .
46007038	Hakina krenku , kru diya paku yo dima hin din hosa siroko , duwa . Ma kru di yo ara senaemkroko , ho ko waenukina .
46007039	Ma ara diya kormina kroko , yo ya kru minki sa penina . Ma yo kru ate kominki kwen ko koma . Hamo ya kru pwosu yo kru tru diwa sen ko bryoko . Ma kudi yo kru trua serakroko yo Krwistin kru sa diwa senina .
46007040	Ma yo heskroko , yoyomkikraha . Nokwa hine bren ko hiwa . Ma no hine hrodi no kesu God ya Dure ko no sena hra .
46008001	No kwasu kudin , dure swokin ko dima daenkrai swa gua kimaewi ho tyerakra . Drinu wike ko harinkrai , kyo ko braemnai dinkrai . Ma hi ko drinu . Braemkiskin ho ko kuae kyosa irinkrai . Ma proekin kronam hoko wike gwin taetaepmo kua Krwistin kronam aikinina .
46008002	Ma kudi kru trua yo ko braemnain kru droko , kru hoa ya braemkin ko yo braema wirin .
46008003	Ma kru diya yo God dima proeka hine pya bruroko , God ya kesu kru ho dima proeka hine pya brenkra .
46008004	Hamo saio , dure swokin dima daemrai ko , kyo naemawe . Gyo braema hoa , tona kritme homin ko ware dumkina . Ma yo ko God nu wirin . Ma God ko trusa yo sa . Tru ko wirin .
46008005	Ma wike ka harinkrai , kwoe me to hyenu hikan ko tona me yomkra ko pya no dinkrai . Hamo hoko drinu kroko ,
46008006	ma kua God ko trusa , to hyenu homite yosa . Mate Yomkra ko trusa , yo ko Yesu Keriso hamo yo God minki gryogryo butmin homa hro , ma kyo kesu homa ware dae hamna kren kyo hi huraiwa .
46008007	Hamo wike butmin ko swa hi ko ko braemkmaepu . Ma wike gwin ko aku pya saio ko tona dima ko yatumki daesu dinkrai kren , aekwa ko saio droko , hine brenkrai hi ko tona dima daen ho no droko , saio hi dra ko hweke hrira dinkrai .
46008008	Ma kudina to , kyo sa kuta God kuri hren braema wirin . Ma kudin ho ko du diroko , God ya gyo ko aiya din braema wirin . Ma dinaemkroko God yo kyo kworin braema wirin .
46008009	Hamo ma gua braeme , guaesa hine bro homrai hoka , wike gwin handuma hine brenaemkrai , ko hweke hrime .
46008010	Ma gu hine hrodi gu ko braemnain kru droko , ma aku tru , tona kritma homin ka aewe ta , hokan ku du , ma kru trua ya hine bren ko aia wirin , ho ya gwa kudra diwa yo kesu kudin gwa dra ho kesu yo dira dikraha .
46008011	Hamo gua braemkin hoa , kru wa braemkinaemkin ho domsorikraha . Ma Keriso yo gua kire ya dware pwete .
46008012	Gua ho hominkrai ko , gua kire gwin ka hin aikinaemkrai ho domsorinkraiha hoko Keriso dima hweke hrenkraiha .
46008013	Hamo kudi kudin nokwa dra hoa no kire domsorioko , saio ko no hote a di , pako no kire ya hweke hrimeda .
46009001	Kronam naekin hoa no ten dwena aenkrake . Ma no ko Yomkra ya tmoe homin pru ten kru wirinne . Ma kua Yomkra Yesu ko no dimaepune . No Yomkra ya tmoe homo gyo kumta Krwistin diskewike .
46009002	Ma wike gwin ka hine brenkrai no ko Yomkra ya tmoe homin kru wirin dinkrai . Ma gyo braema no Yomkra ya no pru ya tmoe hominkrako . Ma no Yomkra ya tmoe hominkra hoe ko guanesa .
46009003	Ma wike gwin ko no begeminkrai ko , nokwasu ya hoe rwyo ko dima tyenkra .
46009004	Ma no tmoe homa kudin me wai me din ko bryoko wirinne .
46009005	Ma Keriso ya tmoe homin wike da ma Yesu ya gmore me Pita me hamo ka hominkrai ko ka runaen kominki tenkrai hamo noke hamin ko bryokaemaepune .
46009006	Ma nokwa Banabas kia sa tmoe ate me homa sere sa kudin me gryo twa taerinkrai ke .
46009007	Ma kru diya yo ami tmoe homoro ya sere me ya kudin twa taerinkrake . Ma kru diya yo deigwenam tmoe homa kudin senkmaepune . Ma kru diya ya mine sip tikmaka , ya tute ko grwiwa dore dinkmaepune .
46009008	Ma kronam hiko wike ka sa tryaike ma God ya koma kesu harike tyenane .
46009009	Moses ya koma kesu kima harina . Mine boromakau ko tmoe homroko , ka mgatram ko kwari puryomoe . Ma God yo boromakau ko dima sa hine brenkrake . Wirin .
46009010	Ma yo kyo dima kesu hine bra hireke tyeteke . Drinu , swa hoko kyo dima kimina . Ma kru tuato , to gyenkra , ma kru truato , drike gaeminkra , tenam tmoe ka homrai ko kudin taerwera .
46009011	Ma kyo Dure ya swa ko , ke dinaekina , gyo dima hreti . Hamo gyo mgakwen trua kua bute taetaepminda daen ko bryokmaepune .
46009012	Ma kudi wike gwin ka hine hrodi hiko bryokaera droko , kyo kesu taerin ko bryoko wirinne . Ma kua taermaekin ko , kyo taerinkmaepu . Kyo wike ka kumta Keriso ya swa daerin ten ko a dureiki . Hakina krenku , pyenkin kua dirai hoko a taen tryeiki .
46009013	Gyo braema wike diko God ya Tempo aewe hokan tmoe hominkraiko , ka kudin hokan taerinkrai . Ma din saio disirin wike ko saio gwin ho dinkrai .
46009014	Hote ho bryoko , Yomkra yo tyete , wike dika God ya swa waenukin tyadaemroko , ka hoe ko ka buten ko bryoko taerinina .
46009015	Hamo mgakwen hakin tru no simaepu . Ma no aekwa hi kimra ko mgakwen tru sera kimaepu . No natumki pwe . Ma nae no rwyo iru kru trua gara ho ko no a .
46009016	No swa waenukin ho naegiminkra dware nae no rwyorin ko bryoko wirin . Ma no ten tru ko aemaepu . Tenam no swa waenukin ho ko naegiminaemkroko , maren no proe ko waenuma hen braema wirin .
46009017	Ma tmoe nae hodra ho homroko , maren no ya hoe se . Ma tmoe hi ko God ya no dima daen hominkra .
46009018	Hamo no ya hoe ko nakoe senkrake . Ma ya hoe nokwa senkra ko hiwa , ware swa nokwa naegiminkra hoko sumsa daeminkra . No swa waenukin ho naegiminkra ya hoe simaekin ko no sera dinkmaepu .
46009019	Ma no ko kru trua no ya tmoe homnada hro senkmaepu . Ma no wike butmin ka hro sen wike dinaeka homaka wike pya gyori God ya to dima tera .
46009020	Ma no Ju wike ko me henkrako , Ju wike ko dinaeka henkra , tenam no ko gyori tera . Ma koma tyen ko no yomkrakinkmaepu , ma no koma hine brenkrai wike ko me henkrako , no ko koma hine bren kru dinaekinkra . Tenam no wike koma hine brenkrai ko gyori tera .
46009021	Ma swa ate koma senaemkin wike , kominki kwehenkrako , no Ju wike ka koma ko hominkmaepu , tenam no ko gyori tera . Hamaka ma no God ya koma ko hro naedmaepu . Ma no Keriso ya koma sa hominkra .
46009022	Ma wike ai dumkin kominki hroko , no ko dinaeka kwehaka , ko gyori tera . Ma no wike butmin ka kronam ho bryoko kweka , wike gwin ko gyori tera .
46009023	Ma no tmoe himike homo , wike ko ware nin ya hupe ko daera yoyomki hunaida .
46009024	Gyo braema kru hwehwemka reisi drai ko , butmin ko hwehwemkin braema , ma kru trusa ko ya hoe sen braema .
46009025	Ma wike dika ko hoda hwehwemkeka dimkweradi , ma ka bute ya hodra hoa ko satomginkrai . Hamo hoe ka ho siweramrai ko domkmaekina . Ma hoe kua siweramrai ko domkin braema wirin .
46009026	Hakina krenku , nokwa hwemkra ko hawyo drimaepu . No boksem dira kroko , no dure hwape hamasa krite hatyen braema wirin .
46009027	No nae no bute minki grwin bro , nokwa hodra yomkrakinkra , kwika no swa waenukin wike gwin naegimra ho , maren no ho ko kwormeda .
46010001	Kire gyoke , no hoda gyo nononkromeda , kua kingwam ko Moses yo ko gyori teti hoke , kronam ko dima pkite ko . Ko u tukramgite teti . Tako , wai dawara ko dure hokan nsori tugitku , pengitku , ko butmin sya kiti .
46010002	Ma ko u me wai dawara me wai bra yeti , tenam ko Moses yominki teti ko hamiti .
46010003	Ma kudin ka diti ko God ya Dura daera hosa kuditi .
46010004	Ma wai ka diti ko God ya Dura daera hosa kuditi . Ma wai ditrnamgite pko , ka de teti ko yae yosa hakina , Keriso dinaekina .
46010005	Hamo God yo ko dima yoyomkmaepu . Ma ko tosuru diroko , ka bute ko to ate ate dei dumkin hokan hamasa bre pkiti .
46010006	Hamo kronam ka homiti hoko naegu , kyo braemkinina . Hamo kronam swokin ka homwera diti ko kyo kesu haminina wirin .
46010007	Ma ko yokingai kritma homa ho dima swa tyeti kyo kesu haminina wirin . Ma Kwonam kima tyen ko , kru ara butmin ko paka kudin dua wai dua asi pi wya grwiwa tmoe homiti .
46010008	Hamo , paku , kwaten kru mate kru ara ko aeng tyaka ka hoe ko wike twenti tri tausin ( 23,000 ) hamo tosuriti . Hakina krenku , gyoke , hamike homromoe .
46010009	Ma kyo God bryoko dyen ko bryoko wirin , aku hokeko wike ho ko Yomkra bryoko dyeti . Hamako , sina ko kuyo tosura naediti .
46010010	Ma ko kyom swa pya tyako , domsorin krua wike ho ko kuyo tosuriti . Hamo kyo kesu kyom swa pya tyenina wirin .
46010011	Ma kronam hoko ko dima pkite , hamo kyo hoko diwa braemkrnaida . Hamo swa hoko Kwonam kimina aera hamo kyo hyaeka hine bra tempwenina , tenam wike aekwa hi praiko , to hyenu ya hoe yen aku ko sem kurinku .
46010012	Hakina kren , kru diya yae ya hina no ko bryoko droko , yae ya braeme .
46010013	Ma kronam naekina gyo bryoko dyera pkinkra hoko to hyenu wike ko dima pkinkra . Ma God ya sem twya hren hoko grurin braema wirin . Maren bryoko dyen hoko pko diroko , gua aia a dimki , God yo gyo taetaepma ten atma homin braema , hamo gyo bryoko hwyen braema .
46010014	Hakina krenku , no sen gyoke , gyo yokingai kritme homa ko dima swa tyenkrai ko hro naendrnai .
46010015	Gyo ko braemkin wike haminku , swa nokwa gyo dima trya ho begemrnai .
46010016	Ma kyo Yesu ya ro dwera hapke gaema , kyo tike byen ke dore kapusnam dripma , God dima gu ko duwa da , Yesu ya kapoe ho bryoko kyo hmene dinkrai . Ma kyo da tkuwa dekano hoko Yesu Keriso ya bute dinaekina dinkrnai .
46010017	Ma da kua dinkrai ko trusa , ma kyo ko wike pya , ma kyo ko bute trusa dinaekinkrai .
46010018	Ma Isrwaeo wike ka homamiti ho kyo hine bruwe . Ma wike dika ko ware gryogryo ko God dima saio disirin ho droko , ko God yominki dina dinaekinkrai .
46010019	Nokwa hi trya ya drike ko nakoene . Ma tona kriteme homin ko dima kudin daen ho ko drike menane .
46010020	Wirin , nokwa trya ko hirike , ware gryogryo ko tona kritme homin ho dima daenkrai , hoko God nu dima daenkmaepu , ko tona swokin ko dima daenkrai . Ma no a gyo tona swokin kominki kudeka ko dima kire dmeda .
46010021	Ma gyo Yomkra ya kapnam hokan wai dua mate kuta tona ate ka kapnam wai dua haminkromoe . Ma hokesu gyo Yomkra ya kudin depkyon hokan kudin dua , mate kuta tona ate ka kudin depkyon hokan kesu dinkromoe .
46010022	Ma dikani gyo hoda Yomkra yo kyo dima kyomknadane . Ma kua aia ya ai dimkrnadane .
46010023	Ma kronam butmin ko kyo homin braema dinkrai . Ma kronam butmin ko duwa wirin , Kronam butmin homin braema , ma kronam butmin ko kyo taetaepminkmaepu .
46010024	Guae gyo taetaepmin hosa hine hya brenkromoe , mate wike gwin ko taetaepmin kesu hine brenkrnai .
46010025	Ma gyo maket aewe hokan saio hro siroko , gyo dinina . Ma hine pya braka saio hiko naemike homireke da tondaeryomoe .
46010026	Kyo braema Kwonam kima tyen ko , to me to hia gryogryo butmin ko Yomkra yanesa .
46010027	Ma kudi kru trua Yesu ko drinu dinaemkin krua kumta gyo dima nominki kudwe du , ma gyo twera da troko nakoe gyo dima dae diroko ho diskinina . Ma kudin gua drai ho ko naemike homireke da tondaerinkromoe .
46010028	Ma kudi kru trua gyo dima harusu saio hiko tona dima daereko dusu , saio ho ko dinina wirin . Kru gua yo dima trya ya hine bren tigmeda .
46010029	Ma nokwa trya ko gua hine bren tigira wirin , kru wa gyo dima trya ho ya hine bren tigmeda hoa no dinina wirin drai . Ma kru tru ya harmaudi , tenam naemo diwa nokwa hodra ko tigrake , tenam kru trua hine bren tigmedane .
46010030	Ma no God dima kudin hi gwa daenkra ko duwa dasu dinkra ho ma naemo diwa wike gwin ko kudin nokwa duwa dra dware ho no dima swa hirike tryaike .
46010031	Himike , gyo kudin deka , wai deka , mate kronam naekin homaka hamo wike gwin ko diwa , God ko yae yo sa hakina din braema .
46010032	Ma Ju wike da ma Grwik wike da mate kru ara , Keriso yana dinkrai gyo ka hin tigromoe .
46010033	Nokwa hominkra ho bryoko hominkrnai . No wike butmin ko no diwa duwa drnaida . Dae nae nosa taetaepmira da hine bren braema wirin . No wike butmin ko taetaepma , God dima gyori tera dinkra .
46011001	Gyo nokwa homra hamrnai . No Keriso ya homa hamike hominkra .
46011002	No yoyomkra gyo dima tenam gyo no dima hine pya brenkrai krenku . Ma gyo nokwa naegimite hoko homiskinkrai .
46011003	Ma no hoda gyo swa hiko yoma hine brunaida . Wike butmin ka ku ko Keriso . Ma ara ka ku ko ka kruha . Ma Keriso ka ku ko God .
46011004	Hamo kru diya God dima swa tyene ma God ya swa naegimin hokan ya ku yokingai me pari haka tya daemroko , yo Keriso ya hi ko hukwae daeraha .
46011005	Ma ara diya yo God dima swa tyene ma God ya swa naegimroko ya ku parinaemkroko ya kru dima hukwae ho daeraha . Yo ko ara ya ku duen ho bryoko .
46011006	Ma ya ku parinaemkroko , ya ku skwiwa gomin ko bryoko . Ma ara ko ka ku sku ko hukwae dyenkrai kren ka ku ko parinina .
46011007	Ma kru ka ku parin ko bryoko wirin , tenam ko ko God ya Dure ya kutekin mena dinaekina kren , ma ara ko kru ya kutekin waenuma nsena dinaekina .
46011008	Ma God yo kru ko , ara ya butensa homaepu . Arasu yo kru ya butensa homina .
46011009	Ma God yo kru homite ko ara ko taetaepminaete wirin . Yo ara homite ko kru ko taetaepminaete .
46011010	Hamo ara ka ku parinkraiko , ka kru ka ko tikminkrai ho naeginkrai . Tenam God ya hupe tyen wike ka hwyenku .
46011011	Ma kyo ko Yomkra ya wike kren , ara ko kru ko tikmu , ma kru ko ara tikmu haminkrnai .
46011012	God yo ara homite ko , kru ya buten ho sa homite , hamo aekwa kru ko , ara kasa hamtinkrai . Ma kronam himike homin butmin yanai ko God yaesa .
46011013	Hamo swa hiko guaesa begema dinai . Ma ara ku parinaemka God dima tyo ma wike gwin ka pake dirai ko bryokaerake .
46011014	Ma to hwora naeginkra ko kru diya ya binwoe ko gawekina kroko , hoko bryokaemaepu .
46011015	Ma ara binwoe gawekemina kroko , hoko ka kutekin aiha . Ma binwoe gawekin ko ko dima dae hoko ka ku parinina .
46011016	Ma kudi kru ara dika swa hi ko ko a droko , kuae kyo da ma Krwistin wike gwin ko kesu kronam hisa naegiminkrai .
46011017	Ma no swa hi tyerakrako , gua kronam waenuma homrai hoko a tye . Tenam gyo gaemroko kronam dukin tru homin braema wirin . Kronam swokinsa hominkrai .
46011018	No swa hi daere ko , gyo gaemroko , wike gwin gua hin tru ma gwin gua hin ko tru haminkrai . Hamo no hin ko swa hoko kukumasa drinu dra .
46011019	( Gyo haminkrai kren kru dukin ko dyen braema . )
46011020	Ma gyo hmene gaeminkrai ko , gyo kumta Yomkra ya ro dwera wirinha .
46011021	Tenam gyo guae gua kudin sa dinkrai , hamakeno , ma gwin gyo gehmenku , ma gwin gyo wai kyomkinsa dua nononkinkrai .
46011022	Ma gua aewe hokan ko kudeka , wai deka hamin ko wirinne . Ma gua hin ko God ya wike gwin ko dima ikaremrnaidane . Ma wike gwin gryogryo dumkin ko hukwaekrnaidane . Ma nogyo dima naerike tmyawe . No gua hi hyenmawe . Wirin . Ma gyo kronamhakina homo no gua hi hyenminbraema wirin .
46011023	Ma Yomkra ya no dima tyosu , no swa hi ko gyo dima tya . Wasi krite sa hakudimiti hune hoke , Yomkra Yesu yo da sete .
46011024	Sa , God dima gu ko duwa da kyasu prite , hi ko no bute dite . Hi ko gyo dima kyena . Hi ko homroko , no braemkinina .
46011025	Ma no kudua wirinku diroko , yo kapusi sa prite , God ya kromam nin homirada swa gumite ko hiwa . Hamo no kapoe dripmasu komdwi . Ma gyo deike wai hi dekano no dima hine brenina .
46011026	Hamo gyo aku dikan da hi mate wai hi me dekano , Yomkra pwen swa naegiminkrai . Gyo hamikesa homroko , aku ya krwyo pkikra hokesu naendinina .
46011027	Hamo kru ara dika ko wai ho me da ho me hamasa droko , ko Yomkra ya bute me ya kapoe ti dima hweke ho hriraiha .
46011028	Hakina krenku , kru ara dika ko da me wai hoko dwerakekano kae ka tyonam ko pitmasa drura diwasu , Yomkra ya da me ya kapusi wai hoko dinina .
46011029	Ma kru ara dika ko Yomkra dima hine handuma brenaemka , da me wai hoko drike dumkina dinaeka , hamasa droko , ka hweke hoe ko kaesa siwekraiha .
46011030	Tenam hakina krenku , kru ara gwin gyo tren taera ai dumka , tosurinkrai .
46011031	Ma kudi kyo kua tyonam ko pitmasa drurasu droko , God yo kyo a begemi .
46011032	Ma Yomkra yo kyo begeminkrako , kua hweke hoe daenkra . Kwika , to hyenu wike butmin begemin aku hoke yo kyo me begemeda .
46011033	Hakina krenku , no kire gyoke , gyo butmin hmene gaema Yomkra ya ro droko , gua kire ko huminina .
46011034	Ma kru diya yo gehmenkroko , yae ya aewe hokan kudinina . Hamo gua gaemrai hokan ko , God ya gyo a begemi . Ma swa gwin aera ko , marensu no kumta dudumi .
46012001	No kire gyoke , no aekwa Dure Waenukina hin gruwa daenkra swa ho tyo , gyo braemkrnaida .
46012002	Sem uminki gyo Krwistin dinaemkin hoke , kronam gua homamiti hoko gyo braemaha . Ma gyo ten atma naegimo yokingai kriteme homina swa tyenaemkin ko dima swa tamamiti .
46012003	Hakina krenku , no hoda gyo braemkrnaida , kru ara dika God ya Dure ko kominki hroko ko Yesu ko swokina din braema wirin . Ma hote hamo wike diko ko God ya Dure Waenukin kominki henaemkroko ko Yesu ko Yomkra hyenu din braema wirin .
46012004	Hingruwa daeskin ko ate ate , ma Dure ko trusa .
46012005	Ma tmoe hominsa ko ate ate . Ma Yomkra ko trusa .
46012006	Ma wike ko kronam ate ate homin braema , hakina kren ko tmoe ate ate hominkrai . Ma God truasa wike butmin ko dima tmoe homin ai daeminkra .
46012007	Hamo Dure Waenukin ya kru ara trusa trusama kominki ho ka kronam ate ate naegiminkra . Hamo hoko wike butmin ko taetaepmo ko waenuma prnaida .
46012008	Ma dure waenukin hoasa kru tru dima braemkin yae ate da , mate kru tru dima braemkin tru dae haminkra .
46012009	Ma Dure hoasa yo kru tru dima dumahaki din kronam dae , ma yo kru tru yo dima ai dae yo trenmin wike ko homo gaikinkrai .
46012010	Ma hoke hamo Dure hoasa kru tru dima tei atma homin kronam dae , ma tru ko God ya tyo tyadaemin dae , ma tru ko dure di ko duwa ma dure di ko swokina ka swa begema braemkin kronam ho dae , ma tru ko swa ate ate braemkininda dae , ma tru ko swa ate ate ka swa drike braemki naegimin ho dae haminkra .
46012011	Ma Dure hoasa yaesa wike gwin ko dima tmoe naekin hingruwa daeka haminkra .
46012012	Ma wike kua bute ko trusa , ma seke ko pya . Ma seke hoko ka bute ko trusa . Ma seke ko ate ate . Ma hote ho bryoko , Keriso ko hakina .
46012013	Hamo Dure truasa Ju wike kyo da ma Grwik wike da mate hro sen wike da ma hro senaemkin wike da kyo wai bra wya naedu diroko kyo butme ko trusa kiti . Hamo Dure hoasa ho kyo dewi .
46012014	Kyo braema kua bute ko seke trusa wirin . Ya seke ko pya .
46012015	Ma dikani karike ya harmaudi noko krite wirin , hakina krenku no ko bute yana wirin dmaudi . Ma yo ko buti heskra .
46012016	Ma dikani kendoka harike tmyaudi no ko kron wirin , hamo no ko bute yana wirin dmaudi . Ma yo ko bute yanesa .
46012017	Ma dikani bute butmin ko kronesa hamroko yo naemike swa tyo daerin braemane . Ma dikani bute butmin ko kehenam sa kroko yo naemike pom daerin braemane .
46012018	Bute ko hakina wirin . Hakina krenku seke butmin ko God ya bute dikan twera dra hokan twetete .
46012019	Ma dikani butmin ko sekesa hamroko , bute ko diwake .
46012020	Hamin braema wirin . Seke ko yae ate ate pya , ma bute ko trusa .
46012021	Hamo krona krite dima harike tyen braema wirin , gu ko no a din braema wirin . Ma ku ya kesu karike dima gu ko no a din braema wirin .
46012022	Kyo hine harike brenkrai , seke tru ko aia wirin dinkrai , ma kudi yo ko wirin hamroko , kyo aiki hwyen braema wirin .
46012023	Ma seke diko kyo hine brenkrai yo tmoe handuma hominkmaepu dinkrai , kyo seke ho ko pitma tikminkrai . Ma seke kua hine brenkrai ho ko waenukina wirin , kyo yokingai waenukin sa bra tikminkrai .
46012024	Ma seke di ko duwada kyo hosa kukumasa tikminkrai . Ma God ya sa kyo hamike horaite . Hamo seke diko aia wirin hoko yo pitma twete .
46012025	Hamo bute seke kaesa gaema grwine brenina wirin . Ko kaesa rwyo matum tikmo matum tikmo haminkrai .
46012026	Ma kudi seke tru ko treru diroko , bute butmin hamosa trerinkrai . Ma kudi seke trua hi hyenmroko , bute butmin ko yoyomkinkrai .
46012027	Ma gyo butmin ko Keriso ya bute ho bryoko . Ma gyo trusa trusama ko ya seke bryoko .
46012028	Ma God yo Sos hokan butmin ko yae yae twete . Hamo God ya tmoe homrnaida pru teti ko ko hya hrete . Psya tru ko God ya swa tyadaemin wike ko hrete , psya tru ko naegimin wike ko hrete . Psya tru ko wike ko kronam tei atma hominkraida hrete . Psya tru ko wike ko trenmin homu gaikinkraida hrete . Ma psya tru ko taetaepminkranaida hrete , ma psya tru ko tikminkrnaida hrete . Ma psya tru ko swa atma tyenkrnaida hrete .
46012029	Ma wike butmin ko God ya pru ten wikene . Ma butmin ko naegimin wikesane . Ma butmin ko tei ate homin wikesane .
46012030	Ma butmin ko trenmin homin wike ko sane . Ma butmin ko swa ate ate tyen wikesane . Ma butmin ko tyo tyen wikesane .
46012031	Hamo gyo yoma hine bra tmoe diko hyena droko , ho dima hine bra senina . Ma aekwa no hoda ten tru waenukin naegimira .
46013001	Ma kudi no swa ate ate wike ka swa tyen braemkroko , ma God ya po penkrai wike ka swa kesu tyen braema kroko , ma no wike dima proeka hine pya brenaemkroko , no swa ko wepi ma bera wyaen dinaekina .
46013002	Ma kudi no naegimin ko waenuka aia kroko no butmin braema gwegwema hominkrai kesu no braema , ma nokwa drinuhaki din ko hyena , hamroko no aengu dima tyo , gu ri atma hrna du yo hamroko , ma no wike ko dima proeka hin pya brenaemkroko , no ko drike wirin .
46013003	Ma gryogryo nokwa taerin butmin sumsa daema ma no bute kesu disinya du disiryoko , no wike gwin ko dima proeka hine pya brenaemkroko , hamroko kronam nokwa homra hoko no taetaepmin braema wirin .
46013004	Proeka hine pya bren kronam ko tmaekinkrai . Ma ho ko gwogwokeka , ireka , swa swokin tyaka , nanesa deka , kyomkeka hamin braema wirin .
46013005	Proeka hine pya bren kronam ko wike ka hweke hyaeka kimin braema wirin .
46013006	Proeka hine pya bren kronam ko hweke diroko yoyomkinkmaepu , ma yo swa dumasa tyo diroko , yoyomkinkra .
46013007	Ma yo pyenkin diroko hoko naedwe dinkmaepu . Yo God ko drinu dinkra kren ya homikraha ko da yo huminkra .
46013008	Proeka hine pya bren kronam ko a wirinki . Yo dyaendyaen hamosa ae . Ma God ya swa naegiminkrai hoko wirinki , ma swa ate ate da ma braemkin hokesu wirinki .
46013009	Tenam kua braemkin ko kukumasa , ma kua swa naegiminkrai braemkin ho kesu kukiskina . Ma braemnain kru yo pko diroko , kukumasa braemkin ko wirinki .
46013010	
46013011	Uminki no kyane hete hoke , no swa me no hin ko kya kukin ka hine me ka swa dinaekina hete . Ma aekwa no ko wimga naedina krenku no kya ka kronam ko hote a homi .
46013012	Aekwa kua dyenkrai ko wai gigin dyenam handuma sorinaemkina dyenkrai hakina dyenkrai . Hamosu kyo God ya tokram tuma dyenu direiki . Aekwa no kukumasa braemkra ma hamosu no yoma braemkinu braemki , God ya no braemkra ho bryoko .
46013013	Hamo aekwa dure hiko kronam haepki trumo yae aepesu hamo aenkrai ko hiwa , drinu din da ma huma paka , proeka hine pya bren hamo . Ma proeka hine pya bren hoko drike hya .
46014001	Hamo gyo wike gwin ko dima proeka hine pya brenkrai kronam ho hodrai dinkrnai . Ma Dure Waenukin yo kronam ate ate hingruwa daenkra ho kesu ko hodai dinkrnai . Ma wike gwin ko dima waenuma naegimin kronam ho ko yoma kentinkrnai .
46014002	Ma kru trua yo swa atma tryoko , yo wike gwin ko dima tmyaepuha , yo God minkisa ho tryaha . Tenam swa hoko wike gwin ko braema wirin krenku . Ma yo swa gwemin hoko , Dure ya ai me tyenkra .
46014003	Hamo kru trua God ya swa tya daemroko , yo wike ko dima ho tryaha . Hamo yo ko taetaepma , gu ko duwa deka hmihmimaka haminkra .
46014004	Ma kru trua ate swama tryoko yae yosa taetaepma trya . Ma kru diya yo God ya swa tryoko , yo Krwistin wike butmin ho taetaepmraha .
46014005	No hoda gyo butmin ko swa ate ate braemkrnaida . Hamo no hin hya gyo God ya swa ko tyadaeminkraida . Tenam God ya swa naegimin kru ko tmoe waenukina hominkra . Ma kru swa yae ate kyo braema wirin hoa tryoko , tmoe ya homra ko drike hyena wirin . Ma kudi kru trua ya trya ho tryoko hoko bryoko . Hamo wike ho prai ko taetaepmo daera braemkin braema .
46014006	Hamo kudi , no gyo dima kumta swa atma tryoko ho ko gyo taetaepmin braemane . Ma no God ya homite da ma ya hamosu homikra da ma ya braemkin da ho gyo dima naegimroko hoko bryokae .
46014007	Ma ware dumkin yokigai , wepi dinaekin , ya wyaen ko waenuma duwenaemkroko , yoke dwen kru yo bure waenuma yen braema wirin .
46014008	Ma kudi kru trua yo kibi ko handuma urinaemkroko , kru dika asi kuta tote timawe .
46014009	Hamo hote ho bryoko , gua swa wyaen ko yae atkroko , naemike ko swa drike ko braemkin braemane .
46014010	Ma to hyenu hikan ko swa ate ate ko pya prai . Ma swa hoko truato drike dumkina wirin , butmin ko drikminsa .
46014011	Hamo kudi kru trua swa ya trya drike ko no braemkinaemkroko , no hin yo ko swa ate kruha , ma yo kesu no ko swa ate kru di .
46014012	Ma gyo hoda Dure Waenukin ya gyo dima daenkra ho siwera dinku , gyo kronam di ko Keriso ya wike ko taetaepmaekina kroko hosa drureka diwa taerinina .
46014013	Hamo kru diya yo swa atma tyerakroko , God dima tyo , swa ya trya drike me tyen braema .
46014014	Kudi no God dima ko swa ate swama tryoko , no dure ya tyenkra ma no hinato tyenkmaepu .
46014015	Ma hamroko , no naemawe , hamo no God dima tryoko , no dure me no hine me hamosa tyenina . Ma no yoke gryoko , no dure me no hine me hamosa ginina .
46014016	Ma kudi , guae gua durasa God gu ko duwa droko , ma kru trua naemike swa gwa trya ko drinu din braemane . Yo gwa trya ko braemkmaepu krenku .
46014017	Ma dini , swa gwa trya ko God gu ko duwa dra , hoko duwa , ma gwa harike trya ko , wike gwin ko taetaepmin braema wirin .
46014018	No God dima gu ko duwa dinkra , tenam no swa ate ko pya tyenkra , ma gyo ko kukumasa tyenkrai .
46014019	Ma no hin ko Krwistin wike gyo aewe tru gaema no gyo dima swa drikmin yaemsin hamosa tryoko bryoko . Ma swa ate pya , ten tausen ( 10,000 ) hamo tryoko , hoko drike dumkina .
46014020	Kire gyoke , gua hin bren ko kya kuku ka hin bren dinaekromoe . Ma kronam swokin hoa gyo kya kukin dinaeknai . Hamo gua hine bren ko , wike wimgen ka hin ho dinaekrnai .
46014021	Ma God ya swa Kwonam kimin ko , Yomkra ya tyen ko , swa ate wike ko kumta no swa ko , no wike ko dima tryoko no wike ko a daerieiki .
46014022	Ma swa atma tyen kronam hoko Krwistin dinaemkin din ko dima naegiminina . Ma Krwistin din ko dima wirin . Ma God ya swa tyadaemo drinu din wike ko dima , da ma drinu dinaemkin wike ko dima ko wirin .
46014023	Ma kudi Krwistin wike gyo butmin gaemo , swa atma tryoko , ma wike gwin , God ko drinu dinaemkin ko kesu kumta hokan proko , gyo ko hmeneyen hoa dike tyen braema wirinne .
46014024	Ma Krwistin dinaemkin kru trua yo pta gyominki po , ma gyo butmin God ya swasa tryoko , yo daereka kronam ya hominkra ho hine bre pen braema . Hanio swa gua tryai butmin ko yo begemina dinaekina .
46014025	Hamo ya hin gwemin ko topkyen ma God ya kinaetegite paka wainso , God dima gu ko drinu pra harike tyaka , God ko drinu gyominki hra , harike tyen braema .
46014026	Hamo gyo naemike homreikike . Ma aku dikan gyo God dima gaemroko , kru tru yo yoke gu ma kru truato ko gyo dima tyadaemo , kru truato God ya yo dima tyo daere ho tyenina . Ma kru truato swa atma tyo , ma kru truato ka swama tryai ho sakrwyo tyenina . Gyo kronam naemike homroko , kronam hoko Krwistin wike ho gaemrai ko taetaepminina .
46014027	Ma kudi , kru trua ya swa ate , tyera kroko , wike haepki o haepki trumo hamo sa tyen ko bryoko . Hamo kru trua twya naedu , kru trua twya naedu haminina . Ma kru truato , swa ho duduma tyenina .
46014028	Ma kudi kru diya tyo tyenin kru tru ko wirinkroko kru wa swa atma tryako , yo swa tyenina wirin . Hamo yae rwyo yo dima swa tyene ma God yominki swa trya ho sa hominina .
46014029	Hamo wike haepki o haepki trumo hamo kasa God ya swa naegiminkrnai . Ma wike gwin ko swa ho tryai daereka , swa ho ko drikminane , ma drike wirinne , harike begeminkrnai .
46014030	Ma kudi kru trua yo God ya swa naegimo , ma wike gwin ko pa daereko , God ya kru tru yo dima drike tru naegimo , kru swa tye hra yo hmitkinina .
46014031	Hamo gyo butmin kru ara , trusa trusama God ya swa naegimroko , gyo butmin braemkeka aikin braema .
46014032	Ma kru God ya swa naegiminkrai ko tikmin kru ya dikan naedrna drna hokan naendinina .
46014033	Kyo braema howa , God yo hamosa pkwaenkmaepu . Waenuma pen yanai ko yo . Hamo kyo kesu yo dinaekrnaida .
46014034	Ma God ya wike ko swa tyenaete gaemroko , ara ko krikrika penina ko swa tyenina wirin . Tenam Ju wike ka koma ya tyen ko harina , ka toko yomkrakin braema wirin .
46014035	Ma kudi ara trua yo swa drike tru braemkira kroko , yo kuta ya aewe hokansu , ya kru dima tondaerinina . Ma ara ko God ya swa tyo daerin aewe hokan ko wike ko dima tyen ko bryoko wirin .
46014036	Ma God ya swa ko gyo dima hya komdwa pkrake dini . Ma God ya swa ko gyo guaesa braemkraike .
46014037	Ma kudi kru diya yo hina yo ko God ya swa tyadaemin kru droko ma ya hina Dure ya no dima kronam tru hingrua daeaha droko hamo gyo braemkrnai swa nokwa hi kimra ko God ya no dima tyo , kimra .
46014038	Ma kudi kru diya swa hi ko hine handuma brenaemkroko , gyo yo dima kesu hine brenina wirin .
46014039	Hakina krenku , no kire gyoke , gyo God ya swa ko aiki naegimaka ma gyo swa ate wike ka swama naegimirakuro gariomoe .
46014040	Hamo gyo kronam naekin homwera kroko , pitmasa hominina .
46015001	Kire gyoke , no sem hupe waenukin ko gyo dima tya , no hote hosa tyera , hamo gyo yoma hine brunaida . Hupe waenukin hoko gyo sem saewi .
46015002	Ma hupe waenukin nokwa gyo dima tya daemo , gyo daera drinu dewi . Hamo gua drinu dewiko yae hamosa aeroko , God ya gua hweke hoe a dae . Ma gua hin ko gyo hamasa drinu dewike .
46015003	Swa nokwa sete ya drike ko hyena . Hamo hoko nokwa gyo dima tya ko hiwa . Keriso ya pwete ko kua hweke dware hoe ko ya sera . Ma hoko sem kwonam kimin hosa bryoko homite .
46015004	Ma kwonam kimin ko harina , yo sa kuta ditrnam mga hro naendu , aku haepki wirinku te ukan hamo yo hote warmo durkyo asite ko dina .
46015005	Ma yo Pita dima ko yatumki taenkisu , yawike kosin ko dima ko marensu taenkite .
46015006	Hamosu wike ya naegimite paib handred ( 500 ) hamo ko ri trusa hokan gaemo , yo hokan taenkite . Ma aekwako , wike ho ko pya prai , ma gwin ko tosurewi .
46015007	Ma yo Jeims dima taenkisu , maren ya wike gwin ko dima taenkite .
46015008	No dima ko marensu taenkite . Hamo no ko kya kronam atma hamtena dinaekina .
46015009	Tenam no ko ya wike ka tmoe homo , marenmarenki kwen kru , tenam no God ya wike ko domsorite kren .
46015010	Ma tenam God ya proekin hoa aekwa no hi hra hwa . Ma ya proekin no dima daete ko hamasa daemaepu . Ma no tmoe ko hyena hominkra , ma ya wike gwin ko kesu tmoe hominkrai , ma ko kukuma hominkrai . Ma no ko naesa hominkmaepu , God ya proekin ko no dima aenku , hoa nominki hominkra .
46015011	Hamo nokwa naegimite da ma ka naegimiti da , kyo butmin swa trusa naegiminkrai . Hamo gyo hoko drinu dinkrnai .
46015012	Ma aku pya kyo God ya Keriso warmo durkyo asite swa tyenkrai . Hamo naemo diwa wike gwin gyo harike tyenkrai wike ko ko hote warmo durkyo asin braema wirin dinkraike .
46015013	Ma kudi swa hoko drinu kroko , Keriso yo durkyo asmyaepuha .
46015014	Ma kudi Keriso ya durkyo asin swa ko drinu wirinkroko , hamroko , swa kua gyo dima tyadaeminkrai ko drike dumkin .
46015015	Hamroko kyo God ya swa kraekraema tyenkrai , tenam kua tyenkrai ko Keriso yo pwo warmo asite ko dinkrai . Ma kudi tosurin wike ko asin braema wirin kroko , God yo Keriso warmo asmyaepuha .
46015016	Tenam tosurin wike ko asinaemkroko , Keriso yo kesu asmyaepuha .
46015017	Ma kudi Keriso yo drinu asinaemkina hamraino gua drinuhaki din ko drike dumkina , hamo gua hweke hoa yae hamo aeka , gyo gwemina huraiha .
46015018	Ma kudi swa hoko drinu kroko , wike , Keriso ko drinu din tosuriti ko gwemgwemkitiha .
46015019	Ma kudi Keriso yo to hyenu hikan sa kyo taetaepmin braema , ma tosuru taetaepmin braema wirin kroko , to hyenu wike ko kyo dima aenuwe din ko bryoko .
46015020	Ma drinu swa ko hiwa , Keriso yo pwo warmo durkyo asite krenku tosurin wike ko kesu warmo durkyo asryeiki .
46015021	Himike , kru trua yo me krenku , kyo tosurinkrai , ma kru tru yo kesu henku , kyo pwen hro askinkrai .
46015022	Ma wike butmin ko pwen braema , tenam kua kingwam ko Adam krenku . Hote ho bryoko , wike dika Keriso kana droko , ko aswyekraiha .
46015023	Himreiki . Yatumki ko Keriso ya asite . Ma aku ya rwyo pkikra hokeko diko ya wike kroko , ko warka durkyo akwasryeiki .
46015024	Hamo diroko , to hyenu hia hoe yekra ko pki . Hokeko , Keriso yo to hyenu wike ka yomkra butmin dmyo wike dikan prai ko kuai God dima dae yaesa yomkraki .
46015025	Ma Keriso ya yomkra kusu , God ya wasi dimki ya karike tukramgite hre .
46015026	Ma wike wasi butmin ko tosura naedesu marensu pwen ko wirinki .
46015027	Tenam Kwonam koma tyen ko God yo gryo butmin ko sakumta ya karike tukramgite hrete . Ma kyo braema howa gryo butmin ko Keriso ya karike tukram aera , ma God ko wirin .
46015028	Ma gryo butmin ko Keriso yo dimasa aesu God ya kya yaesa God ya karike tukram hokan hre aesu , butmin yo dima daete , hamo God yaesa butmin hamo yomkraki .
46015029	Ma swa tru ko wike ka kume ka wike tosurin ko wai bra yenkrai ko drai hoko diwake . Ma kudi tosurin wike ko a asryeiki ko din swa ko drinu kroko , naemo diwa wike ko ka kum tosurin ka dware wai bra yenkraike .
46015030	Ma naemo diwa aku pya wike gwin ko hoda kyo domsorwera dinkraike .
46015031	Kire gyoke , no aku butmin pumaekra . Nokwa irinma harya tenam gyo me no me kyo ko Yesu Keriso yominki hurai .
46015032	Ma no swa ko grwamga tyera . Ma no Epeses hikan ware gryogryo dei dure psaen kominki grwin brenkra ko , nae hodrasa kren , hamo ya hoe ko nokwa naekin senane . Ma kudi tosurin wike ko asin braema wirin kroko , hamroko kwonam kimin ho bryoko hamwe , kyo kudin me wai me kudwe . Tenam ko te ukan hamo ko kyo tosura naedreiki .
46015033	Ko harike kraeroko gyo daerinkromoe . Ma gyo kru kronam swokin kominki pkopkora kuroko , kronam waenukin gua hominkrai ko ka domsorwekraiha .
46015034	Ma gua hmene yen kronam dinaekin ko hro naende , hin bren waenukinsa sinai . Hamake , ma gyo hweke hote turomoe . Ma no hirike tyo gyo hukwaekrnaida , wike gwin gyo God ko handuma braemkinkmaepu .
46015035	Ma hamosu kru trua yo tondaerikraha . Ma tosurin wike ko naemike warka asin braemane dikraha . Ma ka bute ko naerike tike .
46015036	Yato gu ko hmen yen dinaekra . Kyo braema howa , kon ke ko tonam hre pwenaemkroko , yo hote a deri mti .
46015037	Ma kyo raisi ke o wit ke hakin ko tonam hrenkraiko , kyo sem deri mta woi min hakin ko hrenkmaepu , kyo ke hosa hrenkrai .
46015038	Hamo God yo ke butmin deri mtosu tei ate ate trusa trusama daemo drike yenkrai .
46015039	Ma ware gryogryo ka saio ko trusa wirin yae tei ate ate hakina . Ma wike ka saioko yae ate , ma ware gryogryo bun , smire ka saio ko yae tei ate hakiketena .
46015040	Ma kwoe kom gryogryo me mate to hyenu gryogryo ko kesu hakina . Kwoe kom gryogryo ka kutekin ko waenuka yae atkina , ma to hyenu ya kutekin kesu waenuka yae atkina .
46015041	Ma tei ya kutekin ko yae yo sa haka waenukina , ma dwarin ya kutekin ko waenuka yae atkina , ma pute ko kesu ka kutekin ko waenuka yae tei atkina . Ma pute trua kin ko yae ate ma pute tru ya kin kesu yae ate hakiketena .
46015042	Hamo tosurin wike ka aswyekraiko , hote ho bryoko . Ma kyo pwo giwa brenkraiko domka naendinkrai . Ma ho gya breri ka aswyekraiko hote domkin braema wirin .
46015043	Ma pwen kua giwa brenkrai ko drodropka ai dumka diwa , hamo pwen ho ko warka hote asisu aika waenuki .
46015044	Ma pwen kua giwa brenkrai ho ka naedinkrai . Ma yo hote durkyono hoko duren yana . Ma kyo ko to hyenu bute sa sena , hamo kyo duren ya bute kesu sen braema .
46015045	Kwonam kesu harike tyena , kru hya pkiten kru ko Adam , ware ko yatumki yo dae hete . Ma Kru Adam ya mare pkite yo ko ware daenin Dure .
46015046	Ma yo yatumki pkmaepu . Wirin , to hyenu ware henin ko yatumki pkosu ma dure , hamosa henin ko maresu pkite .
46015047	Hamo kru hya Adam ko , to tutusa homina , yo to gite pkite . Ma Kru maresu pkite yo ko kwoe kom hwya pkite .
46015048	Ma wike dika ko ko to hyenu wike kroko , ko ko kru to tutu me homite ho dinaekina . Ma wike dika ko ko kwoe yana kroko , ko ko kwoe kom hwya pkin kru ho dinaekina .
46015049	Ma aekwa kyo kru to me homite yo dinaeka prai , maren kyo kwoe kom hewen hwya pkite kru yo dinaekreiki .
46015050	Kire gyoke , nokwa hi trya daernyai , saio me kapoe me hominko , God ya pra ten braema wirin . Ma mgakwen yokigai naekin ko domkmaekina kroko , hoato mgakwen a domkmaekin ya ri sen braema wirin .
46015051	Swa sem gwemkin hi tyerakra , tuma daernyai . Hamosu kyo butmin a tosurieiki .
46015052	Kyo kibi uru wyaen daereka kyo kron ko katmasa kikimki dro di , kyo katmasa kryo tei atkreiki . Ma tosurin wike ko wawarka durkyo akwasi tei atkina direiki . Hamosu ko hote a tosurieiki .
46015053	Ma kua bute to hyenu hikan kwenkrai ko pwen braema , ma ware hewen dima troko , pwen braema wirin . Hamroko hoko Kwonam kimin ya tyen ko , pwene ko domsorina , dimkina .
46015054	
46015055	Hamo pwen gwa dimkin ko diwake . Ma tren gwa daenkra ko diwake .
46015056	Ma pwen ya ai ko hweke daenkra . Ma hweke ya ai ko koma swa hoka hwya pkinkra .
46015057	Ma kyo God dima gu ko duwa dwe , tenam pwen ko kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya dimkite kren .
46015058	Hakina kren kire gyoke , wike gwin ka kumta gyo dima hamasa tryoko , gyo daeryomoe . Gyo Yomkra ya tmoe aiki hominkrnai , tenam gyo braema Yomkra ya tmoe nakoe dae homroko , tmoe hoko hamasa hominkmaepu , drike direiki .
46016001	Aekwa no God ya wike to Judia hokan prai ko dima sere daen swa tyerakra . No Geresia Krwistin wike ko dima tyo , ka homrnai ho bryoko , gyo kesu hamike homnaida .
46016002	Sande hyaekin , gyo butmin trusa trusama , naekin gua naemo saewi ho gwin ko sa hro pitma tikminina . Hamo maren no pko diroko , gyo sere ko dima daewera a drurieiki .
46016003	No hamosu kumta gua hin bra daewi hoko gaema kru gua sem taerewi ko dima dae ma ka hi kwonam kima naendesu taera , Jerusraem dima pru tenina .
46016004	Ma kudi noke terada hine bruroko , hamroko , no kominki ti .
46016005	Ma no Mesodonia dima ko yatumki ti , ma gyo dima ko marensu kumti . Tenam no Mesodonia gite ko yatumki , kwe hwyasuda .
46016006	Ma no gyominki aku kukuma hi , ma kio aku hokeko , gyominki hmaudi . Hamo no dika terakuro , gyo no taetaepminina .
46016007	No a no gyo ten dure hokan tupma andyonma dyena dinaekin ko bryokmaepu . Ma kudi Yomkra harike tryoko , no aku kukuma pya gyominki hi .
46016008	No Epeses hikan sa heka hroko , Pentikos aku ho pkosu tikraha .
46016009	Tenam God yo ten tmyaete kren wike pya ko Krwistin dwera dinku no hikan haka ko taetaepmira .
46016010	Hamo marenku Timoti yo gyo dima pkroko , gyo yo pitmasa tikmnai , tenam ko ko yomkra ya tmoe homin kru .
46016011	Hakina krenku , kru trua yo ko drike dumkina da yo ko sa margite hrenina wirin . Gyo yo pitma tikmasu , katma no dima pru pkenina . No yo me mate kua kire gwin ko huma pra .
46016012	Ma no kua kire Aporos yo dima swa idima tya hamo yo kua kire kominki kuta gyo dyenina de . Ma yo aekwa ko a ti , yo aku dikan bryokaesu tikraha .
46016013	Gua braeme , Keriso ko drinu da aiki penina . Gyo tempuromoe aikiskrnai .
46016014	Gyo tmoe naekin homroko , God me wike ko dima proeka hine pya brenknai .
46016015	Kire gyoke , gyo braema hoa , Stepana ya gire to Akaia hokan penkrai ko katumki Krwistin diti . Hamo ko God ya wike taetaepminkrai .
46016016	Hamo wike hakemin ka hominkrai ma kominki hominkrai , no gyoke hakina hominkrnaida .
46016017	Hamo Stepana da ma Potuneta da ma Akaika da hamo ka no pkin braema wirin krenku , ka pkewi .
46016018	Ma ko no hin duma mate gua hin kesu duma hamaewi . Hakina kren , kyo wike hakemin ko dima hine waenuma brenina .
46016019	Ma Krwistin wike Asia Prowen hoke prai ka yoyomkin swa gyo dima hre pkrai . Ma Akwira me Prisira ta aewe hokan Krwistin wike ko gaeminkrai ko gyo Yomkra minki waenuma pnaike din swa gyo dima hre traha .
46016020	Kire gyoke , Krwistin wike hikan prai ka yoyomkin swa kesu gyo dima hre traha . Ma kru gyo God ya wike kua kire ko drima krnaiyaeyaeminina .
46016021	Hamo yoyomkin swa hi ko nae no krite me kimra .
46016022	Kru dika Yomkra dima hine pya brenaemkroko , domsorin kronam yo dima pkikraha . Yomkra gu pkrna .
46016023	Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya waenuma pen kronam ko gyo dima kumta yae hamo gyominki hamo aenada .
46016024	No Yesu Keriso ya wike butmin ko gyo dima proeka hine pya brenkra .
47001001	No ko Por , Yesu Keriso ya no pru ya tmoe homnada , tenam God ya tyo diku , kua kire Timoti ki ko , Krwistin wike to Korin hokan penkrai , gyo me God ya wike butmin to Akaia hokan penkrai gyo dima kwo hi kimraha .
47001002	Kuai God me Yomkra Yesu Keriso ti gyo dima proeka waenuma pen kronam daenada .
47001003	Kyo kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso yai me ya God yo dima gu ko waenukina dwe . Kuai yo ko proekin yanai . Ma taetaepmin butmin teinam ko yo .
47001004	Nakoe pyen kyo dima pko diroko , yo kyo taetaepminkra . Hamo pyenkin ko , wike gwin ko dima pko , God ya naemike kyo dima taetaepma ho me kyo wike gwin taetaepmin braema .
47001005	Ma Keriso ya pyen me tren pya dyete , ma kyo ko kukumasa dyenkrai . Ma God yo wike pya hyenma taetaepmo kyo kesu Keriso gitma ko kukuma taetaepmin krai .
47001006	Kyo pyenkin diroko , hoko gua taetaepminaete , mate gyo God ya pra gyoke pnaida . Ma kudi kua ko taetaepmroko ka kesu gyo taetaepminina . Hamo gyo ai ko dima dae , pyenkin kua dyenkrai gyo kesu diwa huma tmaeki penina .
47001007	Hamo kyo hine hrodi gyo bryoko penkreiki . Kyo braeme , pyenkin kua dyenkrai ko gyo kesu ho dyenkraiha . Ma Taetaepmin kua senkrai ko gyo kesu senkrai .
47001008	Kire gyoke , gua braeme , to Asia hokan pyenkin kua dyaewi ko . Pyenkin ho dyaewi ko hyena . Hamo kua ai ko ka dmyaewi . Hamo kyo hine braewi kyo aepesu hamo hwyen braeme wirin dewi .
47001009	Kyo hine braewiko ka kyo begema gyo punai dwekraiha dewi . Ma ko himike homaewi , ma tenam kyo kuae kua ai dima hine brenina wirin , kyo wike tosuru homo durkyo asinkrai God yo dimasa hine brenina .
47001010	Ma yo aku pya kyo pumaekin aku hoke ya kyo taetaepmamite . Ma kyo braeme , yo hote kyo taetaepmi .
47001011	Ma gua guriguri God dima , kyo taetaepmnai droko hoko kyo taetaepmin braema . Hamo wike pya ko kua swa God dima tryoko , God yo daera kyo taetaepmo kyo bryoko pen braema . Hamo wike pya ko God dima aima tyaka gwa taetaepmin ko duwa dreiki .
47001012	Kua hinam irin me tyenkraiko kua pen kronam gyo dima kutyenkraiko , God ya drinusa tyenkra kronam ho me mate ya proekin kronam hoasa kyo tikminkra . Hoko wike ka braemkin ho wirin .
47001013	Kua kwonam hi kimrai ko gyo hyaeka braemkmaekin hosa kimrai . Ma aekwa gyo handuma braema wirin kyo ko . Ma no hoda marensu gyo butmin kyo yoma braemknaida . Hamo kua Yomkra Yesu ya rwyo pkin aku hokeko , gua kyo dima irinkraida . Ma kua gyo dima iru haminina .
47001014	
47001015	Kronam hikin ko no braema kren , no hine bra no kuta gyo dyera de . Diwa gyo hagurmo gyo waenuma pnaida .
47001016	Tenam no hine ko no Masadonia dima take ten dure hokan no gyo dyera de . Ma no hote rwyo pkeka gyominki pera de , tenam gyo no taetaepmnaida no Judia dima tenku .
47001017	Ma tenam no kuta gyo dyera hine hi bra hrenko gyo hine braewi yo naemo diwa hine ate ate brenkrake . No hine himike brenkra hoko nae nokwa hodra sane . Ma nokwa heno dra drike ko wirinne .
47001018	God yo drinusa tyenkra , hamo nokwa heno droko henosa . Ma wirin droko wirinsa .
47001019	Ma nokwa Saris me Timoti hamo kyo God ya kya Yesu Keriso ya swa gyo dima naegimiti . Keriso ko God ya heno dina .
47001020	Tenam God ya swagumin ko Keriso yo . Hakina kren kyo Keriso ya hinam God ya hi hyenminkrai .
47001021	Ma God ya kyo me gyo me ai daenkra . Hamo Keriso yominki aiki hwyen braeme . Hamo God ya kyo sa ri yae yosa hakina hokan twena prai .
47001022	Kua bute ti ya aripe hro kyo ko yana . Ma ya dure kua tyonam hrena , tenam kyo braemknaida kyo ko yana hamo yo gwin ko hamosu kyo dima dae .
47001023	Ma kudi nokwa kro tryoko , God ya gu kro tryaha . Hakina kren no drinu God ya knon ti hi tryaha . Ma no Korin dima tmaepu , tenam no gyo dima pyenkina swa a tye .
47001024	Ma kua gyo dima gyo Keriso dima drinu dnai a harike tryeiki . Tenam kyo braema , gyo sem harike tyena . Ma kyo gyominki homaka gyo yoyomknaida .
47002001	Hakina kren , no naesa hine bra tya , no a ti de . No kuta gyo dima pyenkin daemeda .
47002002	Kudi no gyo dima pyen daeroko , wike dika yoyomkin no dima daemawe . Wike , nokwa pyenkin daen kasa .
47002003	Hakina kren , no kwo ho gyo dima kima . No gyo dima pkroko wike ko no dima yoyomkin daemaekin ko pyenkinsa daen braema .
47002004	No kwo kimaka gyo dima proe hyenke . Ma hokeko no idima bya . No gyo yoyomkinaemkmeda hoa wirin . Nokwa kwo kima gyo braemknaida , no gyo dima proe hyena tyenkra .
47002005	Ma kru trua yo pyenkin daete hoke yo pyenkin hoko no dima daemaepu . Wirin . Yo butmin gyo dima daete , yo gwinsa gyo dima daete . ( No hirya tenam no yo dima swa tukin a tye . )
47002006	Ma kru hi ya hweke hoe ko wike gwin gua yo dima daeti hoko bryoko .
47002007	Hakina kren , aekwa gyo kru ho dima hamaha da hote kyominki gaemwe harinina , pako yo totoka Krwistin kronam ko naediskmeda .
47002008	Hamo nokwa gyo dima tyera , gyo yo dima trnyai , kire kyo gu dima hine pya brenkrai ko dnai .
47002009	No kwo ho gyo dima kima tenam no gyo bryoko dyera , gyo no swa daeritike , ma wirinne , ho braemkira .
47002010	Ma kudi gyo kru di dima ya hweke hamaha droko , no kesu yo dima hamaha di . Ma nokwa hamaha droko , - dini nokwa kronam tru hamaha droko - no Keriso ya hinam gyo taetaepmira .
47002011	Kyo hirinkrai tenam Saiten ya kyo dmyaera dinkrai . Ma ya kronam ko kyo braema hoa .
47002012	Ma no to Troas hokan Keriso ya swa naegimira , kutadi , Yomkra yo sem ten homina dya .
47002013	Ma tenam no kua kire Taites dyenaemku diku , no hine pya brete . Tenam no no kire Taites dyenaemku diku wike hokan penkrai ko dima aenikma , no dumasa Masadonia dima tete .
47002014	Ma aekwa no God ko duwa dra . Tenam kyo aku pya Yesu yo kyo taetaepminkra kren , kyo Keriso ya ai me totetyaka dimkin braema . Ma tmoe kua hominkrai ko God ya tyo wike butmin ko braemkin braema . Swa ya tyo wike butmin ka daera braemkinkrai ko pom waenukina huhurina sato daerinkrai ho dinaekina .
47002015	Kyo ko pauda pom waenukin ho bryoko . Keriso ya disiru , pom ko God dima tenkra . Ma pom waenukin hoko wike God dima tenkrai ko dima da mate God a dinkrai ko dima kesu tenkra .
47002016	Ma wike dika gwemkwerakrai ka pom ho daeryai ko pwen pom dinaekina . Ma wike dika gwemkinaemkroko , pom hoa ko ware daenkra . Hakina kren , kru ara dia yo tmoe hi hominkra ko bryokone .
47002017	Wike gwin ka hin ko God ya swa ko gryogryo twa taerin dinaekina . Ma kua hin ko hakina wirin . Ma God ya kyo pru pkenku , kyo ya knon ti ya swa tryoko pitmasa tyenkrai , Keriso ya tmoe hominkrai ka tyenkrai ho bryoko .
47003001	Ma nokwa swa hi kima hre to gua hyaekeka , gua hine ki ko irin me tryaikedi . Ma dini ki ko wike gwin dinaekinane . Kia kronam swa kwonam kima gyo dima hre trnaidane . Ma dini gyo kia swa kwonam kimnaidane .
47003002	Gyo ko kia reta . Gua hi ko kia proe ti kimina , hamo wike ko ho diwa hyaekin braema .
47003003	Gyo dyen braema , Keriso yaesa kwo hi kima naede , ki gitma hre tete . Ma hike pensore me kimina wirin , hiko God ya Dure me kimina . Ike ti kimina wirin . Wike ka proe ti kimina .
47003004	Ki harike tryai , tenam ki Keriso yo me kren , ki braemkrai , God ya tyena ko hakina .
47003005	Tmoe hi ko kuaesa homin ko bryoko wirin .
47003006	Ma ya kio homo diroko kio ya swagumin nin ya twya tmoe hoa kio homin braema . Ma swa hoko kimina wirin , swa nin hoko ya Dureha . Ma Koma ho kimin ya hoe ko pwene . Ma dure ko ware dyaen dyaen daenkraha .
47003007	Moses ya Koma ko ike ti kimite . Ma God ya ho daete ko ya kae kesu naegite . Ma kae hoko Moses ya tokram kesu sete . Ma kae ho ko wirinkiraku diroko , Isrwaeo wike ko ya tokram a tuma dimaekiti . Ma Koma kae aikin hakin me daete , koma hoko aeroko hoe ko pwensa .
47003008	Hamo God ya Dure ko haka , tmoe homroko , ya ai me kae waenukin ko hyena .
47003009	Ma kronam tru ko hweke homo hoe daenkra ma hoko waenukina . Ma tmoe tru ko God ya penkra hokan ware dyaen dyaen hwyenina daenkra hoko waenukiskina .
47003010	Hamo kyo hirike tmawe , kae ai hyena sem aete , ko wirinkite . Tenam kae ya ai waenukin aekwa aenkra ko hyena .
47003011	Ma kronam naekin ambum kukumasa aemaekina kroko hoko waenukina , ma kronam naekin dyaen dyaen aemaekina kroko hoko waenukina , kandim hyena .
47003012	Hamo tenam kyo himike hine brenkrai kren , kyo ko aiya .
47003013	Kyo ko Moses dinaekina wirin , yo bai braeke sa ya gurite , tenam Isrwaeo wike ko ya tokram kae wirinkra ho dimeda .
47003014	Ma hine brene ko ten dwena . Hamo aekwa kesu ko swagumin brunai kwonam kimin hoko hyaekroko ka hine ko bai me gurinina dinaekinkrai . Ma ko Keriso yominki pkorina kroko , bai gurin hoko sa sirin braema .
47003015	Ma drinu aekwa ko Moses ya Koma hyaekroko bai hoa hin grurinkra .
47003016	Ma bai hoko sa sirin braema . Ma Moses ya swa Kwonam kima tyena ko , yo krwyo kutasu Yomkra ya penkra hokan ya bai ko sa sirite .
47003017	Ma Kwo hokan kima tyena ko Yomkra dina , ya drike ko Yomkra ya Dure . Ma Yomkra ya Dure ko dikan hroko , wike hoko wogitma dinaeka penkmaepu , ko sa sirina .
47003018	Hamo kyo butmin kua tokram ko bai me parina wirin . Hakina kren Yomkra ya ai kae waenukin hoko kua tokram hmiroko wike gwin ko naegiminkra . Ma kae ai min hoko Yomkra yo ko Dure Waenukin , yo gite pkinkra . Kyo atma homroko kyo yo dinaekreiki . Hamo kae hoko hote hyenkinkra .
47004001	God ya kyo dima proeku diku , yo tmoe hi kyo dima dae , kyo homnaida . Hamo kyo tmoe hikan dima totokmaepu .
47004002	Ma kyo kronam diko gwema homaka hukwaekemiti ko hro naediti . Hakina kren , kyo naekin homroko kraekraemin braema wirin . Ma God ya swa naegimroko kua hote atma kraekraema tyen braema wirin . Kyo God ya kinaegite hwyenku kyo kae gitma kwyenkrai . Hamo kyo swa naekin tryoko kyo drinusa tyenkrai . Hamo kyo hoda wike ko ka proenam hokan diwa ko waenumasa penknai dnaida .
47004003	Hamo kudi hupe waenukin kua naegiminkrai ko gwemina droko , wike hoko gwemkin sunam dima treiki ko dimasa gwemina .
47004004	Tenam ko to hyenu hia ya god swokin ya ka hin ko hunara hokan wogitma tikminkra kren ko swa hoko drinu dinkmaepu . Ma kae ko dima kaeminkrako yo ten dwo ko dyen braema wirin . Ma kae hoko hupe waenukin gite pkinkra . Ma hupe hoko Keriso ya ai ho . Ma Keriso yo ko God ya dure ho bryoko .
47004005	Ma kyo kuae kua Yomkra dinkrai . Ma kyo ko Keriso ya hinam gua tmoe hominkrai .
47004006	Tenam sem uminki God dia tyete , hunam hokan kae gu pkna dina kroko , God Hoasa ya kae pru kumta kua proenam kae mina aera . Hamo kyo God ya ai me ya kae ko Keriso ya tokramgite kaemo kyo diwa braemknaida .
47004007	Ma God ya ai waenukin sen kyoko , to dronge me homin hakina . Tenam wike butmin ko braemknaida God ya aiasa kyo tikminkra hiko kua ai wirin .
47004008	Ma aku pya kyo pyenkin dyenkrai , ma pyenkin hoato kyo domsorinkmaepu . Ma aku gwin ko kyo bubutkinkrai , ma kyo hakrako naedweri dinkmaepu .
47004009	Ma kua totetyen wike ko pya , ma kyo kua kire dumkina dinaeka hmaepu . Ma ko kyo kuwyera dinkrai . Ma ko kyo myaepu .
47004010	Aku butmin kua bute domka naedikra tyonam hokan Yesu ya pwen ho sa damga tenkrai . Hamo ya ware ko kua bute tyonam dyen braema .
47004011	Kyo Yesu tmoe hominkrai kren kyo pumaekina . Hamo ya ware ko kua bute domkin naedikra hokan dyen braema .
47004012	Hakina kren , pwen ko kua tyonam tmoe hominkra . Ma ware ko gua tyonam tmoe hominkra .
47004013	Ma Kwonam kima tyen ko nokwa hare tenam no drinu de . Hote ho bryoko kyo Yesu ko drinu Keriso dekano tyenkrai .
47004014	Kyo braema , God yo kua Yomkra Yesu warmo durkyo asite , ma kyo me gyo me Yesu yominki satyoma ya pra treiki .
47004015	Ma kronam hi butmin ko , gyo taetaepminina . Ma God ya proekin kronam ko to hoe hoe wike butmin hamo siroko ko God dima gu ko waenukina dreiki .
47004016	Hakina kren , kyo hine hirike bra kyo totokinku naedwe dinkmaepu . Kua bute ko domkinkrai , ma kua dure ko aku hyaekin ninkinkrai .
47004017	Ma hoko hikina , pyenkin kukina hi dirai hikin ko aku kukumasa aen braema , maren kyo Hewen hokan aku butmin pen kronam dyen braema . Kronam waenuma pen hoa kronam pyenkin ko dmyaen braema .
47004018	Kyo gryo knon me diwa braem ho dima hine brenkmaepu . Kyo gryo knon me dyenaemkrai ho dima hine pya brenkrai . Gryo kua knon me dyenkrai ko aku pya aen braema wirin . Ma kua knon me dyenaemkin ko dyaen dyaen aepesu hamo aenina .
47005001	Ma kyo braemki naedrai prai aewe hi , kua ya tyonam hi penkrai ko kua bute grurioko , God yo aewe Hewen hokan kua peninada tina . Ma aewe yae tin ko aepesu dyaen dyaen penina .
47005002	Aenuwe , kyo prai aewe hokan pyaerin drima prai . Kyo hoda prai aewe Hewen hokan praka byen drimiprai .
47005003	Hamroko kyo bute dumka a hureiki .
47005004	Ma kua prai aewe to hyenunin hi tyonam hwyaka aemi , kyo naemawe dinkrai . Ma kyo kua bute ko hro naedwera dinkmaepu , ma kyo hoda Hewen prai aewe ko kua bute paru kua bute domkin ko atka ware dyaen dyaen hwyen braema .
47005005	Ma God yasa kronam atkin kyo dima pkikra ko sem naegite . Ma ya dure kyo dima daete , tenam kyo braemknaida ya kyo dima dae tikminkra ko waenukina .
47005006	Hakina kren , kyo ko tempumaepu . Kyo braema kua bute ko aewe dinaekina , hamo kyo hikan proko , kyo Yomkra ya aewe penkmaen .
47005007	Tenam kyo hikan hwyaka , mgakwen nakoe dyenaemkrai ho dima hine brenkmaepu , kyo God ya swa ko drinusa dinkrai krenku .
47005008	Ma kyo tempumaepu , kyo hoda bute hi ko hro naede , Yomkra ya aewe hokan huwera .
47005009	Ma kua hin hya hirike brenkrai ko kyo aewe hikan o ma wakan proko kyo ya hodra homwera .
47005010	Kyo butmin ya kinaegite hokan hwyo , ya kyo begemi . Ma ya kyo butmin , trusa trusama to hikan haka homite ko , waenuma heteke ma swokina heteke , hamo kyo hoe ko dukin o swokin sireiki .
47005011	Ma kyo Yomkra dima tempwen braema . Hamo kyo wike gwin ko dima kesu twyo braemkraida . Ma God yo kua kronam butmin braema . Ma no hoda gyo kesu no kronam braemknaida .
47005012	Ma kyo kuae kua hisa hyenminkmaepu . Kyo hoda gyo dima swa tru tyo , gyo kyo dima irin braema . Hamo wike dika kru ya tokram waenukina ho diwa irinkrai , ma ya kronam ho diwa irinkmaepu , hamo gyo ko dima swa rwyo tyen braema .
47005013	Kyo ko nononka hine brenaemkin wikene . Hamaha . Kyo God ya tmoe hi homraiha . Ma kyo braemki yoma homraike . Ma hoko gyo taetaepminaete .
47005014	Keriso ya kyo dima hine pya brenku , ya kyo tikminkra . Tenam kyo braemkrai ko kru trua kua hweke dware pwete , hamo kyo butmin ko yominki tosuriti .
47005015	Yo wike butmin ko dima pwete , hamo wike aekwa ware me hikan prai ko , kae ka hodraisa hominina wirin , ko kru ko dima pwa durkyo asite ya hodrasa hominina .
47005016	Hakina kren , kyo wike ko diwa begeminkrai , to hyenu wike ka braemkin hakin ho me , ko begeminkmaepu . No uminki Keriso hamike begemite . Ma aekwa ko , haminkmaepu .
47005017	Hamo wike diko Keriso yominki huroko , ko ko wike ninsa . Ma brunai ko wirinke . Ninsa .
47005018	Ma kronam hi butmin ko God yasa homina . Yo Keriso yo gitkeka , sem kyo ko ya wasikiti , hamo ya kyo atma homina , kwasu kyo ko kire dinkra . Ma yo tmoe kyo dima daete ko homaka wike gwin yo dima kire dnaida .
47005019	Hamo kua swa ko , God ya Keriso pru kumta wike butmin ko homo yo dima kire dnaida . Ma God yo hweke ka twenkrai ko kwonam kimaepu . Ma ya homo kyo yo dima kire dinkrai ho ya kyo dima naegimite .
47005020	Hamo kyo hikan hwyaka Keriso yo dima tyenkrai . God yasa kyo gitma tyenkra ho bryoko . Hamo kyo Keriso ya hinam tyo , gyo heno du , God ya gyo homo , gua yo dima wasi kinkrai ko naede , ya kire din braema .
47005021	Ma Keriso ko hweke dumkina . Ma kua hweke dware , God ya yo pru yo kua hweke butmin ya butti hrete . Hamo yo ko kru hwekmina dinaekite . Ya hamike homite kren , kyo Keriso yominki huroko , kyo God ya kronam waenukin dyen braema .
47006001	Kyo God yominki tmoe hominkraiko , God ya proekin gyo seti ko hro naedromoe .
47006002	God ya tyen ko hiwa . Nokwa gyo dima proekite aku hokeko , no gua swa daerite . Ma gua naedmaekin aku hoko taenku diroko , nokwa gyo taetaepmite . Gyo daenyai , aekwa ko God ya proekin kronam kentua senina . Dei sen aku ko aekwasa .
47006003	Ma wike ko tmoe kua hominkrai kronam swokin dimeda . Pako ko totmeda , hamo kyo kronam hakin himinkmaepu .
47006004	Ma kyo ko God ya tmoe homin wike hamo kyo kronam hi hominkrai . Kronam pyenkin naekin diwano , kyo kate druki peskinkrai hamo wike gwin ko dima naegikrai .
47006005	Ma ko kyo dima kyomka hawyo gaema hwyaka kuwya wogitmiti . Hamo kyo tmoe hyenma homaka , krogoe aenaemka , gehmen diwa haminkrai .
47006006	Ma kyo kyomkinaemka kate druki , kua braem hosa naegimaka mate wike gwin ko dima proeka homaka God ya Dure ya ai me homaka mate wike gwin ko dima hine pya braka ,
47006007	drinu swasa tyaka tmoe ko God ya ai me homaka haminkrai . Hamake kyo braemkrai kronam kua homrai ko dumasa homrai . Hamo hi ko krarang dinaekina , hamo kyo wike gwin ko kronam dukin dua sen ho me yaka , ka kyo yen ten dwenkrai .
47006008	Ma wike gwin ka kua hi hyenminkrai , mate kua hi suma tyenkrai . Hamake ka kyo dima ikaremake , mate kyo ko duwa dinkrai . Ma wike gwin ka kyo ko kraekraemin wike dinkrai . Ma kyo drinu swasa tyenkrai .
47006009	Kyo ko kru trua braema wirin , ma wike pya ko braema kyo ko . Kyo ko pwen dure dinaekina . Ma gyo kyo diraiha , kyo ware me hurai . Ka kyo kuyenkraiko , kyo tuma yenkmaepu .
47006010	Kyo pyen-kinsu dyenkrai , ma kyo hama yoyomki penkrai . Kyo ko gryogryo pya wirin . Ma kua wike gwin ko dima naegimroko , ko gryogryo minkin braema . Wike gwin ka kyo dyenkraiko , mgakwen dumkina dyenkrai . Ma kyo butmin sena .
47006011	Hamo no kire Korin hokan penkrai gyoke , kyo gyo dima dumasa hi tryaiwa . Kua hine brurai gyo dima naegimraiwa .
47006012	Kua gyo dima proekin ho hyena . Ma gua kyo dima proekin ko tukina .
47006013	Gyo ko no kya kuku dinaekina . Hamo no gyo dima hirike tyera . Hamo gua rwyo kyo dima hamike proeknai . Ma gua proekin naegnyai .
47006014	Ma kire gyoke , wike dika Keriso ya swa ko drinu dinaemkin , kominki tmoe trusa pkori hominkromoe . Gyo hamin braema wirin . Ma dukin me swokin me ko naemake pkori tmoe trusa homin braemane . Ma naemake kae me huname ti pkori hen braemane .
47006015	Ma naemake Keriso me Saiten ti hine trusa bra tmoe trusa homin braemane . Mate Keriso ya swa drinu din wike me mate Keriso ko drinu dinaemkin wike ko naemake hine trusa sen braemane .
47006016	Ma naemake God ya aewe me mate tona wike ka kritme homin kominki tmoe hmene homin braemane . Tenam kyo ko God waremin ya aewe . God yae tyete , no aewe ko no wike ka tonae hokan tiwa , kominki hi . No ko ka God di . Hamo ko ko no wike di .
47006017	Ma Yomkra ya tyete , gyo ko kworu ko kae po guae po hamrai . Hamake ka tmoe swokin naekin homo gua ko taetaepma homromoe . Hamroko no gua swa daerin braema . Ma no ko guaiha . Hamo gyo ko no kya kuku kru kya mate no paku gyoha . Swa hiko Yomkra ai butmin yo dima aenkra ya tyena .
47006018	
47007001	Kire gyoke , kyo dima swagumin butmin hiko gyo sena . Hakina kren , kronam naekin kua dure me kua bute domsormaekina kroko , hoko hro naedwe . Ma kyo hweke dumka yae atka penina . God ya ai dima tempwenme penkwe .
47007002	Gua hine bren kyo dima kukuma tyaenina . Ma kyo kru tru dima hweke hrimaepu . Ma ara tru domsormaepu . Hamake , kraekraema gryogryo taermaepu .
47007003	Ma nokwa swa hi trya ko gyo begemira wirin . No swa tya , kyo gyo dima hine pya brenkrai de . Hamo kyo ware me hwyene o kyo tosurine kyo hmensa hwyenkrai .
47007004	Gua kronam ko no braema kren , no gyo dima irinkra . Ma kyo pyenkin hyena dyenkrai . Ma no tempumaepu . No yoyomkiskinkra .
47007005	Ma kyo to Masadonia hokan taenkewiko , pra aerwa hamin braema wirin . Pyenkin pya diwa , mate grwine bren pya diwa hamaewi . Ma kua proe tyonam tempwen ko ate ate dyaewi .
47007006	Ma God yo wike dika proe ko pyenka msyoro , ya ko hmihmiminkra . Hamo yo Taites pru kumta kyo hmihmima .
47007007	Ma ya pkra dwaresa kyo yoyomkmaepu . Yo kumta gua yo hmihmimeri swa ho tyo kyo daera yoyomkewi . Ma ya tya ko , gyo no diwera dewi de . Mate gyo no dima proeka , no swa a din wike ko dima rwyo tyaewi ko du diroko no yoyomkin hyenke .
47007008	Ma kwo nokwa kima hre to , gua hyaeka , yoyomkinaemkewi ko , no hine kwo ho kimin ko dukmaen , harmaepu . Ma kudi no gyominki ho , gyo kwo ho hyaeka diwa yoyomkinaemku , no diroko no kesu a yoyomki .
47007009	Ma no kwasu yoyomkra , tenam gua yoyomkinaem-kewi hakina wirin . No yoyomkra , tenam gua yoyomkinaemkin hoa gua kronam ko atkeiwi . Yoyomkinaemkin hoko , God ya sa , gyo dima atma homa . Ma kuato gyo tren daemaepu .
47007010	Ma yoyomkinaemkin ko God ya homo , wike ka proenam hine atma bra homo , God ya hamaha din braema .
47007011	Ma gyo dinai , gua yoyomkinaemkin , God ya sa , gua hin sa atma homo , gua ai bari tyaewi ko kyo hweke homaepu dewi . Hamake kyo swa hi dudumwe dewi . Kyo naemike dudumawe da , kyo God dima hweke hikin hren ko bryoko wirin dewi . Ma kru hweke ho homo ya hoe daewe , harike tyaewiko , bryoko .
47007012	Ma nokwa kwo ho kima ko kru hweknai yo dima kimaepu . Ma kru unai yo dima kesu kimaepu . Tenam nokwa kima hiko God yo dyenkra , hamo gyo yoma braemknaida , gyo kyo dima hine pya brenkrai .
47007013	Hakina kren , kyo ko yoyomkewi . Mate Taites ya yomku , kyo kesu yoyomkewi . Ma tenam Taites ya yoyomkinaemku , gyo ko hmihmimo diku , yo hote yoyomke .
47007014	No gua swa yo dima irin me tya , ma nokwa gyo dima hine brenkra ko gyo domsormaepu . Kua gyo dima tyenkrai ko drinu swasa . Hamo hote ho bryoko gua swa no Taitis dima tyako , hoko drinu taenke .
47007015	Gua hamo diroko yo gyo dima hine pya brenkra . Tenam gua ya swa daera homin ko aia . Gua yo dima yoyomka tempwen mesa gu kua aewe dima pkna dewi .
47007016	No yoyomkra , tenam no braema , wike nokwa pru gyo dima trako , gyo ko pitma tikminkrai .
