47008001	Kua kire gyoke , kyo hoda God ya proekin hoato Masadonia hokan , Keriso ya wike ko dima homa ho , gyo braemkisknaida .
47008002	Ma ko pyen hyena dyaewiko , ko hamaha da ko homiskewi . Ma ko hoko diwa hamaha da yoyomkewi . Ma ko sere , me gryogryo me ko pya wirin . Ma ka daewi ko hyena .
47008003	No braemko , ka daemaekin ho ko daewi . Ma hote hata hyenma daewi . Ma hiko ka hodrasa .
47008004	Ko kyo dima idima kenteiwi ko God ya wike to Judia hokan prai ko taetaepmwerada kentewi .
47008005	Kua hin kato kukuma daemaudi dewi . Ma ko hyenmasa daewi . Ma yatumki ko kae ko God dima daewi . Marensu God ya hodra hokan kae ko kyo dima kesu daewi .
47008006	Hamo kyo Taites dima tyaewiko , tmoe hi ko ya hya komdwa kren , yae hamo hominina . Hamo gyo taetaepma tyoro proeki gua daeskin ho sem komdwaewi ko yo me homada wirinmnai .
47008007	Gryo gua sen ko pya . Hamo gyo God ya kya braema , da mate kronam gwin kesu braemki tyenkrai , ma kyo kesu taetaepmaka mate kyo dima proekeka haminkrai . Hamo kyo hoda gyo proekin tmoe hikesu pya taetaepminknaida .
47008008	Ma nokwa koma gyo dima a hre . Ma no wike gwin ko taetaepmin kronam naegima , gua proekin kronam braemkira .
47008009	Gyo braema hoa , Yesu ya proekin kronam ko . Gryo yane ko pya . Ma yo kyo taetaepmirakeka , ya kronam ko kumite . Ma yane ko kumaka guanesa hyenmite .
47008010	Hamo aekwa no hin ko hiwa . Gyo tmoe sem ambum wakan komdwa homiti hoko homa wirinmnaida . Ma gyo guatumki komdwa homiti . Ma gwin ko a diti .
47008011	Hamo tmoe hoko homa wirinma naedinina . Ma sem uminki gyo tmoe hiko aiki homwera diti . Hamo aekwa aikeka homa wirinmnai . Ma aekwa guane aeroko home hominina .
47008012	Ma kudi kru trua daera kroko hamroko , God ya gwa daen ko se . Ma gwa daenkra ko yo braema . Yo braema mgakwen gu dima aenaemkrai ko gu daen braema wirin .
47008013	No harike tmyaepu no tmoe hyena gyo dima dae ma wike gwin ko tmoe kuma dae harmaepu . Ma aekwa gryo guane ko pya aera hamo gyo wike gryo dumku ko taetaepminina . Hamo gua hodrai din ko pya aenaemkroko ka gyo taetaepmreiki .
47008014	
47008015	Ma Kwonam kimin tyen ko harina , kru ara dika ko pya gaemiti ko pya aen braema wirin . Ma kru ara dika kukumasa gaemiti , ko ko kuma aen braema wirin .
47008016	No God ko duwa dra . Tenam yo Taites dima tyo , hamo kyo gyo taetaepmo ya kesu gyo taetaepmira .
47008017	Ma yo kua tyaewi hosa daera heno dmaepu , yo yae kesu gyo taetaepmira de . Ma ya hine ko yo gyo dima tira de .
47008018	Ma kyo kua kire tru pru yominki hamo traha . Ma yoko God ya tmoe homin kru waenukina .
47008019	Ma wike sos yomkra ka gaema swa tyaewi hoke yo so hraewi . Tenam yo kyominki proekin tmoe ho taetaepma hominkrai . Tmoe hi ko kyo Yomkra ya hi hyenmwera . Hamo kyo wike gwin naegimo braemknaida hamo ka hina kyo tmoe hoko drinu ko taetaepma hominkraiha dnaida .
47008020	Ma proekin hyenu daenin hiko kyo pitmasa tikminkrai . Wike gwin ka swa tmyeda .
47008021	Ma kua hodrai ko kronam waenukinsa homwera dinkrai . Yomkra ya dyenkra ho homwera dinkrai hosa wirin , ma wike ka dyenkrai ho kesu .
47008022	Haminku kyo kua kire pru kominki tikraha . Kyo aku pya yo bryoko dyenkraiko , yo dumasa kyo taetaepmira dinkra . Ma yo gua swa waenukin daera ya hina drinu hoda gyo taetaepmira de .
47008023	Ma Taites yo ko no kirenu . Hamo yo tmoe hi nominki hominkra , gyo taetaepinaete . Hamo Krwistin wike gwin kominki treiki . Tenam Keriso drai wike ka ko pru , ka tmoe hominkrai .
47008024	Hamo gua ko waenuma taetaepmroko Keriso drai wike gwin ko daera , braemke ko swa kua tryai ko drinu tryaiha dreiki .
47009001	Ma gyo braemkewi God ya wike to Judia hokan penkrai ko taetaepminin da proekin ko dima hre tenkrai swa gyo dima kwo kimra ko tmoe hyena wirin .
47009002	Ma no braema gyo hoda ko taetaepmwera drai . Ma gua swa ko nokwa to Masadonia wike ko dima irinme tya . Nokwa tya Keriso ya wike to Akaia hokan penkrai ko sen ambum wakan ko , ko taetaepmwerada komdwaewi de . Ma gua ko dumasa taetaepmwera du daereiwi ko wike pya koke homwera dewi .
47009003	Ma aekwa no kire Krwistin kru hiko gyo dima pru twerakraiko nokwa gua swa tya ko drike dumkra dmeda . Ma nokwa tya ko gyo sem gaemin aera hoko ko taetaepminina .
47009004	Ma kudi Masadonia wike ko nominki taka gua haryoko kyo mgakwen gaemaepu droko hukwaekreiki . Ma gua hukwaekrai ko no swa a tye . Kyo hukwaekreiki tenam kua hin ko gyo sem gaemaewi .
47009005	Hakina kren , no hina Krwistin kru hiko pru andu kuta mgakwen gua daewera dewi ko sem daena aeroko taerinina . Hamo kutadi ko sem taerina kroko no kumta hoko dyen braema . Hamo hoko kyo dima naegimreiki gua daenkrai ko tenam gua hoda dinku . Ma kua gyo dima tyaewi ho wirin .
47009006	Ma gyo nononkromoe , kru diya kudin ke ko kukumasa gwyoryoko , drike pya sen braema wirin . Ma diya kudin ke pya gwyoryoko yo drike pya sen braema .
47009007	Hamo gyo butmin , trusa trusama hine yoma bra guae guane naemo hriwera drai hamo hrenina . Hina totokasu hrenina wirin . Ma haryome hiko no tmoe , tenam no wai mga hamtena kren harike hine bra daenina wirin . Ma kru ara dika yoyomki me daenkrai ko God yo ko dima hine pya brenkra .
47009008	Ma God yo gua bute ya hoda yo hote hata daen braema . Hamo aku butmin gua bute ya hodra ko bryoko sen braema , me wike gwin ka buten bryoko aenaemkroko ko dima daen braema .
47009009	Ma Kwonam kima tyen ko harina , wike dika ko buten bryoko aenaemkroko , ya proekin daen ko hoe yen braema wirin .
47009010	Ma God ya kudin ke hrete kyo gworinkrai da , mate da kua dinkrai hakin ho daeminkra yo kudin ke pya pru pko gua hodrai ho ko bryoko daenkra . Hamo ke hoko ya homo deri mta drike hyena yo , gaemin braema . Tenam gua hyenma hrenku .
47009011	Ma yo gyo dima aku butmin pya daemo , gyo bryoko pen braema , hamo gyo wike gwin ko dima pya daen braema . Hamo kua ko dima dae ko saka ko God dima haryeiki gu ko duwa dreiki .
47009012	Tenam gua ho daenkrai ko , God ya wike ka bute ka hodrai taetaepminaete daenkrai . Hamake wike ka hodrai taereka God dima gu ko duwa din braema .
47009013	Hamo gua daenkrai hoa wike gua taetaepmrai ho ka God dima gu ko duwa dreiki , tenam ka dyenkrai ko gyo ko Keriso ya wikesa diskinkmaepu , gyo ko dima daeka ma wike gwin ko dima kesu daeka hamin krai .
47009014	Hakina krenku , ka gua hi God dima tryeki , tenam God ya proekin hyena gyo dima aenku .
47009015	Hamo kyo God dima duwa dwe , ya proekin hyenu kyo dima daete kren .
47010001	No ko Por , hamo no gyo dima swa tyera . Wike ka harike tyenkrai no kominki henkrako , kate druki henkra dinkrai . Ma no to tru hroko kyomkinkra dinkrai .
47010002	Nokwa gyo dima pko diroko nokwa kyom knada swa tgryome . Ma wike dika haryoko , kyo to hyenu gryo hoda drai , drinu no wike hakin ko dima kyomkin braema .
47010003	Drinu kyo to hyenu hikan penkrai . Ma kua totetyenkrai ko to hyenu gryo siwera totetyenkmaen .
47010004	Ma kua totetyenkrai ko to hyenu wike ka totetyen gryo gryo hakina me wirin . Kyo God ya totetyen gryogryo aikin ho me , totetyaka swa kraekraema tyenkrai ka ai ho domsorinkrai .
47010005	Ma wike ko kae ireka God ya swa braemkin ko bryoko wirin haryoko kyo swa hoko domsorinkrai . Ma kua hine butmin ko gaema wogitma Keriso ya swa daera hominina dinkrai .
47010006	Ma kyo gyo tmaekrai , hamo gua hin butmin ko Keriso yo dimasa ae , hamo kudi wike dika ko a droko kua dore ko dima daenina .
47010007	Gyo wike ka tokramsa dyenkrai . Ma kru trua yae hine hrodi yo ko Keriso ya wikene . Yo hine harike bruroko , hamroko , yo hote rwyo yae yo hine brenina . Tenam kyo kesu Keriso ya wike .
47010008	Ma Yomkra ya kyo pru ya hinam naegiminkraida ko nokwa irin swama trya ko no hukwaekmaepu . Tenam kyo ya hinam gyo taetaepmin kren kyo gua hi a domsoryeiki .
47010009	Ma kwo nokwa kimra ko gyo hyaeka tempunaida wirin .
47010010	Kru trua harmaudi , Por ya reta kiminkra ko tuka , aia . Ma yo kyominki hroko , yo ko wikesa , ma yo aia wirin , ma ya swa ko drike wirin , dmaudi .
47010011	Ma kru hikin ko yo braemknada , hamo kyo gyominki hwyenaemka kwo kiminkrai ma gyominki huroko , kronam trusa hamike homreiki . Kronam ate wirin .
47010012	Ma kyo kua rwyo kua braemkin diwa , mate wike dika kyo ko braemnainu dinkrai , ka braemkin diwa ko ko bryokosa a haryeiki . Tenam ko ko nononkinsa . Ka braemkin ko , kaesa diwa begema ko ko bryokosa dinkrai .
47010013	Ma kuae kyo irinkrai aripe ko aera . Ma aripe ho ko , God ya daena . Ma tmoe kesu kyo dima daena . Ma tmoe hiko gyo dima naegiminkrai dware irinkrai .
47010014	Ma tenam kua tmoe ko Keriso ya hupe waenukin gyo dima naegiminku , kyo aripe hoko dmyaen braema wirin .
47010015	Hamo tmoe naekin wike gwin ka homiti ko ma tmoe hoko God ya kyo dima daemaepu , hamo kyo ho dima irmaepu . Ma kyo hoda gyo Keriso ya swa braemkin ho hyenknada , hamo gyo tmoe hyena gyominki homin braema . Ma tmoe hoko aripe God ya hren ko a dmyae .
47010016	Ma tmoe hoko homa naede , hupe waenukin hiko sakuta to ate wike gwin ko kesu naegimreiki . Hamake kyo wike gwin ka tmoe to ate hominkrai ko kesu naegimreiki . Hamake kyo wike gwin ka tmoe to ate hominkrai ko a irieiki .
47010017	Ma Kwonam kima tyen ko harina , kru diya irira kroko , Yomkra ya homite dima irinkna dina .
47010018	Tenam Yomkra ya hina kru hoko duwa droko , drinu kru hoko duwa . Ma kru hoa yae ya hina no ko duwa dra hoko wirin .
47011001	Aenuwe no ko hmen yen krusa . Hamo hmen yen kru ya swa gwin tyera .
47011002	No gwoegwoeka gyo dima , pako wike gwin ka gyo domsormeda . God ya hin kesu harinkra . Gyo ko paku sripen ka penkrai hakina . God ya hin kesu harinkra . Gyo ko paku sripen ka penkrai hakina . Hamo no gyo kru tru dima semira . Ma kru hoko Keriso .
47011003	No tempwenkra pako gyo kru ate dima hine brumeda . Sina , ara Ib dima kraekraema tyete hameda .
47011004	Ma kru trua kumta Yesu kua naegiminaemkin , Yesu ate ya swa , gyo drinu dinkrai . Ma dure tru gua saewi ko , mate hupe tru kua naeginaemkin ko , gyo drinu dinkrai . Uminki kua naegimite hakina wirin .
47011005	Ma gyo harike tyenkrai kru gwin ko ko tmoe homraida pru ten wike yaeyosa hakemina dinkrai . Ma no hin ko ko hato ma no ko hamsya ka tukram hakina wirin .
47011006	Ma dikani , no asi swa tyera hamroko wike kronam kwatensa braemkrai ka tyenkrai hamike tyenkrakedi . Ma no braemkin ko hakina wirin . Kyo sem kua braemkin ko gyo dima naegimite .
47011007	Ma no God ya hupe waenukin gyo dima naegimiteko , ya hoe gyo no dima daenai dmaepu . Ma no nae no kumakano gyosa hyenmite . Ma hoko no hwekene .
47011008	No tmoe gyo dima homiteko , Keriso ya wike gwin ka hoe ko no dima daeti . No ka sere uma taerina dinaekite , ma hoko no gyo taetaepmira .
47011009	Ma no sem gyominki hete hoke kudin dumku gyo dima sere kentmaepu . Ma no goe no gmore Masadonia wike , ka kumta no buta ya hodra butmin ka no dima bryoko sapkiti .
47011010	Ma Keriso ya swa drinu tyenkra ko no dima aera . Hamo no swa hoanam tyerakra , to Akaia hokan sahaka no hosa homihi .
47011011	No naemo diwa hirike tryake tenam no gyo dima proekmaepune . Wirin . God yo braema . No gyo dima hine pya brenkra .
47011012	No tmoe nae hominkra ko hamosa homi , tenam tmoe homnaida pru ten wike gwin ka iri tyaka harmeda kyosu bryokosa hominkrai dmeda .
47011013	Ma kru hoko ko ko tmoe nu homnaida pru ten wike wirin . Tmoe ka hominkrai ko kraekraema hominkrai . Ma ko Keriso ya tmoenu homnaida pru ten wike ko dinaeka kraekraema hominkrai .
47011014	Ma gyo hi diwa gimromoe . Ma Seiten yae yo rwyo kine atma nsa God ya po penkrai kru tru ya kronam dinaekin braema .
47011015	Hakina kren , ya tmoe homin wike ko ko kesu kraekraema tmoe duma homina dinaekinkrai . Ma tmoe ka hamike kraekraema hominkrai ko tuwa wirin . Hamosu tmoe ka hamike hominkrai hoe ko direiki .
47011016	No hote tyera . Ma kru trua ya hin no ko nononkin kru droko hoko bryoko wirin . Ma kudi , gua hin ko atkina kroko , hamaha , hamo no swa irinme tyen braema .
47011017	Ma nokwa hi trya ko Yomkra ya trnya du tmyaepu . Ma kronam himike irin ko nokwasa . Drinu no nononkin wike ko dinaeka trya .
47011018	Ma tenam wike pya ka to hyenu kronam homaka irinkrai kren , no kesu hamira .
47011019	Ma gyo ko braemnai wikesa , hamo gyo nononkin wike ka swa ko yoyomkin me daerinkrai .
47011020	Gua hin ko wike dika gyo dima ikarema tyaka gua nononkin ho diwa gyo tmoe hi homa ho homa du homaka hi ko bryoko dinkrai . Hamake ka gyo dima kraekraema gyo gyori dainam tenkrai . Ka gyo dima gyo kyo dinaekinane hareka gua tokram pkari yenkrai .
47011021	Hamo no hukwaeme tyera , kua kronam hamin ko tempwenkrai .
47011022	Ko ko Hibru krune . No kesu ko Hibru kru . Ma ko ko Isrwaeo wikene . No kesu Isrwaeo wike . Ma ko ko Abraham ya kyankyane . No kesu hiwa .
47011023	Ko ko Keriso ya tmoe homin wike dinkraike . Ma no ko hmeneyen kru dinaekina , ma tmoe ka hominkraiko , nokwa dmyaena . Tmoe nokwa hominkra ko hyena . Ma ko wogitmamitike . Ko no tike me idima yamamiti . Ma ko pumaekemitike . Ma no aku pya pumae ten dyenkra .
47011024	Ma aku yaemsin hamo Ju wike ka no kupyen me yete ko 39 hamo .
47011025	Ma aku haepki trumo hamo Rom wike ka no tike me yeti . Ma aku tru ko ike me no dima dimaka no pwen wyeramiti . Hamake aku haepki trumo no mosornam to , mosoreko waia dua syete . Ma aku trusa , hune me aku me wai surite .
47011026	Ma no to ate ate tenkrako , wai bra aene wya no myaekemite . Mate udin wike da mate Ju wike da mate swa ate wike ka no wyerakemiti . Hamo no to hyenu hokan da mate dei dure hokanko , no tempwen hyena dyamite . Ma wai dawara takurina no tu hmomaeka mate kraekraemin wike no dima kire deka no pwene yera miti .
47011027	Hamo no tmoe ate ate pya hominkra . Ma hune gwin ko no krogoe aen dumkina . Ma aku gwin ko no gehmenka wai garinka haminkra . Ma aku gwin kudin handuma dinaemka , aen ri dyenaemka , bai bryoko brenaemka haminkra .
47011028	Ma kronam gwin pya aera hoko swa a tye . Hamake no Keriso ya wike ko bryoko praike , ma pyen hyena diraikeda , hine pya brenkra .
47011029	Ma kru tru ko ai dumkroko , no kesu ai dumkinkra . Ma tru ko hweke hro totroko , no pyen hyena dyenkra .
47011030	Ma ka no irinknada droko , hamroko no ai dumkin ho dima iri .
47011031	Ma kua Yomkra Yesu yai God ya hisa hiwe , yo braema no kraemaepu .
47011032	Ma no to Damaskis hokan hete hoke , King Aretes ya Gaman kru trua ya ami pru ko to hyenu hoa ya grare inam dwen hokan huma hwyaka , no diwa siweramiti .
47011033	Ma ko no basketnam hre po grare inam gite sya krya tete .
47012001	Nokwa irinme tyera . Ma no braema hi ko kyo taetaepmin braema wirin . Ma no ripe krogoeku Yomkra ya naegite ho tyera .
47012002	Sem , ambum 14 hamo kru tru Keriso ya wike tru , no braema , yo ko , hamo yo Hewen hata hokan dimasa tete . ( No braemkmaepu , yo drinu tetekedi , ma andyoninki dyetekedi , God yasa braema . )
47012003	Ma no hote tyera , kru hiko , ka yo sa Paradaise dima hateti . ( Hiko drinu homitikedi , ma ripe krogoekeka dyetekedi , no braema wirin , God yasa braema . ) Ma hokanko , kronam yaeyosa hakina dyete . Ma wike ka swama tyen braema wirin .
47012004	
47012005	Hamo no kru ho dima iri . Ma no naesa no a irinki . Nae no aikinaemkin kronam hosa tye .
47012006	Ma kudi nae no irioko no nononkmaekina wirin , tenam no drinu swasa tyera . Ma nae no a iri tye , tenam wike ko no dima hine hyenma hamasa brumeda . Ko nokwa homaka tyenkra hosa diwa begmnaida .
47012007	Ma tenam nae no irmeda , kronam ate ate pya yaeyosa hakina dyete hamo , no tren tru dyete . Tren hiko Seiten ya tmoe hominkra . Hamo hoko no yenkra pako nae no irmeda .
47012008	Ma no aku haepki trumo Yomkra dima tyete , tren hiko wirinmna dite .
47012009	Ma ya no dima rwyo tyete , no proeka hamaha din kronam gu dima aen hosa ko bryoko no dite . Tenam gu aikinaemkroko , no ai gu dima aen ko bryokono dite . Ya haru diku no yoyomkra . Hamo no aikinaemkin hi dima irinkra , tenam Keriso ya no tikmikra ai ko no braemkra .
47012010	Hakina kren , no hamaha dinkra . Ma no aikinaemkin diwa mate wike ka no ikarema tyo daera , pyenkin diwa hamikra to tenam Keriso ya tmoe hominku . Hamo no kronam hi dyenkra ko bryoko dinkra . Tenam no aikinaemkroko , no ko aiya .
47012011	No ko nononkin kru ya tyenkra hamra . Hi ko gyo me kren trya . Gyo harinkmaepu , tmoe gwa hominkra ko bryoko dinkmaepu . Ma gyo harike tyen ko bryoko . Ma dikani tmoe nokwa hominkra ko drike wirin di . Hamo gyo wike gwin ko dima ko ko kua wike tmoe homin pru ten wike yaeyosa dinkrai . Ma no ko hamsya ka tukram henkmaepu .
47012012	Ma aku pya no kronam tei atma gyominki haka homite ko braemknaida , God ya no pru ya tmoe hominkra .
47012013	Ma no Keriso ya wike gwin kominki haka tmoe waenuma homiteke , ma gyominki haka tmoe swoma homiteke . Hene . Ma nokwa gyo dima naemike swoma homiteke . Ma nokwa gyo dima sere kentinaemkin dware hoane . Aenuwe , no Keriso ya wike gwin ko dima da mate gyo dima ko bryoko homaepu .
47012014	Ma no gyo dima hi terakra ko 3ha . Ma no gyo dima gryo tru a kenti . No hoda gyo . Ma gua sere ko no a . Tenam kya kuku ko kai kaem dima sere daenkmaen . Kai kaem kasa kya kuku ka buta hodrai hosa ko dima daemin ko bryoko .
47012015	No hine bra no me no sere butmin gyo dima yoyomkin dae , gyo taetaepmira . Tenam no gyo dima hine pya brenkra kren , ma gyo no dima hine kukumasa hine brenkmawe .
47012016	Ma gyo butmin no swa twya haryeiki , hene , yo kyominki henkrako , kyo yo dima tmoe hyena homaepu dreiki . Ma kru trua harmaudi yo kyo dima kraekraema tyete dmaudi .
47012017	Ma naerikene . Kru nokwa pru teti , ka gyo dima kraekraemitike .
47012018	No Taites yo pru to , mate Keriso ya wike gwin ka yominki teti . Hamo gua hin ko Taites ya gyo dima kraeteke . Yo me no me ki kronam trusa homaepune .
47012019	Ma dikani gua hina kyo gyo dima harinkrai , tenam kyo hoda gua kyo dima hine waenuma brunaida . Wirin . Ma kua tyenkrai ko , kyo God ya kinaegite hwyaka , Keriso ya hodra kyo naerike tnyai dra hosa tyenkrai . Kire , kya huminkrai butmin ko gyo taetaepmwera dinkrai .
47012020	Aenuwe , no hin ko , no gua to hokan taenkidi , gyo atkina dye , nokwa dyera din hakin a dye . Ma no kesu . Gyo hoda no naemike homo diwera drai , hakina a direiki . No taenkidi no hin ko kronam grwine bren me gwogwoekin kronam me kepronam grongronkin da mate grimekin da ikarema tyen da mate swa hamasa pipitma tyaka irin me tyaka handuma hominaemkeka hakina dye .
47012021	Ma no tempura no hote kumtadi , wike pya ko kore aeng tyaka mate ka hominkrai hukwaekinaemka po diwa , no God ya hukwae no dima dae no bye .
47013001	Nokwa gyo dyera pkikra ko haepki trumo hamo . Kwonam kima tyen ko harina , kru trua hweke hrena droko , hamo wike haepki o ma haepki trumo ka hweke ho diwa , ka tyenina dina .
47013002	Ma no kru ara digua hweke sem twen gyo dima tyera . Mate wike gwin butmin gyo dima kesu . Ma no msya sem hote gyo dima tete hoke tyeteko mate no aekwa gyominki henaemkinku hote tyera , ma nokwa hote pkikrako gyo butmin dore direiki .
47013003	Ma gua diwekraiko , Keriso ya ai no titwomnam tyo direiki . Ya gyo begemikrako yo a kudropki . Ya ai ko gyo dima naegimin braema .
47013004	Ma yo dei ti hro yetiko , yo aikmaepu . Ma God ya ai hoa yo henkra . Hamo yominki hwyenkraiko , kyo ko aia wirin . Ma kyo gyominki swa tryaiko , God ya ai kua sen ko gyo dima daemwekraiha .
47013005	Ma gyo guaesa begema bryoko dinai . Gyo God ya swa daera drinu da , dumasa homi tenkraike . Ma gyo drinu braemkraike , Yesu Keriso yo gyominki henkrako . Ma kudi , gyo hiko handuma braemkinaemkroko , gyo braemkmaepu howa .
47013006	No hoda gyo braemkraida tmoe kua hominkra ko hoe dumkmaekina wirin .
47013007	Kyo God dima tyenkrai gyo hweke hrimeda . Tenam kyo hoda kyo ko waenuma naegimin wike dwerane . Hoa wirin . Kyo hoda gyo kronam dukinsa hominknaida , hosa . Ma kyo tmoe homa hoe dyenaemkroko , hamaha .
47013008	Kyo drinu swa dima a grwine brureiki .
47013009	Ma kudi kyo ko aikinaemku gua aikroko kyo yoyomkrai . Ma kyo God dima tyenkrai hamo gyo God ya kronam waenukiskin gyoke haknaida .
47013010	Hakina kren , no gyominki henaemkra hike kwo gyo dima hi kimraha . Tenam no gyo dima pkroko , no God ya hinam gyo dima kyomkmeda . God ya ai me gyo aiknaida , gyo hukwaeknaida wirin .
47013011	No kire gyoke , no kwo kimin hiko naedirakra . Gyo kronam waenukiskin hoda dinknai . Ma gyo no swa daerin knai . Gyo grwine brenaemka waenumasa penknai . Hamroko God , yo ko proekin me hine pya bren me waenuma pen yanai yo gyominki hen braema .
47013012	Gyo matum knaiyamo kraiyamo haminknai . God ya wike ka butmin tryaiko gyo waenuma pnaiko drai .
47013013	
47013014	Hamo kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya proekin kronam me God ya proeka hine pya brenkra da mate Dure Waenukin ya kire din kronam gyo dima aepesu aenada .
48001001	No ko Por , hamo kwo hiko nokwa kimra . Hamo wike ka o kru trua ya no tmoe homnada pru tmaepu . Wirin . Kuai God ya Yesu Keriso yo pwo warmo durkyo asiten kru , ta pru no kuta ta tmoe hominkra .
48001002	Ma no kire , Keriso ya tmoe hominkrai , ko nominki hikan prai . Hamo kyo kwo Keriso ya wike to Geresia hokan penkrai gyo dima gyo waenuma praike din swa kwonam kima hi hre traha .
48001003	Hamo Kuai God me kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ta proekin da mate ta kate druki waenuma pen kronam ho gyo dima pknada .
48001004	Keriso yo , kuai God ya hodra hosa homite . Ma hweke kua twenkrai hoe butmin ko ya hro sete . Hakina kren , kronam swoswokin hoka kyo wogitmitiko , Keriso ya kyo hro sa naedina kyo waenuma penkrai .
48001005	Ya himike homite kren , Kuai God ya hi hyenminkwe . Ma yo dima gu duwa dinkwe .
48001006	No proeko , gua hominkrai hupe ho daera girma . God ya gyo Yesu Keriso ya proekin hokan uru , aku pya wirin kinaemku diroko gyo yo kworewi . Hamo gyo swa ate kesu , God ya swa waenukina dinkrai ho daera drinu dinkraiha .
48001007	Ma ya swa waenuka atkin tru ko aemaepu . Ma nokwa harya , tenam ko hiwa , wike gwin ko Keriso ya homite ya drikeko , ko atma tyenkrai . Hakina kren gyo bubutkinkrai .
48001008	Ma kudi kua a ma , God ya po penkrai kru trua ya , kuae kua uminki gyo dima naegimite hakin ho naegiminaemkroko , God ya yo begema pru Hero dima syenina .
48001009	No swa hiko sem uminki gyo dima tyete , hosa no hote tyerakra . Ma kru dia swa naegimo , gua daera seti hakin ho naegiminaemkroko , kru hoko pru Hero dima syenina .
48001010	Nokwa sa hirike tryako , gua hin no wike gwin ka no ko duwa drnaidane . Wirin . No hoda God ya hina no ko kru waenukina hanyada . Ma wike no dima hoda drnai dane . Ma kudi no haryoko no Keriso ya tmoe homin kru hen braema wirin .
48001011	Kire gyoke , nokwa hupe waenukin naegiminkra , wike gwin ka no dima tyena tyenkmaepu .
48001012	Ma kru trua no dima tyo braemkmaepu . Ma kru gwin ka no dima naegi maepu . Wirinsa . Yesu Keriso yasa no naegimite .
48001013	Gyo braema , uminki nokwa Ju wike kua kronam homamiteko . Hamo no God ya wike kuyen kru ko nokwa . Ma no ko domsoriskira demite .
48001014	Ma Ju wike kru gwin , ambum trusa kua kronam homamitiko , nokwa ko dmyaete . Ma kyo kua kigwam kua hwoe ka swa daeritiko , nokwa ko dima hine pya bramite .
48001015	Ma naeme no hamtenaemkin hoke , God ya no proeki hamaha dinku , no ya tmoe hamnada sa hrena .
48001016	Hamo ya kya no dima naegimite , tenam no ya swako , swa ate wike ko dima naegimnada . ? ? ? Yo hoko no dima naegimite kren , no kru tru ya hin bren ho braemkira yo dima tondaermaepu .
48001017	Ma no Jerusraem dima ko no tmaepu , Yesu ya tmoe homnaida yatumki pru tamitiko , ma no ko kagmore pkina , hamo no wike hoko dima swa tmyaepu . No to Arabia dima dumasa tete . Ma no hote krwyo Damaskis dima tete .
48001018	Ma ambum haepki trumo hamo wirinku diroko , no Jerusraem dima kuta Pita minki swa gwin tondaerira tete . Hamo pura haepki hamo ko no yominki hete .
48001019	Ma tmoe homin pru ten kru trua hokan ho no dimaepu . Ma kua Yomkra yagmore Jeimssa dyete .
48001020	Swa nokwa gyo dima hi kimra ko , God yo braema nokwa gyo dima kraemaepu .
48001021	Maren no hokan hwya to Siria da mate to Sirisia dima tete .
48001022	Ma Keriso ya wike to Judia hokan penkrai ko no tokram dyenkmaepu .
48001023	Ma ko no swa sem tyen hosa daera braemkiti . Ma ka tyeti kru hiko sem uminki kyo kuyamite . Ma aekwa yo harya sem uminki ya domsoriramamite hoko kwasu ya trya ko hoko drinu dinkra .
48001024	Hamo ko hoko daera priti , God gu ko hyena duwa diti , tenam God ya hominku diti .
48002001	Ma ambum 14 hamo wirinku diroko , nokwa Banabas hamo ki hote rwyo Jerusraem dima teti . Ma ki Taites twya , yo me teti .
48002002	Nokwa tete ko no ripe krogoeku God ya no dima naegu diku tete . Ma hokanko , no Keriso ya wike ka yomkra ko dima hupe waenukin , nokwa swa ate wike ko dima naegiminkra ho ko dima naegimite . Nokwa sem naegite ho mate aekwa naegiminkra hoko , ko domsora drike yenaemkmeda .
48002003	Ma Taites yo nominki tete , ma yo ko Grik kru hamo ka yo ko kate tiginina dmaepu .
48002004	Ma kru gwin ka tyetiko , yo hamike hominina diti . Ma kru hiko Krwistin wike da kraekraemiti . Ma wike hoko aewswamin ptena dinaekiti . Hamo kyo aewe tru gaemo koke kumta kyominki paka , koma ya kyo yomkrakinaemku , ma tenam kyo Yesu Keriso yominki penkrai kren ko ya drike braemkwera . Ko hoda kyo koma ya tyen hosa homin krai da .
48002005	Ma kyo ka swa daermaepu . Kyo hoda Yesu Keriso ya hupe waenukin ya duma tyen hoko a atma tryeiki . Gyo dima dumasa aepesu aenina .
48002006	Ma kru gwin hoko , ma kru gwin ka ko ko yomkra diti , ma ko ko yomkra di , ma wirin di , no dima ko drike wirin . God yo wike ka pen kronam diwa begeminkmaepu . Ka yomkra hoa kronam tru no dima tmyaepu .
48002007	Ma ko braemkiti , God ya pru no swa ate wike ko dima naegimna da . God yo Pita pru Ju wike ko dima ya swa naegimna hakina .
48002008	Ma drinu God pru no ya ai me swa ate wike ko dima naegimnada . Ma Pita ya Ju wike ko dima naegimna ho bryoko .
48002009	Hamo no dyeteko , Jeims , me Pita me Jon , ko ko yomkra , me ka dyetiko , God ya tmoe atkin hiko no dima dae dyeti . Hamo ko Banabes kia krite gyoriti . Ma kyo tmoe trusa hominkrai kren , kire diti . Ma kyo hine trusa bra priti , Banabes ki tmoe ko swa ate wike kominki homreiki diti . Ma ko ko Ju wike kominki homreikiko diti .
48002010	Ma ko swa kutyaka priti , gi wike mgyore kyominki penkrai ko nononkromoe , ma no kronam hoko hine pya bra tmoe hoko aiki homira dinkra .
48002011	Ma Pita ya Antiok dima pkiteko , tenam ya homra ko swoku no taen twya garite .
48002012	Ma Pita yo , wike gwin Jeims ya pru pkiti ko taenkinaemku diku , swa ate Krwistin wike kominki kudemamite . Ma wike hoko taenku diroko , Pita yo swa ate tyen wike kominki ku dinkra ko yo tempwa naedite . Tenam swa ate wike ka kate tigwera diti ko dima tempwete .
48002013	Hamo Ju wike gwin ko Pita ya homra diwa , ko kesu tempwen wike dinaekiti . Hamako Banabes yo kesu tempwa ka homrai yoke homite .
48002014	Ma nokwa dirako , ko Keriso ya naegimite hoko bryoko homaepu . Hamo no Pita ya homra ho ko butmin ka kinaegite tyete , gu ko Ju kru , ma gu wike swa ate ka kronam ho bryoko hominkra . Ma gu naemo diwa swa ate wike ko dima tyo ko Ju ka penkrai ho bryoko penknaidane .
48002015	Drinu kuai kuaem ko Ju , hamo kyo ko Ju ka dwe drimina . Ma kyo ko swa ate ko ko hwek min wike dinkrai ma kyo ko hakemina wirin .
48002016	Ma kyo braema kru ara dika Yesu Keriso ya swa daera drinuhaki draiko , God yo ko dima dumraiha din braema . Ko Koma daera homroko hoa dumin braema wirin . Kyo kesu Yesu Keriso ya swa ko drinuhaki dinku , God ya kyo dima dumraiha dnada . Koma ya trya homo dumraha din braema wirin . Ma kru trua koma ya tryasa homroko God ya kru ho dima dumraha din braema wirin .
48002017	Ma kudi kyo Keriso yominki hwyo ma God ya kyo dima dumnai du ma wike gwin ka kyo dima haryoko gyo ko hweke min wike , swa ate ko bryoko droko , ma ya drike ko Keriso ko hweke ya tmoe hominkrune . Wirin .
48002018	Ma kudi koma nokwa sem grurite hoko hote twya hriroko , wike gwin ka hin no ko koma kyen kru dreiki .
48002019	Ma no ko koma dima pwen kru dinaekina . Ma koma no yo , pwena . Hamo no God ya tryasa daerinkra . No ko Keriso yome pkori dei buti hro yeti ho bryoko .
48002020	Hakina kren , aekwa ko , nae no ware me henkmaepu . Keriso ya ware no tyonam henkra . Hamo nokwa to hyenu hikan henkrako , God ya kya dima drinu dinku no henkra . Ya no dima proe hyenka ya ware no dima daete .
48002021	Hamo no God ya proeki hamaha din kronamko , no a din braema wirin . Ma kudi kru trua yo komasa homo , God ya yo dima dumraha droko , hamroko , Keriso yo drike dumkina hamasa pweteha .
48003001	Geresia wike gyo ko hmene yen dinaeka nononke mina . Ma ko pitmasa Yesu Keriso dei buti hro yo , pwete ho gyo dima naegimitiko , gua knon me dyena dinaekiti .
48003002	Ma no kronam trusa gyo dima tondaerirakra . Ma gyo God ya Dure ko naemike setike . Ma Koma ya tyo homin krake o ma God ya hupe waenukin ho daera drinu ditike .
48003003	Ma gyo naemo diwa hamike nononma hominkraike . Ma gyo uminki God ya dure ya aime tmoe komdwa homiti , ma aekwa ko guae gua ai me homa wirinmwerane .
48003004	Ma braemkin sem gua saewi ko drike wirinne . Ma braemkin hoko drike kukina saewike .
48003005	Ma God ya dure gyo dima dae gyominki kronam tei atma hominkrako , naemo diwane . Ma gyo koma ya swa ho daera hominkraike , ma gyo Keriso ya swa ho daera drinu dinkraike .
48003006	Ma Abraham yo dima homite ho hine bruwe . Ma Kwo nam kima tyen ko harina , yo God ya swa ko drinu dumaha dinku , God ya yo ko kru duwa dite .
48003007	Hakina kren , gyo braemknai , kru ara dika God ya swa daera drinu dinkrai ko ko Abraham ya kyankya nu ko howa .
48003008	Ma sem uminki Kwonam kimin ko harina , hamosu swa ate wike ko God ya swa ko daera drinu du ya ko dima dumraiha di , dina . Ma swa tru ko Abraham yo dima tyena aerako , gu me kren God ya wike butmin diaesu , waenuma preiki .
48003009	Abraham yo God ya swa daera drinu dite kren , God ya Abraham diaete kren yo waema pete . Hakina kren , wike di ka ko God ya swa daera drinu droko , ko ko Abraham bryoko , God ya ko diae ko waenuma pen braema .
48003010	Hamo wike dika Koma swasa hine hya brenkraiko , ka braeme , ko God ya dore diwekraiha . Tenam Kwonam kimin ko harina , kru ara dika Koma swa Kwonam kimina aera ho butmin hominaemkroko God ya doreko ko dima daekraha .
48003011	Hamo kyo dyen braeme , wike ko Koma gitesa homo God yo ko dima dumraiha dinkmaepu . Ma Kwonam kima tyen ko harina , kru ara diko God ya swasa drinu dinkrai ko God ya ko dima dumraiha din braema . Hamo ko ware me huwekraiha .
48003012	Ma koma dima daerin ko tru , ma God ya swa daera drinu din ko tru . Kwonam kima tyen ko kru ara diya koma ya tyene ho butmin homroko yo ware hamo hikraha .
48003013	Keriso yo , God ya kyomka dore swokin kyo dima daemaeku diku ya sete . Hamo koma hominaemkin hoe ko kyo a direiki , tenam Keriso ya kyo hro sete kren . Kwonam kima tyen ko , kru dika yo dei kom hmigina kroko , God ya dore ko ya sena howa .
48003014	Keriso ya hi homite tenam God yo Abraham dima diaen hoko swa ate wike kesu , Yesu Keriso yo me kren , ko dima daen braema . Hamo kyo Yesu ya tyen ko drinuhaki droko , kyo kesu God ya uminki Dure kyo dima daera dite hoko siwekraiha .
48003015	Nogmore gyoke , to hyenu wike kua hominkrai kronam ho tyera . Kru haepki ta swa tru heno da kwonam kimroko , sem heno diri kren , kru truato grurin braema wirin .
48003016	Ma God ya Abraham me ya kyankya dima swagumite . Ma Kwonam tyen ko harina , ya kyankya ko butmin hamo tmyaepu . Drike hoko , yo wike butmin ko dima tmyaepu . Ya kyankya dra . Drike ko kru trusa . Yo ko Keriso .
48003017	Swa nokwa trya drike ko himike , God ya Abraham dima swagumite hoko yo dumasa homira . Ma ambum butmin 430 hamo wirinkusu koma ko sa braemkiti . Hamo koma hoa God ya swagumin ko ya kyen braema wirin .
48003018	Tenam kudi God ya proeki daenko , koma ma homa sen braema droko , hamroko ya swagumite hoko sen braema wirin . Ma God ya Abraham yo dima swagumite ko yo dima hingrua daeskite .
48003019	Hakina kren Koma ya drike ko naekinane . God ya hoda kyo braemknaida , kronam naekin ko swokinane , ma dukin ko naekinane da ho naegimira . Ma koma hiko , yae hamo ae , Abraham ya kyankya swaguma tyete ya pko wirinki . Ma Koma hiko God ya wike yominki penkrai kru trua daete . Ma kru tru yo God mo , wike mo , dure hokan henkra .
48003020	Ma tmoe ko kru truasa homo ma kru tru yo ko dure hokan hen ko bryoko wirin . Tenam God ko trusa .
48003021	Hakina kren , Koma ko God ya swagumite ho dima a da grwine brenkrake . Tenam ko kudi to hyenu wike ko koma trua kyo dima ware daemaekina droko wike butmin ko koma hoko daera homo God ya ko dima dumraiha din braema .
48003022	Ma Kwonam kima tyen ko harina , to hyenu wike butmin ko , hweka ko butmin , wogitmina penkrai . Hakina kren , wike dika Yesu Keriso ya swa ko daera drinuhaki droko , God ya proekin ko dima daera sem swagumite hoko , ko dima daen braema .
48003023	Ma drinu dinaenaemkin aku hokeko Koma ya kyo wogitmina peti . Hamo kyo wogitmin hokan posu , dumahaki din hoa pkekasu tyae , kae dyeti .
48003024	Hamo koma ko kunai dinaeka ya kyo tikmite . Ma Keriso ya pkekasu Koma ya tikminkra ko tigite . Tenam kyo Yesu dima ya swa ko dumahaki droko , God yo kyo dima gyo dumraiha din braema .
48003025	Ma dumahaki din ko kwasu hiwa . Ma Koma yo ko kuanainu wirin .
48003026	Tenam gyo Yesu Keriso ko dumahaki dinkrai me gyo hoasa yominki hwyenkrai kren , gyo ko God ya kya kuku ho bryoko .
48003027	Gyo ko wai bra hamtetiko , Keriso yo me pkworina . Ma aekwa gyo Keriso yo me pkwori baima bren kra hakina .
48003028	Hakina kren , Ju wike da mate swa ate wike kyo ko drike trusa . Ma wike twa taerin me wike twa taerinaemkin ko kesu bryokosa . Mate kru me ara ko drike trusa . Gyo butmin ko trusa , Yesu Keriso yominki pkworina gyo ko trusa .
48003029	Ma gyo ko Keriso yana kroko gyo kesu ko Abraham ya kyankyaha . Ma uminki God ya Abraham dima swagumite hoko gyo kesu sireiki .
48004001	Ma swa gwin nokwa tyerakra ko hiwa . Hi hamamoha . Kru kya minko hamosu kya hoa yai ya gryogryo butmin ko yaesa sen braema . Ma yo kya kuro , wike gwin ka yo tikminkrai . Ma kya hoko hro sen dinaekina . Ma kya hoko gryo me aewe , me sanam butmin hamo ko yanesa .
48004002	Ma yo ko kya kiskuro kru gwin ka yo me ya gryo me tikmaka mate sanam tmoe hamaka haminkrai . Ka hamike homi troko aku dikan yai ya tyen ho bryokaesu kwori naedin krai .
48004003	Ma kyo kesu kya dinaeka peti . Hamo dure , to hyenu hi tikminkrai , ka kyo wogitma po , ka swa daera homamiti . Hokeko kyo God ya swa handuma braema wirin .
48004004	Ma aku hoko bryokae diroko , God ya kyanu pru msyete . Hamo to hyenu ara tru ya , wike kua haratenkrai kronam ho bryoko , hamtete . Hamta naeduro yo Ju wike ka koma daera ho bryoko homamite .
48004005	Tenam yo wike koma swa daera hominkrai kyo ko , ya kyo hro sete . Hamo ya kyo hro so , God ya wiknaida .
48004006	Hamo God ya gyo naegimo gyo ya kya knaida hamo , ya kya ya Dure pru kumta kua tyonam haka harike tyenkrai , ai , droko ma nai droko harinkra .
48004007	Hakina krenku , gyo ko wike gwin ka tmoe homin wike wirin , gyo ko ya kyaha . Tenam gyo ko ya kya kren , God ya kya ko dima daemaekin ko gyo dima daemikraha .
48004008	Drinu sem uminki gyo God braemkinaemkin hokeko , gyo dure gwin , god nu wirin , ka tmoe homi kweti .
48004009	Ma aekwa kwasu God nu ko gyo ho braemkraiha . Hamo nokwa hi trya ko drinu kwasu God yo gyo braemkraha . Ma gyo naemo diwa hote krwyo to , tona aikinaemkin ka gyo tikmnaidane .
48004010	Ma gyo harike tyenkrai aku hiko hyena , ma dwarin hiko yae atkina , ambum hyaekin swi surin ko yae hakina da ho dima hine brenina dinkrai .
48004011	Hamo no gyo dima hine pya brenkra . Aemi , tmoe nokwa gyo dima hominkrako , maren drike yenaemkmeda hosa tempura .
48004012	Kire gyoke , nokwa gua dware byenkrako , no hoda gyo no dinaeknaida . Tenam no kesu gyo dinaekina . Ma gyo no dima kronam swokin tru homaepu .
48004013	Ma gyo braema howa , no sem uminki hupe waenukin hya gyo dima naegimite hokeko no trerite .
48004014	Ma no tren hoko pyen hyena gyo dima daete . Ma gyo no dima ikarma tmyaepu . Wirin . Ma no gua tonae hokan taenkiteko , gyo no dima naemira pkrake harmaepu . God ya po penkrai kru tru pko tikminkrai hamiti . Ma hoko Yesu Keriso ya pko homwekrai ho bryoko homiti .
48004015	Ma uminki gua hamike yoyomkin me peti ma aekwa yoyomkin hoko diwake . No hinasa harya , kudi gyo hamin braema kroko gua knon hmura no dima daemaekina kroko sem hamina .
48004016	Ma aekwa no drinu gyo dima hi trya , no ko gua wasine .
48004017	Wike gwin wa ko gyo dima hine pya brenkrai , ma ka homwerakrai ko duwa wirin . Hamo ka hodrai ko gyo no kwori , gyo ko dima hine brunaida .
48004018	Ma kutadi , hine pya bradi hoe ko dukmaekina kroko , wike gwin ko dima hine pya bren ko duwa . No gyominki henkra hokesa wirin .
48004019	No kya kuku gyoke , no hote tren tirako , ara ka kya hamtwerakeka gen timgu tren dyenkrai hakra , Keriso ya kronam hoa gua tyonam ho mta homroko naedusu bryokae .
48004020	Ma aenuwe no hoda aekwako , no gyominki hera . Ma no gyominki haka hine ate bren braema . Ma aekwa no gua dware hine ate ate pya brenkra .
48004021	Ma digyo hoda koma ya tyen ho homwera hamroko , nokwa gyo dima tondaerira , ma koma ya tyen hoko gyo daeryaike .
48004022	Kwonam tyen ko harina , Abraham ya kya ko kru haepki dina kya tru ko , tmoe homin ara ya hamtena . Ma tru ko ya runaennu ya hamtena .
48004023	Ma ara ya hrosen hoa kya hamtete ko yae to hyenu wike kua kya hamtenkrai ho bryoko hamtete . Ma ya runaen ya kya hamtete ko God ya sem swagumina kren hamtete .
48004024	Swa hiko kyo dima handruri tyena . Hamo ara haepki ho ti ko swagumin haepki ho bryoko . Ara Heiga ko yae ya hodrasa hominkmaepu . Ma aegu Sainiai hokan swagumin daete yo ko ho bryoko .
48004025	Ma Heiga , yo ko aegu Sainiai to Arabia hokan hra ho dinaekina . Ma yo ko to hyenu Jerusraem ya aekwa hra ho dinaekina . Ya wike butmin ko hoe dumkin tmoe hominkrai .
48004026	Ma to Jerusraem Kwoe Kom Hewen hokan henkra ko naekin hodra ko hominsa . Ma yo ko kuaemeha .
48004027	Kwonam kima tyen ko , Ara digua kotkaika kya dumkroko gyo yoyomkinknai . Ma ara digua kya hamtwera tren dyenaemkroko , yoyomkin me hunai . Ma ara diya ya kru ko yo hro tena ya kya ko pya bra i . Ma ara diya ya kru ko yo hro tmaepu , ma yo kya pya wirin .
48004028	Hakina kren , kire gyoke , tenam God ya swagumina kren , gyo ko God ya kya kuku . Ma gyo ko Aisaek dinaekina .
48004029	Ma aku hokeko , kya tru , wike ka hamtenkrai kronam ho bryoko hamteti . Ma kya tru , God ya Dureme hamtina . Hamo yo dima ikarma tyete . Ma kronam hakin ko aekwa kesu aera .
48004030	Ma Kwonam kima tyen ko naerike tyenane . Ya tyen ko ara hro sen ya kya me ti pru wamo tnai dina , tenam ara hro sen ya kya me ara hro senaemkin ya kya ti tai ya gryo tikmo sen braema wirin .
48004031	Hakina kren kire gyoke , kyo ko ara tmoe hominda hro sen , ya kya wirin . Kyo ko ara hro senaemkin ya kya .
48005001	Aekwa kuae kua hodraisa kwehwyenkrai . Ma Keriso ya kyo hma hrena kren kyo kwensa . Hakina kren kyo wogitminaemkin wike ko dinaeka kwehwyenknai . Wike gwin ka gyo hote ka tmoe homnai du daeryomoe .
48005002	Gyo no swa daenyai . No ko Por . Nokwa gyo dima tyera . Kudi gyo heno du ka kumta gua kate tigroko , hamroko ya drike ko Keriso ko gyo dima drike wirin .
48005003	Nokwa yoma tyera , kru diya heno du ka ya kate tigroko yo koma trya butmin daera hominina .
48005004	Ma digua gyo koma tyen homo God ya gyo dima dumraiha dnada , hamroko gyo Keriso yominki henko kwori guaesa traiha . Ma God ya proeki gyo taetaepma hamaha din braema wirin .
48005005	Ma kyo hoda God ya kyo dima dumraiha dnada . Hamo kyo ho huma penkrai . God ya Dure ya homin braema . Tenam kyo God ya swa ko drinu dinkrai kren .
48005006	Tenam kyo Yesu Keriso yominki pkorina , kua kate tigine ma tiginaem kroko drike trusa . Drike hyena ko , kyo God ya swa ko drinu deka wike gwin ko dima proeki hine pya brenin hosa .
48005007	Gyo waenuma hwyeti . Ma kru diya tyo gyo drinu din swa ko hro naedewike . Ma ya naerike tyo , gyo ya swa ko drinu dewike .
48005008	God ya sem gyo diwa hrena , ya wirin .
48005009	Wike ka harinkrai , yist kukumasa parawa me butkaeroko , butmin ko rurwa hyenkinkrai .
48005010	Ma no hin ko Yomkra ya gyo taetaepmin braema . Tenam kyo Keriso yominki hwyenkrai kren , no braema gyo hine atma a brureiki . Hamo kru diya gyo dima swa ate naegimo diroko gua hin ko atkewi , ma kru hoko no braema wirin hamo God ya kru ho dima dore daenada .
48005011	No kire gyoke , ma kudi nokwa kate tigin kronam naegimra ko dukra ko duro , ma naemo diwa ko no wyerane . Ma kudi swa hoko drinu kroko , hamroko no Keriso yo dei buti hro yo pwete swa ho ko naegimrako , wike ka hine ko tigi pyen daen braema wirin .
48005012	Ma wike dika gyo dima tyo , gua hin ko tigu gyo hin ko atma bruroko , hamo no hoda wike hoko kate tigin kronam butmin homnaida . Hamo kaesa ka two tiginina .
48005013	Ma no kire gyoke , God ya gyo dima ko koma wirin da hreya gua hinsa bra hominknaida . Ma gua braeme , guaesa homrai hoa gua bute ka hodrai hoa gyo tikme .
48005014	Koma butmin ya drike ko trusa hiwa , guae gyo dima naemike hine brenkrai , hote ho bryoko , wike guae po penkrai , ko dima proeka hine pya brenknai .
48005015	Ma gyo ko ware gryogryo tonen ko dinaeka , guae rwyo kyomku rwyo kyomku hamroko braeme , guaesa rwyo gyo butmin domsorin braema .
48005016	Hamo nokwa tyerakra ko hiwa , Dure ya gyo tikmroko , gua bute ya hodrai ko homin braema wirin .
48005017	Tenam kua bute ka hodrai ko tru , ma Dure ya hodra ko tru . Hamo ti dure hokan ko totetyenkrai . Hamo gua hodrai ko homin braema wirin .
48005018	Ma Dure ya gyo gyori troko , Komato gyo tikmin braema wirin .
48005019	Kyo braema hoa kua bute ka hoda dinkraiko , ko kronam swokin ate ate homwera dinkrai .
48005020	Ma Tona ate , krite me homa hro hoa , taetaepmnada kentika , kutya yaka , haminkrai . Ma wike gwin ko wasika , totetyaka , gwoegwoekeka kyomka , kae ka hi hyenmaka , haminkrai . Ma wike gwin ko ridwa , yae po yae po , hamo grwine brenkrai .
48005021	Ko wai swokin dua nononka gwoegwoekinkrai . Hamake ko ro gaema , kudin pya dua kronam ate ate pya hominkrai . No sem gyo dima tyete ho hote tyera , wike dika kronam himike hominkraiko God ya ko tikmin braema wirin .
48005022	Ma Dure Waenukin yo kronam waenukin wike ko dima daeminkra ko hiwa . Proeka hine pya bren kronam , da mate yoyomkeka kate druki waenuma paka proekin kronam da mate kronam dukin da mate drinuhaki din da ho daeminkra .
48005023	Hamake kate druki homaka bute ko kae tikminin da daenkra . Ma kronam hiko koma wirin .
48005024	Ma wike dika haryoko kyo ko Yesu Keriso yana droko , ka bute ka hodrai ko tuma yeti .
48005025	Dure ya ware ko kyo dima daena . Hamo kyo ware me hurai hiko , ya tikminina .
48005026	Hamo kuae kyo rwyo irinka , wike gwin ko dima hamasa tyaka rwyo gwoegwoeku rwyo gwoegwoeku haminkromoeda .
48006001	Kire gyoke , kudi kru trua hweke hre diroko , wike diko God ya dure ya kominki hra wike hoka kru hwekmin ho duduminina . Ma proekin mesa dudumnai . Hamo guae braeme , pako Saiten ya gyo tranmeda .
48006002	Ma gua kire ka pyenkin naekin taera to diroko , gyo ko taetaepminknai . Hamroko gyo Keriso ya koma homnai din ko ho homnaiha .
48006003	Ma kudi kru trua ya hina ya hi ko hyena , ma wike gwin kato ya hi ko kukina droko , hamroko kru hoko yae yo rwyo ho kraeraha .
48006004	Ma kyo butmin , trusa trusama , tmoe kua hominkrai ho , druri begiminina . Hamo kronam hoko duwadi , yae yo rwyo irin braema .
48006005	Tenam wike butmin kyo kua pyen mesa hama tmoe hominkrai .
48006006	Ma kru diya Keriso ya swa yo dima naegimo , ya gryo waenukin tru kru yo naegiminkra yo dima kesu daenina .
48006007	Guae gyo rwyo kraeromoe . Kru ara trua God dima ikarmroko , God yo hukwaekin braema wirin . Kru trua kudin ke naekina hriroko , yo kudin tei hosa sen braema .
48006008	Ma kudi ya hin hya ko buta hodrasa hine pya bruroko , hoe ko pwensa . Ma kudi ya hin ko Dure dima sa hine bruroko , ya dure ko ware dyaen sekraha .
48006009	Hakina krenku kyo kronam waenukin homaka totokinaemka hamosa homi troko gaemin aku ko hoe direiki .
48006010	Ma kudi kyo kronam waenukin homaekina kroko wike gwin ko dima hominina . Ma wike dika Keriso ko drinu dinkrai , ko ko kua gire ho bryoko kren , kronam waenukin ko dima ko hya hominkwe .
48006011	Ma gyo dinai , nokwa no kriteme hi kimra ko hyena .
48006012	Kru gwin dika hoda gua kate ko tiginina da swa pya tyenkrai , kae kosa topkyen ho iri skwerinkrai . Ma ka ho hominkraiko , pako Keriso ya dei buti pwete kronam pyenka hakin koke simeda .
48006013	Ma kru dika kate tigin kronam ho hominkraiko , me koma gwin tyen ko homin kmaepu . Ko hoda gua kate tigu maren ko gua kate tigrai ho iri twyera .
48006014	Hamo no ko , kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya dei buti pwete swa hosa irmaekina . Tenam pwen dei hoa dware sa , to hyenu hi ko no dima pwena dinaekina , ma no ko to hyenu hi dima pwena .
48006015	Hamo kru digwa gwa kate tigina kroko gu hoko hine pya brurome . Ma kru digwa ya gwa kate tiginaemkina kroko gu kesu hine pya brurome . Ma gua hin ko hine nin , ho dimasa hine pya brenina .
48006016	Ma wike dika kronam hi dima hine pya bra homwera drai kronam waenuma pen ko ko dima senada . Ko dima ae , mate God ya wike butmin ko dima ae hamnada .
48006017	No kwasu swa ko hoe yerakra . Kru trua no dima swa pyenkin tru tnyome , tenam no bute ure ko naegiminkra no ko Yesu ya tmoe homin kru .
48006018	Kire gyoke , kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya proeka hamaha din kronam ko gyo dima aenada . Haminina .
49001001	No ko Por . Hamo nokwa kwo hi gyo dima kimira . Ma no ko Yesu Keriso ya tmoe homin kru hamo no ya hodra ho homnada pru tena . Hamo no God ya wike to Epesis hokan penkrai gyo dima kimrako , kru ara dika ko drinuhakida kua ware ko Yesu Keriso yominki pkorina penkrai gyo dima kimra .
49001002	Kuai God me Yesu Keriso ta gyo pitma tikmo yoyomkin me waenuma pnaida .
49001003	Ma kyo kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso yai me ya God yo dima gu ko duwa dinkwe . Tenam kyo Keriso yominki pkorina , hamo yo kyo dima Kwoe Kom ka kronam waenukin kyo dima daemite .
49001004	Ma to hyenu hiko hominaemkin hoke , God ya kyo Keriso yo me pkorina dite , hamo yo kyo yanamira dite . Hamo ya kyo dirako , kronam swokin tru kyo dima ae dimaepu .
49001005	Tenam God ya kyo dima hine bra proeka , Yesu Keriso ya dima tyo , ya homo kyo ko ya kya dite . Tenam hiko ya hodra ho homite .
49001006	Hakina kren kyo God ya hi hyenmwe , tenam yo kyo dima proeka ya kya kyo dima hingruwa daena kren .
49001007	Tenam Keriso ya pwete kren , kua kronam swokin hoe ko ya sete . Hamo kua hweke ko ya hamaha dite . God ya proekin hoa .
49001008	Ya kyo dima hine bra proekin ko hyena .
49001009	God ya braemkin ho himiramite ko sem hine bra gwemin ho Keriso ya kyo dima naegimite .
49001010	Ma hiko ya braemkin ho homiramite . Hamo aku hoko pko diroko kwoe me to hyenu me ko gaemo Keriso ya hya andumki .
49001011	Tmoe butmin ko God ya hodra ho himinkrai . Hamo God ya homira droko , homo taenkin braema . Ma kyo ko Keriso yo me pkwae diroko God ya kyo ko yanamite .
49001012	Ma kyo kuatumki Keriso dima dumahaki dina kren , kyo God ya ai waenukin ho dima gu ko duwa dwe .
49001013	Ma gyo kesu God ya swa daereka drinuhaki diti hoa gyo dei senku gyo ko God ya wike hoa . Hamo gyo Keriso ya swa drinu dina kren , God ya aripe gyo dima hro , gyo ko nana dite . Aripe hoko Dure Waenukin howa . Ya sem gyo dima daera din ho .
49001014	Ma dure hoko hikina . God ya mgakwen kyo dima daerada tyena kroko hoko kyo diwa braemkinkrai ya kyo dima daerada naerike tyenko . Hamo kyo braema wike diko yana kroko , ka naekin homwera droko yo homin braema . Hakina kren , kyo ya hi hiwe .
49001015	Ma no daerite ko gyo Yomkra Yesu ya swa daereka drinuhaki diri ko dewi . Hamo gyo God ya wike ko dima hine pya brenkraiko du daerire .
49001016	Hamo nokwa God dima duwa din swa tyerakrako gua swa kesu tyenkra .
49001017	Ma no kuai waenukin Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya God yo dima tyo ya Dure gyo dima dae gyo God braemkraida .
49001018	Ma no hoda yo gua hin tyae , gyo ya hodra ho braemknaida . Hamo ya wike dima daenkra ko waenukiskin hosa daenkra .
49001019	Ma kua ya swa ko drinu du , ya ai kyo dima dae tmoe homin braema .
49001020	Ma ai gyominki henkra ho me sa Keriso ko pwo ai ho me yo satyoma warmo asi tena , hewen hokan penkra .
49001021	Hamo Keriso yo aekwa hokan pakano , to hyenu yomkra da mate wike yomkra drai ko da butmin ko yasa tikmra . Hakina kren , ya hi ko hyena . Ma wike yomkra hamosu pkwekrai ko kesu yasa tikmi .
49001022	God yo tmoe butmin ko Keriso yo dima hre yasa tikminkra . Ma Krwistin wike butmin kesu kua Yomkra ko yasa .
49001023	Ma Krwistin wike kyo ko Keriso ya bute dinaekina . Hamo aekwa yo ko dure , ma kyo ko ya bute . Ma yo hoda tmoe butmin to hyenu hikan homa wirinma naedinkra .
49002001	Ma semsoge uminki gyo kronam ate ate pya homaka hweke twamamiti . Hamo hoa gyo ko yo , tosurina dinaekina .
49002002	Ma gua to hyenu peti aku hokeko , gua gryo dima hine pya braka mate wike gwin ka kronam ho diwa , gyo kesu hamike homiti . Ma gyo sem uminkiko , dure swokin kwoe mo to hyenu mo , dure hwape kwenkrai ka yomkra tyo homamiti . Ma aekwa wike diko God ko , ko a dinkraiko , dure swokin hoa ko tikminkra .
49002003	Ma drinu semsoge kyo butmin hamike homamiti . Kua hine bra kua bute ka hodrai hosa kyo homamiti . Ma kudi kuae kua dure me kua hin me kua bute ka hodu , daera hosa homi troko , kyo God ya kyom direiki .
49002004	Ma God yo kyo dima proeka hine pya brenkra .
49002005	Kyo ya swa daerinaemkin hokeko kyo tosurina dinaekina kweti . Hamo God ya Keriso dima tyo , ya kyo homo warkiti . God ya proekin howa kyo dei dwen tonae dima a sryeiki .
49002006	Yo Yesu Keriso me kyo me homa satyomo yominki kwoe kom hokan paka yomkra kreiki .
49002007	Ya ho homite ko himike . Tenam yo hine bra ya proekin aepesu aenin ho Krwistin wike kyo dima naegu braemknaida .
49002008	Hakina kren God ya gyo dima proekinku , gua hweke hoeko a sireiki . Ma gyo swa ho daerekano drinu , duwa diti . Ma hoko gua tmoe homrai dware ho wirin . Ma hiko God ya sumsa daenkra ho . Hakina kren , kru tru yae yo irin braema wirin .
49002009	
49002010	God ya kyo homite . Ma aekwako kyo Yesu Keriso yo me pkori hwyaka kronam waenukin homnaida . God ya sem tmoe hoko hine bra hrete .
49002011	Ma swa ate wike gyoke , Ju wike ka gyo dima harike gyo ko kate tiginaemkin dinkrai . Ma kasa ko kate tigina dinkrai . ( Ma kronam hiko wike kae ka butensa hominkrai . ) Ma kronam sem guae homiti ho hine brenina .
49002012	Ma aku hokeko gyo Keriso ko braemkinaemka wenema peti . Hamo gyo ko God ya aripe hrenaemkin guae gua kuma grnaegitesa peti . God ya gyo dima swagumin tmyaen . Hamo swa hoko sem ya swaguma taeri twen ko dima aete . Ma gyo to hikan hwyaka harinkmaepu , gwamgu no pwa to waenukin dima tmawe harmaepu . Ma God yo kyo taetaepmin kra harmaepu .
49002013	Sem uminki gyo God dima ko wena dinaekina peti . Ma Yesu Keriso ya pwenku God ya kyo sa kumta yo kuri hrena prai .
49002014	Keriso yasa kyo ganeswamite . Hamo Ju wike da mate swa ate wike ko , grare hrena dinaeka ridwa yae po yae po hamiti ma ko , kwasu tei trusa drai . Tenam yesu Keriso ya bute me grare hoko kya kyo ko trusada prai .
49002015	Hamo Koma Ju wike ka tweti hoko ya grurite . Hamo wike tei haepki ho tiko hote trusa diti . Hamo ko yominki pkwo kireda ganeswamiti .
49002016	Keriso ya dei buti hokan pwasu , kae rwyo a du , rwyo a du hamike petiko , ya grura naedite . Hamo ya dei buti pwete hokeko , wike tei haepki ho tiko , yasa kumta trusada hrena prai .
49002017	Hamo Keriso ya kumta hupe waenukin wike swa ate ate ko dima naegimite . Swa ate God ko braema wirin wike gyo dima naegimaka , mate Ju wike God braemkin wike ko dima kesu naegimite .
49002018	Keriso yo me kren , Ju wike me swa ate wike kyo butmin kua Dure ko trusa . Hamo kyo kuai ya pra dima ten braema .
49002019	Hamo aekwa swa ate wike gyo ko wasi wirin . Kwasu gyo ko God ya gire .
49002020	Gyo ko God ya aewe dinaekina . Ma God ya tyo tyen wike da mate , tmoe homin pru ten wike ko ko hruke yen wike . Ma rwanai gyaeri ko Yesu Keriso .
49002021	Hamo aewe hoko , ya kriteme tikminkra . Ma aewe hoko ya butmin tu , waenuka hyenkroko , God ya aewe Tempo dinaekina , ya tua winku diroko hiko Yomkra gwane dikraha .
49002022	Ma aewe Keriso ya tikra ko yo me pkwaen wike gyo da mate swa ate wike . Ma God ya dure yo hokan henkra .
49003001	Hakina kren , nokwa Por , ma no yesu Keriso ya tmoe hominkra hakina kren ko no wogitmiti . Hamo no swa ate wike gyo dima God dima tyenkra .
49003002	Hamo gyo daermaepu God ya gyo dima proeka gyo waenuma praida . Hamo yo tmoe hiko no dima daete .
49003003	God yo hamosu homi krako sem gwenmina ae , marensu no dima naegimite . ( No uminki swa hoekin hiko gyo dima kimite .
49003004	Ma Keriso ya swa gwemina nokwa braemkimire hoko gyoke hyaeka diwa braemknaida . )
49003005	Semsoge swa gwemin hiko God ya wike ko dima naegmyaeapu . Ma aekwako , God ya dure ya God ya tyo tyen wike da mate ya tmoe homin pru ten wike ko dima naegimite .
49003006	Ma swaguma gwemin hiko Keriso ya pwasu , swa ate wike ko kesu Ju wike ko me pkwaeti . Hamo God ya ko taetaepmo , waenuma pen braema . Hamo ko ko gire trusa , tenam ko God ya sem swaguma tyena kren . Yesu Keriso ya homina swa ate wike ko dima kesu aera .
49003007	Hamo no God no tmoe homnada ai me kronam tru braemkin yae tei atkina no dima daete . Hamo no ko ya tmoe homin kru .
49003008	God ya wike gwin ko ko hata dae , ma no ko mare pken kren , no ko hamsya . Ma yo tmoe hiko no dima daete . Keriso ya swa waenukin , swa ate wike ko dima naegimnada daete .
49003009	Ma God ya hamosu homikra butmin ko sem gwemina hamo yo no ho naegimnada .
49003010	Ma aekwa tmoe ho ko sos ko dima dae , hamo God ya po penkrai wike ko God ya braemkin ate ate braemkraida .
49003011	Ma God yo uminki himike homira hin brete . Ma ya homira ho hine breteko , kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya homite .
49003012	Ma kyo , Yesu Keriso God ya pru pken kru , yo dima yo ko drinu droko , kyo tempwen dumka , God ya pra ten braema .
49003013	Hamo no gyo dima tyera tenam gua dware , ten nokwa hi dirako , gyo pyenkromoe . Ma hiko gyo taetaepminina .
49003014	Hakina kren , no God ya kinaegite tama drima pra .
49003015	Ma wike Hewen penkrai da mate to hyenu hikan penkrai wike da gyo butmin God ya hi sena penkrai .
49003016	No God dima tyera , hamo ya dure ya ai gyo dima dae , gyo aikin braema .
49003017	Ma gyo Keriso ko drinuhaki dinku gua tyonam hra , hamo gya wike gwin ko dima proeka hin bren ko hyena .
49003018	Ma no hoda God ya wike butmin gyo braemknaida , God ya gyo dima hine pya brenkra ho braemknaida .
49003019	Ma no hoda gyo ya proekin kronam yoma braemknaida , ma kyo butmin braema wirin . Ma no hoda ya proekin hoko gua tyonam tornyada .
49003020	Ma God ya ai me ya hin kua proenam hominkra ko hyena . Kua hine brenkrai me kua kentinkrai ko kukiskina .
49003021	Hakina kren , kronam waenukin Krwistin wike , kyo Yesu Keriso ya hi satyoma , hyenmaka , God dima ehya , gu ko duwa dinkwe . Aku butmin dyaendyaen hosa haminkwe .
49004001	No wogitmina hrako , tenam no Yomkra ya tmoe hominku . Hamo no gyo dima yoma tyera , God ya gyo dima tyete hoke , gyo dima naemike prnaida tyena kroko gyo hamo penina .
49004002	Hamake ma gyo irin me wirin , gyo kate druki paka dyeskinina , wike gwin ka homrai ko .
49004003	Ma Dure waenukin yo waenuma pen kronam gyo dima daekraha . Hamo gyo hmene waenuma pen kronam ho pitma tikminknai .
49004004	Ma bute ko trusa , ma Dure kesu trusa . Hakina kren God ya gyo uryako , gyo waenuma pen sunam dima tnaida .
49004005	Yomkra ko trusa , hamo kua dumahaki din ko trusa yo dimasa aera . Ma wai bra hamten ko trusa .
49004006	Ma wike butmin kua God ko trusa . Kua yomkra ko yo .
49004007	Keriso ya naekin kyo dima sumsa trusa trusama daemo taeriti .
49004008	Ma Kwonam kima tyen ko harina , Yo komgite terakekano , wike gwin kesu taera tete . Ma yo braemkin kronam tei ate ate , wike ko dima sumsa daemite .
49004009	Ma komgite tete swa hoa ya drike ko naekinane . Ya drike ko komegite hwya msyete . Yo to hmyaete syete .
49004010	Kru ho msyeteko , to kupram hwyano , hote kwoe kom dima tete troko kwoe Hewen dima tete . Hamo yo kwoe me to meko , ya aia torina aenkra .
49004011	Hamo kru hoko , kronam ate ate braemkinko , wike ko dima sumsa daemiteko , wike gwinko ko pru , ya tmoe taminkrai . Ma gwin ko tyo tyen tmoe daemite . Ma gwin ko Keriso ya hi braemkin aemkin wike ko naegimraida daemite . Ma gwin ko wike tikmaka God ya swa naegiminkrai .
49004012	Keriso ya himike homite tenam God ya wike butmin ko Keriso ya tmoe homnaida . Hamo Keriso ya bute aimnada .
49004013	Hamo kyo God ya kya ya tmoe hmene homi troko kyo ya swa drinuhaki droko kyo ho braemkraiha . Kyo a kya kuku dinaekreki . Maren kyo Keriso yo dinaekreki .
49004014	Hamroko , kyo hote a kya kuku dinaekreki . Ma kraekraema tya daemin wike ko kumta kae ka hinamin atokma naegimo , wike ko hine waenuma brenkmaepu . Hamo hoko hwore mtaka dma gyawinkrai hakina , hote hamo kraekraemin wike ka wike gwin ko dima hamike naegiminkrai .
49004015	Hamo gyoke , hamromeda . Ma gyo swa drinu tyen ho dumasa , proekin me naegiminina . Hamo kyo kesu kronam ate ate Keriso ya homite kyo kesu hamike homwe . Yo ko kua ku kren .
49004016	Ma bute butmin ko ya tikminkra kren , seke butmin ko bryoko penkrai . Ma kro trusa trusama ka tmoe kae bryoko homroko , bute butmin ya ai ko bryokosa penkrai . Tenam braeken ka braeke dima hine bro , ma braeke ka braeken dima hine bro haminkrai kren . Ma kro ka drimin hokan taerina .
49004017	No Yomkra ya hinam gyo dima tyera , braeme , gyo God braemkinaemkin ko dinaeka hamasa promoe . Ka hin ko drike dumka hunamsa penkrai .
49004018	Ma ware God ya daenkrako , ko simaepu , tenam ko a deka nononki hwyenkrai .
49004019	Ma ko kronam swokin homano , hukwae dyen braema wirin .
49004020	Ma Keriso ya kronam braemkin ko hakina wirin .
49004021	No hin gyo Yesu ya swa ko gyo daera naedewiha . Swa nu ko Yesu ya swa ho naegimo gyo ho daerewiha .
49004022	Hamo gua kronam brunai , ya naerike tyo hamike homi kwamiti kren guae gyo rwyo ho domsorinkraiha . Hamo hoko ya goda yae rwyo domsorite .
49004023	Ma aekwako , gyo hine ninma bra hominina .
49004024	Gyo hote krwyo wike nin dinaeka , God dinaeknai . Hamo kru nin hoa ya kronam ko waenukin hakinina .
49004025	Hakina kren , kraekraema tyen kronam ko hro naednai . Tenam Keriso ko bute ma ya seke ko kyo hiwa .
49004026	Ma kudi aku tru gu kyomkroko , gwa kyomkire ko yae hamo ae troko tei sryome . Pako gu hweke hrimeda .
49004027	Pako ya ten tmyo Saiten ya pkmeda .
49004028	Ma kru dia yo ko udina kroko hro naedna . Hamo yo tmoe komdwa homaka sere sa , ya kudin twa taera , wike mgyore ko taetaepminina .
49004029	Ma gyo kyomka grnyonka hamasa tyen kromoe . Taetaepmin swasa tyenina . Swa waenukin , naerike gua trya hosa wike ko taetaepmo ko aiki waenuma penknai .
49004030	Ma kudi swa gwa naerike tyo , God ya Dure waenukin yo pyenkmaekina kroko swa hoko tryomoe . Tenam Dure hoko God ya aripe kyo dima hrena . Hamo kyo ko yana . Ma aripe ho ya drike ko , aku tru God ya gyo hmora to waenukin hokan twe .
49004031	Hakina kren , kyomka ai bari tyen kronam ko hro naednai . Hamake ikema tyaka swa swokin hamasa tyaka haminkrai ho kesu hro naednai .
49004032	Gyo wike gwin ko dima proeka hweke ka gyo dima hominkrai ko hamaha droko , God ya Keriso dae , gua hweke ko hamaha dite . Hote ho bryoko gyo kesu wike gwin ka hweke hamaha dinina .
49005001	Tenam gyo ko God ya kya kuku , hamo ya gyo dima hine pya brenkra , hote hamroko gyo yo dinaeknai .
49005002	Ma gua ware ko hine pya bren kronam hoa hoko tikminina . Keriso ya kyo dima hine pya bra , ya ware ko kyo dima daete . Ma God dima daeteko , dine disiru pom waenukina mto God ya daera duwa dinkra hakina .
49005003	Ma tenam gyo ko God ya wike kren , gyo kore aeng tyaka , kronam grimekeka hakemin ko gyominki swa tyenina wirin .
49005004	Hamake gyo su tyen kesu ko bryoko wirin . Hoko naede , God dima ehya dinknai .
49005005	Ma gyo yoma braemkinina , kru ara di ko aeng tyaka , kore tyaka , grimeka hakemina , ( god tru dima hine brenkrai ko hakina ) , hamo kru hakemin ko God me Keriso ta wike tikmwekraiko , wike hakemin ko hoko dyen braema wirin .
49005006	Hamo gyo braema , wike gwin ko gyo dima nononkin swa tyo , daera drinu dromoe . Hakina kren , God ya kyom ko , wike ya swa daera hominaemkrai ko dima pki .
49005007	Hakina kren , wike hakemin kominki kireda promoe .
49005008	Gyo guaesa petiko , hunamsa peti . Ma gyoko , Yomkra ya wiku diroko , gyo kae ti penkrai . Hamo , kru kae ti penkrai ho bryoko gyo kesu kae ti penknai .
49005009	Ma kae hoa kronam waenukin ate ate hominkra .
49005010	Ma gyo , naekin homo Yomkra ya diwa yoyomkroko , hoko braemkinina .
49005011	Hunam prai wike ka hominkraiko drike dumkina , hamo gyo wike kronam hakemin kominki hominina wirin . Hamo ko kae dima gyori pkinkrai .
49005012	( Ma ka gwema homrai ko no a tye , no hukwaekinkra . )
49005013	Ma hamosu kronam butmin ko taen tyosu ka homiri teinam ko taenku dyen braema .
49005014	Kronam naekin ko kae ti proko , taenku dyen braema . Hakina kren , Kwonam kima tyen ko harina krogoe aerurai , gyo asnyai . Hamo Keriso ya kae gyo dima kaemra .
49005015	Hakina kren , gua braeme , gua penko , nononkin wike ka penkrai hamike promoe . Braemnain wike ka penkrai gyoke hamike penknai .
49005016	Gyo tmoe naekin homin braema kroko hamike homnai , tenam aku hiko swokina kren .
49005017	Hakina kren gyo hmene yen dinaekromoe . God ya gyo naekin homnai dra hoko drurinknai .
49005018	Gyo wai wain pya dua nononkinkromoe . Hoko gyo domsorin braema . Dure waenukina gua tyonam tori henina .
49005019	Gua kire kominki swa twyerakroko , Kwonam kimin yoke waenukin ho ya swa rwyo tyo , matum rwyo tyo , hamike tyenina . Hamake yoke gwin wike ka hine bra gin ho gika mate Sam hokan kimin ho gua proe me Yomkra dima yoyomki ginina .
49005020	Ma gyo kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya hi hyenmaka Kuai God yo dima ehya dinina .
49005021	Ma tenam gyo Keriso dima hine waenuma brenkrai kren , gyo wike gwin tikmo ka rwyo matum gyo tikmo haminina .
49005022	Ma ara , kru min gyoke , gwa kru dima harinkrai , gu ko no yomkra dinina , gwa Yomkra ya swa daera hominkra hakina .
49005023	Ma kru ka runaen tikminkra ko , Keriso ya Krwistin wike ko tikminkra ho bryoko . Ma Keriso yasa ko Krwistin wike ka Yomkra . Ma ko ko ya bute ho bryoko .
49005024	Hakina kren , ara ko ka kru ka swa daerinknai , Krwistin wike ko Keriso ya swa daerinkrai hakina .
49005025	Ma kru gyoke , gua runaen dima proeka hine pya brenknai . Keriso yo Krwistin wike ko dima hine pya braka , ya ware ko dima daete haminina .
49005026	Ya himike homiteko , tenam ya swanam Krwistin wike ko God dima daeramite . Ma yo ko wai me sorite .
49005027	Yo hoda Krwistin wike ko tupe dumka kronam swokin tru hominaemku , ko yae yanamiramite .
49005028	Ma kru ko kae ka bute dima hine pya brenkrai , ho bryoko ka runaen dima hine brenina . Ma kru diya ya runaen dima hine pya bruroko yo yae rwyo yo dima hine pya brenkraha .
49005029	( Ma kru ara trua yae ya bute dimako , yo a din braema wirin . Kyo ho dima kudin daemaka tikmaka haminkrai . Keriso yo hote haminkra ya Krwistin wike ko dima hamike tikminkra .
49005030	Tenam kyo ko ya bute seke . )
49005031	Kwonam kima tyen ko harina , hakina kren , kru trua yo yai yaem kwori , ya runaen yominki pkoroko , tiko haepki wirin , ti ko trusa dina .
49005032	Swa Kwonam tyen hiko drike hyena aera , Keriso ya Krwistin wike ko dima .
49005033	Hamo swa hiko gyo dima kesu aera , kru butmin gyo gya runaen dima hine pya brenknai , guae gyo dima proeki hine pya brenkrai haminina . Ma ara gyo gua kru dima hine waenuma brenknai .
49006001	Kya kuku gyoke , gyo Krwistin dina kren , guai guaem ka swa daera hominina . Kronam hiko duwa .
49006002	Gyo guai guaem ko dima hine waenuma brenknai dina . Ma swa hi ya hoe hokan kimin ko swagumin hya ho dimina .
49006003	Ya hoe tyen ko hiwa , hamroko gyo to hikan aku pya waenuma hwyen braema .
49006004	Ma kya kai kaem , gyo gua kya ko dima kronam tru naekin homu ko pyenka kyom kroko kronam hakin ko hominina wirin .
49006005	Ma wike twa taerin gyoke , guanai ka tmoe ko tempwen me hominknai . Ma hin haepki hominina wirin . Gyo Keriso ya tmoe hominkrai hamike hominina .
49006006	Ma ka pa dyo , gyo tmoe waenuma hominkrai tenam ka gyo dima waenuma brunaida , hokesa wirin . Ma gyo God ya hodra hosa hominina . Gyo ko Keriso ya wike twa taerin ka hominkrai hamike hominina .
49006007	Ma wike twa taerin gyo gua tmoe homakano yoyomkinme hominknai . Guae kua Yomkra ya tmoe hamike hominina . Wike ka tmoe hominkrai hakina wirin .
49006008	Braeme , Yomkra yo wike butmin trusa trusama ka hominkrai waenukin hoe waenukin daemi . Yo wike diko twa taerin me mate dika ko ko twa taerinaemkina kroko ko dima daemi .
49006009	Ma wike anai gyo kesu , wike gua twa taerin ko dima hine brenknai , hote ho bryoko hine brenina . Ma gyo tempwen swa ko dima tryomoe . Nononkromoe , gyo me wike gua twa taeryai me , guanai ko trusa . Yo Kom Hewen hokan pra . Ma ya begeminkra ko maka trusa .
49006010	No swa ko hoe yerakra , hamo no swa tru hi tyera . Gyo , Yomkra yominki penkrai , gua ai ko , ya ai hyenu home hyenminina .
49006011	Hamo napu me kwe , me totetyen gryo gua bute tikminin butminko , God ya gyo dima nakoe daena kroko home hrenina . Hamo Saiten ya gyo dima kraekraema satomgirakuro gyo aikisa hureiki .
49006012	Tenam kyo to hyenu wike ko dima tote tyenkmaepu , kyo tona swokin ate pya ko dima totetyenkrai .
49006013	Hakina kren , God ya napu ko aekwa brenina . Hamo aku swokin hoko pko diroko totetyen ka kumta gyo domsorwera pko diroko , ka ten dwen braema . Hamo gyo totetiwa , to kwomga , gua to ko guae hamo hwyen braema .
49006014	Hamo gyo huma tmaeki hunai . Ma gyo drinu swa ko beretima gua kmaeke hokan tuma draekinina . Ma dumasa hominin ko gua napu .
49006015	Ma gua karike bren ko , God ya swa waenukin ko kyo ganeswamite swa hoko naegimwera tmaeki hwyenknai .
49006016	Hamo kyo God ya swa ko drinu droko , hoko gua kwe . Ma gyo kwe hoko sa , hwyo swokin yanai ya aepin tu dei tin men hoko gyo dima siru pkeka , gua kwe tori , dei ko gotin braema .
49006017	Ma God ya kyo hro sen ko gua hati .
49006018	Gyo himike homwerakekano God dima kenti ya gyo taetaepmna dnai . Ma kronam tei ate ate , dikan pko diroko , Dure ya tyo diroko , God dima tyenina . Hakina kren , gyo paka hawyo driminkrai , gyo naede hamaha dwe dromoe . Hamo gyo butmin God ya wike ko dima guriguri tyenknai .
49006019	Ma gyo no hi kesu God dima tyenknai . Ma no ya swa tyerakroko yo no dima swa naegimo , no tempwenaemka swa hoko yoma tyo , God ya swa sem gwemkin hoko no naegimin braema .
49006020	Ma swa Waenukin hi me kren , no ko Yomkra ya swa tyo tyenin kru . Hamo no wogitmina hra . Ma gyo God dima tyaka harnyai , yo swa hi tyenkrako , swa hiko yoma tyenina dnai . Ma yo yomasa tyen ko duwa , harnyai .
49006021	Kua kire Tisikis yo kesu Yomkra ya swa waenuma naegiminkra . Hamo yo tmoe nokwa hominkra ho naegimo , gyo braemknaida .
49006022	Hakina kren , no yo pru kuta kua naemike prai swa ho twya , mate swa gwin gyo dima tyo , gyo daera hine saeknaida .
49006023	Kuai God me Yomkra Yesu Keriso ti Krwistin wike butmin gyo dima waenuma pen kronam dae mate hine pya bren kronam dae mate God ya swa ko drinu dina dae hami .
49006024	Ma wike dika kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso yo dima hine pya aepesu brenkraiko , God ya proekin kronam ko dima aenada .
50001001	No ko Por , hamo Timoti ki ko Yesu Keriso ya tmoe homin kru . Hamo kwo hi ko kia Piripai Krwistin wike gua yomkra da mate gyo taetaepmin wike butmin hamo gyo dima kimrai .
50001002	Kuai God me Yomkra Yesu Keriso ta waenuma pen kronam ho gyo dima daenaida .
50001003	Ma aku dikan no gyo dima hine brakano , no God dima gu ko duwa dinkra .
50001004	Hamo no gua hi God dima tryoko , no yoyomkin me sa tyenkra .
50001005	Tenam nokwa taenkite aku hokesa hwya hupe waenukin naegimo , gyo no taetaepma pketi pkroko aekwa hiwa .
50001006	Hamo no braema God ya tmoe waenukin hi gyo dima komdwa homite ko hamosa troko , aku Yesu Keriso ya pkikra hokesu naendi .
50001007	No aku butmin gyo dima proeka hine pya brenkra . No himike hine brenkra , tenam no wogitminaemkina ha ma aekwasu wogitmina hikan prako , tmoe waenukin God ya no dima daete ko , gyo kesu nominki hominkrai .
50001008	Nokwa gyo dima hine brenkra hi ko , Yesu Keriso ya proenam gite pkinkra da , drinu sa trya , God ya po daerya .
50001009	Ma no God dima tyo , gua hine bra proekin ko hyenmnada dinkra . Hamake waenuma braemki yoma begemin ho gyo dima daemnada .
50001010	Hamo gyo kronam drike hyena diwa sasu , hamo Keriso yo krwyo pkikra aku hoko gyo hukwae a direiki , gua hweke sorinku .
50001011	Marensu Yesu Keriso yo kronam waenukin ate ate gyo dima daekraha . Hamo wike gwin ko diwa God ya hi hiwekraiha .
50001012	Kire gyoke , no hoda gyo braemkrnaida , kronam no dima pkra hi ko Keriso ya swa wike ko dima naegimo taetaepminkra .
50001013	Hamo Sisa ya aewe tikmin wike da ma wike gwin hikan hurai ko butmin braema no ko Keriso ya tmoe homin kru kren ko no wogitmina hra .
50001014	Ma no wogitkina hra kren kua kire ko Yomkra drinu pken swa ko tempwenaemka naegiminkrai .
50001015	Ma wike gwin ko gwoegwoeki grwin bren me tyadaeminkrai . Ma gwin ko hine waenuma bra naegiminkrai .
50001016	Wike hi ko proeka waenuma naegiminkrai , tenam ko braema God ya no dima naegimin tmoe ho daenku .
50001017	Hamo wike gwin ko waenuma tyaedaeminkmaepu . Kae ka hi sa hyenminkrai . Ka hin ko no wogitmina hra ko , hamike homo pyen hyenu no dima pknada .
50001018	Hamaha , no yoyomkra . Kraekraemaka ma drinu naegimaka , hamo Keriso ya swa tyadaeminkrai . Hamroko no yoyomki .
50001019	Tenam no braema gua God dima tyenkrai kren ma Yesu Keriso ya Dure ya no taetaepmo , maren no aewe hi ko hro ti .
50001020	Ma no tmoe hi ko a kwori , no hoda no tempwenaemka hama homira . Hamo no pumaudi ma no a pumaudi , hamroko no Keriso ya hi sa hye .
50001021	Ma kua hurai ya drike ko naekinane . No hin ko no hikan hroko , Keriso ya tmoe sa homi . Ma kudi no puroko , no hote dmyo hata homiski .
50001022	Ma kudi no hikan hamosa hroko no kru ara pya taetaepmin braema . Haku diku no ten di simawe dra .
50001023	No hin ko haepki aera . No hoda kuta Keriso minki hera dinkra . Hamo ho ko waenukiskina .
50001024	Ma kudi no to hikan no hamo heskroko , duwa . Hamroko , no gyo taetaepmin braema .
50001025	Hi ko no braema kren no hi . Hamo no gyominki hroko gyo taetaepmo gyo Yesu ya swa ko drinu da yoyomki hureiki .
50001026	Maren no hote kumta gyominki hroko , gyo no dima yoyomkreiki tenam gyo Keriso yominki hurai kren .
50001027	Ma no hine hya ko gyo Yesu Keriso ya swa waenukin daerin wike ko dinaeka hunai . Ma no kuta gyo dimaekinkra ma gyo dyenaemkroko no daerikra ko gyo butmin ko hin trusasa swa waenukin naegimrai ko du daerira .
50001028	Gua wasi ko dima tempwenaemka dimkreiki , tenam God yo gyo taetaepminku .
50001029	Tenam gyo Keriso ya tmoe dae homraiko hoko waenukina ma drinu din hosa wirin . Gyo ya tmoe homroko tren me pyenkin me dyen braema .
50001030	Kwasu gyo nominki tmoe tukin , totetyen dinaekin hi homwe . Ma tmoe hoko nokwa homo gyo dyeti . Ma totetyen hoko yae hamo aeskra .
50002001	Ma gyo Keriso yo minki huroko gyo ko aia , ma ya proekin ko gyo dima aera , ma gyo Dure yominki swa tyenkrai . Ma gyo gua kire ko dima proekinkrai .
50002002	Hamroko , gyo yoyomkin hyena no dima daena , gyo hine trusa bra mate proekin ko trusa mate dure kesu ko trusa hamike penina .
50002003	Guae gua hi sa hiromoe . Wike gwin ka hi hinai .
50002004	Gyo ko taetaepminknai , gua tmoe sa hine brenkromoe .
50002005	Yesu Keriso ya hine bra homite ho bryoko hominkrnai .
50002006	Yo ko God sa . Ma yo wike gaema totetyaka God yo bryoko pera dmaepun .
50002007	Yo yae yane ko hro naende yo wikma hamto wimga yo tmoe homin kru dinaekite .
50002008	Hamo ya hi ko yaesa himaepu .
50002009	Hakina kren , God ya warmo yo durkyo asite , ya hi hyenma hata kome hrete . Ma wike gwin ka hi ko kumite .
50002010	Hamo wike butmin Hewen penkrai da ma to hikan penkrai da ma to tukram penkrai butmin ka Yesu ya hi hya , yo dima tama drima preiki .
50002011	Hamo ko harwekraiha , Yesu Keriso ko Yomkra hyena . Ma ko kuai God ya hi kesu hirieki .
50002012	Sen gyoke , uminki no gyominki ha hoke , gyo no swa daera homaewi . Hamo aekwa no gyominki henaemkroko , uminki homaewi hamike hominina . Gyo tmoe ko homakano God dima tempwen me hominkrnai . God ya gyo taetaepmite , hamike guae gyo taetaepminkrnai .
50002013	God yo aku butmin gyominki haka gyo dima homo ya hodra ho homwera dinkrai .
50002014	Gyo nakoe homroko grwin swa min hominkromoe .
50002015	Huneko , pute ko kae daenkrai . Hote ho bryoko , gyo wike kronam swokin hominkrnai kominki huraiko , gyo ko dima ware swa naegimroko , gyo ko dima kae daenkrai . Hamo diroko , Keriso ya pkin aku ho pko diroko , no gua kronam diwa iri . Ma no tmoe ko hamasa homaepu dikraha .
50002016	
50002017	Dikani no kapoe ko smyaudi . Hoko gua dumahaki din God dima hoe hyena dinaeka daenku , no kapoe ko hokan ti dripmaudi . Hamroko no yoyomki .
50002018	Ma gyo kesu yoyomkrnai , hamo kyo hmene yoyomki pwe .
50002019	Ma kudi Yomkra ya hoda droko , hamosu no Timoti pru gyo dima ti . Hamo ya krwyo kumtasu gua prai swa ho tyo daera no hine saeka , yoyomki .
50002020	Timoti kia sa gyo dima hine pya brenkrai .
50002021	Ma wike gwin ko kae ka hodrai hosa hominkrai , Yesu Keriso ya tmoe hominkmaepu .
50002022	Gyo braema Timoti ko waenukina . Swa dukin naegima hominkraiko , kya kai taetaepma hominkrai hakina .
50002023	Ma kronam naekin no dima pkrako no natumki braemkroko , no dumasu yo pru gyo dima tikraha .
50002024	Ma kudi Yomkra no ten homroko , no kesu kuta gyo dyera ti .
50002025	Ma no hin ko Epaprodaites pru gyo dima ti . Gua yo pru ya kumta no waenuma taetaepminkra .
50002026	Yo gyo dyera da hine pya brura , tenam gyo yo trerire ko du daera gyo yo dima hine pya brumeda .
50002027	Ma drinu yo sem trera pwerake . Ma God ya yo proeke . Ma yo dimasa proekmaepu , no dima kesu proeke . Yo pyen hyenu no dima dimeda .
50002028	Hakina kren , no yo pru gyo dima trnada . Gyo yo diwa yoyomkreiki .
50002029	Ma gyo yo diwa yoyomkinme krnayaemnai , yo ko Yomkra ya wike kren , gua gmore bryoko . Hamo kru hakina ko dima duwa dinknai .
50002030	Tenam yo Keriso ya tmoe homira kren , ya ware ko yo hine brumaepu . Gyo kumta no taetaepmin braema wirin kren , ya kumta no taetaepma .
50003001	No kire gyoke , no swa hiko kwasu hoe yerakra . Ma gyo Yomkra minki hwyenkrai kren yoyomkinknai . Swa no sem kimina hote kimin ko totokmaepu . Ma no hamroko ho ko gua taetaepminina .
50003002	Braeme , kru kronam swokin homrai , ko kate tigwera dinkrai hoa , ko ko dedure psaen dinaekina .
50003003	Kate tigin kronam ya drikenu ho ko kuasa sena . Tenam kyo God ya dure me God dima tyenkrai . Ma kyo Yesu Keriso yominki hwyenkrai . Ma kua hin ko kua bute graegite homin kronam hosa dima hine pya brenkra ko bryoko wirin .
50003004	Ma kudi no hoda droko no kronam hoko hine tuma bren braema . Ma wike gwin ka hine brenkrai ko kate tigroko hoato kyo taetaepmikraha dinkrai , no kesu hine harike hyenma bren braema .
50003005	Hamo no aku ko krigwotesin so diroko , ko no kate tigiti . Ma noko Isrwaeo kru . Ma no kingwam ko Bensamin . Nai naem ko yae Hibru , hakina kren no kesu Hibru kru sa . Ma Koma tikmin ko ne . No ko Paresi .
50003006	Ma God ya tmoe aima hominko ne . No Keriso drai wike kuyeramite . Ma koma ko no tru kimaepu . No hin ho ko butmin ko drike hyena harin braema .
50003007	Ma aekwa no hin hoko drike dumkina , tenam kwasu no Keriso braema kren .
50003008	Ma kronam hisa wirin , kronam gwin ko drike kukiskina , Yomkra Yesu Keriso ko no Yomkra kren . No Yesu Keriso ya kronam sano , kronam gwin hro naende . No hine hrodi kronam butmin ko mon dinaekina . No Keriso sa hoda .
50003009	No yominki sa hera . Ma aekwa no koma swa homaka naesa no ko duwa dinkmaepu . Keriso ya no homite kren , ya no ko duwa dinkra .
50003010	No Keriso yoma braemkira . Ma ya durkyaete ai ho sa braemkira , ma ya tren dyete noke dyera . Ma ya pwete kronam ho noke sera .
50003011	Hamo no pwo , ya no hote warmo durkyo asira .
50003012	No a hari , Keriso ya kronam waenukin hi ko no sem sa bryoko naendire harin braema wirin . Ma no tmoe yoma hominkra , hoe ho sera . Tenam Yesu Keriso ya no hro sena kren .
50003013	Kronam hiko no sem sere ko da hine harike a bre . Ma margite homa ho ko hine a bre . Andunaegite hoe simaekin ho sa sera hine brura .
50003014	Hamo no dumasa hwemkra . Hoe hoko ware dyaen dyaen kome hokan senina . Yesu Keriso ya God ya hinam kyo urite .
50003015	Kru ara dikua kyo Yesu ya swa yoma braema kroko , kyo hin himike bren ko bryoko . Ma kudi gua hin bren ko ate kroko , God ya gyo dima pitma naegimi .
50003016	Ma kronam kyo sem sen ho hama homwe .
50003017	Kire , gyoke , gyo no kronam diwa hominknai . Ma kyo wike gwin kesu kronam waenukin naegimo , hominknai .
50003018	No sem gyo dima tyamama , ma aekwa no hote byen kron wai me tyerakra , wike pya ko hamasa hurai kren , Keriso ya debuti pwete swa ho dima wasikinkrai .
50003019	Ko Hero dima sryeiki , tenam ka hin hya ko to hyenu gryo-gryo bute ya hodra hosa hine pya brenkrai .
50003020	Ma kyo ko Hewen yana , hamo kyo Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya Hewen hro msya kyo taerikra ho humrai .
50003021	Yo kua bute domkmaekin ho sa atma ya bute waenukin hamike homi twe ti . Hamo ya aime butmin yae yana mi .
50004001	Hamo kire gyoke , no gyo dima hine pya brenkrako gyo dyera . Gyo yoyomkin no dima daenkrai . No gyo dima iria . Hamo gyo ko Keriso ya wike , hakina kren gyo hamikesa hunai .
50004002	Ma ara Yodia me Sintiki gi hin trusa brunai . Gi ko Yomkra ya wike kren apoe auke du haminkrnai .
50004003	Ma no taetaepmin kru gu ara hi ti taetaepmna . Ti nominki taetaepma swa waenukin naegimiti . Kru Kremen me wike gwin ka hi ko ware Kwonam hokan kimina aera . Ko kesu nominki homiti .
50004004	Ma Keriso yo gyominki henku , yoyomkinknai . No hote tyera gyo yoyomkinknai .
50004005	Gyo wike butmin ko dima kate druka pnai . Yomkra pkmae ko kurya .
50004006	Gua hodrai ko hine pya brenkomoe . Gua hodrai ko God dima tyenknai . Ma nononkromoe God dima duwa din kesu tyenknai .
50004007	Harasu , God ya waenuma pen kronam hoko kyo handuma braemkin braema wirin , ma hoasa gua hine bren tikmin braema . Gyo ko Keriso yana .
50004008	Kire gyoke , kronam diko dukin me drinu kroko , hoko gua hinam twenina .
50004009	Ma swa me kronam diko nokwa gyo dima naegimina kroko hoko hominina . Ma God ya kyo dima waenuma pen kronam daenkrako yo gyominki henki .
50004010	No gyo dima duwa dra tenam no Keriso ya tmoe hominkra , hamo gua no dima hine brenkrai ho naegimaewi . Songmena gua hine bren ko no naegmaepu . Gua no taetaepminkra hine brenkrai ko naendmaepu . No taetaepmin ten ko wirin krenku .
50004011	Nokwa hi trya ko tenam no hin wike ko no taetaepminkmaepu deka hine bra tmyaepu . No sem braemke no nakoe mgakwen sa aeroko hoko bryokaera dinkra .
50004012	Ma no gehmenka gryo dumka hamo pen ko no braema . Ma kudin pya sen hokesu no braema . Ma kwasu kronam hi ko no braemkra , kudin din mate kudin dinaemka pen ma gryo pya ma aenaemkroko hokesu no yoyomkinkra .
50004013	Keriso ya ai no dima daenku , kronam naekin no dima pkroko , no bryoko din braema .
50004014	Ma no pyenku gua no taetaepmaewi ko waenukina .
50004015	Piripai wike gyo braema no sem Mesodonia kwori kumta Keriso ya swa waenukin tyadaemira pketeko , gua sa no yoyomkin me no pyenkin me tyo daera taetaepmiti .
50004016	No Tesarenaika ho , gyo aku naemo taetaepmin no dima hre ta ke .
50004017	Ma no hine hya ko sumsa taerin ko hine brumaepu . No hoda kronam waenukin hoe gyo dima pkrnada .
50004018	Hamo sere gua hre pko sa , kwo ko hi kimra . Gua hre pke ko bryoko , hyena . Epaprodaites yo gua daewi ko sa kumta dae sasu , no bryoko sa pra . Gua daewi ko God dima daenkra ho bryoko , yo pom waenukin ho daera , duwa dra .
50004019	Ma Yesu Keriso yo God ya hinam hokan gua hodrai butmin gyo dima daemikraha .
50004020	Hamo kuai God ya hi sa hiwe .
50004021	No kru ara Yesu Keriso ya wike butmin gyo dima duwa dra . Ma kua kire nominki hikan hurai ka kesu gyo dima duwa drai .
50004022	God ya wike hikan prai butmin ko da ma king hyenu ya aewe tmoe homrai wike ko kesu gyo dima duwa din swa tryai .
50004023	Ma Yesu Keriso ya proeka higruwa daeskin kronam ko gyo butmin gyo dima hamo hrnada .
