51001001	No hi ko Por . Hamo God ya tyo diku , Yesu Keriso ya pru , no ya swa naegimirakra , mate no kire Timoti ki God ya wike Korosia hokan penkrai kua goe gmore hamo Keriso yominki hwyaka ya swa ko drinu da hamike penkrai , gyo dima kwo hi kimraiha .
51001002	
51001003	Ma kyo God , kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso yai , ho yo dima kyo gua swa tyaka , ehya dinkrai .
51001004	Tenam kyo daerewiko , gyo Yesu Keriso ya tyen ko drinu da , God ya wike butmin ko dima hine pya brenkraiko , du daerewi .
51001005	Ma swanu ko gyo dima yatumki hupe tyaewiko , gua Hewen dima yoyomkin me ten ko howa . Ma gua siwekrai ko Hewen hokan tikmo aera .
51001006	Ma hupe waenukin hoko daeru diroko kronam waenukin pkinkrai . Ma Hupe hoko to hyenu tako gyo daera ya drike ko gyo duma braemkewi .
51001007	Ma kua kire Epapra , yo Keriso ya swa gyo dima naegima . Ma kua ri ko ya sa , Keriso ya swa waenuma naegiminkra .
51001008	Ya kyo dima tyako , Dure ya hine pya bren kronam gyo dima daenkra ho tya .
51001009	Hakina kren , kyo gua swa daera dumasa gua hi ko God dima tyenkrai . Ma kyo God dima tyo gyo ya hodra ho gyo braemknaida . Mate braemkin kronam butmin Dure ya daenkrako gyo braemnaida .
51001010	Hamroko gyo God ya gyo homnaida du , gyo homin braema . Hamo gua hominkrai drike dukinsa yekraiha . Ma gyo God ya kronam kronam braemkirakeka hote hata hyenma braemkin braema .
51001011	Ma kyo God dima kentryai , ai waenukin butmin gyo dima dae , gyo aiknaida . Hamroko kronam naekin gyo dima pkroko , gyo katma kyomkinaemka tmaeki pen braema . Hamake , gyo yoyomkeka , kuai dima gu ko duwa din braema . Yo gu diwa bryoko dite . Gua siwekraiko , God ya wike ka kae sunam hokan gua hi kimina .
51001012	
51001013	Ma hunam ya aia gyo tikmo hwyaewiko , God ya gyo taera kumta ya kyaa tikma penkra hokan twena prai .
51001014	Kyo ko sem wogitmina dinaekina hwyo ya kyo hmuri twa . Drike hoko kua hweke ko ya hamaha de howa .
51001015	Keriso ko God ya kya . Yae yo dinaekina ma kua yo dimaekina wirin . Yo ko yatumki hamtena , hamo gryo homin butmin ko ya hya ku .
51001016	God ya Keriso yo me gryo butmin homite . Ma Hewen me to hyenu me gryo kua dyenkrai me kua dyenaemkin mate duren me mate wike yomkra butmin ko ya homite .
51001017	Ma kudi ko yominki pkorina kroko , gryogryo butmin ko kae ka ri hokan pen braema .
51001018	Ma yo ko Krwistin wike ka ku . Ma yo ko bute ya ware yanai . Yo kya rwa hamten yo howa . Ma yo pwa hote durkyo asite tenam kronam butmin ko ya hya homite kren .
51001019	God yo hoda ya ai butmin ko ya kya ya sina dite .
51001020	God ya hin breteko , yo to hyenu da mate Hewenin butmin hamo ya kya ya dei buti pwete hoke yo dima hote rwyo pknaida .
51001021	Uminki gyo God ko kwori yo dima ko wasikiti , tenam gua hine bren ko swoka kronam swokin hosa homiti .
51001022	Ma ya kya ya pwete hoa gyo ganeswamite . Yo hoda ya gyo homo gyo hweke dumka waenu yaeyosa haka ya kinaetegite , pknaida .
51001023	Gyo Keriso ya hupe daerewiko , gyo drinu dewi . Hamo God ya penkra gyoke hamike preiki . Ma hine hoko tuma bra hro naedromoe . Ma hupe waenukin hoko Por nokwa naegiminkra . Hupe hiko wike to hoegite hoegite penkrai ko dima naegimite .
51001024	Ma no gyo taetaepmaka pyenkin dyenkra ko no yoyomkinkra . Tenam no sos taetaepmaka tren dyenkrako , Keriso ya tren dyete , hoe ko , nokwa dyenkra .
51001025	Hamo God ya pru no Keriso ya wike ko taetaepmin tmoe hominkra . Hamo yo nokwa gyo taetaepmrada dite . Ma tmoe ko hiwa ya swa butmin yoma naegimnada .
51001026	Ma swa hiko yo sem uminki wike butmin ko dima gwemite . Hamo kwasu ya wike ko dima hi naegimraha .
51001027	Ma God ya hine bra hrete ko yo swa sem gwemin ho ko ya wike ko dima naegimrada dite . Swa waenukin gwemin hiko wike butmin ko dima naegimin ko bryoko . Ma swa gwemina dinkrai hiko Keriso yo gyominki henkra . Hamo marensu gyo God ya ai waenukin sireiki .
51001028	Hakina kren , kyo Keriso ya hupe ho wike butmin ko dima naegiminkrai . Kyo braemki pitmasa naegiminkrai . Kyo hoda wike trusa trusama naegimaka gyori God dima hapkwe . Hamroko God yo ka braemkin kronam diwa ko ko Keriso yominki hwyenkrai din braema .
51001029	Ma no tmoe hi homa naedira kren , no aiki hominkra , Keriso ya ai hyenu daena krenku . Hamo no ai ho me tmoe idima hominkra .
51002001	No hoda gyo braemknaida , no tmoe hyena gyo dima homaka mate Reodisia wike ko dima da mate wike gwin , no toknam braemkinaemkin wike ko dima kesu tmoe hyena homina .
51002002	Nokwa tmoe hamike homite kren gyo aiki matum hine pya bro natum hine pya bro hamnaida . Hamo gyo yoma bra braemkroko , gua dumahaki din ko aikin braema . Hamroko ko God ya swa sem gwemin hoko braemkin braema . Ma hoko Kerisoha .
51002003	Yo me kren , God ya braemkin butmin kyo dima naegu dyen braema .
51002004	Hamo nokwa gyo dima hi tyerakrako , wike gwin ka gyo dima swa hamasa kraekraema tyo me gua hine hrodi , swa hoko drinu dini droko , swa hoko daeryomoe .
51002005	Ma no bute ko gyominki hmaepu , ma no duresa ko gyominki hra . Ma gyo aiki hmenesa Keriso ya swa ko drinuhaki da hamike hruaiko no diwa yoyomkra .
51002006	Tenam gyo Yesu Keriso ko gua Yomkra dina kren , gyo yominki hunai .
51002007	Ma gyo yominki ho huraiha , hoko gyo ko dei droke dinaekina ma droke ko tonam idima bro to tuka henkrai , hote ho bryoko gua hine bren yo dima ko haminina . Hamo gyo aiki hwyen braema . Gyo dima naegimiti , hamin braema . Ma gyo , God dima gu ko waenukina dinknai .
51002008	Ma wike gwin kae ka hine drike dumkin bra , gyo kraekraema tryoko , gua braeme , pako ko hareka kraekraema ka gyo hro simeda . Ma ka braemkin ko soge swa ka kigwam ko naegimrai me mate tona kwoe tikminkrai ka kesu ko dima naegimiti . Keriso ya naegimaepu .
51002009	Yo to hyenu hikan heteko , God ya kronam butmin ko , yo dima torina hete .
51002010	Ma gyo Keriso yominki hurai kren , God ya ware kesu gyo dima torina hra . Yo ko prist me ka koma butmin ka ku ko ya .
51002011	Gyo Keriso yominki pkwaena kren , kua bute ka kronam swokin homwera dinkraiko , ya tigi hasirite . Wike ka kya ka kate tiginkrai ho dinaekina me hoko yae ate .
51002012	Ma gyo wainam syeti , ya drike ko gyo Keriso yo me giwa brena dinaekina . Ma gyo wai mga ya naedu huriti . Tenam gua hin God ya ai yaeyosa hakin home Keriso warmo durkyo asite ko drinu diti kren .
51002013	Uminki gua kronam swokin homamiti hoa , gyo ko pwena dinaekina kweti . Gyo ko swa ate kren , God ya tyo Kwonam kimin ko gyo hyaekin braema wirin . Ma aekwako , God ya gyo Keriso me hopma warmo asite . Ma kronam swokin kua hominkrai ko ya hamaha dite .
51002014	Ma koma kua homnai du kyo hominaemkinkrai ko kwonam kima hrena , ma God ya hoko grura sa ta dei buti hro baku me tukwa yete .
51002015	Ma Keriso yo dei buti hokan haka dure swokin me ka koma ai ko grura domsorite . Ma yo ko totetyen wike ka bring dinaekina . Ya ko dmyaete . Ma ka krite pupuma yo andu to , ko ya mare tetiko wike ka kron ti topkyen teti .
51002016	Hakina kren kru trua kudin gua dinkrai me wai kua dinkrai ko koma hrioko senina wirin . Hamake wike gwin ko aku gwin ko yae ate da , mate dwarin nin diwa ya ro gaemwe da , mate peskin aku ho pko diroko kronam ate ate hominkromoe dinkrai .
51002017	Ma hoko gigin dinaeka , ya naegimo dyenkraiko hamosu homwekrai ho naeginkrai . Ma driknu ko Keriso .
51002018	Ma kudi kru trua harike tryoko no ko hyena tenam no ripe krogoekeka andyon yaeyosa dyenkra kren . Ya haru gyo daera guae gyo begema kyo andyon hakin dyenaemkin kren kyo duwa wirin haryomoe . Ma kru hakemin ka harinkrai gyo hukwaehukwaemasa kwenknai . Ma ko tyenkrai gyo wike God ya po penkrai ko dima ko hine hya brenknai . Kru hakin ko kae ko ireka , ka hine brenko , ko ko aiya dinkrai .
51002019	Ma ko Keriso dima hine bren ko hro naedina . Ma Keriso yo ko kua ku . Ma ku ko bute ka kudin daenkra . Hamake ya bute drimin tintin bra aiki hen braema . Hamo ya hyenkin ko God ya hoda hamikesa hyenkikraha .
51002020	Ma gyo Keriso yo me pwena dinaekina . Hamo tona , to hyenu me kwoe tikminkrai ko kwasu gyo a tikmi . Ma tenam naemo diwa gyo to hyenu hiya wike dinaeka hwyenkraike .
51002021	Tenam naemo diwa gyo koma hakin hokan dima hine brenkraike . Hi bryoko dirome da mate hoko drome da mate mgakwen tru guryome dinkrai .
51002022	Kudin koma swa hi tyen ko domkmaekina ya swa tyen . Koma hiko wike ka hine bra tyena .
51002023	Ma koma ya trya gyo dumasa wike God ya po penkrai ko dima hine hya braka , hukwaehukwaema hwyaka , ma bute ya hodra ho dima grwine braka hominina . Ma kua diwa hine bren ko koma hi ko bute ya hodra seraku ten dwen braema wirin .
51003001	Ma God yo Keriso yo pwo warmo durkyo asite hokeko gyo me satyomite . Hakina kren , gyo kwoe kom Hewenin ho dima hine brenknai . Keriso yo hokan kingka God yo kuri ya krit dunaete hoke penkra .
51003002	Hamo gua hine bren ko wakansa dima hine brenknai . To hyenu kronam ko hine pya brenkromoe .
51003003	Ma gyo ko tosurina dinaekina . Ma gua ware ko Keriso yome gwemki God yominki hwyenkrai .
51003004	Hamo gua ware teinamnai ko Keriso ya . Ma ya taenku gyo ko taenku gyo hmene ya ai waenukin hokan yo me hureiki .
51003005	Hakina kren gyo , kore aeng tyen ka kronam hakuro kuyenina . Ma gua kron me diwa hoko seri dinkromoe . ( Tenam gryo pya hoda din ko gryo kritme homin ho dima hine pya brena dinaekina . )
51003006	Tenam wike gwin ko kronam hakin homaka mate God ya swa daerinaemka haminkrai kren , God ya ko dima kyomkikraha .
51003007	Ma sem uminki gyo wike hakemin kominki kwaka kronam hiko homamiti .
51003008	Hamo aekwa gyo kronam hakin ko hro naednai . Hamake gyo hamasa kyomkinkromoe . Ma aeng tyaka , kyomkeka haminkromoe . Ma ikaremaka su tyaka haminkraiko , gua mgatramgite mten ko bryoko wirin .
51003009	Hamake gyo matum kraekraema tyo , matum kraekraema tyo haminkromoe . Tenam kronam brunai gua homiti ko hro naedewi kren .
51003010	Ma gyo aekwa ko kronam nin ho saewi . Ma kronam nin hiko God ya homina . Hamo yo kronam hiko homo yae yo bryoko homira . Hamo gyo yo braemknaida .
51003011	Hakina kren Ju wike da mate Ju dinaemkin wike da mate kate tigin wike da mate kate tiginaemkin , wike hakemin ko ko trusa . Ma wike swa ate da mate wike bai dumkin da mate wike hro sen da mate hro senaemkin ko ko drike trusa . Keriso yasa ko drike hyena . Ma ya dure ko gyo butmin gyominki henkra .
51003012	Hakina kren gyo ko God ya wike . Ma yo gyo dima hine pya braka gyo ko yana dite . Hamo gyo proekin kronam me taetaepmin kronam , me irinaemkin me mate kate drukin kronam da mate kyomkinaemkin kronam ko baima bra huma penina .
51003013	Hamake , irinaemka wike gwin ko dima kyomkinaemka mate , wike gwin ka gyo dima swoma homo hamaha dinina .
51003014	Ma kronam hi homakano mate kronam tru ko , wike ko dima proekin me pkori hominina . Hamo gyo pkwo trusa dinaekin ko bryoko .
51003015	Ma Keriso yo kyo kate druki pnaida hin bren daenkra . Ma kua kronam naekin homwerada drurinkrai hin bren hokan kyo dima naegiminkra . Ma God ya gyo uriteko gyo hmene kate druki waenuma praida . Hamo gyo God dima gu ko waenukina harinina .
51003016	Gua proe ko Keriso ya swa waenukin ya aeweha . God ya braemkin ho me , gua wike gwin ko dima matum naegimo matum naegimo haminina . Hamo gyo God ya swa yoke gika , mate Yesu ya swa naegimo gika , mate Dure ya naegimo gika haminknai . God dima yoke gikano hine harike bra gika , God ko duwa dinknai .
51003017	Ma gua kronam naekin homaka mate swa naekin tyaka haminkraiko , Yomkra Yesu ya hi hyenminknai . Hamaka gyo Keriso yo dima tyo mate ya Kuai God dima gu ko duwa dinina .
51003018	Ara kore min gyoke , gua hin ko hirike brenina no kru ko no yomkra dinaekina . Gyo ko Keriso yana kren , gyo hamike hominina .
51003019	Ma kru ara min gyoke , gua runaen ko dima proeka hine pya brenina . Ma ko dima kyomka kronam swokin homromoe .
51003020	Ma kya kuku gyoke gyo Keriso sena kroko guai guaem ka swa daera hominknai . Hamroko , God ya diwa duwa dikraha .
51003021	Ma kru ara kya kuku min gyoke gua kya ko dima kronam naekin homo kya ho proe pyenka gua tyo daera a waenuma homreiki , hakina kren ko dima hamike homina wirin .
51003022	Ma wike hro sen gyoke , gyo , wike gyo twa taerin ka swa daera hominknai . Ma ko gyo ha diraiko , tenam ka gyo dima hine waenuma brunaida kren , gyo tmoe waenuma homrai ho ko bryoko wirin . Tenam gyo God dima hine waenuma brenkrai kren , tmoe waenuma hominknai .
51003023	Ma gyo tmoe naekin homroko , aiki hominknai . Gua hina hirike brenknai tmoe hiko Yomkra ya tmoe , wike ka tmoe homaepu .
51003024	Gyo braema , hoe Yomkra ya tikminkra , ya wike ko dima daemi gyo dima kesu daemi . Tenam Keriso ko , drinu ya gyo hro sena kren , yo ko gua Yomkraha . Hamo gyo ya tmoe hominknai .
51003025	Hamo kru ara dika kronam swokin homina kroko ka ho homiri dware ko hoe direiki . Tenam God yo wike butmin ko kronam trusa begeminkra .
51004001	Ma wike yomkra gyoke , wike gwin gua tmoe homnaida twa taerina ko dima kronam swoma homromoe , waenumasa hominknai . Gyo nononkromoe , gua Yomkra ko Hewen hokan penkra .
51004002	Ma God dima tyenknai . Tyankano , krogoekinaemka hin yoma bra God dima ehya dinina .
51004003	Hamake kua swa kesu God dima tyenina . Gua hirike tyenina , Keriso ya swa sem gwemin naegiminin ten tyaenina dnai . Tenam swa hoa dware no kwasu wogitmin aewe hi praha .
51004004	Hamo gyo God dima tyo , nokwa swa ho waenuma naegimo , wike ko drike yoma sen braema . No hamikesa naegimin ko bryoko .
51004005	Ma gyo braemkisu wike Krwistin dinaemkrai ko dima pitma swa tyenknai . Ma aku dikan ma to dikan gyo Keriso ya swa tyen braema kroko tyenina .
51004006	Ma gyo di dima aku butmin swa tryoko gua swa ko dore waenuka drike minsa ko dima tyenina . Ma ka gyo dima naerike tondaeru diroko gua rwyo tondaeryai hoe ko ko dima dumasa tyenina .
51004007	Ma kua kire Tisika yo ko kru waenukina , hamo yo Yomkra ya tmoe nokwa hominkra hupeko ya gyo dima tyekraha .
51004008	Hakina kren no yo pru gyo dima tikraha . Ma no yo pru kuta kua naemike hominkrai swa ko gyo dima twyo daera saekin braema .
51004009	Ma Onesimas yo ko gua wike , ma yo ko Krwistin kru waenukina , hamo yo Tisika tike ti . Hamo ta gyo dima hokan homrai swa butmin gyo dima twyekraiha .
51004010	Ma Aristasa ko wogitmina nominki hra . Hamo yo gyo dima duwa din swa hre traha . Ma Mak , Banabas ya mote yo kesu gyo dima duwa din swa hre traha . ( Ma kudi Mak yo gyo dima taenku diroko , gua yo tikmnai sem nokwa tya hominina . )
51004011	Josua , ya hi tru ko Jastes , yo kesu , gyo dima duwa dra . Ma kru haepki trumo hiko Ju wike , hamo ko Keriso ya swa ko drinu dinkrai . Hamo ko , God ya wike tikminkra tmoe ho nominki hominkrai . Ma ko waenuma no taetaepminkrai .
51004012	Ma Epapres yo gyo dima duwa dra . Yo kesu gua kireha . Hamo yo ko Yesu Keriso ya tmoe homin kruha . God ya gyo taetaepmnada yo God dima idima tyenkra . Hamo God yo gua hine bren waenuma homo , gyo aikeka kru aiipe ka braemkin hakin gyo ke braemki , mate Keriso ya swa ko drinu da , God ya hodra duma homaka , harike tyenkra .
51004013	No diwa braema , yo gyo dima tmoe idima hominkra . Ma yo to Raodisa me Hireporis wike ko dima kesu tmoe idima hominkra .
51004014	Ma kua dokta Ruk , ma kyo yo dima hine pya brenkrai , me Dimas ti gyo dima duwa din swa hre traha .
51004015	Ma gyo Keriso ya wike to Raodisa hokan prai , ko dima duwa dnai . Ma ara Nimpa me Keriso ya wike ya aewe hokan gaeminkrai , ko dima duwa dnai .
51004016	Ma reta hiko gyo hyaeka naedeno , mate hre to , Krwistin wike to Raodisa hokan gaemrai ka hyaekinina . Ma reta Raodisa wike ka gyo dima hre ta kesu gyoke hyaekinina .
51004017	Ma Akipa yo dima hirike tnya , kire , Yomkra ya tmoe gwa hominkra gu homa wirinmna dnai .
51004018	No ko Por hamo swa hiko nokwa kimra , Gyo waenuma pnai . No hi ko Por . Ma auri sen no krite kwarin hoko nononkromoe .
52001001	Nohi ko Por , hamo nokwa mate Saires , Timoti hamo kyo Keriso ya wike , to Tesaronaika hokan penkrai , gyo dima kwo hi himraiha . Ma gyo ko Kuai God me kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ta wike .
52001002	Kyo aku hyaekin God dima tyaka gyo butmin hamo God dima duwa dinkrai . Hamo kyo gua hi me gua swa kesu yo dima tyenkrai .
52001003	Kyo kuai God dima tryoko kyo braemkrai , gyo kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya swa ko drinu da hamike hwyo kyo dyaewi . Ma gyo yo dima hine pya brenku , tmoe idima homo , kyo dyaewi . Hamake gua Yesu Keriso ya homikra huma po kyo dyaewi .
52001004	Kire , gyoke , kyo braema God , ya gyo dima proeka hine pya braka , gyo ko yanamira ya aripe twete .
52001005	Ma kyo Yesu Keriso ya hupe waenukin gyo dima naegimiti . Ma kyo swasa tmyaepu . Kyo Yomkra ya Dure ya ai me tyaewi . Ma kyo saena swa hamasa tmyaepu . Ma drinu swa tyenkrai hosa tyaewi . Ma gyo braemkewiha , kua kronam gyominki paewi hoke , gyo braemkewi . Ma hoko gyo taetaepminina .
52001006	Ma gyo kua kronam me Yomkra ya kronam bryoko homewi . Ma gyo pyenkin kesu pya dyaewi . Ma gyo swa hoko daerekano yoyomkin me daerewi . Yoyomkin hoko Yomkra ya duregitma pkina .
52001007	Gua hamike hominku , Keriso ya wike to Masadonia me to Akaia hokan penkrai , ko gua hominkrai diwa koke hamike hamwera dewi .
52001008	Ma Yomkra ya swa naegimraiko , pi wyaen dinaekina hamo to Masadonia da mate to Akaia ko butmin hamo totaewi . Ma hokesu gua God ya swa drinu drai hupe hiko to butmin daerewi . Hakina kyo swa tru a tryeiki .
52001009	Ma wike ho ka tyenkrai , kyo gua to dima pkewiko , gyo kyo dima kua aewe dima pknai dewi , ma gua kraekraemin tona ko hro , Tona Hyenu waenukin warmin yo dimasa hine brenkrai . Yasa ko drinu tyenkra . Ma yo dima swa tryoko yo daerin braema .
52001010	Ma gyo God ya kya Yesu , yo yai ya pra hokan hwya msyekra aku ho huma penkrai . Ma ya kya Yesu yo pwo diroko , yai ya homo , hote yo durkyo asite . Ma hamosu God yo kua hweke dima kyomka , begemroko , Yesu ya kyo taetaepmo , kua hweke dware dore a direiki .
52002001	Kire gyoke , gyo braema , kua kuta gyo dima naegimaewiko , kyo drike dyaewi .
52002002	Ma gyo braema , kyo to Tesaronia hokan dima pkenaemka to Piripai hokan po , kyo dima kronam swokin homitiko , ma hokan ko kyo pyenkin hyena dyeti . Ma kua God ya kyo gitka ai kyo dima dae , ya hupe gyo dima tempwen dumka aiki naegimiti .
52002003	Ma kua tyenkrai ko kraekraemin swa wirin . Kyo sere gaemin swa hakin ho hine brenina wirin . Hamake kyo swa atokma tyenkmaepu .
52002004	God ya kyo bryokae diku kyo ya swa tyenkrai . Hamo wike ka kyo tmoe kua homrai ho diwa duwa drnaida wirin . God yasa kyo dima duwa dnada . Tenam God ya kua hin bren me kua proe ko yo diwa braemkra .
52002005	Gyo braema kuasa gyo dima hamasa ti twom me kraekraema tmyaepu . Ma kyo sere dima hine braka , swa handruri tmyaepu . God yo braema .
52002006	Ma kyo wike gwin ka , kua hi hyenmnada haminkmaepu .
52002007	Ma kyo ko Keriso ya tmoe homin wike , hamo kyo kua tmoe homin dware gyo dima tyo , gyo daenaida kentin ko bryoko . Ma kyo gyominki hwyaka swa aiki tmyaepu . Kyo ko ara ka kya kukin tikminkrai ho dinaekina .
52002008	Ma tenam kyo gyo dima hin hyenma braka kyo God ya hupe waenukin gyo dima naegimewi . Ma hosa wirin , gua dware kyo tosurweramaewi . Kyo gyo dima hine pya brenkrai .
52002009	Aenuwe kire , gyoke , gyo braema howa kyo hu aku butmin tmoe tukin idima homaka , gyo dima God ya hupe tya daemewi . Ma kyo tmoe hamike homewiko kuae kua kudin twa taerwera homaewi . Kua gua kudin droko , gyo tmoe hyena homeda .
52002010	Kua kronam ko gyo braema . Ma God ya kesu braema . Kyo Krwistin wike gyo dima hine swokin tru aemaepu . Kua penkrai ko waenuma sa hwyenkrai . Kronam swokin tru wirin .
52002011	Ma kyo braema , kyo , kru trua ya kya ko dima trusa trusama naegiminkra kyo kesu gyo dima hamike naegimewi .
52002012	Kyo gyo dima idima tya naegimeiwi . Keriso ko kua Yomkra dinina deka , ma God ya gyo waenuma tikmira dinkra deka ma gyo naemike hunai God ya gyo diwa duwa droko hamikesa hwyenina dewi . Ma ya wike tikmikra ko yo hoda gyo kesu tikmira hamo ya kaegite hunaida dewi .
52002013	Ma kyo God dima duwa dinkrai drike ko hiwa . Ma kua God ya swa gyo dima naegimo , gyo daera hiko drinu haki dewi , hamo swa hoko God ya swa , wike kaesa hine bra harike tyen braema wirin dewi . Ma drinu , hiko God ya swa . Ma God yo ya swa daerin wike ka hinam hokan ya hine bren ko dima twenkra .
52002014	Kua gmore gyoke , sem Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya wike to Judia hokan penkrai ko dima homiti kronam trusa ho bryoko gyo dima kesu ho homaewiha . Ma hoko gua wike ka gyo dima swoma homewi , Ju wike ka kesu ko dima hamike homiti .
52002015	Ma ko Yesu Keriso yeti . Ma ko sem uminki kua kigwam ko ka kuyeti . Ma ka kesu kyo kuwyeramiti . Ma God yo ko dima kyomkra . Ko wike butmin ko dima kyomkinkrai kren .
52002016	Ma kyo wike , swa ate ko dima ko , Yomkra ya ka hweke hamaha dmaekrai swa ho twyerakuro , ka kua ten dweti . Ko hamike hominku , kronam swokin ka homi tenkrai ko torina howa . Hamo God ya kyom ko kwasu ko dima pkina .
52002017	Nogmore gyoke , kyo gyo kworewi hoke , kyo nononkmaepu gyoko . Kyo gyo dima hine pya braka , hote kuta diwera dinkrai .
52002018	Kyo hoda katma kuta gyo diwera dewi . Ma nokwa aku naemo rwyo kuta gyo dyera da ten ho drurinkra . Ma Saiten ya kua ten dwa .
52002019	Kire gyoke , kua Yomkra Yesu ya rwyo pko diroko , kua gyo yo dima naegimaka , mate kyo gyo me kren , ireka yoyomkeka hamreiki .
52002020	Drinu gyo ko kua irin me kua yoyomkin .
52003001	Ma kua hine braewiko , gyo bryoko praike , ma wirinne , harewi . Hamo kyo huma pra diku hamo kyo Timoti gyo dima pru to ma kyo hikan kumasa hureiki .
52003002	Timoti ko kyominki God ya tmoe homaka mate Keriso ya hupe ho naegimaka hamikra . Hamo kru ho ko pru , gyo dima ta .
52003003	Yo Keriso ya tyen ko hote naegimo pyenkin pko diroko , gyo ware Ten trai hote krwyo ten ate tmeda . Ma gyo braema , pyen hoko , God yo hoda kyo kesu dinaida .
52003004	Ma kyo gyominki hwyeti hoke , gyo dima tyeti kyo hamosu tren me pyenkin me diwekraiha harewi . Haru gyo braemkewi , kronam hoko dumasa hi pkeha .
52003005	Hakina kren no Timoti pru gyo dima ta . No aku pya huma paka hine bra gua penkrai ko naekraike dinkra . Hakina kren no Timoti pru ta . Hamo yo kuta gua Yesu ya swa daeri praikedida ho braemkira . Ma Saiten ya gyo bryoko diwo , gyo toninakroko kua tmoe , gyo dima pya naegimiti hoko , drike dumkina howa de .
52003006	Ma aekwasu Timoti yo rwyo pkere . Ma ya tyere ko gyo God dima hine pya brenkraiko de . Ma gyo gua kire ko dima kesu proeka hine brenkraiko de . Ma ya tya gyo kyo diwera hine pya brenkraiko de . Hote hamo kua gyo diwera hine brenkrai hakina .
52003007	Ya harike tyo , pyen me tren kua dyenkrai ko hamaha de , tenam ya tya gyo Yomkra yominkisa proko , kyo yoyomkinsa preiki .
52003008	Kyo God dima yoyomkrai , gyo waenuma penku .
52003009	
52003010	Hu aku pya kyo proe hyenu tyaka , God dima kentinkrai , kyo kuta gyo diwa , Keriso ya kronam gwin gua braemkinaemkrai ho naegimo , gyo yoma braemkrnaida .
52003011	Ma kyo hoda kuai God me kua Yomkra Yesu tasa kua ten tmyo , kyo gyo diwera twekraiha .
52003012	Hamo Yomkra yo gua proenam ko proekin taetaepmin hine bren hoa gua tyonam aeka hyenknada . Hamroko , gua hine bren ko kua hin bren hakin gyo dima kesu bryoko aen braema .
52003013	Hamo God ya hin bren hakin dae , gyo aiki , Yesu ya wike ko me rwyo pkroko , hamroko gyo guai God ya pra hokan hwyo , begemo , kronam swokin tru a dye .
52004001	Kire gyoke , swa tru tyera , kyo sem gyo dima naegimewi pen kronam diko God ya diwa duwa dinkra ho . Hamo kyo braema , gyo hamikesa homi hwyenkrai . Hamo Yesu ya hinam hi tyera , kronam hoko gyo braemki naedewi kren hosa hamike homo hyenkna .
52004002	Tenam gyo braema , kua Yomkra Yesu ya hinam , kua gyo dima naegewi .
52004003	Ma God ya hoda gyo hweke dumka paka , kore aeng tyenaemka waenumasa penknai dinkra .
52004004	Ma kru trusa trusama gua runaen kominki God ya knon ti me wike ka knon ti bryoko hwyenknai .
52004005	Gua hin ko min psaen ka hin dinaekromoe . Wike dika God braemkinaemkrai ko haminkrai . Ko dinaekromoe .
52004006	Ma Krwistin kru trua ya kire dima kronam swokin hikin homromoe . Kua semina tyaewi ko kru dia hamroko , Yomkra ya dore yo dima daeko dina .
52004007	God ya gyo , taera two , gyo kumta yominki hwyaka kronam swokin homnaida urmaepu .
52004008	Hamo wike dika swa hiko a droko , ko kru ho dima a dmaepu , ko God , yo ya dure gyo dima daenkra , yo dima a draiha .
52004009	Ma gyo wike diko ko kesu Keriso ko drinu drai ko dima hine brenkrai kronam hoko no gyo dima kimra ko drike wirin . Tenam God ya gyo dima sem naegima mate gua ko dima hine bro , ka rwyo matum gyo dima hine bro himinkrai .
52004010	Ma drinu , gyo God ya gire to Masadonia hokan penkrai ko dima proeka hine pya braka , taetaepmaka haminkrai . Ma kyo hoda gyo hamikesa homi hwyaka kronam hoko hyenminknai .
52004011	Ma gyo hine yoma brasu himike hominina gyo grwine bren ko naede , kate druki penina . Wike gwin ka naemike homroko hoko kaesa hamike hominina . Ma gyo hanyai ma no nae no sere tmoesa homi hera dinkrnai . Kua sem gyo dima tyaewi hosa haminina .
52004012	Ma gyo hamike homroko , wike dika , Yesu ko Keriso dinkmaepu , ko gua pitma pen kronam ho diwa , gyo ko wike waenukina din braema . Ma mgakwen , gua buta hodra ko wike gwin ko dima a kentryeiki .
52004013	Sen gyoke , wike tosurin ka penkrai ko gyo tuma braemkrnaida . Hamroko gyo a totokreiki . Wike gwin ko God ya pra hokan pwera huminkmaepu , ko dinaekmeda .
52004014	Kua hine hiko drinusa , Yesu yo pwa naede hote durkyo warka asite . Hakina kren kua hin hi kesu ko drinu swa . God ya , Keriso ko drinu da tosuriti wike ko , Yesu yo me taera ti .
52004015	Swa hiko Yomkra ya tyete , ma Yesu ya rwyo pkin aku hokeko , wike dikua kyo ko ihya me hurai kyo kuatumki a treiki , yae wike sem tosurin ko katumki treiki .
52004016	Ma God ya ai baru ya po penkrai kru trua tyo , God ya kibi uru , Yomkra yo yaesa Kwoe kom hokan hwya msye . Hamo wike dika ko ko Keriso ya wike sem tosurina kroko , ko katumki warkreiki .
52004017	Hamuro ma wike ihya min kyo gaema , wike katumki , kwoe u nam traiko , kyo hmene Yomkra ko durhwap hokan tupmreiki . Hamo kyo Yomkra yominki hokan aepesu hureiki .
52004018	Hamo gua kire ko dima matum hmihmimu matum hmihmimu haminknai .
52005001	Kire gyoke , gyo braema , Yomkra ya rwyo pkin aku swa ko , no hote a kimi .
52005002	Gyo braema hiwa , Yomkra ya pkin aku ko udin wike ka hunam pkinkrai hami .
52005003	Ma wike harwekraiha , kyo ko bryoko prai , grwine bren wirin , kronam ate ate wirin haryeiki . Harekosu domsorin aku ko taenkikraha . Ma domsorin hiko katmasa pki , ara ka kya hamtwera tren dyenkrai hakina . Ma domsorin tren hiko , wike ko krya hwara taka gwemkin braema wirin .
52005004	Ma gyo hunam dinaekin penkmaepu . Hakina kren , aku hoko pko diroko , gyo a gigirmreiki , udin wike ka pko , wike ka diwa girminkrai a hamreki .
52005005	Tenam gyo butmin ko kae ya wike gyo ko hunam ya wike wirin .
52005006	Hakina kren , kyo wike gwin ka krogoe uma aerwenkrai haminina wirin . Hamo kyo wai swokin dua krogoe uma aenaemka hamike pen ko bryoko .
52005007	Tenam hune hokeko wike ko krogoe aenkrai . Ma huneko , ko wai pya dua nononkinkrai .
52005008	Ma kyo ko aku ya wike , hamo kyo krone dro diwa hine bra penina . Ma kyo God ya tyen ko drinu deka , yo dima hine pya braka hamike uroko , hoko kyo napu ma mgenkrai hakina . Ma kua hine brenkraiko , Yesu yo kyo dima heno du ya to dima twekrai hoko kua ku tikmin ko yo .
52005009	Tenam God yo , kyo ya kyom dinaida yo kyo taeri tumaepu . Yo kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso yo gitma hamo kyo ware dinaida .
52005010	Uminki ya kyo dima pwete . Ma kyo ihyama hwyene o ma tosurin hamroko ya pkikra hokeko kyo yominki hwyen braema .
52005011	Hakina kren , gyo gua kire ko dima gua homnai ko waenukina da , aekwa ho homrai haminina .
52005012	Ma kire gyoke , wike dika gyominki tmoe homaka Keriso ya ten waenukin naegiminkrai gyo ko dima hine waenuma brenknai .
52005013	Gyo ko dima hine yoma waenuma bra swa tyenknai , tenam tmoe ka hominkrai kren . Hamo gyo grwin bren dumka , hine bren trusasa waenuma penknai .
52005014	Kire gyoke swa hi kesu tyera , wike dika kudropkroko ko braeme dnai . Ma wike dika tempuroko , ka hine hyenmin swa ko dima tyenina . Hamake wike dika aikinaemkroko ko taetaepminina . Ma gyo wike butmin ka nakoe homroko huma pa dyenknai .
52005015	Ma wike dika gyo dima kronam swokin homroko , gua hoe ko dima homromoe .
52005016	Gyo yoyomnkin mesa penkrai .
52005017	Gyo aku pya God dima swa tyenknai .
52005018	Ma kronam naekin gyo dima pkroko , God dima gu ko duwa dinknai . Gyo Keriso yominki henkra kren , God ya gyo hamike homnai dinkrai .
52005019	Ma Dure Waenukin ya gyo dima tmoe tru homira du , gyo howa wirin dromoe .
52005020	Ma kru trua haryoko swa tru hiko God ya no dima trya du , gyo haryomoe hoko howa wirin dromoe .
52005021	Ma kronam hoko bryoko dinai . Ma dudumadi , diko dukroko ho senina .
52005022	Ma diko swoku diroko hoko siromoe .
52005023	Ma God yo waenuma pen kronam kyo dima daenkra , hamo yaesa gyo tikmu gyo ya kronam dinaekreiki . Hamo me ya gua hine da ma gua dure da ma gua bute ko ya tikmnada . Hamo Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya pkikra hokeko , gua hweke dimeda .
52005024	Ma God ya gyo urite kren , ya gyo homin braema . Ya tyen ko ya dumasa hominkra .
52005025	Kire gyoke , kua hi God dima tyenknai .
52005026	Ma gyo Keriso ya wike ko diwano knaiyaeminknai .
52005027	No Yomkra ya hinam gyo dima tyera , swa kwonam hi kimra ko Keriso ya swa drinu drai wike butmin ko dima hyaeknai .
52005028	Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya proekin kronam ko gyominki aepesu aenknada .
53001001	Por me Saires me Timoti hamo kyo swa hi kwo nam Tesaronia Krwistin wike gyo dima hi kimraiha . Hamo gyo ko Kuai God me Yomkra Yesu Keriso tana .
53001002	Ma ti proekin kronam me waenuma pen kronam gyo dima daemnada .
53001003	Kua kire gyoke , kyo gyo dima aku butmin God dima duwa dinkrai . Hiko bryoko , tenam uminki gyo God ya swa ko drinu dini diti , ma aekwa gyo God ya tyena ko drinu dinkrai . Ma gua proekin kronam uminki ko kukumasa , ma aekwako , gyo wike gwin dima proekinkrai .
53001004	Hamo hamike hominkrai kyo Keriso ya wike ko dikan gaemrai kyo gua swa tyaka irinkrai , tenam wike gwin ko gyo dima a da , kyomka , tren daeko , gyo God ko kwormaepu .
53001005	Hakina kren , kyo braema God ya gyo begemroko yo gyo bryokosa begemi . Hamo God ya wike butmin tikmroko ya gyo kesu tikmi . Hamo gyo aekwa pyenkin diraiha .
53001006	Ma God ya naekin hominkra ko duwasa . Ma wike gyo dima pyenkin daeraiko , hamosu ya ko dima pyenkin dae .
53001007	Hamo gua pyenkin aerako ya homa naedi . Ma kua pyenkin kesu homa wirinmi . Yomkra Yesu ya po penkrai wike ka ai ko deia ruruinkrai hakina ko me Hewen hokan hwya msyo , wike dika God me Keriso ta swa daera a dinkrai ko dima dore daewekraiha . Hamake pyenkin gua dirai ko ya homa naedi .
53001008	
53001009	Hamosu wike hoko dore swokin direiki . Ko Yomkra yo me ya pkori po pen kronam ko ko kworyeiki .
53001010	Ma Yesu ya rwyo pkikra aku hokeko ya wike ko yo dima yoyomka ya hi satyomreiki .
53001011	Hamo kyo aku butmin gua hi ko God dima tyenkrai . Kua tyenkraiko , God ya gyo homo , Keriso ya wike ka penkrai kronamko , gyo hakina penkraida . Ma gyo dukin kronam hoda droko , ya ai me homa naedu , gyo Yesu ya swa ko drinu dinkrai , hoko drinu dreiki .
53001012	Hamroko gua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya hi matum hyenmo matum ya gua hi hyenmo hamake God me Yesu ka proekin kronam hamike hominkrai kren .
53002001	Kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya rwyo kumta kyominki gaemin swa ko hiwa .
53002002	wike ko harewi Yomkra ya rwyo pkin aku ko sem pkina dewi . Ma no gyo dima yoma tyera , hupe hoko daera nononka , no naemawe da hine pyenma bruromoe . Ma gyo hine hrodi , kyo swa gyo dima harike naegimitike . Ma kwo tru kima gyo dima hre ta hoke di .
53002003	Ma wike gwin ka naerike kraekraema tyo diroko drinu dromoe . Aku hoko sem pkmaepu . Hamosu wike pya ko God ko a dusu , kronam swokin yanai , yo marensu Hero dima sye , yo taenkusu , aku hoko pki .
53002004	Ma yo wike ka god dinkrai ho me mate gryogryo di wike ka ho dima guriguri tyenkrai hoko yo a dikraha . Ma yo yaesa hyenmikraha . Hamo ya hari , butmin ko nae dmyaena di . Ma yo kuta God ya aewe Tempo ta paka hari , no ko God di .
53002005	Ma gyo swa hiko nononkewike . No sem uminki gyo minki hete hoke tyete .
53002006	Ma kronam ho pkmaeku ten dwenin ko gyo braema . Ma aku bryokae pkosu , Kru Swokin ho yo taenki .
53002007	Ma Kronam Swokin Gwemkina ko sem komdwa hominkra . Ma kronam hamosu pkikrako , a katma pki , ma kru ya ten dwenin hoko , ka yo sa tosu , kronam hoko pki .
53002008	Marensu Kru Swokin ho yo taenki . Ma marensu Yomkra Yesu ya kumtasu , ya mgatram huhurin ai me ya kae ai yaeyosa hakin home kru ho ye .
53002009	Ma kru swokin hoa Saiten ya hinam kumta ai hyenka tei ate ate kronam pya kraekraema homi .
53002010	Hamake yo wike domsorwekrai , ko dima swa swokin ate ate kraekraema tye . Ma wike hoko gwemkreiki , tenam ko drinu swa daera yoma simaepu krenku . Ma kudi ko sena kroko a gwemkreiki .
53002011	Hamo God ya kraekraemin ya ai pru ka hine nam homo , hamo ka hine bra kraekraemin ko drinu dinkrai .
53002012	Hakina kren , wike dika , God ya swa ko duma dinaemka , kronam swokin dima yoyomka pena kroko , God ya ko begema hoe daekraha .
53002013	Kire gyoke , gyo me kren , kyo God dima ehya dinkrai . God ya gyo dima proekinkra . Uminki God ya gyo seteko , gyo gwemkmeda . God ya dure ya ai me , gyo ya wike yaeyosa haknaida , tenam gyo God ya swa ko drinu dinku .
53002014	God ya gyo haknaida urite . Ya kyo pru Yesu ya swa gyo dima naegimiti . Ma ya gyo Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya ai gyoke taerinina .
53002015	Hakina kren , kire gyoke , drinu swa , kyo gyo dima naegimiti mate kwonam kesu kima hre tete hoko tuma sinai .
53002016	Kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ma kuai God ya kyo dima hine pya brenkra , ma ya proeka tempwen dumka hin yomeka kronam hakin gyo dima daena ,
53002017	hamo ya gua hin taetaepma , ai daemo , gyo swa dukin tyaka kronam waenukin homaka hamin braema .
53003001	Kire gyoke , swa hoekina tyerakrai . Gyo kua hi Yomkra dima tyo , kyo ya swako , to hoehoe tamaka , naegimo wike ko daera , Yomkra ya hi hinaida . Gua daera homiti , koke homnaida .
53003002	Ma hi kesu kua God yo dima tyenina , wike swokin ko kyo domsorweraku diroko , ya kyo taetaepminina dnai . Tenam ya swa kua naegiminkrai ko daera drinu dinkmaepu kren .
53003003	Ma Yomkra ko atmaekina wirin . Yo gua hine taetaepmo aiku , Swokin nai ko ya ten dwe .
53003004	Ma Yomkra yo kyo dima hine bren dae , kyo braemkrai , gua braemkin ko bryoko . Hamo kyo braema , gyo kua tyen daera yae hamo homi kwe kwyenkrai .
53003005	Ma Yomkra yo gua hin dudumo , gyo God ya hine pya braka proekin kronam braemknaida . Ma kate drukin kronam Keriso ya daeminkra ho kesu yo gyo braemknaida .
53003006	Kire , gyoke , kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya hinam gyo dima twyera . Gyo Krwistin wike dika kudropka peskrai ho kua tyeti ko hominaemkrai , wike hakin ko me hwyenina wirin .
53003007	Gyo braema , gyo kesu kua hometi ho bryoko himinina . Kyo gyominki hwyetiko , kudropkmaepu .
53003008	Ma kyo wike ka kudin kyo dima dae diroko , sere me twa taeriti . Kyo hune me aku me tmoe idima homaka , gua sere kyo dima daemeda .
53003009	Ma kua gyo dima naegiminkrai dware hoe kentin ko bryoko . Ma kyo hakina hometi , gyoke diwa homnaida .
53003010	Ma kyo gyominki hwyeti hokeko , kua hariti , wike dika tmoe ko hominaemkroko ko ko kudin dinina wirin diti .
53003011	Kyo swa hi tryai tenam kyo daerewiko , wike gwin gyominki hwyenkraiko kudropkemena . Ma wike gwin ka hominkraiko , ko hamasa tondaetondaeri kwenkrai .
53003012	Hamo kyo Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya hinam wike hakemin ko dima tnyai ko braeme , ko kae ka kudin tmoe homaka , pitmasa penkna dinina .
53003013	Ma gyo kronam dukin homaka kudropkromoe .
53003014	Ma kudi kru trua swa kua kwonam hi kimraiko , yo daera a hominaemkroko yominki tmoe homromoe . Hamrosu yo hukwaekin braema .
53003015	Ma gua kru dima gua totetyen kru mromoe , ma gua gmorema naegimnai .
53003016	Ma kua Yomkra , yo ko waenuma pen yanai . Yaesa waenuma pen kronam gyo dima daenada . Ma yo gyominki penknada .
53003017	Ma swa hiko nae no kritme kimra . No gyo dima duwa dra . No hi ko Por . No himike , no hi ko no kwo reta ti kiminkra .
53003018	Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya proekin kronam gyo dima aenada .
54001001	No ko Por . Ma God ya Yesu Keriso dima tyo , ma ya no dima tyete ko no ya tmoe homna dite . Ma God ko kua kwe . Ma Yesu Keriso yo ko kua ten tmyenin kru .
54001002	Ma Timoti , gu ko no kyanu dinaekina . Kia God dima hine brenkrai ko trusa . Hamo no kwo hi gu dima kimra . Ma kuai God me Yomkra Yesu Keriso ti gu dima waenuma pen kronam da mate dore katma a daemaekin kronam hoko gu dima daenada .
54001003	No hoda gu to Epesis hokan pnada . Ma sem uminki no Mesodonia dima terakra , gu dima tya , ho hote tyerakra . Ma hokan ko wike gwin ka kronam ate ate naegimo diroko , gwa ko gara ka ten duna .
54001004	Ko song swa kae ka hin sa brenkrai . Ka kingwam kahwoe swa hosa tyo wike ko daerekano , ko drike ko diwake dike druri tyo tyo haminkrai . Ho ko hro naendrnai . Ma God ya hodra braemkin ko ya swa duma haki dasu braemkinkrai .
54001005	Ma nokwa swa hi trya drike ko hiwa . Wike gwin ko dima proeka hine pya brenina . Hamroko kua hine ko hine swoswokin a brureiki . Kyo God ya swa ko drinu din braema .
54001006	Ma wike gwin ko kronam hikin ko a dekano , swa ate ate hamasa kutyenkrai .
54001007	Hamo ko hoda God ya koma naegimwera dekano , ma swa ka aiki naegimrai ya drike ko , ko kesu braema wirin .
54001008	Ma kyo braema , koma ko , kyo God ya hine bra tyo ho bryoko homroko , koma hoko duwa .
54001009	Ma koma ko wike dukin ko dima hrimaepu . Wike kronam swokin ko dima hrena . Wike kae ka hodrai sa hominkrai da ma God ko a drai da ma su tyenkrai da ma kai kaem kuyenkrai da ma wike gwin kesu yenkrai , kore aeng tyenkrai da ma kru ko kaesa tmoe hominkrai da ma wike ka kum uma taerinkrai da ma kraekraeminkrai da ma kronam gwin naekin ko kronam waenukin ko a deka haminkrai , koma ko , wike hakemin ko dima aera .
54001010	
54001011	Kronam waenukin hoko , God waenukin ya tyena . Hamo ya tyo hupe waenukin hoko nokwa naegiminkra .
54001012	Ma no kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ko dima duwa dra . Tenam ya hine bra no ya tmoe waenuma homikraha da ya ai no dima daete .
54001013	Aenuwe no sem uminki ko , no yo dima ikaremaka yo dima kronam swokin homaka homite . Ma nokwa hamike homite ko , tenam Keriso ko , no handuma braemkmaepu , ma no ya swa ko drinu dmaepu . Ma yo no dima dore katma daemaepu . Yo no dima proeka hine pya bra , ya tmoe no dima dae homrnada .
54001014	
54001015	Ma swa hi tyen ko drinu , hamo gyo drinu pryaha dinina . Yesu Keriso yo to hyenu hikan dima pkete ko wike ka hweke hoe sera pkite . Ma kronam swokin hominkrai hya ko nokwa .
54001016	Ma Yesu yo no hweke dware dore katma daemaepu . Ma yatumki ko ya pa dyen kronam no dima naegimite . Marensu wike gwin ko Keriso ko drinu da ko dyaen dyaen huwekraiha , ko no kronam dyen braema .
54001017	Ma kua Yomkra God , ya sa aepesu henkra , yo ko pwen braema wirin , ma wike kato yo dyen braema wirin , ma ya kin tei atkin ko yo dima yae aepesu aenkrna da ya hi hiwe .
54001018	Ai , Timoti , wike sem gu dima tyaewi , gu tmoe waenuma aiki hominkrna dewi .
54001019	Ma gu God ya swa ko drinu da , hine waenumasa brenkrna . Ma wike gwin ka hine bra tyenkrai dukin sa homna du ko daerinkmaepu . Ma God ya swa ko drinu drai ko domsorewi .
54001020	Ma kru Haiminia me Aresaenda ti hamike homroko , no ko kworu , Saiten ya ti dima dore daekraha . Ko God dima su tmyeda .
54002001	Ai , swa hya ko hiwa , no hoda gu God yominki swa tryoko , wike gwin ka swa yo dima tyo , ya ko taetaepmnada . Ma yo dima kesu duwa dinina .
54002002	Ma kua Gaman da ma kua yomkra gwin ka hi me ka swa ko God dima tyenkrna . Hamo kyo grwine brenaemka , waenuma paka , God ya hodra ho homi pen braema .
54002003	Kyo hamike homroko , God , kua taetaepmin kru , ya hin hi ko duwa din braema .
54002004	Ma yo hoda wike butmin ko ya kronam nu braemku yaesa ko tikmo Saiten ya tikmin ko hro naendrnada .
54002005	Ma God ko trusa . Ma ganeswamin kru tru ko God mo wike mo dure hokan hra , ho ko kru Yesu Keriso .
54002006	Yo ko wike butmin kua rauwetyenin kru . Ma aku God ya swa gumite hoko taenkuro , ya wike butmin kua hweke dware pwete .
54002007	Hamo God ya no ya swa hi wike swa ate ate ko dima dumasa tyadaemrada sa hrete .
54002008	Hamo gyo sos hokan gaemraiko no hoda kru diko God yana dina ka krite hatyoma haka , ko grwin bren naende , ma kronam swokin homin naende , God yominki swa tyenina .
54002009	Ma ara ko kesu , ko bai , sere hyehyenka kineka , waenukin , twa taera bro , kru ka dinaida brenina wirin . Bai , sere kuka waenukin ho twa taera brenina . Ma yokingai twoi armin da mate kore hakin arma ka kerebrin yabrenina wirin . Hamake ka ku kesu pripriminina wirin .
54002010	Ma ara , diko God yana dinkrai , ka kine ko wike taetaepminina .
54002011	Ma ko swa naegimo , ara ko swa dumka , kate druka , daeriskinina .
54002012	Ma ara ka naegimrai ko no heno dinkmaepu . Hokesu ka kru ko ka yomkraki ko no a dra . Ko swa dumka penina .
54002013	Tenam God ya Adam ko yatumki homite , ma Ibi ko maresu homite kren .
54002014	Ma Adam ko Saiten ya kraero , yo totmaepu . Ma Ibi su toti hweke komdwa hrete .
54002015	Ma ara dika ko God ya swa ko daera drinu deka , yo wike gwin proeka hine pya kate druki God ya penkra hamo paka , kya ko hamtwerakuro , God yo ara hoko tikmikraha .
54003001	Ma wike ko harinkrai , ma kru diya ko Keriso ya wike tikmira droko , yo tmoe waenukin hodaha .
54003002	Ma wike gwin ka Keriso ya wike tikminkra ko , yo kronam swokin homra ko dike swa tyen ko bryokaemaepu . Ma yo ko ara trusa . Hamo yo pitmasa paka , hine yoma waenuma bra , swa waenuma naegima , swa gan tyenaemka paka , wike koesin ko dima tyo kumta no aewe kudua swa tye pwe dinin kru hakin ko bryoko .
54003003	Ma yo wai kyomkin pya dua kyomkin kru hakin ko bryoko wirin . Yo pitmasa paka kate druka hakin ko bryoko . Hamake yo swa kyokyo tyenina wirin .
54003004	Yo yae ya gire ko waenuma tikminina . Hamake ya kya ko kai ya tyo daera pitma hominina .
54003005	Tenam yae ya gire ko waenuma tikminaemkroko , yo naemike God ya gire ko waenuma tikmin braemane .
54003006	Ma kru di yo Yesu ya tra kwatema komdwa troko , gyo kru hoko sa tikmin tmoe daeromoe , pako yae yo rwyo ireko , Saiten ya hoe ya sena ho bryoko yo kesu simeda .
54003007	Hamake wike Krwistin dinaemkrai ko kesu ya kronam diwa , kru hoko duwa du , kru hosa senina , pako yo taka Saiten ya dainam hokan tota hukwaekmeda .
54003008	Ma dikon wike , ko kesu ko gyo wike gwin ko ko dima waenuma hine bro diwa , kosa taerinina . Ma ko swa gan rereka , swa hamasa ti twom me sa tyaka , wai kyomkin pya deka , sere hyena siwera drai wike ko taeriome .
54003009	Ma wike diko God ya swa ko daera drinu da , hin haepki brenaemkrai wike taerinina .
54003010	Ma yatumki ko tmoe gwin ko dima dae homaka , ko tmoe swokin homu dyenaemkusu ko taetaepmin tmoe taerin ko bryokaera .
54003011	Ma ka runaen ko , ko kesu swa hamasa tyenaemka , wike ko hweke hrirai hamasa taen tya kwenina wirin . Ko hamasa yoyomka , tmoe handuma hominaemka haminina wirin .
54003012	Ma dikon wike ko kae ka runaen trusa trusama taerinina . Hamo kae ka kya kuku da ma gire gwin da mate ka kudin me gryogryo butmin ko waenumasa tikminina .
54003013	Tenam taetaepmin tmoe ho ko waenuma homroko , ka hoe dinaekin ko wike gwin kato wike hoko waenukina dinkrai . Ma hokesu ko Yesu Keriso ya swa ko drinu da wike gwin naegimin braema .
54003014	Ma no hamosu kumta gu dyera hine brura . Ma kudi no katma pkenaemkroko , kronam tru taenku diwa , hamo no kwo hi kimra , gu God ya wike ko naemike penkrai hoko braemkrnada . Ma ya wike ko , God yo aepesu henkra ya aewe Tempo ko ko howa . Ko ko ya aewe hruke dinaekemina , ko drinu swa tye hwyenkrai .
54003015	
54003016	Ma drinu , God kua braemkrai ko yae atkina . Yo wikma hamteti , ma ya dure ko hweke me wirin . Ma yo ta , God ya po penkrai wike ko dima taenkite . Ma wike ko ya swa ko wike to hyenu hoe hoe hokan penkrai ko dima naegimo daera drinu haki dinkrai . Ma yo aekwa kin tei atkina hamo kwoe kom hokan pra .
54004001	Ma Dure waenukin yo sem dumasa tya , marenku wike gwin ko God ya swa ko drinu dinkrai hoko naendreiki . Hamo ko hohorinai ka swa mate tona ka swa daerieiki .
54004002	Ma swa hoko , kraekraemin wike ka twyekraiha . Ma ko domsorwekrai hoko ko hine brumaepu .
54004003	Ka naegiminkrai ko , ara taerin ko koma , mate kudin gwin din ko koma harinkrai . Ma kudin hoko God ya homite , hamo wike God ko drinu drai ma ya swa ko duma trya kyo God dima duwa dasu dinina .
54004004	
54004005	Gyo God dima twyasu dinku , God yo bryoko dinkra .
54004006	Ma gu swa hiko Keriso me kua goe gmore ko dima naegima tryoko , gu ko Yesu Keriso ya tmoe homin kru waenukina . Swa gu dima sem naegimite ho ko gu hine bra hominkrna .
54004007	Ma God ko a deka , kraekraemin ma tryoko swa hoko gu kesu gu a dna . Gu gwae gwa hin ko pitma tikmna .
54004008	Ma gwa bute tikma , swa reri kapoe sen ko duwa , ma God ya hodra homin ko waenukina , tenam hoko kyo hikan prai taetaepmaka , ma pwo diroko hokesu tataepmin braema .
54004009	Ma swa hi ko drinu , hamo gyo hine brenina . Hamo kyo tmoe idima hominkrai , tenam God yo ko warmin kru yo aepesu henkra , yo ware aepesu henin ko wike butmin ko dima daen braema , ma ya swa ko drinu drai wike ko dima ware aepesu henin daenkra .
54004010	
54004011	Hamo swa hiko wike ko dima naegimo ka hominina .
54004012	Ma wike ka harmaudi , gu ko kwaten kru sa harmaudi , hamaha drome . Ma gu kronam waenukin homaka , swa waenukin tyenina . Hamaka wike gwin ko dima proeka hine pya bra , God ko drinu deka , hine waenumasa brenina . Hamo Keriso drai wike ko kronam ho diwa , ko kesu hamike homin braema .
54004013	Ma wike ko gaemo diroko , God ya swa Kwonam kimin ho , wike ko dima hyaeka , drike ko dima naegiminina . Ma no kesu pkroko hamike hami .
54004014	Kronam gwa homaekin , God ya gu dima daea hoko , wike yomkra ka krite gwa ku ti hraewi hoke sa , hro naendrome .
54004015	Gu kronam hoko aku pya hominina . Hamroko , wike gwin ko gwa waenuma tra ho dyen braema .
54004016	Ma braeme , gwa hin ko naemike brenkra ma gwa naemike naegiminkra ko . Ma gu hamike sa naegimi troko , gwae gu taetaepmo mate wike gwa tyo daerinkrai ka kesu gu taetaepmin braema .
54005001	Ma gu wike yomkra ko dima kyomkrome . Ma yo dima tyerakroko , gwai dima tyenkra harike sa tyenkrna . Ma kwaten kru ko dima ko gwa gmore ko dima tyenkra ho bryoko tyenkrna .
54005002	Ma ara sem ari ko dima kesu , gwaem dima tyenkra harike tyenkrna . Ma ara paku ko dima ko gwa gwauke , gwapoe ko dima tyenkra harike tyenkrna . Ma ko dima hine waenukina sa brenina .
54005003	Ma ara diya yo ko kwire nu kroko , ko dima hine pya brenina .
54005004	Ma ara kwire hoko ya kya kuku ko pene , ma ya kyankya ko paka God ya tmoe homwera droko , ko yatumki kae ka gire ko dima tikminina . Kai kaem ka ko tikmiti kren , kwasu ka rwyo ko tikminina . Tenam God ya hoda kyo hamike homrnai dinkra .
54005005	Ma ara kwire nu drai , yo taetaepmin wike ko wirin sa , yae yo kumasa penkra hamo ya hoda God ya yo taetaepmnada droko yo hu aku butmin yo dima kentinkra .
54005006	Ma di yae ya bute sa tikmira droko , yo ko sem pwena dinaekina .
54005007	Hamo swa hiko tyenina , wike gwin ka gyo duma homo dimaepu dmeda .
54005008	Ma kru diya yo ya wike ko pitmasa tikminaemkroko , yo God ya swa ko drinu dinkmaepuha . Hamo God ya swa ko drinu wirin drai wike ko ko duwa wirin ma God ya swa ko drinu dano , ma ya gire ko waenuma tikminaemkroko yo ko swoswokina .
54005009	Ma ara kwire diya ya hoda ya hi kimna droko , ya ambum ko pya ( 60 ) hamo sena , ma yo kru sem sen so paka ari kroko ya hi kiminina .
54005010	Ma wike gwin ka harike tryoko yo ko duwa no droko , ma ya kya kuku pitma tikmo ma wike ka ya aewe dima pko kudin daemaka , ma Krwistin wike ko taetaepmaka hamaka , hamroko ya hi kimin ko bryoko .
54005011	Ma ara kwire tru ya ambum ko pya wirin kroko , ya hi kimrome . Tenam ko kru taerwera hine braka ko Keriso ya tmoe hro naendmeda .
54005012	Ma ko sem swa guma tyen hoko kiroko , ko a dreiki .
54005013	Ma ko himike hominkrai , ko tmoe handuma hominaemka , kuta aewe tru aewe tru swa hamasa tyenkrai . Ma ka tryai hoko taen tyen ko bryoko wirin .
54005014	Hakina krenku , no hin ko ara paku kwire ko hote kore sa , kya bra iwasu , ka gire ko pitma tikminina . Hamroko , wike ka kyo dima grwin brenkrai , ko kyo dima swa swokin tyen braema wirin .
54005015	Tenam gwin ko sem Keriso ko hro , Saiten ya tra mare taewi .
54005016	Ma ara diya yo ko Keriso yana ma ara kwire tru ko ya wike kroko , ya yo tikminina . Hamroko Krwistin wike gwin ko tmoe hoko ko dima daenina wirin . Hamo ara diko kwire nu kroko , Krwistin wike ko ko taetaepmin braema .
54005017	Ma wike dika ko yomkra tmoe waenuma homroko , ko dima hine pya brenina . Ma wike di ko God ya swa tyadaemaka , naegimaka hamroko , ko dima hoe haepki daenina .
54005018	Tenam God ya swa Kwonam kimina aera ko , ware gryogryo ko gua tmoe homroko , gyo ya mgatram kwari , aene sa dwo kudin daenaemkinkrai hamromoe . Ma Kwonam kimin tru ko hiwa , kru diya yo tmoe homroko , ya hoe senina .
54005019	Ma kudi kru trua kumta yomkra wae ko hweke hrere ko droko swa hoko daera katmasa drinu drome . Ma kudi kru haepki o haepki trumo ka kumta hene , yo drinu hweke hrere dusu , hoko drinu dna .
54005020	Ma wike diko kronam swokin homo diwa sa kumta , wike ko gaemroko kronam ka hominkrai ko hote homromoe dinina . Hamroko gwin ko daera tempwa a hamreiki .
54005021	No ko God me Yesu ma ta po penkrai wike ka kinaengite henkra , hamo nokwa gu dima trya hiko dumasa hominina . Ma wike gwin sa begemaka , ma wike gwin ko ko no kire kren a begemi , hariome .
54005022	Ma wike diko God ya tmoe homwera droko , hamo gu katma gwa krite God ya tmoe homira dra ya kuo ti hriome . Pako hweke ya hrenkra gu ke homeda . Gu pitmasa prna .
54005023	Ma gu wai nu sa dinina wirin , gu wai wain kesu kukumasa dinina hamo gwa gen tren me mate tren gwin gu aku pya dyenkra ho taetaepminina .
54005024	Ma wike gwin ka hweke ko wike ko dyen braema . Hamo hoko begeminkrai . Ma wike gwin ka hweke ko hamosu taenku dyen braema .
54005025	Hote ho bryoko , kronam waenukin ko topkyenku dyen braema . Ma katma dyenaemkroko , marensu taenku dyen braema .
54006001	Ma wike diko ko ko tmoe homnaida hro sena kroko , kru ko hro sen ko dima hine pitma brenina . Pako wike ko God ma kua naegiminkrai ho dima hine pitma brumeda .
54006002	Ma kudi kru ko hrosen ko Krwistin kroko , wike ka hro sen ka ko kagoe dinaekina kren , ka ko dima swa swokin hamasa tyenina wirin . Ko ka tmoe ko aiki hominina , tenam kru ko hro sen ko God ya wike hamo ko ko dima hine pya brenkrai .
54006003	Ma kudi kru trua yo swa hikin ko yo a da , ate naegimaka , Yesu Keriso ya tyete ko yo a da , ma God ya hin ko yo a dinkra .
54006004	Hamroko yo ireka , nononka hamasa gwoegwoeka grwine bren swa kutyenkra .
54006005	Hamo wike gwin ko irin me kutyaka , ma ka ku ko krwyo nononka , duma tyenaemka swa swokin da ma hine swokin brakano drinu swa God ya tyen ko nononkinkrai . Hamo ka hin ko God dima tryoko , kyo sere me gryogryo pya taerwekraiha dinkrai .
54006006	Ma drinu kyo God yo minki swa tryoko kua sen ko hyena , tenam naekin kyo dima aeroko hoko bryoko dinkrai .
54006007	Ma kyo to hikan dima pketi hoke , gryo tru sapkmaepu . Hamo kyo to hi ko hro troko gryo tru saten braema wirin .
54006008	Ma kyo ko kudin me bai me bryoko aeroko , kyo bryoko dinkwe .
54006009	Ma wike dika ko sere hyenma taerwera dinkrai ko Saiten ya dainam taka totwekraiha . Hamo dai hoa hin kwaru nononka pyenkin diwekraiha .
54006010	Tenam sere dima hine pya bren ko hweke teinam . Ko ho siwera hine pya brenku , ko God ya swa drinu drai dinkrai ko hro naende proe pyenkin dyaewi .
54006011	Ma kire , gu ko God ya wike hamo gu kronam hakin ko hamrome . Ma gu God ya kronam ko homaka , ya swa drinu deka , wike gwin ko dima proeka hine pya braka , kate druki penina .
54006012	Ma gu Keriso ya swa ko drinu da troko , ho ko hwemkinkrai ho bryoko . Hamo gu aiki hwemkeka hoe ko ware dyaen dyaen God ya gu senina de , hoko yoma sina . Ma ware dyaen dyaen hi sinada God ya gu urite . Wike pya ka kron ti hokan gwa hweke hro naendu God ya hamaha du no ware dyaen dyaen sere ko du daerewi .
54006013	Ma God yo ko ware daenkra kru yo pra , ma ya pru pken kru Yesu , yo Ponties Pairet yo dima swa waenuma taen tyete , yo kesu pra .
54006014	Hamo no gu dima yoma hi tryaha , God ya gu homna de hoko yoma hominina . Yesu Keriso yo rwyo pkosu naendin braema .
54006015	Ma aku God ya hyete hoko bryokaesu taenkikraha . Ma God ko ai butmin yo dima aera , yo ko yomkra hyena , ma king butmin ka yomkra ko yo sa .
54006016	Yo aepesu yae hamo henkra . Ma ya penkra ko k'ae yaeyosa hakina . Kyo kuta kurin braema wirin . Ma kru truato yo dimaepu , ma kru trua yo dyen braema wirin . Kyo yo dima hine waenuma brenkwe . Ya sa kyo dyaen dyaen tikmin ko bryoko . Drinu .
54006017	Ma wike dika ko ko grygryo namin wike kroko , ko dima trnya , ko kae rwyo iriomoe . Ma gryo katma domkmaepu ho dima hine pya brenina wirin . God dima sa hine pya brenknai . Yo gryo gryo pya kyo dima daenkra ko kyo yoyomkrnaida .
54006018	Hamo wike ko dima tyna ko tmoe ate ate waenukin hominina . Hamo wike gwin ko dima kesu gryo ma sere pya hamo daeminina .
54006019	Hamosu gryo ko bryoko ae . Hamrosu ko drinu hwyenu huwekraiha .
54006020	Hamo Timoti , gu God ya gu dima daea hoko pitma tikmna . Hamake wike gwin ko swa drike dumkin kraekraema tyaka hi ko braemkinina dinkrai , hamo swa hoko gu me tyo tyo haminina wirin .
54006021	Ma wike gwin ka harewi , kyo sem braemkin kronam saewi , ma ko God ya braemkin hro naendewi .
55001001	No ko Por , no ko Yesu Keriso ya tmoe homin kru . Tenam God ya pru no kuta ware swa ya sem swagumite ho , hamo kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso yominki pkori henkra ho naegimrada .
55001002	Timoti , gu ko no kya , hamo no hoda gu dima kwo hi kimira . Hamo Ai , hoko God , me kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ta waenuma pen kronam me kate drukin me ganeswamin kronam hamo gu dima daenada .
55001003	No God dima duwa dinkra . No ya tmoe homaka , no hina ya tmoe ko no swoma homaepu dinkra . No kigwam ka homiti hakina hominkra . Hamo no huaku butmin God dima tyaka no gua hi hiwa yo dima ehya dinkra .
55001004	Gwa byen ko no nononkmaepu . Ma no hoda gu dyera hine pya brenkra . Hamo no gu diwa yoyomkira .
55001005	No braema Yomkra ya swa ko drinu sen ko gwa hwoe Roasi me gwaeme Unise ta drinu sen ho bryoku gu kesu sena howa .
55001006	Hakina kren gu nononkrome , no krite gwa ku ti hrete hoke , God ya proekin gu dima daete hamo hoko pitma tikmna .
55001007	Tenam Dure , God ya kyo dima daenkrako , yo tempwen kyo dima daenkmaepu . Ya ai me proekin me kuae kua hine tikmnai da kyo dima daenkra .
55001008	Hakina kren kua Yomkra ya swa naegimroko , gu hukwaekrome . Ma no dima kesu hukwaeme , ma no wogitmin aewe hikan pra , Keriso ya swa naegiminkra kren . Ma pyenkin gu dima pkrako , tenam gu hupe waenukin naegiminku , hamo God ya ai gu dima daen ho me , homina .
55001009	Ma ya kyo taetaepmite kren , kyo a gwemkreiki . Tenam yo hoda kyo ko yana mirakinku . Ma ya hamite , tenam kua homiti ho wirin , tenam yae ya proea hodra ho homite . Ma yo proekin hiko , sem aku hiko pkinaemkin hoke , yo Keriso pru , ya kyo dima daete .
55001010	Ma aekwa ya kyo dima kua ware daen kru Yesu Keriso yo gitma naegimite . Ma pwene ya aiko , ya hoe yete . Hamo hupe waenukinko , ho hre pko , ware dyaendyaen naegimite .
55001011	God ya no pru ya hupe waenukin ho naegimnada .
55001012	Hakina kren no pyenkin hi dyenkra . Ma no braema yo no tikminkra , tenam no braema , ya swa ko drinusa . Ma no braema ya no dima daete hoko ya tikma , aku ho pkosu naedi .
55001013	Hamo drinu , swa nokwa gu dima naegimite hoko gu yoma homnada . Ma drinu din , me hin bren kua sen , tenam kyo ko Yesu Keriso yominki hominkrai kren , hoko hro naedrome .
55001014	Ma Dure Waenukin yo kyominki henkra ya ai dae , kronam waenukin gu dima dae gu tikmna din , hoko pitma tikmna .
55001015	Gu braema wike butmin to Asia penkrai ko taewi . Hene ma Paigeres me Hemogenes ti kesu , no hro taewi .
55001016	Hamo Yomkra yo Onesipores ya gire me ko dima proeknada . Tenam ko aku pya no taetaepmo no yoyomke . Tenam no ko wogitmina henkra hamo ya no dima hukwaekmaepu .
55001017	Ma yo to Rom taenkino yo dumasa no dyera drure . Drureka no dya .
55001018	Hamo Aku ho pko diroko Yomkra ya yo dima proeknada . Ma to Epeses hokan ya no taetaepmite ko gu braema howa .
55002001	Ai gu aikna . Proekin kronam ko kyo sem sena . Tenam kyo Yesu Keriso yominki hurai kren .
55002002	Ma gu swa nokwa naegimo gu me wike pya ko daerewi , swa hoko sa , wike dika kyo braema ko kraekraemin braema wirin , ko dima naegimo , ko kesu wike gwin naegimo haminkrai .
55002003	Ma gu kesu pyen dyenkna . Gu ko Yesu Keriso ya ami kru kren .
55002004	Ma amiko , tote tiroko , yo ami yomkra ya yo dima duwa dnada hamo ya tmoe ko wike gwin ka hominkrai hamike a homi .
55002005	Ma swa rerin kru trua resi dira hwemkeka yo homnaidin hoko daerinaemkroko yo hoe sen braema wirin .
55002006	Ma kru diya sanam tmoe hyena homroko , kudin gaemin aku hokeko ya hya senina .
55002007	Gu nokwa hi kimra hine bruna . Tenam Yomkra ya taetaepmo gu drike butmin sen braema .
55002008	Gu Yomkra Keriso braemkna . Yo pwa durkyo asite . Ma yo ko Debid ya kyankya . Hamo no hupe waenukin naegimo ho kesu naegiminkra .
55002009	Tenam no hupe waenukin naegiminkrako , no pyenkin dyenkra . Ma no hweke hyena hrena dinaeka no krite ko auri sen me kwarina . Hamo God ya swa ko auri sen mena wirin .
55002010	Hakina kren no pyenkin butmin diwa , hamaha da , hiko bryoko dinkra , tenam God ya wike ko me kren . Tenam ko ri gwemkinaemkin koke sinaida . Ma hiko Yesu Keriso yo hre kyo dima pkina . Ma hiko pkeka , kine waenukin dyaendyaen dyenin kesu sapkina .
55002011	Hiko drinu swa tyena . Ma kyo yominki pwena kren , kyo yominki hureiki .
55002012	Ma kudi kyo pyenkin diwa tempwenaemkroko kyo yominki yomkraka hwyen braema . Ma kudi kyo yo dima kyo gu braema wirin droko , ya kesu kyo dima no kesu gyo braema wirin dikraha .
55002013	Ma kudi kua harano , ya swa ko drinu dano ma kyo swa hoko hominaemkroko ya homirada tyen ko ya homi . Tenam yae yo dima kraen braema wirin .
55002014	Ma swa hiko hote tyo wike ko braemknaida , tenam gyo God ya kron ti hwyenkrai kren gua braeme . Gyo swa dware grwine brenkromoe dna . Swa hikin tryoko ya hoe ko a duki . Hamroko wike pa daeryai ko domsorinkrai .
55002015	Gu tmoe waenukinsa hominkra kren , God ya kron ti hukwaekinkmaepu , tenam God ya swa drinu tyen ko dumasa naegiminkra kren . Ma gu hamikesa homi troko , God ya gu dima gu ko waenukina din braema .
55002016	Ma wike dika God ya swa Kwonam kimin ko hyaeka hiko drinu wirin dini da mate swa drike dumku hamasa tryai kominki gaema kurome . Swa hikin ko wike kruru God kwori wenma tenkrai .
55002017	Swa harike naegimrai ko wonama saio dinkrai hakina . Kru haepki ta harike naegimewi ta hi ko Haimenes me mate Pirita ta .
55002018	Hamo ti drinu swa tyenkrai ko hre diroko ma Keriso ya wike gwin ko God ya swa ko drinune ma wirinne harike hin brenkrai , tenam ta tyenkraiko , kyo sem durkyo asina dinkrai .
55002019	Ma god ya hruke aikin yen ko gyogyotma kirin braema wirin . Ma swa hiko hokan kimina , Yomkra yo braema wike yana ko . Ma truko , ma wike dika kyo ko Yomkra yana droko , kronam swokin ka hominkraiko hro naednai .
55002020	Ma aewe hyenu tyonam hokanko , dise me mereki tei ate ate pya aerurai . Gwin ko sirba me homina . Ma gwin ko gor me homina . Ma gwin ko dei hohomina ma gwin ko to dronge me homina . Ma gwin ko , yae aeku , aku susupmasa hominina . Ma gwin ko , aku butmin hikansa hominkrai .
55002021	Ma kru ara diya kronam swokin , ko hro naedroko , God ya tmoe , yaeyosa hakina yo dima daen braema . Tenam yatumki ko yae yo Yanai dima daenku , tmoe dukin butmin yo homaekina , hamo Yanai ya tmoe yaeyosa hakina yo dima daen braema .
55002022	Ma kwaten kru ka hodrai hoke trome . Ma kronam dukin me drinu din me mate hine pya bren da mate kate druki waenuma pen kronam hakin homwe dinkna . Hamaka gua hine ko hweke dumka paka Yomkra ya taetaepmnada urinkna .
55002023	Ma wike dika hin dumka swa swokin hin grua tmyaekin kominki grwin brurome . Gu braema hoe ko grwin bren hyena .
55002024	Ma Yomkra ya tmoe homakano grwin brenkrome . Yo wike butmin ko dima proekinkna . Yo ko kyomkinaemka waenuma naegiminkna .
55002025	Ma God ya swa a drai wikeko , ko dima kate druki , ka tryaisa duduma hominkna . Tenam dikani God ya ko dima tyo ko krwyo drinu swa daera braemkmaudi .
55002026	Hamo Saiten ya sa ya dainam hre ya tmoe hominkrai , hamo ka nononkin ko hro , krya ten braema .
55003001	Gu braemkna , hoe yen aku hokeko , pyen hyena pki .
55003002	Wike ko grimeka , irika , sutyaka , kai kaem ka swa daerinaemka , wike gwin ka ko taetaepmo ko dima duwa dinaemka , God dima hine brenaemka hamreiki .
55003003	Ko proekinaemka , wike gwin ka hi domsoreka , kyomka , ko kronam dukin diwa ko a deka , hamreiki .
55003004	Ko kraekraema wike domsoreka , kae ka bute tikminaemka , ka ku ko rwu ireka , hamake ma ka hodraisa yoyomkin me homaka , God ya hodra ko a yoyomkinme , homreiki .
55003005	Ka hisa ko God ya wike da , ma ko God ya ai ko a dinkrai . Hamo gu wike hakemin kominki kwenkrome .
55003006	Ma wike hakemin gwin ko wike gwin ka aewe ta ara aikinaemkinko , ka yomkrakinkrai . Ara hoko hweke ka twenko , kaesa begema ko ko hweke min ara da , ka hweke ho dima hine pya brenkrai . Hamake ara ho ka hine bra homwe drai ko ate ate .
55003007	Ma ka tyenkrai , kyo braemkwera diskinkrai . Ma ko swa driknu braemkin braema wirin .
55003008	Hamo sem Janes me Jambres ti Moses ya tyenko , ko a diti , hote ho bryoko wike hoko swanu ko a dinkrai . Ma ka hine handuma brenkmaepu . Ma ko God ya swa drinu ko dumahaki dinkrai ma ko handuma wirin .
55003009	Ma ko ten wenkin ten braema wirin . Tenam ko hamako , wike gwin ka nononkin direiki . Hote ho bryoko ko Janes ma Jambres ti dima hamike hometi .
55003010	Hamo gu nokwa naegiminkra , da mate nokwa hodra hamike hominkra . Ma gu nokwa dumahaki me mate nokwa kate druki padyeskin me mate no proekin ko gu dyenkraha .
55003011	Mate ko no yo , no tren diwo , gu dyeteko , to Antiok da mate to Ikoniem da mate Ristra hokan no dima hamike homitiko . Ma ka no dima kronam swokin homitiko , no padyeskite .
55003012	Ma wike dika hoda Yesu yominki haka God ya tmoe homwera droko wike gwin ko kronam pyenkin ko dima daen braema .
55003013	Ma wike kronam swokin hominkrai da mate kraekraemin wike ko kronam swokinsa aku butmin hominkreiki . Ma ko wike gwin dima kraekraeminkrai ko mate kae rwyo ko dima kraenkrai .
55003014	Ma swanu gu dima naegimo , gu drinu dite , hoko tuma sina . Kru gu naegimiti ko gu braema .
55003015	Ma gu braema gu kyan hokesa hwya , God ya swa Kwonam kimin ho komdwa braemkite . Ma ya swa hoko Yomkra ya braemkin gu dima daen braema . Ma Yesu Keriso yo dima dumahaki dinku braemkin hoa gu hipya gwemkinaemkin sunam dima ten braema .
55003016	Ma God ya swa Kwonam kimin butminko , God ya dure ya wike ko dima naegimo , ka kimiti . Hamo swa nu Kwonam kimin hoa ten kweroma homo diwa hamike homrome da , duma homnaida naegimin braema . Hamike waenuma pen kronam kesu naegiminkna .
55003017	Hakina kren , kru ara dika God ya tmoe hominkraiko , ko tmoe dukin ate ate butmin braemkin braema .
55004001	Hamo ihyamin me tosurin me ko God me , Yesu Keriso ta kinaetegite hwyo , Yesu ya ko begemi . Ma ya kingka kumtasu wike ko tikmi . Hamo nokwa ta kron ti gu dima yoma hi tyera ,
55004002	God ya swa naegiminkna . Wike ka gu garme , gu asi yoma aima tyenkna . ( Ma aekwa ko naegimin aku o ma naegimin aku wirin . ) Gu yoma naegimakadi kronam swokin diroko hamike homromoe deka , mate dukin homo diroko hamike homnai da kate druki huma penkna .
55004003	Hamosu wike ko swa drike men a daeryeiki . Ma ka hodrai sa homwera dreiki . Ma ko naegimin wike gwin , pya uru , kumta ka daerwera drai ho naegimreiki .
55004004	Ma ko swa nu a daeryeiki . Ko song swasa daerwera dreiki .
55004005	Ma kronam naekina pko diroko , gwae gwa kronam ko yoma tikminkna . Ma pyenkin pko diroko , hamaha da , pa dyenkna . Ma Hupe waenukin naegimin tmoe hoko hominkna . Ma gu ko God ya tmoe homin kru kren , tmoe gwa homaekin tru aeroko hoko hominina .
55004006	Ma ka no God dima daewekrai teikron ko sem kurya . No ware hiko kwasu hrerakra .
55004007	Nokwa resi dinkra idima hwemkite . No ten butmin hwemkite . Ma no God dima drinu din ko kwormaepu .
55004008	No waenuma paka totetiwa dimkinku no hoe ko wakan aera . Ma aku hoko pko diroko Yomkra , begmin kru waenukin hoa hoe ko no dima dae . Ma hoko no dimasa wirin . Wike dika yo dima hine pya bra , yo huma penkrai , ko dima kesu dae .
55004009	Gu no dima pkmaekra hamo ten yoma drureka diwa pkna .
55004010	Demes yo to hyenu hi dima hine pya braka , yo no kwori to Tesaronaika dima ta . Ma Kresen yo ko Geresia dima ta . Ma Taites yo Damatia dima ta .
55004011	Hamo Ruk yasa nominki hra . Hamo gu Mak diwa yo me pkna . Tenam yo no taetaepma , tmoe hi homnada .
55004012	Ma no Tisikes pru , yo Epesis dima ta .
55004013	Hamo gu pkerakekano , no kio baiko , Kapes ya tikmnada hro pke hamo gwa sapkna . Mate kwo kesu sapkna . Ma kwo dei kau me hominko , no hoda gu dumasa sapkna .
55004014	Ma Areksanda , auri tmoe homin kru , ya no domsore . Ya homa ko Yomkra ya hoe yo dima dae .
55004015	Hamo gu yo kesu gwa braeme , tenam yo kyomka kua swa ko ya ten dwamamite .
55004016	Ma hya no begemwera begemitiko , kru trua no taetaepmaepu . Ko butmin no hro krya hwariti . God ya ka homrai dware hoe daemeda .
55004017	Ma hokeko Yomkra yo nominki hete . Ma ya aiko , no dima daete . Hamo no ya swa idima naegimo , swa ate wike pya daeriti . Hamo ko no pwen nyaida sa teti .
55004018	Hamo Yomkra ya no sa , kronam swokin no dima hominkraiko butmin ko hro , ya no sata Hewen hokan pitma tikmi . Ma yo dima ko , ai waenukina yae dyaen dyaen hamo aenkrada . Haminina .
55004019	Ma no duwa dra Prisira ma Akwira ti dima , me Onesipora ya gire ko dima kesu .
55004020	Erastes yo Korin hokan penkra ma no yo hro pke . Ma no Tropimes ko Mileta hokan hro pke , tenam yo treru diku .
55004021	Ma gwa pkmae ten diroko dumasa pkna ma kio aku hokeko gu gwatumki pkna .
55004022	Ma Yomkrako , gwa dureminki pnada . Ma God ya proekin kronam butmin gyominki aenknada .
56001001	No hi ko Por , ma no ko God ya tmoe homin kru , ma Yesu Keriso ya no pru ya tmoe homnada . Hamo nokwa gyo dima kwo hi kimraha .
56001002	Ya hamo homina kren , kyo ware dyaen dyaen ho sinaida . Ma God yo ko kraekraemin kru wirin . Yo to me kwoe me hominaemkin hoke ware dyaendyaen hiko kyo dima daeko da swagumite .
56001003	Ma aku God ya swaguma hrete hoko pko diroko , swa hoko naegimite . Ma hupe hoko God , kua ware daenin kru ya no dima tyete , hamo no hupe hoko hi naegiminkraha .
56001004	Ma nokwa Taites gu dima kwo hi kimra . Kuai God ko trusa krenku , hamo gu ko no kyanu . No hoda Kuai God me Yesu Keriso kua ware daenin kru ta proeki hamaha din me ganeswama waenuma pen kronam gu dima daenknada .
56001005	No gu to Krit hokan hre gu hokan tmoe di ko hominaemkin hoko pitma homaka , Keriso ya wike tikmin yomkra ka hi hyaeka hrenina de . Ma nokwa gu dima tya hoko hine brenkna .
56001006	Nokwa tyako , kru yomkra , yo Keriso ya wike tikmirakroko , wike ka dyenkrai yo hweke katma a hrimaeku dyenkrai , kru hakinsa hrenina . Ma yo ko ara trusa . Ma ya kyako , ko God ya swa daera drinu dinkrai hakinsa ko bryoko . Hamake ko yai yaem ta swa daerinaemka kae ka hodraisa hominkrai hakin ko hrenina wirin .
56001007	Tenam God ya wike tikmin kru yo God ya tmoe tikminkra kren , hamo yo kronam swokin homo wike ka yo dyenku duwa wirin . Hakina kren , kru preprekminka , kepro kikika , wai pya deka , sere pyasa serada hine pya braka , hamin kru ko sirome .
56001008	Ma yo kronam hikinsa homroko bryoko . Yo wike ko gyori kuta ya aewe hokan kudeka mate kronam dukinsa hine braka , katma kyomkinaemka , kronam dukinsa homaka , mate God ya kronam homaka , mate yae ya hodrasa tikmaka hominkra kru hoko bryoko .
56001009	Hamake swa diko kyo braema swa hiko drinu drai ma yo kesu swa hoko drinu dra hamroko yo ko bryoko . Hamo yo wike gwin ko dima swanu ho dumasa naegimaka ko taetaepmaka mate wike gwin ko swanu ho ko a da kweroma naegimraiko , ya duma naegimin braema .
56001010	Tenam wike pya , ma gwin ko Ju wike ma ko hupe waenukin daera drinu dano , ma ko hote swa ate nononma tyo , wike gwin ko swa ho daera dumahaki dinkrai .
56001011	Hakina kren swa ka naegiminkrai ten dwen ko bryoko . Tenam ko kru me ara me ka kya kuku ko dima swa dukinaemkin naegimo ko ho daera drinu dini da ma drinu wirin da harinkrai . Ma ka hamike naegimrai tenam ko sere taerwerada . Hamo kyo swa hiko daera hukwaekewi .
56001012	Kru tru , yo ko Krit naegimin kru , hamo ya swa sem duma tyete , Krit wike ko aku butmin kraekraeminkrai . Ma ko ko ware gryogryo swokin dinaeka , kudropka , grimeka , hakina howa dina . Hakina kren , gwa ko dima hanya , gyo haminkromoe dna . Haryoko ko God ya swa ko drinu din braema .
56001013	
56001014	Hamake ko Ju wike ka soge swa ko a da , wike gwin ko swanu ko a da ka gyo kronam wike ka homnai din ko ho kesu a daeryeiki .
56001015	Ma wike kronam waenukinsa hominkrai , ka hine bren ko kronam butmin ko waenukina . Ma wike dika God ya swa a da , kronam swokinsa hine brenkrai ka harinkrai kronam butmin ko swokinsa dinkrai .
56001016	Ma ka titwom me harike tyenkrai , God ko kyo braema dinkrai . Ma ka hominkrai hoa , God ko ko braema wirin dinaekina . Ma ko wike gwinko , ko a da , prikmroko kronam waenukin homin braema wirin .
56002001	Ma swa diko God ya swa ho bryoko , hosa naegiminkna .
56002002	Ma kru yomkra ko dima tyenkna , ko wai pya dinaemka , swa drikminsa tyaka , kae ka hodrai tikmaka , God ya swa daera braemki drinu deka , wike gwin ko dima hine pya bra , God ya tmoe kwori naedwera dromoe , dinkna .
56002003	Ma ara yomkra ko dima kesu tyenkna , ko God ya tmoe homin ara ko dinaeka hwyenknai dna . Gyo swa swokin tyaka , wike ka hi domsoreka , wai wain pya deka hamin ko bryoko wirin dinkna .
56002004	Ko kronam waenukinsa homaka , ara gwin ko naegimo , koke ka kru me ka kya kuku ko dima hine pya bra , ka hodrai kae tikma , kore tyenaemka , aewe pitma tikma , ka kru ka hodrai daeka haminina . Hamroko , wike gwin ko God ya swa ko swokina din braema wirin .
56002005	
56002006	Hamake , kwaten kru ko dima tyenkna , ka hodrai ko kaesa tikminknai .
56002007	Ma gu kesu nakoe homirakekano pitma waenumasa hominkna . Ma gu swa naegimaka , gan swama o rerin swama naegiminkrome .
56002008	Swa drike minsa tyenkna . Pako wike gwin ko gu ko swokina dmeda . Hamo wike dika gu a drai ko hukwaeka swa swokin kyo dima tyen braema wirin .
56002009	Ma wike hro senko , kanai ka swa daera taetaepma hominknai . Ma kanai ka ko dima naerike tryoko ka swa rwyo kyasiri kyomka tyenkromoe .
56002010	Hamake ka gryogryo uma taerinina wirin dna . Ko kronam waenukin ka hominkrai ho naegu wike gwin ka diwa harieiki , God ya swa ko drik mena howa din braema .
56002011	God ya wike butmin ko dima ya proeki hamaha din kronam naegimina kren ko ware sen braema .
56002012	Ya proeki hamaha dina kren hoa kyo dima naegiminkra , kronam diko God yo a dinkra hoko kyo hro naede , to hyenu gryogryo kua idima hodrai ko hro naede , kuae kua hodrai tikmaka , kronam waenukinsa homnai dinkra .
56002013	Kyo hamike homaka mate aku tru kua God , kua ware daenin kru Yesu Keriso ya pkikra aku ho huminkrai . Hamo kine waenukin me kyo dima taenkin braema .
56002014	Ma yae yo kyo dima daete . Pako kyo aku butmin kronam swokin , homeda . Ma kyo ko ya wike . Hamo ya kyo homite kren kyo hweke dumka , dukinsa homwera dinkrai .
56002015	Hamo gu swa hiko ko dima naegiminkna . Naegimaka tnya , tmoe waenukinsa homaka , swokin ko homromoe dna . Gu ko God ya pru pkena kren , hikesu naegimna . Pako ko harmeda gu ko kukina dmeda .
56003001	Gwa wike ko dima tyenkna , nononkromoe , gyo tikminkrai ka swa daera , kronam waenukinsa hominknai hanya .
56003002	Ko dima tnya , swa swokin , wike ko dima tryomoe dna . Ma ko dima kire da , kate druki waenuma paka , haminknai dna .
56003003	Tenam kyo kesu uminkiko , kyo ko nonononka , God ya swa ko a da , hweke twaka , kuae kua hodraisa taermaeka , mate wike gwin ko dima gwogwoekeka hamamiti . Hamo wike gwin ka kyo dima a du , kua ko dima a du hamamiti .
56003004	Ma God , kua ware daenin kru ya proeka hine pya bren kronam kyo dima naegimite .
56003005	Pako kyo swokin simeda ya kyo taetaepmite . Ma kua waenuma homiti hoa dware ya kyo taetaepmiteke . Hoa wirin . Yo kyo proeka dore daen ko yo a da kyo taetaepmite . Ma ya Dure dima tyo , Dure ya kyo sora ninma hamtete . Ninma hamtena kren ware nin hwyen braema .
56003006	God ya Dureko Yesu Keriso kua ware daen kru yo dima dae ma ya kyo dima hyenma dripmo torite .
56003007	Hamo ya proeki hamaha din kronam hoa God ya kyo dima dumraiha dnada . Hamo kyo yominki dyaendyaen hamo pen braema . Kyo hi siwera da huma penkrai .
56003008	Swa hi ko drinu .
56003009	Ma swa nononka hamasa kutwyaka , grwine bra , gua kigwam gua hwoe ka hi hyaeka song twya , koma swa twya , grwine bruroko gu me wirin . Ko ko drike dumkina .
56003010	Ma kru ara dika grwin bren swa tyo diroko , wike gwin ko swa ho dima drinu di , ma gwin ko drinu dinaemku , haminkrai kru ara hakin ko dima aku haepki hamo haryome da no mate yominki swa tyenina wirin .
56003011	Gu braema kru ara hakemin ko hweke mina . Wike gwin ko ya homra diwa , duwa din braema wirin .
56003012	Ma no Atimes o ma Tisikis gu dima pru ti . Ma yo gwa pra hokan taenku diroko , gu no dima pkna . Ma kyo akuko , no to Nikoropis hokan pi .
56003013	Ma kru Senes , yo ko koto swa tyenin kru , me Aporo ti twerakuro gwa ti taetaepmna . Ma ti naekin taera twerakuro gwa ti taetaepmna .
56003014	Ma kua wike ko tmoe dukin hominkrai ko duwa . Hamroko kua bute ka drinu hoda drai ho daen braema . Ma kua wike ko tmoe drike dumkin hamasa homin ko duwa wirin .
56003015	Ma wike nominki prai ka gu dima duwa din swa tryai . Hamo gu kesu Keriso ya wike ko dima duwa din swa tnya .
57001001	No ko Por . Hamo no Keriso ya dware wogitmina hra . Nokwa Timoti ki kwo hiko , kua kire Pairimon gu dima kimrai . Ma gu ko kia kirenu . Ma gu me kyo tmoe trusa hominkrai .
57001002	Ma Keriso ya wike gwa aewe gaeminkrai gyo dima da , kua auke Apia gu dima da , mate Akipas gu kesu . Ma gu Saiten dima totetyenkra , hamo kia gyo dima kwo hi kimraiha .
57001003	Hamo Kuai God me Kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ta proeki hamaha din kronam me ganeswama waenuma pen kronam gyo dima daenaida .
57001004	Kire Pairimon , no aku dikan God dima swa tryoko , no gu nononkinkmaepu . Ma no God dima duwa dinkra .
57001005	Tenam no daerinkrako , gu Yomkra ko drinu deka , kru ara God ya wike ko dima hin pya braka hoda dinkra .
57001006	No God dima tyenkra ko hikina , kyo me gyo me , kyo kire da penkrai tenam kyo Yesu ko drinu Keriso dinkrai , hamo kyo Keriso yominki kwenkraiko , ya kyo tikmo , kyo waenuma penkrai ho yoma braemknaida .
57001007	Kire , gua proekin ko yoyomkin hyena no dima dae no hin taetaepmo no aikinkra . Gu God ya wike butmin ka hin taetaetpmo yoyomkinkrai .
57001008	Tenam hakina kren , no hine himike brura , gu me no me ti ko Keriso ya gire kren , no ko gua goe , hamo kronam tru homaekina ae homna din braema .
57001009	Ma no gu dima proekinku swa hirike a tye . No gu dima tondaerira . Hene , drinu noko Por . Ma God ya pru pkin ko Yesu hamo ya no pru , no ya tmoe yaeyosa hakina hominkra . Tenam Keriso ya dware no wogitmina henkra .
57001010	Swa nokwa gu dima tondaerya ko Onisimas yo gitma tondaerira . Yo ko no kya . Ki ko Keriso ya gire . Ma no wogitmin aewe hikan haka nokwa God ya swa naegimo ya daera drinu de . Hakina kren no ko yai dinaekina .
57001011	Yo sem uminki ko , gyo taetaepma tmoe waenuma homin braema wirin . Ma aekwa ko yo ko taetaepmin braema .
57001012	Hamo no hote yo pru krwyo gu dima tnada . Ma no proe ko yominki tra .
57001013	No hoda yo nominki henina . Hamo no wogitmin aewe hikan hrako , hupe waenukin ya dware . Gu no taetaepmin braema wirin kren , ya no taetaepmnada .
57001014	Hamo nokwa gu riru gu no taetaepmin ko no a . No hoda , gwaesa hine bra no taetaepminina . Ma gu a droko no a homi .
57001015	Ma uminki Onisimas yo gu kwori , aku kukuma ha , ma hamosu yo kuta guminki aku pya hen braema .
57001016	Hamo aekwa yo ko hro sa naedu kwen kru hosa wirin , kwasu ya drike ko hyena . Yo ko Keriso ya gire hamo yo ko kia gmore . Hamo no yo dima hine brurako , yo ko drike hyena dra . Ma ya drike gu dima ko naemikene . Yo tmoe homroko drike hyena . Ma yo ko Yomkra yagmore .
57001017	Ma kudi gwa hin ko ki ko tmoe trusa hominkrai da no dima duwa dinkra ko yo dima kesu duwa dna .
57001018	Ma kudi yo kronam swokin tru gu dima homina kroko ma yo sere tru sa hote rwyo daemaepu kroko no sere kwonam hokan kimna .
57001019	Hikan ko nae no krite me kimra . Por nokwa gu dima rwyo dae . ( Ma no gu dima a tye , ma uminki nokwa gu taetaepmu , warka aike , ho gu nononkmeda , a tye . )
57001020	Kire ki ko Keriso yo gite hurai , hamo kronam himike homroko no hine bren ko yoyomkikraha .
57001021	No swa hi kimrako no braema nokwa hi tondaerya ko gu homikraha , ma gwin kesu homi .
57001022	Hamake no ri homa humna . No hin ko maren God ya , gua guriguri trya ko , yo daerin braema . Maren yo no gyo dima daen braema .
57001023	Ma Epapres yo nominki wogitkina hra ko , Yesu Keriso ya dware . Hamo ya gyo dima duwa din swa trya .
57001024	Ma kru tmoe trusa nominki hominkraiko , Mak me Aristakas me Dimas me Ruk hamo , ko butmin duwa din swa gyo dima tryai .
57001025	Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya proekin kronam butmin gyominki hnada .
58001001	Semsoge God yo ya tyo tyen wike ko dima ten aatma tyo , kua kigwam ko dima tyadaemamiti .
58001002	Ma aku hi praiko , to hyenu hi hoe myaeku , God ya kya dima tyo , ya kyo dima tyete . Ma God ya tyo , yo to me kwoe me gryo butmin ko ya homite . Hamo to hyenu hiko hoe myaeku , God ya ya kya dima tyo , ya kyo dima tyete . Ma God yo tyo , yo to me kwoe me gryo butminko ya homite . Hamo to hyenu hiko hoe myaeku , God ya tyenku , gryo butmin ko yana kikraha .
58001003	God ya kae hyenu waenukiskin hoko , ya kya ko God ya gingin dinaekina hamo ya kae hoa kyo dima naegiminkra . Yasa tyo , to hyenu gryo me kwoe me ko tikminkra . Ma yo , wike kua hweke hoe ko ya so diroko , God yo kua hweke hamaha dite . Hamo yo Kwoe Kom ta , God , ai butmin sen hoa krite dunaetegite hoke penkra .
58001004	Ma God yo ya kya ya hi hyenmakano , ma ya po penkrai dure ka hi ko kukumite .
58001005	Ma God ya po penkrai dure ko dima hirike tmyaepu , gyo ko no kya harmaepu , ma no ko guai dmaepu . Ma hokesu ya po penkrai kru trua ya swa tyakano ya kumta no dima ai din braema wirin .
58001006	Ma God yo ya kya rwa to hyenu dima pru syerakekuro tyete , dure nokwa po penkrai gyo yo dima swa waenukin tyenina .
58001007	Ma dure nokwa po penkrai ka swa tyaka tyete , ko ko hwore dinaekina . Ma ko ko dei rurinkra hakina .
58001008	Ma yo ya kya swa tyaka tyete , God , gwa po penkrai ko aepesu preiki . Gwa wike ko waenuma tikminkra .
58001009	Ma gu kronam dukinsa hoda dinkra . Ma dukinaemkin ko gu a dinkra . Hoa dware gwa God ya gu sa hrete . Ma yo gwa hi hyenmite . Ma wike gwa po penkrai ka hi ko kukumite .
58001010	Ma yo swa hi kesu tyete , Yomkra , gu uminki , to hyenu me kwoe me homite .
58001011	Ma marensu ko ko wirinki . Ma gwa hamosa hi .
58001012	Ma ko bai brunai dinaeka grwa prima hro naedu atki . Ma gu atkin braema wirin . Gwa hakiskina henkra . Gwa ware ko wirinkin braema wirin .
58001013	Ma God ya harmaepu dure nokwa po penkrai trua dima gu no krite dunaetegite hikan po , nokwa gwa wasi ko taera kumta gwa karike tukram two , gwa titima pna dmaepu .
58001014	Ma dure God ya po penkrai ko naekinane . Ko ko dure , ma ko God ya tmoe homaka , ya pru sya , wike wa , ware dyaendyaen huwekrai ko taetaepminina .
58002001	Hakina kren swa kua daeriti ko drinu swa , hamo kyo tuma senina . Hamo kyo ten atema tenina wirin .
58002002	Ma dure God ya po penkrai ka kusya kua kigwam kua hwoe kai ko dima tyetiko drinu taenku dyeti . Ma kru ara dika swa hoko daera hominaemkiti ka hoe ko dore swokinasa bryoko seti .
