58002003	Hamo kutadi kyo ware dyaen dyaen hwyen swa hoko daera hine brenaemkroko , hamroko kua krya hwara taka gwemkin sunam ko diwake . Ma Yomkra yo sem ware aepesu yae hamo hwyenin ho naegimite . Ma swa hoko wike ko daera drinu diti .
58002004	Ma hokeko , God yo kesu tei ate ate homaka , ya Dure , yae ya hinasa , ya kronam waenukin ko wike ko dima daemamite .
58002005	Ma God ya harmaepu dure ya po penkrai ka , to nin pkikra , kua gyo dima naegimraiko , ka tikmreiki dmaepu .
58002006	Ma sem kru trua tyo , Kwonam kimin ko harina , ma to hyenu wikeko , ko ko nakinane , hamo God gu ko dima hine brenkra . Ko ko kukiskina . Ma gu ko tikminkra .
58002007	Ma gu dure gwa po penkrai ko dima tyo ko kukuma hyenkiti . Ma gu wike ko dima tyo , ko kukumasa hyenkiti . Gu yo homa kine yo dima dae , mate ya hi hyenma , mate to hyenu gryo butmin ko ya tikmnada yo dima daete .
58002008	Kwonam kimin ko harina , God ya tyo , to hyenu gryo butminko ya tikmna dite . Ya tyen ko butminsa . Ma aekwa , to hyenu gryo butminko , wike ka tikmu kyo dimaepu .
58002009	Ma kyo Yesu dyenkrai . Ma God ya tyete ko aku kukuma , Yesu yo ko hamsya dure ka tukram po , ma dure God ya po penkrai ko hata po , haminina dite . Tenam God yo kyo dima proekinku , Yesu yo wike butmin ko dima pwerada . Ma aekwa kyo dyenkraiko , ya kutekin me mate ya hi ko hyena , tenam ya pwete ko yaeyosa hakina .
58002010	Ma God yo wike me gryo me homa tikmin kru , hamo yo Yesu dima tren ma homo , yaeyosa hakite . Ma hi ko bryoko . Tenam yo wike gwin ko kesu ya kronam waenukin ho ko sinaida . Tenam Yesu ya tyo , ko ware dyaendyaen hwyen braema .
58002011	Yo wike ka hweke ko sora wirinminkra . Ma yo me ma wike ka hweke ya homo , tupe dumkra , ko butmin kai ko trusa . Hakina kren Yesu yo wike hakin ko dima no gmore na uke ko din ko yo hukwaekinkmaepu .
58002012	Ya God dima tyete gwa homiteko , no gmore ko dima tye . Ma ko gaemroko , no gwa swa waenukin ko dima tye .
58002013	Ma yo hote tyete , no hin God ya tyenkra ko drinusa tyenkra dra . No hiwa hamo kya kuku God ya no dima daete ko no me hurai .
58002014	Ma tenam God ya kya kuku dra , ko ko wike hamo ko ko saio me kapoe me hakina . Hamo Yesu yo ko dinaekite . Yo to hyenu wikekite . Ya himike homiteko tenam yo pwa Saiten ya waa ai domsorirada . Ma Saiten yo ko pwen waa ai yanai .
58002015	Hamo wike dika pwene dima tempwa ya tmoe homiti ko kwasu tmoe hoko wirinkite .
58002016	Ma ya po penkrai ko taetaepminkmaepu . Ma Kwonam kimin ko harina yo ya kyankya kosa taetaepminkra dina .
58002017	Hakina kren yo yagmore ka penkrai kronam hosa bryoko pkite . Hamo yo ko ka God dima swa tyen kru waenukina . Ma yo wike ka hweke hamaha din braema .
58002018	Tenam Saiten yo yo bryoko diwo yo tren dyete , hakina kren Saiten yo kyo dima kumta bryoko diwo diroko , Yesu taetaepmin braema .
58003001	Hakina kren , Krwistin goegmore gyoke , God ya gyo kesu urina . Yesu yo dima hine brunai , God ya yo pru kumta prist hyenu tmoe homira pkite .
58003002	Tmoe God ya yo dima daete yo hoko waenuma homite . Yo Moses ya God ya aewe hokan tmoe waenuma homite , ho bryoko yo kesu tmoe waenuma homite .
58003003	Ma kru dia aewe tryoko , kyo ya hi hyenminkra . Ma kyo aewe ya hi hyenminkmaepu . Hote ho bryoko , Yesu ya hi hyenmin ko bryoko . Ma Moses ya hi ko kukumasa hyenmin ko bryoko .
58003004	Kyo braema , aewe butmin ko wike ka tinkrai . Ma to hyenu gryogryo butmin ko God ya tina .
58003005	Ma Moses yo God ya aewe hokan tmoe waenuma homite . Ma yo kronam gwin God yo hamosu swa tyekra ho tyete .
58003006	Ma Keriso yo ko duma homin kru . Hamo kya hoa , yai God ya aewe ho tikminkra . Yo ko tikmin kru hya . Ma kyo ko ya aewe , hamo kyo aiki , God ya homikra ho huma penkwe .
58003007	Hakina kren Dure Waenukin ya tyenkra , gyo aekwa God ya swa daerekano , gua hina no a dinkromoe .
58003008	Isrwaeo wike ko hamamiti . Ma ko drni tonae hokan , God dima a da swa twya God bryoko dyeti .
58003009	God ya tyete , drni tonae hokanko , ko ambum 40 hamo no tei atma homaka , ko hwya dyeti . Ma ko hote no bryoko dyeti .
58003010	Hakina kren no ko dima kyomkite . Ko aku pya no swa daera ko a diti .
58003011	Hamo no ko dima kyomka , swaguma tyete , to nokwa ko dima dae ko hokan krite hro pmaekina , ma ko hokan dima a treiki .
58003012	Hakina kren , no kire gyoke , gua braeme , pako gua hin swoka , God ware men yo kwori kromoe .
58003013	Ma teikron ko bryoko aeroko , gyo aku hyaekin , gua kyo taetaepmo rwyo taetaepmo haminknai . Pako hweke ya gyo dima kraekraemo gua proe ko tukmeda .
58003014	Ma kutadi , uminki , kua drinu diti hoko aekwa kesu drinu droko , kyo Keriso yo me kyo me tmoe hmenesa homin braema .
58003015	Kwonam kimin ya tyenko , kutadi gyo aekwa God ya swa daeryoko gua proe tukromoe , gua kigwam ka God ya swa a diti hamromoe .
58003016	Ma wike dika God ya swa daera yo dima a ditiko , wike dikane . Moses ya to Ijep hokan hwya gyori tete wike hoko howa .
58003017	Ma God yo wike di ko dima ambum 40 hamo kyomkiteke . Wike hwekmin ko dima . Hamo wike hoko to wike dumkin hokan tosura naediti .
58003018	Ma God ya twya swagumite ko to nokwa ko dima daeka krite hro pnaida daen hokan ko a treiki . Ma yo wike di ko dima tyeteke . Ya swa daera a diti wike ko dima .
58003019	Hakina kren kyo dyenkrai , ko to hokan dima tmaepu . Ko God ya swa daera drinu dmaepu kren .
58004001	Krite hro pen swa God ya swaguma tyen , kyo kesu sen braema . Hakina kren braeme , pako , gyo trua krite hro pen hoko God ya gyo dima swaguma tyete ho , senaemkme .
58004002	Ma hupe waenukin kua daeritiko , ka daeriti ho bryoko . Ma swa ka daeriti ko taetaepmaepu . Tenam ko daerekano ko swa hiko drinu dmaepu .
58004003	Hamo drinu haki dinkrai wike kuasa krite hro pen , God ya swaguma tyete ho sen braema . God ya tyete , no ko dima kyomka swaguma tyenku wike hiko to wa ko , nokwa ko dima krite hro pnaida daen ko a treiki dite . Ma ya hirike tyete , yo tmoe homa wirinmiteko , to hyenu homa naedite hoke .
58004004	Kwonam kimin ya tyenako , God yo aku deihraen hoke ya krite hro pete , ya homra ko winkinku .
58004005	Ma swa hoko hote tyena , ko nokwa ka krite hro pnaida to daen hokan dima a treiki .
58004006	Ma wike dika katumki hupe waenukin hoko daeriti , ma ko krite hro pen hoko simaepu , tenam ko God ya swa ko drinu dmaepu . Hakina kren wike gwin ko taermaekina prai .
58004007	Hi ko waenuma naegi God yo aku trnu hya hrete . Hamo aku hoko aekwa . Ma ambum pya wirin kusu yo King Debid dima tyete , Kwonama kimin ya sem tyen ho . Ma gu God ya swa aekwa daeryako , gwa proe tyonam ko tukrome .
58004008	Ma kutadi Josua yo sem Isrwaeo wike ko dima krite hro pen God ya swagumite hoko ko daena kroko hamosu God yo aku trusa yo swa hote a tye .
58004009	Ma kronam ko hikina , God ya wike ka krite hro pen ko aera , God ya aku deihraen hoke krite hro pete hakina .
58004010	Ma kru ara dia krite hro pen , God ya tyete , ho siroko , tmoe ya hominkra ko hro naede , krite hro pen braema . God ya tmoe homa naedite ho bryoko .
58004011	Hakina kren kwasu kua tmoe waenuma hominkwe , hamo kyo krite hro pen hoko sen braema . Ka senaemka kworiti , tenam ko God ya swa drinu dmaepu kren , ma kyo ko haminina wirin .
58004012	God ya swa ko ware ai mena , krarang tu dinaeka braebraekme kyomekina . Hamo yo titigi kuta ware me dure ta pkwaen hokan timinkra . Yo durenum ka kuta kro drimin hokan timinkra . Yo wike ka hodrai me ka hin bren proe tyonam hokan begeminkra .
58004013	Kronam trua toko God dima gwemkin braema wirin . Kronam butmin hominkrai ko God dima topkyen taensa aenkra . Ya kron ko butmin hamo dyenkra . Ma kyo hamosu kua hominkrai butmin yo dima twyekraiha .
58004014	Hamo kua braem hoko tuma senina . Ma Yesu , God ya kya , yo ko kua swa , God dima tyen kru hya . Yo God ya penkra hokan dima tete .
58004015	Kua swa God dima tyen kru hya hiko , yo kua aikinaemkin kronam ho dima proekinaemkin kru wirin . Kua swa tyen kru hya ko hra , ma Saiten yo kronam ate ate butmin kyo dima bryoko dyenkra hoa sem yo bryoko dyeteko , yo hweke hrimaepu .
58004016	Hakina kren kyo tempwenaemka God ya penkra dima tenkwe . Yo kyo dima proekinkra . Hamo aku dikroke ya taetaepmin hoda droko ya proeka dore katma a daemaekin kronam ho kyo dyen braema .
58005001	Ju wike ka God dima swa tyenin kru hya ko kru , yo ko wike gwin ko bryoko . Hamo ko yo sa hrena , hamo wike ka swa God dima swa tyenkrada . Mate wike ka dine da mate kudin gwin dae ka hweke dware disirnyaida sapkrai hoko God dima disiri haminknaida .
58005002	Ma tenam yae yo kesu ai dumka dropkinkra yo wike gwin dika nononka hweke twenkrai ko dima proekin swa tyen braema .
58005003	Ma tenam yo kesu ai dumka dropkinku hamo yo wike ka kudin ka hweke dware hosa disiri daen braema wirin , yae ya hweke dware kesu daenkra .
58005004	Ma kru trua yo yaesa haryoko no ko God ya swa tyenin kru hya ko nokwa din bryoko wirin . God yasa prist hya taen twenkrako uminki Eron ya hete ho bryoko hunada .
58005005	Hote ho bryoko Keriso yo yaesa God ya swa tyenin kru hya hera dmaepu . God yaesa yo sa hro tyete , gu ko no kya , no aekwa gu hamtra .
58005006	Ma God ya swa tru yo dima tyete , huka trya gu ko no dima swa tyenin kru hya , gu ko Merkisadek yo dinaekra .
58005007	Keriso yo to hyenu hikan hete hokeko , God dima byen me kentite tenam God yasa pwen ten dwen braema . Ma tenam yo yae ya hodra sa kentmaepu yo God ya hodra hosa kentinku , God yo ya swa daerite .
58005008	Ma yo ko God ya kya , ma yo diwa braemknada , God ya swa sa daera homin hoe ko tren dyen braema .
58005009	Ma yo waenumasa hete kren , yo ko ware dyaendyaen yae hamo hen yanai . Hamo wike dika ya swa daera homraiko , ko ware dyaen dyaen yae hamo hwyen ho sen braema .
58005010	Ma God ya yo sa hro tyete , yo ko prist hyenu hya ko yo . Yo ko Merkisadek yo bryoko .
58005011	Ma kyo swa hiko pya tmyaekina aera . Ma gyo dima naegimin ko tuwa , tenam gyo katma a braemkmaekrai .
58005012	Gua Krwistin diti ko sogmena . Ma gyo wike gwin naegimin hurai ko bryoko . Ma gyo haminkmaepu . Ma gyo hoda kru trua God ya swa hya naegiminkraiko , gyo dima hote naegimnada . Ma gyo kudin tukin dinaemka , yae hamo tute doresa de penkrai .
58005013	Ma kru kano tute doresa dinkraiko ko kya dinaekina . Ma kya kronam ko hikina , diko dukwa , ma diko swokina hoko ko braemkmaepu .
58005014	Ma kudin tukin ko wike wimgen kana . Ko sem kronam ate ate homin braema kren . Hamo kronam diko duwa ma diko swokina ko braema .
58006001	Hakina kren , kyo Keriso ya swa ko yatumki naegimo daeriti , ho braemki naedesu , ya swa aikin naegiminina . Ma ko swa yatumki kyo naegimiti , ma gyo tmoe drike dumkin hro naede , God ya swa ko drinu da haminknai . Mate swa hosa hote naegimin ko bryoko wirin .
58006002	Ma wai nam mga hamten kronam da mate krite ka ku ti hren kronam da mate pwen dure ka aswekrai kronam da mate ko begemin aku swa hosa naegiminkromoe .
58006003	Swa gwin kesu naegimiskwe . Ma God ya bryoko droko , kyo homreiki .
58006004	Ma wike dika God ya swa sem braemka kworyoko , mate ko naemike krwyo , ka hweke hote homin braemane . Ma ko ko God ya kae mena . Ko Hewen ya daenkra ko kukuma dyeti . Ma ko Dure waenukin seti .
58006005	Hamake ko braemkiti .
58006006	Ma ko hoko butmin braemki naeduro ko butmin hoko kworiti . Hamo ko rwyo sapkroko ka hweke hro naedin braema wirin . Tenam ko hamroko ko God ya kya hote dei buti hro , baku me tukwa yeti ho bryoko . Ma hoko wike ka kron ti hukwae daenkrai .
58006007	Ma to God ya tikminkrako waia sureka so diroko sanam gryogryo mtinkrai . Hamo to hoko wike di ko dima gyena kroko , ko sanam gryo ko hokan taerin braema .
58006008	Ma to dikan tupete me skupeyai kasa mtroko to hoko drike wirin . Hamroko to hoko God ya yo dima gu puna du , to hoko deia duen braema .
58006009	Kire gyoke , kyo swa hirike tryai , ma kyo braema maren gyo a domsoryeiki . Gyo dei senku . Kyo braema gyo deike waenuma yenkrai .
58006010	Ma God yo ko begemin kru swokina wirin . Yo tmoe gua homitiko a nononki . Gua Krwistin wike ko taetaepmiti , da mate aekwa hi taetaepminkrai kesu gua yo dima hine bren ho naeginkra . Hamo hoko a nononki .
58006011	Kyo hoda gyo butmin ya tmoe yoyomki me homaka hoe yenina . Hamo gua hoda diwera drai ko pki .
58006012	Gyo kudropkromoe . Gyo wike God ya swako drinu deka huma penkrai ko dinaekinknaida . Hamroko God ya twya swagumite ho sen braema .
58006013	Ma God ya Abraham dima swaguma tyeteko , nokwa homira da tyen ho duma homikraha . Ma tenam ko kru tru , yo bryoko hata hmaepu kren , ma yae yosa hansa tyete .
58006014	Ya tyete , no gu dima swaguma hadruri twyasu gua kyankya hyenma dae .
58006015	Ma Abraham yo huma pete , hamo God ya swaguma tyen hoe ko dyete .
58006016	Ma kru trua , drinu homira swaguma tryoko yomkra tru ya hi hyasu , kru trua yo swa tru tyen braema .
58006017	Wike dika God ya swagumin hoe ho siwekraiko , God ya ko dima harite ya homira da tyen ko atokma a homi . Hamo swa hiko ya hinam hyete .
58006018	Hakina kren kronam haepki hiko atkin braema wirin . God yo kraekraema tyen braema wirin . Ma kyo , sem tempwa krya yo dima teti . Hamo ya kyo tikminkra . Hamo kyo aikeka God ya tyen ho tuma sinai .
58006019	Ma swa hiko kno tike dinaekina . Yo ko tuwa . Swa hiko God ya aewe hokan bai tyonamgite ta , God ya penkra hoke ten braema .
58006020	Yesu ya , kyo taetaepmira , yatumki hokan dima tete . Ma yo ko God ya prist kru hya , ma yo ko Merkisedek ya kronam ho bryoko dyaen dyaen henkra .
58007001	Merkisedek yo ko tonesu Sarem wike ka king . Ma yo ko God Hyenu Hya ya prist tmoe homin kru . Abraham ya yo tupmete , yo king wike gwin kuwya naede rwyo pkete hoke . Ma hokeko Merkisedek ya yo tupma hagurmin swa tyete .
58007002	Ma gryogryo Abraham ya taerite butmin ko bekesin hamo aeroro , truko yo dima daete . Yo gryo butmin hamikesa daemite . ( Merkisedek ya hi drike ko Waenukin Yanai . Ma tenam yo ko Sarem wike ka king , ya hi tru ko ganeswama waenuma pen yanai . )
58007003	Ma yai yaem ta hi da mate ya kigwam ka hi ko kwonam kimina aemaepu . Yo hamten aku da mate ya pwen aku kesu kimaepu . Ma yo ko God ya kya dinaekina . Hamo yo ko God ya prist kru yae dyaendyaen hamo henkra .
58007004	Hakina kren ya hi hyenu gyo dinai . Abraham kua kigwam yo wasi ka gryogryo bekesin yo dima trusa trusama daemite .
58007005	Ma Ribai ya kyankya , ko God ya tmoe hominkrai ma koma swa ya tyenko , Isrwaeo wike ka gryo gryo bekesin hamo aeruroko ko trusa trusama taerinina . Ma wike hoko goe gmore hamo ko swa trusa tyenkrai , ma ko ko Abraham ya kyankya .
58007006	Ma Merkisadek yo ko Ribai ya kya wirin . Ma yo Abraham ya gryo bekesin trusa trusama taera hagurmin swa yo dima tyete . Kru , God ya swaguma yo dima tyete hoa dae taerite .
58007007	Ma kyo kronam hiko braemki naedrai , kru diya yo hagurma swa tryoko yo ko hyena . Ma kru yo swa ho daera siroko yo ko hamsya .
58007008	Ma God ya tmoe homin wike ko gryo bekesin aeruroko ko trusa trusama taerinkrai ma ko ko to hyenu wikma hwyaka tosurinkrai . Ma Merkisadek yo trusa trusama taeritekeda yo hra . Kwonam kimin ko harina .
58007009	Ma kyo hirike tmyawe , Abraham yo bekesin ae ya trusa daeteko , Ribai ( ya kyankya ko bekesin aerwo ka trusa trusama taerinkrai ) ma ya kesu daete .
58007010	Ma hokeko , Ribai yo hamtenaemkina . Hamo kyo hirike tmyawe , Merkisadek ya Abraham tupmete ko yo Abraham ya kigwam ya bute tyonam aete hoke .
58007011	Ma Ribai ya wike ko God ya prist tmoe homamiti , ma koma ka sen ko Isrwaeo wike ko dima daeti . Ma kudi Ribai ya wike ko God ya prist tmoe ko waenumasa homo , wike ko waenuma proko , maren God ya prist tmoe homin kru tru Merkisadek yo dinaekin ma yo Eron ya kronam dinaekina wirin , yo kumta atma homin ko drike wirin .
58007012	Hamo kudi God ya prist tmoe homin wike ko atma hriroko , hamroko koma kesu ko atma hrenina .
58007013	Ma swa hiko kua Yomkra yo dima tyete ma yo ko tei ate ma ya tei ko ware gryogryo ya , disiri God dima daemaepu .
58007014	Kyo braema kua Yomkra ya kigwam ko Juda . Ma Moses ya tyen ko tei hoko God ya prist homnai dmaepu .
58007015	Ma kyo swa hi ya drike braemkrai . God ya prist tmoe homin kru tru ko Merkisadek ya kronam dinaekina taenkite .
58007016	Ma yo ko God , ya prist tmoe homin kru hete . Ma to hyenu wike yomkra tmoe homrai hna du hmaepu . Wirin . God topkomnai dyaendyaen yae hamo hen ya hinam hna dina henkra .
58007017	Tenam Kwonam kima tyen ko harina gu no prist tmoe yae dyaendyaen hamo hominkna . Merkisadek ya tei ka homamiti haminina .
58007018	Ma God yo koma , sem daeteko , ai dumka tmoe hominaemku diku hro naedite .
58007019	Tenam Moses ya komako kyo waenuma pitmasa homin braema wirin . Ma kwasu swa tru twya hrena aera . Swa ho me kren kyo taka God dima kurin braema .
58007020	God ya Keriso ko prist tmoe homininada swa gumite . Ma uminki God ya prist ka tmoe komdwetiko , God ya ko dima swa twya swagumaepu .
58007021	Ma Yesu yo , God ya prist tmoe homin krukiteko , Yomkra ya sem yo dima swagumina . Ma ya hin atma a bre . Gu ko no prist tmoe homin kru , ware dyaendyaen hamo hominki .
58007022	Swa haepki atma tyen tru ko Yesu uo tmoe waenuma homa hoe yete .
58007023	Ma swa haepki hi ti ko ate . Tru ko God ya prist tmoe homin wike sem hwyeti ko pya . Ma ko tosurekano ka tmoe ko naediti .
58007024	Ma Yesu yo dyaendyaen hamo henkra . Hamo yo God ya prist tmoe , kru tru dima daemaepu .
58007025	Hakina kren aekwa , hu aku butmin , kru ara dika , Yesu ya hinam , God dima tera droko ya taetaepmo ko gwemkin braema wirin . Tenam yo dyaendyaen hamo haka , God minki ko dima swa tyenkra .
58007026	Hamo Yesu ko kua buta ho dinkrai ho ko God dima tyen kru . Ma yo ko waenu yaeyosa hakina . Ma yo ko hweke wirin . Hamo hwek min wike ko ri tru po , ma yo ri tru ko , hata Hewen hokan penkra .
58007027	Ma yo ko God , ya prist hyenu hya sem uminki homi hwyeti ko dinaekina wirin . Ko hwek mena kren ko aku hyaekin ware gryogryo ka hoe hyenu God dima dae disirisu , mate wike gwin ka hweke dware kesu dae ka homamiti . Ma ya hoe hyenu ya daete ko trusa . Ma yo aku trusa daete wike butmin ka dware . Yae ya bute me ya ware me butmin hamo daete .
58007028	Koma Moses ya hreteko , wike waenukinaemkin ko God ya prist hyenu hya taeri twenkrai . Ma God ya swaguma ya kya sa hrena kren yo ko dyaendyaen waenumasa henkra .
58008001	Ma swa kua hi tryai drike ko hiwa . God ya prist tmoe homin kru hyenu hakin ko hra . Hamo yo King Hewen hokan penkra ya krite dunaetegite hoke penkra .
58008002	Ma yo God ya aewe hokan prist tmoe homin kru hyenu ka ri waenu yaeyosa hakina hokan hominkra . Ma hoko prai aewenu , wike ka timaepu . Yomkra yae tina .
58008003	God ya prist hyenu hyenu ko taeri two , butmin ko gryogryo sumsa dae mate ware gryogryo hoe hyenu ko God dima daenkrai . Hakina kren kua swa , God dima tyen kru , yo kesu mgakwen daen ko bryoko .
58008004	Ma kutadi yo to hyenu hikan hroko , yo prist tmoe homin braema wirin . Tenam God ya prist wike gwin ko hurai hamo ko gryogryo , Ju wike ka koma ya tyen ho bryoko daenkrai .
58008005	Ma prist tmoe ka hominkraiko , ko Hewen hokan homrai ya , gingin ho diwa hominkrai . Ma Moses yo God ya prai aewe tira miteko . Ma God ya yo dima tyete , gu braeme nokwa aegu hokan gu dima naegimite hoko butmin bryokosa homna dite .
58008006	Ma aekwako , prist tmoe yesu ya hominkra ko hata , waenukina . Ma ka homiti ko kukumasa duwa . Hamo hote ho bryoko , God ya kronam nin , ya wike ko dima tyen ko waenukina . Tenam ya swaguma tyete , hamosu kronam waenukina pkiko dite .
58008007	Ma kutadi , God ya uminki tyete ko waenukina haomroko swa tru tyen braema wirin .
58008008	Ma God ya wike ka kronam waenuma hominaemku diwa tyete , no hamosu aku ho pkosu kronam nin homa Isrwaeo wike me Juda wike ko homnaida swagumi .
58008009	Ma kronam nin hoko , nokwa ka kigwam ko dima tyete , no krite me ko gyori to Ijep hro pketi hokeko , bryoko wirin . Ko no kronam hami ka homnaida ho ko kyete kren , hamo no ka swa daermaepu .
58008010	Ma no Isrwaeo wike ko dima kronam hi nokwa homa koke homnaida tye . No hamosu koma ko ka hine bren hokan hre . Ma no ka proenam hokan kimi . Hamo no ko ka God . Ma ko ko no wike .
58008011	Hamo wike ko ka kire dima a hirike tryeiki , gyo Yomkra braemknai , a haryeiki . Tenam ko butminsa , kukukemin da mate hyenhyenu da ko butmin no braemkreiki .
58008012	Hamo no ka hweke hamaha da nononki .
58008013	God ya kronam nin homa gyoke homnaida swaguma tyenku , swa hya tyete ko brunaimite . Ma mgakwen naekin ko brunai kroko , hoko wirinkin braema .
58009001	Kronam homa homnai din sem hya swaguma tyeteko , wike ko God dima hine hya bren swa twyerakroko , koma ko aete . Ma ri , God dima hine hya brenin wike ka homina aete .
58009002	Ma ko prai aewe tru ko kusino ma ri hoegite hoko yae yosa hakina diti . Ma tyonam hokan ko twan twenin ri da mate deipkyon tru hokanko , da , God yana tweti .
58009003	Ma bai me ridrurin margite hokanko , prai aewe tru ya hi ko Ri waenukiska yaeyosa hakina diti .
58009004	Ma tyonam hokanko , deipkyon ko gor me kusi homa hrena hete . Hamo ko pauda pom min ti hokan disiriti . Ma kronam homa homnaida swagumin ya deipkyon ho kesu braeke braeke butmin ko gor me kusi homa hrena hete . Ya tyonam hokanko , tigwote gor me homa tyeti . Ma maena ko tyonam hokan twena aete . Ma tru ko Eron ya deigan , tnrnaepen minkite , ma tru ko ike haepki hokan ko homnai din me mate homromoe din swa ko hokan kimite . Hamo butmin ko tyonam hokan aete .
58009005	Ma deipkyon komgite hokanko , kwoe kom wike pi min ka drike ko God ya pmaekin ri ko hokan peti . Ka piko , draekdraemo , ri , God yo wike ka hweke hamaha dite komgite hokan pariti . Ma aekwa himo ko , gryogryo butmin hi ya drike naegimin braema wirin .
58009006	Hamo gryogryo hoko hamo tweti . God ya prist wike ko aku butmin kuta prai aewe trua tasu ka tmoe hominkrai .
58009007	Ma prist kru trua hya hoasa prai aewe tru ho ya tyonam tenkra . Ma yo ambum hyaekin aku trusasa tenkra . Ma yo terakekano , kapoe me sasu , kuta God dima daenkra . Ma hiko yae ya hweke me mate wike ka nononka hweke twaewi ho me kren , kapoe sasu tenkra .
58009008	Ma kronam himike hominkrai kren , prai graegite yae hamo hroko prai aewe tru dima ten ko aemaepu .
58009009	Hakina kren aekwa , aku hiko kyo dima piksa ma naegiminkra . Ma ya drike ko gryogryo , proekin dae mate ware gryogryo God dima disiri daenkraiko , kru dia daera ya hin ko homa waenuma homin braema wirin .
58009010	Tenam hiko kudin me wai din me mate wai tyen kronam tei ate ate ma hiko bute homin komasa . Kronam hiko ya ae , kuta God ya kronam nin pkosu naedreiki .
58009011	Ma aekwa kronam waenukin kyo aekwa hi diraiko , Keriso yo prist tmoe homin kru hya hera pkite . Ma prai ya haka tmoe hominkra ko waenukiskina . Hamo prai hoko wike ka homaepu .
58009012	Keriso yo prai tyonam ta Ri Waenukiskina yaeyosa hakin hokan tete . Yo hokan ta min nanigos me min kau bi ka kapoe ko yo satmaepu . Yae ya kapoe me satete . Hakina kren , God ya kyo dima kyomkin ko wirinkite . Hamo kyo ya to hokan dyaendyaen pen braema .
58009013	Ma wike ko koma tru kiroko ko min nanigos kapoe me min kau kore kapoe dridripma mate min kau ya saio disiru dua naede kauka tiku prist ka ti ho kwya wike hwekemin ko dima hryohryomu , God ya ko dima a din ko naedin braema .
58009014	Hiko drinu hakina kren Keriso ya kapoe ko drinu , God ya wike kyo dima kyomkrai ko naedin braema . Yo Dure dyaendyaen henkra yo minki henkra yae yo God dima daete . Kua hine bra nononma homroko ya kapoe me sora hasirin braema . Hamo God , ware me henkra , ya hodra hosa homin braema .
58009015	Hakina kren Keriso yo kronam nin homa homnaidin swaguma hrete . Hamroko kru ara diko God ya ura hagurmo dyaendyaen hamo hwyen braema . Ma hiko homin braema , tenam kru tru yo pwete kren . Hamo kronam hya homa homnaida swaguma hre ae wike ko hweke tweti , hoe sen ko hmori tweti .
58009016	Ma kru trua ya gryo taernaida hamroko yo kwo kimasu pwenkrai . Hamo kru diya kwo ho tikmra ya kru kwo ho kima yo drinu pwo diwasu gryo hoko wike di ko ka hi kiminina kroko ka taerin braema .
58009017	Tenam kru kwo ho kimin ko yo pwenaemkroko kwo hoko yae hamo ae .
58009018	Hakina kren kronam hya homa homnaida swagumin ko kapoe me komdwasu homiti .
58009019	Semina Moses yo koma , homnai din me homromoe din butmin wike ko dima naegimite . Naegima naede ya min kau kore me mate mine nanigos ka kapoe tua , wai sa kapoenam dripmasu , min sip ya mten kapoekina taera , kose ya hi ko hisop hosa ho me , koma kwo ti hryohryoma mate wike butmin ka buti kesu hryohryoma hamite .
58009020	Hryohryoma tyete , kapoe hiko kronam homa homnaida swaguma tyenko God ya gyo daera hominina , ma hoe yen ko hiwa dite .
58009021	Hote ho bryoko Moses ya prai me gryogryo butmin God dima duwa dinkrai hoko kapoe me hryohryomite .
58009022	Ma drinu , koma ya tyen ko gryogryo butmin ko kapoe me hryohryomo gryogryo hoko sora duwa dinkrai . Ma kapoe dripmroko , hweke ko sora hamaha din braema .
58009023	Ma gryogryo hoko kwoe kom gryogryo ko bryoko , hamo ya ko hamike sora dumite . Ma kwoe kom gryogryonuko , waenukiskina hamo truasa hata ko sorin braema .
58009024	Keriso yo God ya aewe yaeyosa hakin wike ka krite me tin , aewenu ho dinaekin , hokan dima tmaepu . Ma yo Hewen dima ta . Yo God ya kinaegite haka kua swa tyenkra .
58009025	Ma Ju wike ka prist God ya tmoe homin kru hyenu hya yo ambum hyaekin butmin God ya aewe waenu yaeyosa hakin tyonamgite terakekano yo ware gryogryo ka kapoe me sasu tenkra . Ma Keriso ko yae yo aku pya daenkmaepu .
58009026	Ma kudi yo hamroko yo to hyenu komdwa homite hoke , kumta aekwa himroko yo aku pya tren dyenkra . Ma yo homaepu . To hyenu hoe yerakra himroko , yo aku trusa taenki , yae yo rwyo dae , hweke wirinmnada .
58009027	Ma wike butmin ka pwen ko trusa . Ma hamosu God ya ko begemi .
58009028	Hote ho bryoko , God ya Keriso daete ko trusa . Yo wike pya ka hweke wirinmnada . Ma yo hote pkikrako , hweke sora hominaete wirin . Yo wike dika yo huma penkrai ko taera tikmira .
58010001	Ju wike ka koma ka naegiminkrai ko kronamnu ho bryoko wirin . Ma koma hoko kronam waenukin hamosu pkikra kukuma ho dinaekina . Ma ko ware gryogryo disiri daenkraiko , ambum hyaekin haminkrai . Ma naemike , ware gryogryo disiri daenkrai hoa wike dika God dima pko koma ya ko dumnaiha din braemane .
58010002	Ma kutadi wike dika God ko duwa du , ka hweke ko drinu sora naedu ka hina hweke ko yae hamo aera din braema wirin . Ma ware gryogryo God dima disiri daen ko naedin braema .
58010003	Ma aekwako , ambum hyaekin wike ko ware gryogryo disiri daeminkrai , hamo ko ka hweke dima hine braka haminkrai .
58010004	Tenam ko min kau kore me nanigos ka kapoe ko hweke sorin braema wirin .
58010005	Hamo diku , Keriso yo to hyenu dima pkeraka God dima tyete , gryogryo hoe hyenu ko gu a dra . Ma gu bute homa ho no dima daea .
58010006	Ma gu ware gryogryo ambutmin wike ka hweke sornyada , deipkyon ti hro disirinko , gu yoyomkmaepu .
58010007	Hakina kren , no God no hi hraha . No gwa tmoe homirakrako no swa ko me Kwonam hokan kimiti ho bryoko .
58010008	Ma ya tyete , gu hweke sornyada gryogryo hoe hyenu me mate ware gryogryo disiri daenkrai ko gu yomkinaemka a dinkra . Ma hi butmin daenkra ko koma tyena .
58010009	Harano , ya tyete , no God no hiwa no gwa tmoe homira . Ware gryogryo hoe hyenu daenkrai God ya wirinmite . Ma Keriso ya hoe ko hyena . Hamo ka ri ko ya sete .
58010010	Tenam Yesu Keriso yo God ya hodra ho homa yaesa kyo dima daena kren kyo ko waenu yaeyosa hakina .
58010011	Ma Ju wike prist tmoe hominkrai ko aku butminsa ka tmoe homaka mate ware gryogryo hoe hyenu ambutminsa bryokosa daenkrai . Ma hiko ka hweke sorin braema wirinsa .
58010012	Ma Keriso yo ko hoe hyena ma hoe hyenu ko trusa Keriso yo daete . Ma ya daete ko dyaendyaen yae hamo aenkra . Hamo yo God ya krite dunaete hoke penkra .
58010013	Hamo yo hokan huma paka , God ya ya wasi ko ya karike tkyo hre diwasu .
58010014	Yo hoe hyenu trusa daesu , wike diko ka hweke ko sora naede ya ko homa naedu ko ware dyaendyaen hureiki .
58010015	Ma Dure Waenukin ya kesu ya braemkin kyo dima tyete .
58010016	Yomkra ya tyete , no hamosu no kronam homa homnaida swagumin tru ko dima tye . No koma ko ka proe tyonam hokan hre . Ma no ka hin bren hokan kimi .
58010017	Harasu ya tyete , no ka hweke ko hote a hine bre .
58010018	Hakina kren hweke ko hamaha dinku , kyo gryo dae hweke hamaha dnaida hote daen braema wirin .
58010019	Kire gyoke , hakina kren , kyo dumasa God ya aewe yaeyosa hakin ya tyonam dima ten braema . Ten ko Yesu ya pwa homina kren .
58010020	Yo ten nin tmyete . Ma ware ten ho bai me ridwen hoko ya bute .
58010021	Kwasu kua prist hyenu yo God ya aewe tikmna .
58010022	Hamo hakina kren kyo God kuri twe . Kua hin me kua proe me tyenina . God ya homite ko drinu dinina . Ma kua proea hweke hin brenkrai ko sora , ma kua bute ko wai me sora haminina .
58010023	Kua hoda diwera dinkrai ko kyo direiki harwe . Tenam God ya kyo dima twya swagumite hoko a kye .
58010024	Hakina kren kyo wike gwin ko dima hine braka ko taetaepmo kronam waenukin homaka mate kae matum taetaepmo matum taetaepmo haminkwe .
58010025	Ma Krwistin wike kua hmene gaema swa tyenko naedinkromoe . Ma kyo wike gwin ka hominkrai hominina wirin . Kyo himwe , matum taetaepmo matum taetaepmo hamwe . Tenam Yomkra ya pkin Aku ko sem kurya kren .
58010026	Ma kudi kyo Keriso ya swa naegimo braemkino , ma kyo dumasa kuta hweke hrioko , ma gryo hoe hyenu kru kua hweke homaekin hoe ko wirin .
58010027	Hakina kren , wike dika God ko ko a droko , ka begemin me dei kyomekin ho dima tempwa huma pen braema .
58010028	Ma kru diya Moses ya koma kyo , kru haepki o haepki trumo ka diwa tyo diroko ko yo proekin braema wirin . Ko yo pwene yenkrai .
58010029	Ma gua hin ko nakoene , kru ara trua God ya kya ko yo a droko , ma kronam homa homnaida swagumin ko ya kapoe me ya hweke sorin ko drike dumkina da , yo Dure wike proekinkra yo dima ikarmaka hamroko yo hoe ko swokina dye .
58010030	Tenam kyo braema kru dia tyete , hweke hoe ko nokwa dae dite . Ma ya hote tyete , Yomkra yo , ya wike begemi .
58010031	Ma toti taka God waremin ya krit nam durin ko tempwen hyena dyen braema .
58010032	Gyo braemknai , kronam sem gyo dima pkitiko , ma hokeko , God ya kae gyo dima kaemo , pyenkin ate ate pkite hoa gyo dimkmaepu .
58010033	Ma wike ka gyo taen ikarema tya ya domsoru tren dyeti . Ma aku gwin gyo tren dirai kominki hwyeti .
58010034	Hamo wogitmin wike ka pyenkin gyo kesu dyeti . Ma ka gua gryogryo uma taeru diroko , gyo hamaha da yoyomkiskiti , tenam gyo braemkewi , guane waenukin gwin ko dyaendyaen aenku .
58010035	Hakina kren gua tempwenaemkin kronam ko hro naedromoe . Tenam hoe hyena ko gua siwekrai kren .
58010036	Hakina kren gyo huma penkrai . Hamo God ya hoda dra homin braema . Marensu ya gyo dima swagumite gyo sen braema .
58010037	Tenam Kwonam kima tyen ko harina , kru dia pki ko din ya pkin aku ko kurya .
58010038	Ma no wike diko no hina ko ko duwa dekano ko no swa ko drinu da rwyo no kwori troko , no ko dima a yoyomki .
58010039	Kyo rwyo taka gwemkin wike ko dinaekina wirin . Kyo ko drinu din wike , hamo kua dure ko gwemkin braema wirin .
58011001	Ma dumahaki dinkrai drike ko hikina , kua hina naekin kua hodrai ko hoko taenkin braema .
58011002	Ma God ya wike semsoge kweti ko dumahaki diti kren , God ya ko dima bryoko dite .
58011003	Kyo dumahaki da hine bra braemkwe . God ya to me kwoe me homite ko ya swa me . Kua dyenkraiko yo gryo kua dyenaemkin me homina .
58011004	Ma Eibo yo dumahaki dasu ya God dima gryo hoe hyenu daete ko duwa . Ma Kein ya gryo hoe hyenu God dima daete yo kukumasa duwa . Eibo ya dumahaki dite , God ya yo dima dumraha dite . Hamo God ya Eibo ya daete ho diwa duwa dite . Ma Eibo ya pwete . Ma ya dumahaki din ho kyo dima naegiminkra .
58011005	Ma Inok ya dumahaki dite kren yo pumaepu . God ya sa tete . Ma drura diku naediti . God ya satenku . Kwonam kima tyen ko harina , yo satenaemkin hoke , God yo yo dima yoyomkite .
58011006	Ma kru ara trua God ya swa daera drinuhaki dinaemkroko , God ko yo dima yoyomkin braema wirin . Tenam kru ara diya God dima tera kroko , yatumki dumahaki da , God ko drinu pra dasu , yo druryoko , yo ka hoe daemi dinkrai .
58011007	Ma Noa ya dumahaki dite . God ya yo dima tyete kronam tru gu aekwa dyen braema wirin , hoko hamosu pki ko du yo dumaha dano yo mosore hyenu tite . Ya gire ko hokan warkiti . Ma to hyenu butmin wike ko dore dyeti . Ma Noa ko , God ya tyete , Noa ko duwa dite . Tenam yo ko dumahaki din kru kren .
58011008	Ma Abraham ya dumahaki din hoa God ya uru to , God ya tyete , gu to , to nokwa gu dima daera swagumite ho dae dite . Haru diroko ya tonae ko hro yo braema wirin hoke tete .
58011009	Ya dumahaki dinku yo to , God ya yo dima dae ko da swaguma tyen kuta hokan koisen ma hete . Ma yo prainamsa hete . Ma ya kya Aisaek me Jeikop ti kesu prainam hwyeti . Ma God ya ti dima kesu sem swaguma tyen hoasa aete .
58011010	Tenam Abraham yo to hyenu , God ya hine bra duduma tikra ho huma pete . To hyenu aewe ho ka hruke ko aepesu hamo penina .
58011011	Ma Abraham ya dumahaki dite . Ma yo sem kru korkite ma ya runaen Sera kesu arika kya simaekina wirin . Ma Abraham ko ai kite . Ya hina God ya yo dima swagumin ko dae ko dite .
58011012	Hokeko Abraham ko sem pumaekuru , ma kru trusa hoya kyankya sa wikminkiti . Kwoe kom pute ko naemo , ma wai dawara dni ko naemo ho bryoko preiki .
58011013	Ma wike hi dumahaki diti ko butmin tosuriti . God ya ko dima swagumiteko ko simaepu . Ma ko hoko wenema dyeti . Diwa duwa da taen tyeti , kyo ko keisensa , to hyenu hiko kua to nu wirin .
58011014	Ma kyo braema wike gwin ko harike tyenkrai , kyo to tru diwa sa kuanamwe dinkrai .
58011015	Ma ko to ka hro pkrai ho dima hine brenkmaepu . Ma kudi ko haminakroko ko krwyo ten braema .
58011016	Ma to waenukin ka hodrai ko Hewen . Ma ko God dima tyaka gu ko kua God droko , God yo hukwaekmaepu . Tenam yo to tru hyenma kana tina kren .
58011017	Ma Abraham ya dumahaki din hoa God ya yo bryoko diwo ya kya Aisaek ya hoe hyenu ho yo dima disiriramite . Ma Abraham yo , God ya yo dima swaguma tyeteko , ya kya trusa drike hyenu ho a daemaekina daete .
58011018	God ya yo dima tyete , gwa kyankyako , nokwa gu dima swaguma tyete ko Aisaek yo dima pkreiki dite .
58011019	Ma Abraham ya hin ko God ya Aisaek ko warmo durkyo asikraha dite . Ma drike ko harike tyen , Aisaek ko pwa durkyo asina dinaekite .
58011020	Ma Aisaek ya dumahaki dite hoa yo Jeikop me Iso ti dima hagurmo waenuma pnaida swa tyete .
58011021	Ma Jeikop ya dumahaki dasu hamo yo pwerakeka yo Josep ya kya trusa trusama hagurmo waenuma pnaida swa tyete . Ya gumo tya ya krite ko hokan hro bindima paka God dima duwa dite .
58011022	Ma Josep ya dumahakida kuta ya pwerakeka , Isrwaeo wike ka to Ijep hro twekrai swa tyete . Hamake ma ya bute homwekrai swa ho kesu tyete .
58011023	Ma Moses yai yaem ti dumahaki da kwaka Moses yo hamta naede dwarin haepki trumo hamo yo gwema hreti . Ti dyete yo ko kya waenukina . Ma ko king ya swa dima tempwenaemka prikma hama seti .
58011024	Ma Moses yo wimga dumahaki dekano , yo king ya paku ya kya dinkrai ko yo a dite .
58011025	Ma yo God ya wike kominki paka ka pyenkin dyerada . Ma yo hweke diwa kukuma yoyomkin ko yo a dite .
58011026	Ya hin ko God ya pru pkin kru yo me kren , ka yo dima ikarmin ko bryoko . Ma Ijep ka gryogryo waenukin ko drike wirin .
58011027	Ma Moses ya dumahaki din hoa yo to Ijep hro teteko , yo King ya kyom dima tempumaepu .
58011028	Ma yo dumahaki dina kren yo guri ten ro swa tyete . Ya tyo diroko ko kapoe inam dwen hokan kukusiti . Hamo God ya po penkrai kru trua , Pwen Kuyen kru , yo kumta Isrwaeo wike ka kru kya rwa myeda .
58011029	Ma Isrwaeo wike ko dumahaki diti kren ko sya Wai Kapoekin kitiko , to krikina dinaekina kiti . Hamo Ijep wike ko kesu sya kwerakeko , ko waia damga dyomgiti .
58011030	Ma Isrwaeo wike ka dumahaki dinku ko to Jeriko grare graegite sen hro aku deihraensin hamo , haguru , grare ko yaesa grwyorite .
58011031	Ma kore tyen ara Reihab ya dumahaki dinku , yo wike dika God ya swa daerinaemkin wike ko kuyeti hokeko , yo me myaekina naediti . Tenam yo Isrwaeo wike aewswamin trai ko taetaepmite .
58011032	Ma no swa gwin kesu tmyawe . No Gidien da , Barak , da Samson da Jepta , da mate Debid me Samue da mate God ya tyo tyen wike gwin ka swa tmyaeko , teikron wirinkra .
58011033	Ma ka dumahaki diti hoa ko tonesu tru minki totetiwa dimkiti . Ko dumasa homo diroko God ya swaguma sireiki dite , ko seti . Ma ko msaen raion ka mgatram ko kwakwariti .
58011034	Ma dei ko idima bu duo ka gruwiti . Ma wike gwin ko krarang m e kuwyerakiti , ma ko kumyaepu . Ma kosu ai dumkiti ma ko hote aikiti . Ma ko totityaka aewena wasi gwenin ko ka dimkiti .
58011035	Ma ara ka dumahaki dinku ko wike tosura hote durkyo asiti .
58011036	Hamo gwin ko ko dima ikarema , kupyen me kuyeti . Hamake gwinko ka kriteko auri sen me pupuma wogitmin aewe dima gyori teti .
58011037	Hamake ko ike me hatiya yaka , mate ka bute ko so me dure hokan drureka , krarang me tuma kuyeti . Ko min sip me min nanigos ka kate baima bra kwehwyeti . Ko gryogryo dumkina . Hamo wike ka ko dima kronam swoswoma homamiti .
58011038	Ma ko to hyenu hikan ko dima ko bryoko wirin , tenam ko ko waenukina kren . Ma ko dni tonae hokan mate aegu tukram aewe dumkin to inam hokan ae kweti .
58011039	Kyo wike butmin hika dumkahaki diti kren , kyo ka hi ko nononkmaepu . Ma ko God ya swaguma tyete hoeko , ko dimaepu .
58011040	Tenam God ya hine bra dudumite ko yo kronam tru kyo dima hrera . Ya hine bren sem sa homite ko sem dimkite . Ma ya hoda ko , kyomesu ko dumraiha di ,
58012001	Ma wike sem uminki homo dyeti ka kyo dima tyenkrai wike ko pya kyo hawyo prai . Hakina kren kronam naekina kua ten dweri ko tmiwa hweke kua twenkrai ko hro naede , resi da idima hwehwemke .
58012002	Ma kua kronko Yesu dima kukma diwe . Ma yatumki kyo ya swa ko drinu diti , ma marensu kua haryeiki gwa swa ko drinusa dreiki . Drinu , yo dei buti pwen ko yo a dmaepu . Ma tenam yoyomkin hyenu dyekra krenku yo dei buti pwen ko hukwae dye ma yo hoko hine brumaepu . Hamo yo aekwako , God ya krite dunaete hoke pra .
58012003	Gyo hine yoma brunai , kronam ya dyete ko . Wike hwek min ka yo dima a diti . Hakina kren gyo totoka naedwero haryomoe .
58012004	Tenam gyo sem hweke yominki totetyaka tosurmaepu .
58012005	Ma gyo nononkraike , God ya gyo taetaepmira swa tyete , tenam gyo ko ya kya krenku .
58012006	Tenam kru diko yomkra yo hoda drako , ya duminkra . Ma wike diko ya kya kuku dinkrako , ko hweke hrioko , ka dore kesu daenkra .
58012007	Hamo gyo pyenkin diroko , hiko naia ya daeraha . Gyo pyenkin diroko gyo braema , ma God ya gyo dima naemike homroko ya kya yo dima homite ho bryoko homraha . Ma kya yaiminki haka hweke hrae yai ya yo dima dore daemaepune . Kya hakin ko hrake . Wirin .
58012008	Ma kudi guai ya gyo dima dore daenaemkroko , ya kya butmin ko dima dore daenkra haminaemkroko , drike ko gyo ko ya kyanu wirin , gyo ko korkom kya .
58012009	Ma kuai to hyenu wike , ka kya kyo dore daemo kyo ko dima hine waenuma brenkrai . Hisa bryoko mate hata , kyo kuai Kwoe Kom penkra ya kyo dima naemike homroko kyo heno da kyo waenuma hwyen braema .
58012010	To hyenu hikanko kuai ka aku kukumasa ka hine ko duku diroko kyo dima dore daemamiti . Ma God ya kua duknaida , dore kyo dima daenkra , tenam ya kronam waenu yaeyosa hakin kyo kesu sinaida .
58012011	Ma kyo dore dirai hoke , kua hin ko kyo yoyomkmaepu . Ma marensu , wike dika dore ho dyenku , ko hoe ko kronam dukin me waenuma pen me hamo sireiki .
58012012	Hakina kren , gua krite kudropkin hatyoma mate gua tama ai dumkin ho aimnai .
58012013	Hamake gyo ten dukinsa troko gua karike bisayen ko domsorinaemkroko gaikin braema .
58012014	Gyo wike butmin kominki ganeswama bryokosa penknai . Hamake gyo kronam waenu yaeyosa hamikesa penknai . Haminaemkroko Yomkra yo dyen braema wirin .
58012015	Gua braeme , God ya proeki hamaha din kronam ko hro krwyo tromoe . Kru , ara trua dei ko mokekin hakromoe . Hyenkekasu ya dore hoa pyenkin daeminkra .
58012016	Kru trua Iso ya God dima a dite hamrome . Ma yo ko rwa , ya simaekina , ma yo hro sete . Tenam kudin teikron trusa dinin ho hro sete .
58012017	Ma gyo braema hamosu yo hoda yai ya hagurmin swa tyerada dite ko ma yai yo dima daemaepu . Tenam yo homiteko , hote atma homin braema wirin . Ma yo byen me drimaka sera dite .
58012018	Ma gyo Isrwaeo wike ka guri braemkit gyoko himinkmaepu . Ko aegu Sainyai dima tadi , dei rurin hyenku ma hwore mtaka hunamka hungyoru handuma dimaepu .
58012019	Hamake kibi ko ureko , swa tru tyo wyaen sa daeriti . Ma ko swa hoko daereka priti , kyo swa wyaen hakin ko hote a daeryeiki diti .
58012020	Tenam swa ko dima tyenku , kudi kru trua me ware gryogryo trua aegu ho guryoko gyo ike me ware gryogryo hoko tuma yenina .
58012021	Ma kronam hoko yae ate , hamo Moses yo kesu tempwete .
58012022	Ma gyo ko aegu Saion dima pkinaha . Ma gyo God ware men ya to Jerusraem Hewen penkra hokan dima pkina . Ma hokan ko wike God ya po penkrai wike ko pya .
58012023	Gyo God ya kya rwa dika hi ko Hewen hokan kikimina , ka yoyomkin me gaemrai dima pkina . Gyo God dima pkina . Wike butmin ka begemin kru ko yosa . Gyo wike waenu yaeyosa hakin ka dure ko dima pkina .
58012024	Gyo Yesu yo dima pkina . Yo kronam nin homa homnaida swaguma hren ho homite . Gyo ya kapoe dima pkina . Ya kapoe ya swaguma tyen ko drike hyena . Ma Eibo ya kapoea ya tyen ko drike hyena wirin .
58012025	Hakina kren , gua braema , kru diko swa tyen kru ya tyo , daereka haryomoe no ya swa a daeri haryomoe . Sem , kru trua God ya swa tyo ma wike dika ko a daeryeiki drai marensu ko dore diwa ka krya hwara tmae ten dumkiti . Ma kru trua Hewen hokan paka tyo kyo daerinaemkroko kyo krya ten braemane .
58012026	Ma hokeko swa ya trya wyaen hoa to ko gigirite . Ma aekwa ya swagumina aerako no to sa a domsori Hewen kesu domsori .
58012027	Ya homira da swa tyen ko ma gryo gryo nokwa homin ko no to ko kokoma kuwya domsori . Ma kokominaemkrai gryogryo ko yae hamo ae .
58012028	Hamo kyo ehya dwe tenam God ya wike tikminkra ko kokoma hoe yen braema wirin . Hamake kyo God dima ehya deka , ya kua naerike tnyai dinkra harike tyenkwe . Kyo tempwen ma ya hi hyenminkwe .
58012029	Tenam kua God dei dinaeka , gryogryo butmin domsormaekina .
58013001	Gyo Keriso din wike ko dima goegmore da ma hote ko dima hine pya brenknai .
58013002	Hamake gyo wike koesen gua aewe dima pko diroko , gyo pkraike dinknai . Sem wike gwin ko hamitiko , wike God ya po penkrai ko dima kudin dwe diti . Ma ko braemkmaepu ko ko God ya wike .
58013003	Hamake gyo wike dika wogitmin aewe prai ko dima hine brenko gyo kominki wogitmin hokan pena dinaekinknai . Hamake gyo wike tren min ko dima hine brenkraiko , gyo wike trenmin dyenkrai , haminina .
58013004	Ma kru trua ara sema naeduro , wike butmin ko ti dima hine waenuma brenknai . Hamo kru yo kesu ya runaen minki sa kwenina , mate ara yo kesu ya kru minki sa kwenina . Tenam wike dika kore aeng tyaka mate kru trua kru trua ya runaen uma tyawenkrai da mate ara trua ara tru ya kru uma tyawenkraiko , God ya ko begemi .
58013005	Ma gyo sere dima hine pya brenkromoe . Guae guane naemo aeroko hoko bryoko dinknai . Tenam God ya tyete ko , no gyo a kwori , ma no gyo hro a ti dina .
58013006	Hakina kren , kyo tempwen dumka twye , yomkra yo ko no taetepmin kru , hamo no a tempwi . Kru trua yo no dima naemike .
58013007	Gua yomkra ka God ya swa gyo dima naegimitiko , hamo gyo ka hwyeti me ka tosuriti ho kesu dima hine brunai . Hamake ka hina God ya swa ko drinu diti hoko gyoke haminknai .
58013008	Yesu Keriso yo ko te me aekwa me dyaendyaen hakiskina henkra .
58013009	Ma ko kronam ate ate naegimaka gyori ten atma tromoe . Ma God ya proeki hamaha din kronam ko kua tyonamgite ai dae sen braema . Ma kyo kudin ko koma da homroko ai sen braema wirin . Hamo wike gwin koma ho daera hominkraiko , hoa ko taetaepmaepu .
58013010	Ma prist wike , ko Ju wike ka God dima hine bren sunam hokan tmoe homaka ware gryogryo saio disiri twenkrai , hokan twena kroko din braema wirin .
58013011	Ma Ju wike ka prist hyenu hya yo ware gryogryo kapoe ko sa , ri waenu yaeyosa hakin hokan dima hata , hweke dware daenkra . Ma ware gryogryo ho pwereko , wike ka aewe graegite hokan disirinkrai .
58013012	Tenam hakina kren , Yesu yo kesu to hyenu hokan graegite pwete . Tenam wike hweke twenkraiko , ya kapoe me sora naedu ko hote hweke dumka hunaida .
58013013	Hakina kren , kyo aewe graegite kuta hukwae ya dyete kyo me diwe .
58013014	Tenam kyo to hyena hikan topkomnai hamo a hureiki . Kyo to hyenu pkirakra ho humrai .
58013015	Hakina kren kyo aku butmin God dima gu ko duwa dinkwe . Kua God dima duwa dinkrai ko hoe hyena Yesu yo dima daenkrai . Kua daenkrai ko , kua titwom ka tyenkrai gu ko kua Yomkra dinkrai howa .
58013016	Ma nononkromoe , gyo kronam dukin homaka , gua kore ko taetaepmo matum rwyo taetaepmo haminknai . Tenam kronam himike himinko hoe hyenu daenkrai hakina . Hamo God yo diwa yoyomkinkra .
58013017	Hamake wike gyo tikminkrai ka swa daera hominknai . Ma gua dure ko , ka tikminkraiko , aen braema wirin tenam God yo ka hominkrai ho tondaeru diroko ko rwyo hoe tryeiki . Hakina kren kudi gyo ka swa daera homroko , hamroko ko tmoe ko yoyomkin me homin braema . Ma himinaemkroko , ko yoyomkinaemka homin braema . Hamroko ko gyo taetaepmin wirin .
58013018	Gyo kua hi ko God dima yae hamo tyenknai . Ma kyo braema kua hin bren tyonam ko hweke tru aemaepu . Ma tenam aku butmin kyo hoda kronam dukinsa homwera dinkrai .
58013019	Ma no gyo dima tyera gyo God dima idima tyo ya no pru no rwyo gyo dima ti .
58013020	Kua Yomkra Yesu , yo ko min sip tikmin kru hyenu , tenam ya hoe ko hyenu ma yo pwete . Ho me krenku , swagumin hyenu ya hoe yete . Ma yo pwo diroko , God ya yo warmo durkyo asite . Ma God yo ko waenuma pen Yanai ya tmoe homaka gua mgakwen naekin hoda drai gyo dima daen braema . Ma Yesu Keriso yo kua tyonamgite homo , kyo ya hodra homin braema . Ma kae waenukin ko Keriso yo dima dyaen dyaen aenada . Haminina .
58013021	
58013022	No gmore gyoke , no hoda gyo swa hiko huma paka daenyai . Ma hiko gyo taetaepminina . Ma swa hi kimrako gawa wirin .
58013023	No hoda gyo braemknaida , kua gmore Timotiko , wogitmina hra ko hma hre yo ta . Ma kudi yo katma hikan dima pkroko , no gua pra troko yo me pkikraha .
58013024	Hamo gua duwa dwekrai ko gua wike yomkra ko me God ya wike butmin ko dima tnyai . Hamo Krwistin wike to Itari hokan penkrai ka kesu gyo dima duwa drai .
58013025	Hamo God ya proeki hamaha din kronam gyo dima aenada .
59001001	No ko Jeims . Ma no God me kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ta tmoe homin kru . Hamo nokwa gyo dima kwo hi kimra . No God ya wike to hyenu hoe hoe penkrai gyo dima duwa dra .
59001002	No gmore gyoke , kronam ate ate gyo dima bryoko diwera pko diroko , gyo hine himike brenina , God ya kyo tikminkra dinknai .
59001003	Tenam gyo braema , gyo bryoko dyen ko pko diroko , gyo Keriso ya swa ko drinu da yae hamosa kwen braema .
59001004	Ma gyo kworinaemka yae hamosa kuroko gyo bryoko pen braema .
59001005	Ma kudi gyo trua kukumasa braemkinaemkroko , yo God dima tyo , ya braemkin , kru ho dima dae . Tenam God ya daen kronam ko wike butmin ko dima waenuma hyenma daenkra .
59001006	Ma gyo God dima kentikano , gyo bubutkinaemka hine hirike brenknai , kyo sireiki dinina . Ma diya bubutkroko yo ko wai dawara ya takurin hakina . Hamo huhurina sasirinkra hakina .
59001007	Kru ara diya yo kronam naekin homira da hinesa pya bruroko yo ho ko homin braema wirin , yo ko hakina . Yo hine himike brenina wirin , no Yomkra dima gryo tru se ko dinina wirin .
59001008	
59001009	Ma Krwistin wike diya yo sere me gryo pya wirinkroko , God ya yo satyomo yoyomkinina .
59001010	Ma Krwistin wike dika sere me gryo hyenma aerurai gyo kesu yoyomkinina , God ya gyo samsya kumo diroko .
59001011	Teia hwireka kia kose ko kakaiku ruru ko toten brenkrai . Hamo ya kine ko domsorinkrai . Hote ho bryoko sere namin kru ya tmoe homi tra ko wirinki .
59001012	Ma kru ara diya bryoko dyen yo dima pko diroko , yo God ya swa ko drinu dinkra kren yo yoyomkra . Ma bryoko dyen hoko ya dimkroko , hoe ko ware yo se . Ware hoko , god ya swagumina , hamo wike dika God dima hine pya brenkrai ko ware ho siwekraiha .
59001013	Ma kutadi kru tru yo hweke hrimaekin ho yo bryoko diwo diroko yo haryome , hiko God ya bryoko dira drome . Tenam God ko kronam swokin hoa yo bryoko dyen braema wirin . Ma wike ka hweke twenkraiko , God ya pru twenkmaepu .
59001014	Ma wike ko kronam swokin ka hoda drai hoasa ko bryoko dyenkrai . Ka hoda drai hoasa sa take dainam mgenkrai .
59001015	Ma kronam swokin ka hoda drai hoko kya gen penkrai hakina marensu hweke ko kyama hamtenkrai . Ma hweke ko wimga naedeno pwen hamtenkra .
59001016	No gmore gyoke , kronam hakin hoa gyo dima kraekraeme .
59001017	Gryogryo dukin sumsa daenkra butmin ko God ya Hewen hokan hwya pru msyenkra . Ma Kwoe kae yanai yo atka hunamkinkmaepu .
59001018	Ma ya hoda du , kyo pkena . Hamo gryogryo gwin ya homin ko hurai , ma kyo ko hya .
59001019	No gmore gyoke , swa hiko gyo braemknaida . Gyo butmin katmasa daerako , ma hminsa tyenknai . Hamake katma kyomkinkromoe .
59001020	Wike ka kyom hoa , God ya waenuma homira din ko hoe yen braema wirin .
59001021	Hakina krenku kronam swokin ko wama hasinyai . Hamake God sa ko yomkra dinknai . Ma ya swa gua proenam hokan twenkra hoko senina . Hamo swa hoko gyo taetaepmo gyo a gwemkreiki .
59001022	Guae gyo kraeme . Ya swa ko daeriskromoe , daera hominknai .
59001023	Kru ara diya God ya swa daera hominaemkroko , yo kru tru yo waigiginam yae ya gingin dira hakina .
59001024	Yae yo tuma diwa takano , katmasa yae yo dyere ho ko nononkinkra .
59001025	Ma kru ara dika God ya koma waenukin homnai din hoa wike wogitmina dinaekin ko hmura two taminkrai , ho ka tuma diwa , daera nononkinaemka hamosa homi tenkrai , ho ka tmoe naekin homroko God ya ko taetaepmo ko waenuma preiki .
59001026	Ma kudi kru ara trua ya hine harike bruroko no God dima hine braka yo dima duwa da haminkrai , ma ya ti twome ko yo tikminkmaepu , hakina kren , yae yo dima rwyo kraekraha . Ma ya God dima duwa dinkra ko drike wirin .
59001027	Kuai God ya hine bren ko hiwa , gyo yo dima drinu hine waenuma brenkroko , gyo kya mgyore me mate ara kwire ten min ko tikminina . Hamake to hyenu kronam dika gyo domsorwera kroko , gua ka ten dunai , pako ho ka gyo domsormeda .
59002001	No gmore gyoke tenam kua hin bren ko kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso , kae waenukin yanai , yo dima drinu dinkraiha , hamo gyo wike ka bute graegite diwa , kronam ate ko dima hominkromoe .
59002002	Ma kutadi kru tru ya krite itkoe nam mgin gor me homina ho mga , mate bai waenukin bra , gua gaemrai yo ke pko , mate kru tru sere pya aenaemkin me mate bai domkin mga yoke pko , hamroko ti ke pko diroko , gyo kru bai waenukin brere yo dima , gu ri waenukin hikan pna da , mate kru sere pya aenaemkin yo dima ko gu wakan hna , o ma gu tmoe ti hikan no karike tkyo pna droko , gyo gua wike ko dima hine atma bra kronam swokin ko dima begemweraha . Hamo gyo hine swokin me ko begema diwa , gyo hweke mina howa .
59002003	
59002004	
59002005	No gmore , gyoke no gyo dima proekra . Ma gyo daenyai , wike diko to hyenu gryogryo pya aenaemkin ko , God ya ko taera twete , hamo ko ya swa ko drinu dinkrai . Hamo God ya swaguma tyete ma wike dika no dima hine pya brenkrai ko nokwa ko tikmikraha .
59002006	Ma gyo wike sere pya aenaemkin ka hi kuminkraiha . Ma wike dika gyo dima pyen hyenu dae , gyo sa bigi begemin kru ko dima hatenkraike . Sere min wike ka .
59002007	Hi waenukin ko gua sena kren ho dima swa swoma tyenkrai .
59002008	Ma Hewen ya king ya tyo homnai din tru ko Kwonam kimin ko harina , wike gyo kuri penkrai ko dima hine pya brenknai , guae gyo dima hine pya brenkrai ho bryoko . Ma gyo hamike homroko , gyo waenuma ho homraiha .
59002009	Ma wike ka graegite gyo diwa begemroko , gyo hweke hriraiha , ma gyo hamroko koma ya tyen ko ho kiraiha .
59002010	Tenam kru trua koma tru kiroko , koma butmin ko ya ho kiraha .
59002011	Tenam kru trua tyete , gyo kore aeng tiromoe dite kru hoasa hote tyete , gyo wike tuma yenkromoe dite ma kudi gyo kore aeng tyenaemka , ma gyo wike sa tuma ryoko , gyo ko koma kyen kru howa .
59002012	Ma koma diya wike ko hma hre tenkrai hoa wike ko begemi . Ma hoko kyo dima hami . Hamo gyo wike hakemin ka tyenkrai me ka hominkrai , gyoke haminknai .
59002013	Tenam God yo kru o ma ara tru diya sem wike gwin ko dima proekmaepu , hamo God ya yo begemroko yo dima a proeki . Ma begemin kronam ko proekin kronama dmyaena .
59002014	No gmore gyoke , kru trua swa hirike tryoko , no Keriso ya swa ka drinu dinkra , da ma ya hominkra ko bryoko naegiminaemkroko , hoko duwane . Hamroko ya drinu dinkra hoa yo taetaepmo yo warkike .
59002015	Ma kudi gua gmore o ma gua uke ko bai handuma aenaemkroko me ka butea hoda kudin pya dwera ma pya sen braema wirin . Hamroko gua haryoko God ya gyo taetepmo gyo waenuma preiki . Ma kyo aku hokeko , gyo kikima , waenuma paka , kudin waenukin dinknai ma ko pumaeku , gua ka bute tikmin gryogryo daenaemku gua ko dima harike tyen ko duwane .
59002016	
59002017	Ma kua dumahaki din ko hakina . Kyo swa hosa tyaka , tmoe hominaemkroko swa hoko pwen swasa .
59002018	Ma kru tru ya harmyaudi , kru tru yo God ya swa ko drinu dinkra . Ma kru tru ko tmoe hominkra . Haru diroko nokwa rwyo trya , kru tru ko God ya swa drinu dano ma yo tmoe hominaemkroko , kru hoko no dima naegrya . Hamo tmoe nokwa hominkra hoa naegrya ko God ya swa ko drinu dra .
59002019	Ma gu harinkrake , God ko trusa , dinkrake . Duwa . Ma tona swokin ko kesu harinkrai , drinu God ko trusasa da tempwa gigirinkrai .
59002020	Gu nononkina howa . Gu hoda kru trua gu naegimnadane . God ya swa ko drinu dano ya tmoe hominaemkroko hoko wike taetaepmin kronam wirin .
59002021	Ma kua kigwam Abraham yo naemike homo God ya yo ko duwa diteke . Yo himite . Ya kya Aisak ko ya God dima dae , kyorin ti hrete howa , God ya yo ko duwa dite .
59002022	Ma gu drike dimaepune . Ya drinuhaki da , tmoe ya homite ko pkori homite . Ma tmoe ya homite hoa ya dumahaki din ko dumite .
59002023	Ma Kwonam kima tyen ko harina , Abraham ko God ya swa ko drinu dina dite hamo God ya tyete yo ko kru duwa dite . Hamo Abraham ko God ya kire diti .
59002024	Hamo gyo diraiha , wike ka naemike hominkraiko , God ya ko dima dumraha dinkra ma gwin duwa wirin dinkra . Gua drinu din hosa wirin .
59002025	Ma kore tyen ara Reihab ya homite ko God ya dumraha dite , tenam ya duma hominku . Yo Isrwaeo kru aewswamin teti ko ya taetaepmo ko krwyo teti ko , ten ate teti .
59002026	Hakina kren , wike ka bute ko dure dumkina kroko , bute hoko pwena . Hote ho bryoko dumahaki da tmoe hominaemkin ko pwena dinaekina .
59003001	No gmore gyoke , gyo gua wike pya ko naegimin tmoesa homwera dromoe . Tenam gyo braema , wike gwin ko kukumasa begemi , ma naegimin wike kyo ko idima begemi .
59003002	Kyo butmin kweroma hominkrai . Ma kudi kru ara trua ya tyenkra hokan kweroma tyenaemkroko , yo ko waenukiskina . Hamo yo kronam butmin ya hominkra ko yae tikmin braema .
59003003	Ma kyo haminkrai , mine hose ka mgatnam ko auri me mgenkrai , tenam kua hoda drai ko ka homnaida . Ma kua hoda dike tnai droko ko tensa .
59003004	Ma mosore hyenu ka kronam dima hine bruwe . Ma ko ko hyena . Ma hwore mtaka mosore satenkra . Ma mosore ho sure ire dimin ko kukuskina . Ma Kru mosore ire dimin kru yo dike tnada dudumroko ko hoke tenkrai .
59003005	Ma kua ti ko sure kukin hakina . Ma yosu kukina , ma yae yo irinkra ko hyena .
59003006	Ma kua ti ko dei tine dinaekina . Yo ko swoswokina . Hamo yo kua tyonam haka ya swokin ho ko kua bute butmin hamo prnyenkra . Yo ko dei dinaekina , kua hominkrai butmin ko deia duenkra . Ma dei hoko Hero hokan hwya pkina .
59003007	Ma wike ko ware gryogryo butmin kyaerin braema . Ma ko sem kyaekyaemiti . Ko ware gryogryo tona , smire da mate dwo tenin mate bun kesu butmin kyaekyaeminkrai .
59003008	Ma kru truato ti ko kyaerin braema wirin . Ti ko swokina . Ma kyo hoko tikmin braema wirin . Ma yo ko wai swokin mena .
59003009	Ma kyo kua ti me kua Yomkra kuai God yo dima gu ko duwa da mate wike kyo bryoko God yae yo bryoko homiteko , ko dima gu puna dinkrai .
59003010	Ma mgatram trusa hoke ehya din swa twya mate swa swokin twya haminkrai . No gmore gyo haminina wirin .
59003011	Ma to kupram wai ko ga dore dinaekin me mokekin ti pkori paka trusa mtenkmaepu .
59003012	No gmore , dei tai ko orib ya ke yen braema wirin . Mate tike byen greip ko tai ke yen braema wirin . Mate wai damena min ko wai ga dore dinaekin braema wirin .
59003013	Ma gyo kru trua yo ko braemnain kru me ne . Hamo yo waenuma paka irinaemka tmoe waenuma braemkin me homo kyo diwa , ya braemkin kronam braemkin braema .
59003014	Ma kudi gu ko waka , pateka , grimeka hakina homroko , gu ireka , no ko braemnain kru drome . Tenam gu haryoko gu drinu swa dima hweke hriraha .
59003015	Braemkin hoko Hewen hokan hwya pkinkmaepu . Hoko to hyenu yana . Ma hoko God ya braemkin ho dinaekina wirin . Hoko tona swokin ka braemkin ho bryoko .
59003016	Ma wike dika grimeka , gwogwoeka haminkrai ko kesu tmoe , kronam swokin ate ate pya hamasa hominkrai .
59003017	Ma braemkin kronam Komgite hwya msyenkra ko duwa . Ma msya tru ko kate druki , hamaha da proekeka hakina . Ma drike ya yenkra ko kronam waenukinsa . Ma a din kronam me mate hwekmin ka gyo begeminkrai hakina wirin .
59003018	Ma wike gwin dika ko hoda wike ko ganeswama waenuma pnaida , droko , hamroko wike hakemin ka hominkrai ko dei ke dinaekina hre mto kronam dukin taerin braema .
59004001	Ma grwin bren me totetyen ko dikan hwya pkinkraike . Ka hwya pkinkrai ko , gua bute ya waenuma pwera dinkra , hoa gua tyonam grwin brenkrai .
59004002	Gyo hoda gryogryo siwera drai ma hoko sen braema wirin , hakina kren gyo wike tuma wyerakinkrai . Ma gua hoda drai ko aiya , hamo gua hoda taerinaemkroko grwine bra totetyenkrai . Ma gua hoda drai senaemkinkrai tenam gyo God dima kentinkmaepu krenku .
59004003	Ma gua kentinkrai ko gyo senkmaepu , tenam gua hoda drai ko swokina kren . Ma gryogryo gua kentinkrai , ko guae gua bute sa tikmu gyo yoyomkin me penkraida .
59004004	God ya tyo daera hominaemkin wike gyoke , gyo braemkinkmaepune , gyo to hyenu kronam hia gyo kire dina kroko gyo ko God ya wasiha . Kru ara diya hoda to hyenu hi ya kire dira kroko , yo ko God ya wasi kiraha .
59004005	Gua hina haryomoe Kwonam tru kima tyen ko drinu wirin haryomoe . Ya tyen ko , dure God ya kyo dima daete ya hoda ko hyena .
59004006	Ma God ya proekin ai ko hata . Ma Kwonam kima tyen ko harina , ma wike irinme tyenkrai ko , God yo ko gara ten dwenkra . Ma yo wike kate drukin ko dima proekinkra .
59004007	Hakina kren God ya hoda dra ko , gua hoda drai ko bryoko . Hamake , Saiten ya pko diroko , ya ten dwo yo krya ti .
59004008	Ma gyo kumta God kuri hunai . Ma God yo kesu gyo kuri ti . Ma hweke twenkrai gyo gua krite sosomnai . Ma hweke twaka wike gwin begemnai gyo gua proe waenumnai .
59004009	Gua yoyomki gan tyenkrai ko atma hro gyo byendrimnai .
59004010	Hamo Yomkra ya kinaetegite gua hi kumnai hamo yo gyo satyomi .
59004011	Gua kire matum begemo matum begemo haminkromoe . Kru diya Krwistin kru begemroko yo Koma begemraha . Ma gu Koma begemroko gu ya swa daera hominkmaepuha .
59004012	God ya sa ko Koma dae begemin kru . Ma ya sa ko domsoreka taetaepmaka hamin braema . Hakina krenku gwa hin ko gu ko naekin krune , hamo gua kire begemin braemane .
59004013	Ma wike digua harinkrai , ma aekwa di , ma te di , kyo kuta to tru sa ambum trusa dinaekina hureiki . Ma hokan ko , kyo bisnis tmoe homaka , sere hyenma taeryeiki dinkrai . Ma kru digua haryoko gyo no swa daenyai .
59004014	Ma gyo braema wirin , ma kronam tru te taenkikrako . Ma gyo ko dei tuke dinaekina . Hamo hoko diwa katma gwemkinkrai hakina .
59004015	Hamo gyo hirinknai , kudi Yomkra ya hoda droko , kyo hi homa , ho homa , hamreiki dinknai .
59004016	Ma gyo irin me sa tyenkrai ko dukmaen .
59004017	Hakina kren , kru ara diya kronam waenukin diko yo braema yae homaekina ma yo homaepu kroko yo hweke hriraha .
59005001	Ma kwasu sere namin wike gyoke , no swa daenyai . Gyo idima byendrimnai , tenam yoyomkinaemkin hyena gyo dima pkikraha .
59005002	Ma gua gryo gryo ko domkina . Ma gua bai ko papare ka dina .
59005003	Ma gua gor me gua sirba ko usigena sena . Hamo usigen hia , gua hominkrai ho dima tye . Hamake gua saiyo ko dikraha , deiya dwyenkra hakina . Aekwa aku hiko hoe yerakra , ma gyo sere pya gaema hreskeiwi .
59005004	Ma wike gua sanam tmoe hominkrai ko dima sere daemaepu . Hamo ka a din swa gyo daenyai . Ma wike gua sanam gryogryo gaeminkrai ka uryai ko , God ya kehenam mtenkra , Yomkra ai butmin sen yo dima .
59005005	Gyo to hyenu hikan paka , kudin waenukin dua mate bai waenukin bra , tmoe hyena hominaemka , hamasa swa reri hamike paka , ptoke minkinkrai , hamo kuyen aku ho pko diroko , gyo ko sem ptokmena kren kuyenina .
59005006	Ma gyo sem wike gwin ko begema kuyetiko , ma ko hweke hrimaepu . Ma ko rwyo gyo dima totetyen braema wirin .
59005007	No gmore gyoke , gyo yomkra ya pkikra aku ho huma penkrai . Ma gyo braema kru sanamnai yo drike yo gaemira huma penkra . Ma Kwoe hwyaen aku hokeko yo wai surirada huma penkra .
59005008	Hamo gyo kesu huma pakano , totokromoe , tenam Yomkra ya pkin aku ko kurya kren .
59005009	No gmore gyoke , gyo guaesa swa swokin matum tyo tyo haminkromoe . Hakina kren pako God ya gyo begemeda . Begemin kru ko kurya , yo sem taenkmaekra .
59005010	No gmore gyo , God ya tyo tyenin wike ko Yomkra ya hinamsa tyamamiti ho braemknai . Ma ka pyenkin me mate tren me diwa huma peti kyoke hamike homwe .
59005011	Ma ko huma peti kren kyo harinkrai ko ko yoyomkin wike dinkrai . Ma kru Joub ya huma pete swa ko gyo daerinkrai . Ma gyo braema ya huma pen aku ko wirinku diroko , Yomkra ya yo taetaepmite ko . Tenam Yomkra ya proekin ko hyena kren .
59005012	No gmore gyoke , swa hiko nokwa gyo dima yoma tyerakra . Hamo gyo hi ko dima hin pya brenkrai . Gyo swa tru swaguma tyerakeka , mgakwen tru , ya hi me tryomoe . Ma gyo Hewen ya hi da mate to hyenu ya hi da mate gryogryo tru ya hi me tryomoe . Gyo naekin tmoe homwerakroko , kyo homwe disknai . Ma gyo a homreiki droko , a homreiki disknai . Hosa hamike homroko God ya gyo a begemi .
59005013	Ma pyenkin trua kru o ara digyo dima pkeke . Hamo gu God dima tyenina . Ma kru ara trua yo yoyomkrake . Hamroko yo God dima duwa da yoyomkin yoke ginina .
59005014	Ma kru ara trua yo tren menane . Hamroko gu Sos yomkra wike ko uru pknai . Ko kumta Yomkra ya hinam God yo dima , yo dima tyenina . Hamake ko owera orib sa ya ku ti dripminina .
59005015	Ma ka God dima tyen hiko ka dumahaki din hoa kru ara tren min hi ko gaimo asi . Yomkra ya yo gaima hweke ya hren ko hamaha di .
59005016	Hakina kren , hweke gua twen ko gua kire ko dima matum wainsae matum wainsae haminknai . Hamake gua kire dima God dima matum tyo matum tyo hamroko gua tren ko wirinki . Ma kru ara waenukin ka God dima tyenkrai ko ko ai hyena .
59005017	Ma Iraija ko to hyenu wike kyo bryoko . Ma yo God dima idima tyaka wai pru suryome du diroko , wai ko surmaepu . Hamo to hokan ko , ambum haepki trumo ma tru ko braeke wai ko surmaepu .
59005018	Ma yo hote God dima tyo diroko , wai ko idima surite . Suru to ko wai menkusu , kudin yon ko deri mta drike yeti .
59005019	No gmore gyoke , kudi kru ara trua drinu swa ko yo daera a du ma kru ara trua yo hipya rwyo sapkroko , gyo braemknai , kru ara diya hwekmin ko hipya , pkroko ya dure ya pwen ten dwen braema . Hamo hweke pya ya twen ko hamaha din braema .
59005020	
60001001	No ko Pita , hamo no ko Yesu Keriso ya tmoe homin kru tru . Hamo kwo hiko nokwa God ya wike to Ponta me Geresia me Kapadosia me Asia me Betenia hokan dima krya hwara teti , gyo dima kimra .
60001002	Uminki , guai God ya gyo taeri twenko , ya hoda ho kren . Ma ya Dure ya homo , gyo tei atka waenuka , Yesu Keriso ya swa ho daera dumahaki du , ya kapoe me gua hweke ko sora wirinmite .
60001003	Tenam yo kyo dima proe pya tyenkra , kyo ware nin seti . Kua ware nin seti ko , God ya himite . Yesu ko to gyenam ae God ya yo warmo durkyo asite . Hamo kyo huma posu , God ya kumta kyo taeri .
60001004	Taerasu Hewen hokan ya wike ko dima waenukinin daemo kyoke taerin braema . Hamo hoko yo Hewen hokan tutuma , guana hrena tikminkra . Ma hoko domka wirinkin braema wirin .
60001005	Hamo , God ko drinu dinkrai gyoke , hoko guana . God ya aia , gyo tikminkra . Ma hoa gyo tikmo , marenkuro ya gyo taetaepmo gyo dei duen tonae a sryeiki . Ma kronam hoko to hyenu hia hoe yekra aku hoke , taenki .
60001006	Hamo gyo yoyomkinina . Ma aekwako , gyo yoyomkinaemkin dirai . Hiko bryoko . Tenam pyenkin ate ate ka gyo bryokae bryokaemrai .
60001007	Ko hoda braemkwera gyo God dima drinu dumahaki dinkraike , ma drinu dinkmaepune . Ma kyo braema howa , gor ko , doomsorin braema , hamo gor ko , dei me bryoko dyenkrai . Ma gua dumahaki din ko gor ho dinaekina wirin . Gua dumahaki dinko , gor ko dimkina . Hankina kren , gua dumahaki din kesu bryoko dyen braema . Hamroko grurin braema wirin . Hamo maren Yesu Keriso ya pkikra aku hokeko gua hi ko hyenmreiki .
60001008	Ma gyo yo dyenaemkrai ho yo dima proekinkrai . Ma aekwako , gyo yo dyen braema wirin , ma gyo yo dima dumahaki dinkrai . Hakin kren gua yoyomkin ko hyena , waenukina . Yoyomkin hiko yae ate , kyo swama tyen braema wirin .
60001009	Tenam gua dure ko sem ware sena kren , gwemkin braema wirin . Hi siwera krenku , gyo yo dima dumahaki dinkrai .
60001010	Ma kua dure gwemkinaemkin swa hiko God ya tyo tyen wike ka swa hi ya drike ko naenam aerake da drureka diwa tyeti , God ya gyo dima daekra hiko taenkiko diti .
60001011	Ma ko hoda braemkwera , kronam hiko aku dikroke naekina taenki pkmawe da druriti . Ma aku hiko , Keriso ya Durea ka tyonam haka tyete , marensu Keriso yo tren tei ate ate diwosu ya hi hireiki .
60001012	God ya tyo tyen wike hi ko dima naegimi tyete , tmoe ka hominkrai ko kae ko sa taetaepmin braema wirin . Tmoe hoko gyo taetaepmin braema . Ma ka tyeti , kru aekwa hupe waenukin hi gyo dima naegimo daerewi hote ho bryoko . Ma Dure Waenukin ko God ya kom Hewen hokan pru psya , ya aime hupe waenukin hi naegimreiki . Ma hupe hiko , wike , God ya po penkrai kokesu , daera braemkwera dinkrai .
60001013	Hakina kren , gua bidore ko hine yoma braka tmoe waenuma homin braema . Hamo gyo hine yoma bra pa diwo , Yesu Keriso yo taenki ya gyo dima daemo siwekrai ho dima yoma hine brenknai .
60001014	Ma gyo God ya tyo daera hominknai . Ma sem uminki gyo nononki hwyetiko , gua hodrai ya gyo tikmite . Pako hine hoa gyo tikmeda .
60001015	God gyo urite ko waenukina , hakina kren gyo kronam naekin homroko God ya kronam waenukin hosa bryoko hominknai .
60001016	Kwonam tyen ko harina no ko waenukiskina henkra . Hakina kren , gyo kesu waenuma hwyenknai dina .
60001017	Ma gyo God dima swa twyerakekano , yo dima ko ai dinkrai . Yo kyo butmin trusa trusama kua hominkrai ko diwa , bryoko sa begeminkra . Hakina kren , gyo aku naemo to hyenu hikan hwyakano , gyo yo dima hine waenuma brenknai .
60001018	Tenam gyo braema sem uminki , gua kigwam ka kronam drike dumkin gyo dima naegimo , gua homamiti . Hamo God ya gyo hro sa , hmora two teti . Ma ya gyo hro sete hoe ko , gyo braemaha . Ma hoko mgakwen domkmaekin , sirba me gor hakina wirin .
60001019	Ma ya gyo sumsa hro sete hoe hyenu , hoko Keriso howa yo ko min sip bi dinaekina , swokin tru wirinsa .
60001020	To hyenu hominaemkin hoke , God ya yo diwasa hrete . Ma ya taenkiteko , aekwa to hyenu hoe ko , ya kyo taetaepmira .
60001021	Ma ya pkinku , gyo God ko drinu hra dinkrai . Ma ya Keriso yo to gyenam ae , ya warmo asu diroko God ya hi hyenmite . Hakina kren gyo God ko drinu dinkrai . Hamake gyo yoyomkin me tmaeki po , ya kumta gyo taeryaida .
60001022	Hamo gyo drinu swa hoko daera homaka kronam swokin , gua sem homewi hoko guaesa hro naede , mate wike gwin dika Keriso ya swa drinu dinkrai , ko dima drinu proeki , hine pya brenkrai . Hamo gyo ko dima proeki hine pya bro , matum proeki hine pya bro haminknai .
60001023	Gyo ware nin sena . Ma hoko guai guaem ka gyo hamo dwe dimaen . Ware ka daen hoko wirinkin braema . Ma nin hiko yae dyaendyaen hamo aen braema . Tenam ware dyaen dyaen swa ko Keriso ya sapkina .
60001024	Ma Kwonam kima tyen ko harina . Kru ara butmin ko kose dinaekina . Ma ka kutekin ko kose ka ruru yenkrai hakina . Ma kose ko kakaiku diroko ka ruru kesu kakaika kwerinkrai .
60001025	Ma Yomkra ya swa ko aepesu dyaendyaen yae hamo ae .
60002001	Hakina kren , hweke gua hominkrai butmin ko hro naednai . Guae gyosa ko duwa deka wike gwin ka kronam swokina wike gwin ko dima bukramgite tyenkromoe . Hamake korenkeka , aengengkeka , wakeka , haminkromoe . Swa swokin hamasa tyaka haminkromoe .
60002002	Hamo kya kwatema hamtrai ko dinaekinknai . God ya swa ko tute dore dinaekina , hamo ho dima hine pya brenknai . Ma gyo hodroko , braemki aikeka hweke ya dore ko gyo dyen braema wirin .
60002003	Ma Kwonam kima tyen ko , guaesa drureka Yomkra ya proekin kronam ko .
60002004	Hakina kren gyo yo dima pknai . Ma yo ko ike warmen ho dinaekina . Ma kru ara ka hinko , ike ho ko swokina da hro naediti . Ma God ya hin ike ho ko waenuku diku yasa hrete .
60002005	Ma gyo kesu ike waremen no dinaeka pknai . Kumta tyenina , no hiwa , gu kyo sa hre , gwa Dure ya aewe kutinina . Hamo gyo hokan hwyaka , God ya prist tmoe homin dinaeka , ka hoe hyenu , God dima daenko Yesu Keriso yo dima daesu ya daenina .
60002006	Tenam Kwonam kima tyen ko , Ike tru , ya hoe hyenu ko , nokwa diwa sa hrena . Ma ike hiko to Saion krigwotnam hokan hrera . Hamo kru ara dika yo dima dumahaki droko , ko yo dima totokin braema wirin .
60002007	Hakina kren wike digua yo dima dumahaki dinkrai , ike hiko drike hyena . Ma wike dika yo dima dumahaki dinaemkroko , Kwonam kima tyen ko , ma aewe tin wike kato , ike hiko bryokmaepu diti . Marensu wike butmin ka hin , ike ho ya drike ko hyena , ike gwin butmin ko yasa dimkina dyeti .
60002008	Ma Kwo tru hokan tyen ko , Ike hiko wike ko hokan totora toten braema .
60002009	Ma gyo ko ya taeri twena . Gyo ko King ya prist . Gyo ko ya wike waenu yaeyosa hakina . Hamo gyoko yae yana . God ya gyo taeri tweteko , gua wike gwin ko dima ya homite ho naegimnaida . Ma ya gyo uru , gyo hunam ko hro naede , kumta kae waenukin sena .
60002010	Ma uminki ko , gyoko God ya wike wirin , guae hamasa kweti . Ma aekwa , gyoko God ya wike , hamo yominki hurai . Sem uminki God ya proekin kronam ko gyo braemkmaepu . Ma aekwa ya proekin kronam ko gyo ho sa naedraiha .
60002011	O Kire gyoke , gyo ko tonesu ate wike dinaekina , hamo gua bute ya kronam swokin hoda duro , daeryomoe . Gua bute ya hoda me mate gua dure ya hoda ho ta grwine brenkrai .
60002012	Gyo wike God dima hine brenaemkrai kominki hwehwyenki gyo pitmasa kwenknai . Hamo ka gyo ko swokina dasu , maren ko gua kronam waenukin ho diwasu ko braemkwekraiha . Ma aku God ya pkikra hoke ko God ko duwa dwekraiha .
60002013	Ma gyo ko yomkra yana kren , to hyenu wike kua yomkra ka swa pa daerinknai . Ma king hyenu , wike butmin tikminkra ya swa kesu daerinknai .
60002014	Hamake , Gaman wike , King ya pru , ko wike kronam swokin hominkrai ko dima hoe swokin daenkrai da mate wike kronam waenukin hominkrai ka hi hyenmaka haminkrai ka swa kesu daerinknai .
60002015	Ma God ya hoda gyo kronam waenukin homnaida hamo wike nononkin ka swa swokin tyenkrai kronam waenukin hoa ka aten dwenknai .
60002016	Ma gyo wogitminaemka guaesa kwenka , kronam swokin hominkrai ko katryomoe . Gyo ko God ya hro sena dinaekina hunai .
60002017	Ma gyo wike butmin ko dima hine pitma brenknai . Ma wike dika Keriso ya swa ko drinu dinkrai ko dima proeki hine pya brenknai . Hamake gyo God dima tempwenknai . Ma King yo dima kesu hine pitma brenknai .
60002018	Ma tmoe homin wike gyoke , gua tikmin wike ka swa daerinknai . Hamake ko dima hine pitma brenknai , yomkra waenukin ko dimasa wirin , tmoe hyenma daenkrai ko dima kesu , hine pitma brenknai .
60002019	Ma kudi gyo pyenkin diwa kyomkinaem kroko , tenam gyo braema hiko God ya hodra ho krenku , maren God ya gyo taetaepmo , gyo waenuma preiki .
60002020	Ma kudi gyo kronam swokin gua homa dore diwa kyomkinaemkraiko hoe waenukin sen braemane . Wirin . Ma kudi gyo kronam waenukin homo , gyo dima pyenkin dae diroko , God ya gyo hagurmi .
60002021	God ya gyo uriteko , kronam hikin dyenknaida . Ma Keriso ya tren dyete gyo dima . Hamo gyoke tren diwa hamike homnaida .
60002022	Ma yo hweke tru hrimaepu . Ma yo swa tru kraekraema tyo , daermaepu .
60002023	Ma ka yo dima ike arema tyakmyetiko , yato rwyo ko dima hoe ikarma tmyaepu . Ma yo tren dyetiko , yato ko dima kyom swa tru tmyaepusa . Ma ya hine ko God dimasa hrete . Tenam yo ko dumasa begemin kru kren .
60002024	Keriso yaesa kua hweke ko ya sa , ya buti hro , dei buti hokan pwete . Ya hamike homite kren , tenam kyo ko hweke dima pwen wike dinaeka , kronam waenukin sa hominknaida . Yo yeti kren , gyo ko gaia waenukina .
60002025	Ma gyo ko min sip dinaeka ka ten ko kwori atokma teti . Ma aekwa gyo krwyo pkina . Min sip tikmin kru gua dure tikmo ya mare trai .
60003001	Hote ho bryoko , ara kormin gyoke , gua kru ka tryai daerinknai . Ma kudi kru gwin ko God ya swa ko dumahaki dinaemkroko , ko gua hamike homrai diwa , ko kesu dumahaki din braema . Ma gyo swa tru tyenina wirin .
60003002	Tenam gua kore tyenaemkin me gua God dima hine bren hoko ko dyen braema .
60003003	Ma guae gua bute waenuknaida kutekin driminkromoe . Gyo gua binmten waenuknaida homaka , bai waenuka naekin bra kutekin drimu waenuknaida hamike hominkromoe .
60003004	Haminaemka kronam hisa hominknai . Gua kineko guae gua kronam howa . Paku ko kate druki kroko , ari ko kate druki kroko , God ya diwa , drike hyena howa dinkrai .
60003005	Sem uminki ara dika God dima hine breti , ka kine ko ka kru ka swa daeriti .
60003006	Ma Sera yo hamike homite . Yo Abraham ya tryasa daera homamite . Ma yo dima ko nanainu demite . Hamo kudi gyo kronam waenukin sa homaka mgakwen dima tempwenaemkroko , gyo ko Sera ya pakunuha .
60003007	Hote ho bryoko , kru ara min gyoke , gua runaen kominki paka braemknai , ka bute ko aia wirin . Hakina kren ko dima hine pya brenknai , tenam ko kesu gyominki , ware dyaendyaen God ya daen ho siwekraiha . Hamo gyo kronam himikesa homi proko , gyo God dima twyerakroko kronam ate ten dwen braema wirin .
60003008	Aekwa no hoda swa hiko wirinmira . Hamo gyo hine trusa brenknai . Hamaka gyo rwyo proeku rwyo proeku haminknai .
60003009	Hamo kru dika gyo dima kronam swokin homo diroko matumke kronam swokin ko dima homromoe . Ma ko gyo dima a du diroko , ya hoe ko dima a dinkromoe . Hamo diroko , himinina . God dima tyaka , wike hoko hagurmna dinina . Tenam God ya gyo ura tyete ko harite , nokwa gyo hagurmi ko dite .
60003010	Kwonam kima tyen ko harina , kru dia yo hoda waenuma pera droko , swa swoma tyaka , mate kraekraema tyaka haminkrai ko hro naedinina .
60003011	Hamaka kronam swokin hominkrako hro naede , kronam waenukin sa hominina . Hamo yo hine yoma bra , tmoe waenuma homaka wike gwin ko dima kire dinina .
60003012	Tenam yomkra yo wike dukin butmin ko , ya kron me diwa taetaepminkra . Ma ka yo dima tryoko yo daerin braema . Ma yo , wike ka hweke twenkrai ho diwa ten dwenkra .
60003013	Ma kudi gyo hine yoma bra tmoe waenuma homwera droko , kru diya gyo domsorin braemane .
60003014	Ma gyo kronam waenukin homaka , pyenkin pko diroko , gyo yoyomki hwyenkrai . Ma gyo wike gwin ko dima tempuromoe . Hamaka hin pyenma aatma bruromoe .
60003015	Ma gyo Keriso dima ko gua proe me waenuma braka , Yomkra ko yosa dinknai . Gua siwekrai ko yatumki hine bra huma pakadi , aku tru kru trua tondaeru diroko gua siwera huma prai drike ho tyenina .
60003016	Ma gua rwyo yo dima tyen ko pitmasa hmihmima tyenina . Ma gua hin bren ko , hweke ae diroko , sonyai . Hamo kudi kru gwin ka Keriso ya wike gyo dima ikarema tyaka gua homrai ko swokina droko , marensu ko gua kronam waenuma homrai ho diwasu , hukwaekwekraiha .
60003017	Ma kudi God ya hoda droko , kronam waenukin gua homrai dware pyenkin gua sirai hoko bryoko . Ma kudi kronam swokin gua homrai dware hoe swokin siroko , hoe sen ko bryoko ma kronam swokin gua homrai ko bryoko wirin .
60003018	Keriso yo aku trusa kua hweke dware pwete . Ma yo ko kru waenukiskina . Hamo yo wike hwekmin ko dima pwete . Ya gyo sa kumta God kuri hrete . Hamo ka yo yetiko , yo wike dinaeka ho yeti . Ma ya dure ko warki asina hra .
60003019	Hamo ya dure ko kuta dure wogitkina hurai ko dima naegimi kwete .
60003020	Sem uminki Noa ya mosore tite hokeko , wike God ya swa ko a du , God yo ko tmaekite , ka dure ko howa . Ma wike kukumasa ko mosornam teti ka sa dei seti . Kru ara krigwotesin hamosa ko waia kumyaepu .
60003021	Hamo wai hiko aripe hro naegimna dinaekina . Ma wike wai bra hamtenkrai hakina . Ma hoko gyo taetaepmin braema . Ma hoko gua bute ho tupe sorin braema wirin . Hoko gua proe sa soru waenukinina . Hoko God dima swagumin howa . Yesu Keriso warmo asite kren gyo yo dima ware sena .
60003022	Hamo yo sem Hewen dima tena . Yo God ya krite dunaetegite paka wike God ya po penkrai hyenu hyenu da mate gwin ka ai hata ko hote hamsya Keriso ya tukram penkrai .
60004001	Tenam Keriso yo tren hyena dyete kren , gyo kesu hine hamike hine bra aikinknai . Ma kru ara dika ko tren diroko , hweke ka twenkrai ko hro naedraiha .
60004002	Hakina kren , gyo to hyenu hikan hwyakano , bute ya hodra hominkromoe , gyo God ya hodra hosa hominknai .
60004003	Gyo sem uminki , wike God braemkinaemkrai ka hodrai homo gyoke homamiti . Gyo kore aeng tyaka , wai pya dua nononkeka , kudin hyenma deka , pi grwika , mate gryo kritme homin ho dima gu ko duwa da kronam swokin homaka homamiti .
60004004	Hamo aekwa gyo kronam swokin hominkrai kominki kwenaemku , ko gyo diwa , gigirma , ikaremenkrai .
60004005	Ma ko hamosu ka homiti ko God dima tryeiki . Hamo God ya wike waremin da mate tosurin wike ko begemira humra .
60004006	Hakina kren yo uminki kusya hupe waenukin hiko tosurin wike ko dima kesu naegimite . Ma ko begemitiko ko ware hwyeti hoke . Wike butmin hamo begemikra hote hakina . Hamo hupe waenukin hi ko dima idima naegimite , tenam ko atka dure kroko God ya henkra ho bryoko hunaida .
60004007	Ma aekwa ko gryogryo butmin ka hoe yen aku ko sem kuria . Hamo guae gyo tikmaka , hine pitma bra God dima tyenknai .
60004008	Ma gua hine hya brenko , wike gwin ko dima hine pya brenknai . Tenam hin pya bren kronam ko hweke pya katinkrai .
60004009	Ma wike gua aewe dima pkroko , totokinkromoe .
60004010	Ma God ya gyo dima trusa trusama daemin ho me tmoe homaka wike gwin ko taetepmaka haminknai .
60004011	Ma kru ara diya naegimin braema kroko , God ya swa naegiminina . Hamo kru ara diya wike gwin taetaepmin braema kroko , God ya ai , yo dima daen ho me taetaepminina . Hamroko wike gwin ko ho diwa , ko Yesu keriso ya hinam God ko duwa din braema . Tenam kae me ai me ko dyaendyaen yanesa .
60004012	No kire gyoke , gyo bryoko diwo gyo tren diwa , gimromoe . Hamo gua ho dirai ko ate da gyo gimromoe .
60004013	Wirin , gyo yoyomknai , Keriso ya tren dyete , gyo hmene ho diraiha . Marensu gyo ya kae waenukin diwa yoyomkin hyena dyen braema .
60004014	Ma tenam gyo ko Keriso ya wike kren , ka gyo dima ikarma tyakmiroko , gyo yoyomkisknai . Tenam ya drike ko God ya dure waenukin ko gyominki henku .
60004015	Ma kudi gyo kru trua pyenkin dira , ya teinam ko , yo ko wike tuma yena o ma , yo ko uma taerina o ma yo wike gwin ka tmoe hamasa domsorina kronam hamike homin ko bryoko wirin .
60004016	Ma gyo Krwistin dina kren , hamo gyo pyenkin diwa hukwaekromoe , God dima duwa dnai , tenam gyo Keriso ya hi sena kren .
60004017	Begemin aku ko pkirakra . Ma God ya wikenu ko katumki begemi . Ma kyo kuatumki begemroko , wike gwin God ya hupe waenukin daera ko dumahaki dmaepu , ko ko naemawe .
60004018	Ma Kwonam kima tyen ko harina , wike dukin ko , tmoe hyena homo diroko , ka gwemkin ten dwen braema . Hakina kren wike hwekmin ko ko God dima a dinkrai , ma ko dike treikike .
60004019	Hakina kren , wike dika pyenkin diroko , tenam ko god ya hodra ho kren , hamo ko tmoe waenuma homaka ko homiten kru ya swa ko drinu dinkrai , tenam yo homira da swagumin ko yo dumasa hominkra .
60005001	No ko yomkra . Hamo nokwa yomkra gyo dima kimra . Ma Keriso ya tren hyena dyeteko , nae no kron me dyete . Hamo kae taenkikrako , no kesu se .
