60005002	Ma nokwa gyo dima tyera , min sip gua tikmnada , God ya gyo dima daen ko gyo pitma tikminknai . Ma gyo ko totoma tikminkromoe . God ya naemike tikminknai dra hamike tikminina . Ma tenam gua tmoe homa sere sen hosa wirin . Gyo tmoe waenuma hominknai , tenam gyo wike taetaepmwera kinku .
60005003	Ma wike diko gua tikmnaida God ya daete , ko dima yomkrakromoe . Gua waenuma homrai ho diwa , koke hamike homin braema .
60005004	Hamo sip tikmin kru hyenu yo pko diroko , gua ku kusinin waenuka , kae min yae hamo aen ho taerwekraiha .
60005005	Hote ho bryoko , kwaten kru gyo , kru yomkra ka swa daerinknai . Ma gyo butmin ko , wike gwin ka tmoe homin wike dinaekinknai . Tenam Kwonam kima tyen ko harina , God yo wike kae ko rwyo irinkrai ka ten dwenkra . Ma wike ka ko rwyo irinaemkraiko yo taetaepminkra .
60005006	Guae gyo kuminknai , God ya krite aikin tukram hokan hwyenknai . Hamo aku tru dikan ya gyo ko bryokae diwasu , ya gyo satyomi .
60005007	Ma gua hine pyenma brenkrai butmin ko yo dima hrinai . Tenam yo gyo dima hine pya braka tikminkra .
60005008	Ma gyo braeme , pa dinai . Saiten ko gua wasiha . Yo ko msaen raion dinaeka gehmenka itki kwehaka , kru o ara tru tuma ya dira drurikwenkra .
60005009	Hakina kren , gyo God ya swa ko drinu dinkrai . Ma Saiten ya homiraku diroko ten dunai . Tenam gyo braema , wike gwin God ya swa drinu dinkrai , to hyenu hoe hoe penkrai , ko kesu pyen hikina dyenkrai .
60005010	Hamo gyo aku kukuma pyenka hikin diroko , God yo ko proeki hamaha din teinam nai . Ma ya gyo uru gyo Keriso yominki to kae men hokan dyaendyaen penknaida . Ma ya gyo dudumo gyo bryokaereiki . Hamo ya gyo ai dae , hruke aikin ryeiki .
60005011	God ko ai yanai . Hamo ai hiko yae aepesu hamo aenada . Haminina .
60005012	Nokwa kwo goma gyo dima hi kimraha . Ma Saires ya no taetaepmra . Nokwa hin brura ko Saires ya Krwistin tmoe ko waenuma hominkra . No hoda gyo dima tyera , gua hominkrai ko duwa . Hamo nokwa braemkra ho tyera , kronam hiko God ya proeki hamaha din kronam ko hiwa . Hamo gyo ho me aiki hwyenina .
60005013	Ma Krwistin wike , to Babiron hikan prai , ko ko gua uke ho bryoko tenam God ya ko kesu taeri twena kren , gyo dima duwa drai . Ma no kya Mak ya kesu harya .
60005014	Gyo Krwistin wike ko diwano , ko knaiyaeminknai , hoko gua proekin naegiminina .
61001001	No ko Saimon Pita , hamo no Yesu Keriso ya tmoe homnada pru pkina . Hamo kua God , ma kua ware hro sen kru Yesu Keriso ka kronam waenukina krenku , gyo dumahaki din kronam sena , kua sen ho bryoko , gyo dima hi kimraiha .
61001002	Ma proekin kronam da mate waenuma pen kronam ko gyo dima aenada . Tenam gyo God ma kua yomkra Yesu Keriso ti braemkrai kren .
61001003	Drinu yo ko God , ya ai ko hyena , hamo ai hoko kyo dima daena . Hamo kyo God ya kronam ho diwa , homin braema . Kru trua kyo urite . Ya kronam waenukin me ya kae waenukin ho kyoke sinaida . Kyo yo braemkroko sen braema .
61001004	Ma ya sem swagumite hoko , kyo dima daena . Hiko ai hyena , waenukina . Hamo kyo hi me sena kren to hyenu gryo domsorwerakrai hoato , kyo domsorin braema wirin . Hamo gyo God ya kronam ho bryoko hwyen braema .
61001005	Tenam hakina kren gyo dumahaki diskin kromoe . Kronam waenukin me hopma hominknai . Hamo braemkin me mate kronam waenukin me hopma hominknai .
61001006	Hamake gua bute ya hodra tikmaka mate gua braemkin home pkori hominknai . Hamake kronam pyenkin ko pko diroko gyo aiki hamosa hwyenknai . Hamake ai ho sa naede , God ya kronam hrenina .
61001007	Hamakeno wike gwin ko dima proeknai , gua goe gmore ko dima proekinkrai ho bryoko . Ma gyo kronam hamike homakano ko dima hine pya brenina .
61001008	Ma kronam hikin ko gyo dima aenina . Ma kudi kronam hikin ko gyo dima hyena aeroko , gyo kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ko braemki gyo tmoe aiki waenuma homreiki .
61001009	Ma kru dia kronam hikin ko yo dima aemaepu , kru hoa wike me gryo yo kuri hurai ko dyen braema , ma wike kukuma wenema hurai ko yo handuma dyen braema wirin . Hamake kru ho hweke sem ya uminki twete ko sorina yo nononkite .
61001010	Hakina kren , kire gyoke , God ya gyo urite ho , mate ya gyo taera twete ho dima hine bra , aiki homo hoko gyo dima aepesu yae hamo aenina . Gyo hamike homroko gyo totin braema wirin .
61001011	Hamo Kua Yomkra me kua gwemkin ten dwen kru Yesu Keriso , yo kyo aepesu tikmikra hokeko ya gyo kesu hamo tikmi .
61001012	Swa hiko sem naegimo , gyo braemkewi hosa hote naegimira gyo braemknaida . Ma drinu swa hoko gyo tuma sena .
61001013	Ma no hin no hra hike , kronam gua braemkiti hoko gyo hote hine bra braemknaida .
61001014	Ma no braema no bute ko sem hro naedirakra . Kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya no dima harike tyete .
61001015	Hakina kren nokwa gua braemkin ten ko homasu , no puroko , maren kronam hiko gyo a nononkreiki .
61001016	Ma kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya ai me pkite ko , kyo wike ka song swa hakin ho gyo dima tmyaepu . Kuae kua kron me ya aiko kyo ho dyetiha .
61001017	Ma kyo hokan hwyo , kuai God ya hi hyenmo , God ya kae nam waenukin hokan swa tru tyete ko , hiko no kyanu , no yo dima hine pya brenkra du daeriti .
61001018	Ma kyo yominki , God ya aegu ti hokan hwyo , wyaen hoko kom Hewen hokan tyo pko daeriti .
61001019	Hakina kren kyo God ya tyo tyen wike ka tyeti ko daera drinu diti . Ma aekwa kyo drinusa dinkrai . Hamo gyo kesu ka swa daera drinu din ko bryoko . Ka swako , hunamku , twan kaema hrena dinaekina . Hamo ukan kwoe kaekirakuro mate dwarin gye ya kae gua tyonam mtroko , naedi .
61001020	Ma gwin gyo nononkroko , ma swa hiko nononkromoe . Kronam tru hamosu pkikrako , God ya tyo wike ko daera kwonam kimiti hoko kru trua yae ya kumasa drike hoko naegimin braema wirin .
61001021	Tenam hamosu pkin swa ko , kru trua ya tyera tmyaepu . Ma wike dika God ya durea ko tikmo , God ya ko dima tyen ko hosa naegimiti .
61002001	Sem uminki wike kraekraema naegiminkrai ka Isrwaeo wike ko dima naegimiti . Hote ho bryoko wike kraekraema naegiminkrai wike ko kumta gyo dima kraekraema naegimreiki . Ko swa kraekraemin me domsorin swa ate ate pya tyaka , mate Yanai , ya ko hro sete ko , kyo yo braema wirin haryeiki . Hamo hoko kae kosa rwyo domsoryeiki .
61002002	Kae ko rwyo domsoryoko , wike pya ko kore aeng tyaka , kronam swokin tei ate ate homo diwa , ko ke hote hamike homwekraiha . Hamo wike gwin ka kronam swokin ka hominkrai ho diwa , Ten Drinu hoko swokina dreiki .
61002003	Ma wike riorekin ka gyo dima kraekraema naegimaka sere taerweraha . Hamake ko tei ate ate kaesa hine bra , naegimreiki . Ma Kru ko begeminkra yo sem huma penkra . Ma ko domsoron Kru yo krogoe aenkmaepu .
61002004	Ma wike God ya po paka hweke tweti , God ya ko hre tmaepu . Yo ko Hero hokan wogitmite . Ma ko sen me pupuma hrena hunam hokan kwenkrai . Ko hokan ko begemin aku hosa humrai .
61002005	Ma kru ara sem uminki peti ko kesu God ya pru wai aene hyena wya , wike God ko ko a diti , butmin ko waia kuyete . Ma yo Noa me wike dehraensin hamo kosa tikmo waia myaepu . Ma Noa yo kronam waenukinsa hominknai da naegimite .
61002006	Ma God yo to Sodom me Gomora ti kesu begema dore daenina dite . Tonesu haepki hi ti ko , God ya dei me disirite . Hamo , wike dika God ko a drai ko dima pkikra ho naegimo ko braemknaida .
61002007	Ma Rot ko duwa kren , God yo yosa sete . Ma wike ko koma daerinaemka , ka buta hodra hosa hominku Rot yo ho diwa a dite .
61002008	Ma kru dukin hoko kominki aku pya hwyadi , ko kronam swoswokin ka homrai ho diwa mate ka swa swokin tryai ho daera yo a dite .
61002009	Ma bryoko dyen ko God ya wike ko dima pkroko , Yomkra ya ko taetaepma ten dwen braema . Ma Yomkra yo braema , kru ara kronam swokin hominkrai ko dima hoe swokin dae , begemin aku hokesu hoe ye .
61002010	Ma wike dika ka buta hodra hosa homaka God ya ko tikmin ko , ko a dinkraiko , marensu ko hoe swokin direiki .
61002011	Ma einso wike kome penkrai ka wike hoko ka dimkina . Ma ko God ya kinaetegite huroko ko wike ho ko dima tyakmyenkmaepu .
61002012	Ma kru hakemin ko ka bute ka hodrasa hominkrai . Ko ko ware gryo gryo dei duren dinaekemina . Ma wike ka kuyenkrai . Ka braemkinaemkin ho dima tyakmyenkrai . Hamo ware gryogryo domsorinkrai ho bryoko wike gwin ka ko domsoryeiki .
61002013	Ma ko kronam ate ate pya hominkrai kren wike gwin ka ko dima hoe swokin rwyo daereiki . Ma ko aku kaekin ka hin ko , bute ka hodraisa homaka yoyomkin hyenano dinkrai . Ma ko kronam kraekraema gwegwema homaka gyominki paka kudinkrai . Ma ka gwema hominkrai ho dima yoyomkinkrai .
61002014	Ma ko aku butmin ara kore tyenkin ho dima tuma kukminkrai . Ma ko kronam swokin diwa riorekinkrai . Hamake wike aikinaemkin , gyori , dainam taminkrai . Ma ka proe ko tuka grimekemena . God ya ko sem begema , hamosu ko dore direiki .
61002015	Ma ten dumasa ten ho ko taka kwori , hamasa nononki kwenkrai . Ma Barem , yai ko Bio , ko ten ya tete hokesa tenkrai . Ma kru hoko sere serada hine pya braka hweke hrerakite .
61002016	Hamo yo hweke hreraku , ya min donki ya wike swama tyaka yei dite . Ma yo ko God ya tyo tyen kru . Hamo yo nononma homiraku ya min donki ya diwa ten dwete .
61002017	Ma kru ho ko ko to kupram wai dumkin dinaekemena . Ma ko ko hwore mtaka hwora u satenkrai hakina . Hamo God ya ka ri ko hunam hokan hrena .
61002018	Ma ko irika swa drike dumkinsa hamasa tyenkrai . Hamake ko bute ya hodra swa tyenkrai hoko daima hrenkrai . Hamo wike dika kronam kweroma hominkrai ko , ko ko hro naedwerakrai , ko dima hote dainam tnai dinknai .
61002019	Ma ka tyenkraiko , guae gua hodraisa hominina dinkrai . Ma tmoe ka hominkrai ko domsormaekinsa hominkrai . Ma kudi kronam trua kru tru dimkina kroko , kru hoko kronam yo dimkire ho ya tmoe hominkra .
61002020	Ma kudi wike dika to hyenu kronam seti , ma ko kua warmin kru kuwa hro to , Yomkra Yesu Keriso braemkino ma ko to hyenu kronam ko hro krya kutano mate to hyenu domsorin kronam hoko hote homroko hamosu ka pen kronam ko swokiskina . Ma uminki ka peti ko kukuma bryoko .
61002021	Ma kudi ko kronam dukin ko braemkinaemkroko hoko kukuma duwa . Ma ko braemkino mate God ya homnai din ko hro naedin ko duwa wirin .
61002022	Kronam ko dima pkewi ko naegimin braema ma swa tong swa ko duma pkinkra . Msaen ko kae werano hote rwyo hokan dima tenkrai . Ma tru ko mine ko wai me tua sora naeduro ko rwyo kuta pkeme kae purinkrai hokan dima tenkrai .
61003001	No kire gyoke , nokwa kwo uminki gyo dima kimite ko mate tru kesu hi kimraha . Ma kwo haepki kimrako nokwa gyo dima tyo , gua hine bren waenukin sinaida .
61003002	Hamo God ya tyo tyen wike ka tyeti ho , mate kua Yomkra , kua ware daenin kru ya homnai dinko , ya tmoe homin wike ko dima tyo , ka kuta gyo dima tyeti , hamo gyo swa hoko nononkmeda .
61003003	Ma swa hiko gyo guatumki braemknaida , hamo to hyenu hi ya hoe yen kuru , wike gwin ka buta hoda du hominkrai ko pkreiki .
61003004	Ma ko kumta gyo dima ikarema tyaka tondaeryeiki . Yo hote rwyo pkiko diteke . Hene . Ma yo diwake harwekraiha . Kuai ko sem tosuriti . Ma to hyenu komdwa kumta aekwa , kronam butmin ko bryokosa .
61003005	Ma ko braema , ma ko hine handuma brumaepu , ma semsonge God ya swa me kwoe me to hyenu me homite . Hamo to ko wai hokan hwya wai me homite .
61003006	Ma wai ko aenewya to hyenu hi domsorite .
61003007	Ma Kwoe me to me , aekwa hi praiko , God ya tikmra , marensu yo hote dei me domsori . Hamo ya ko tikmo kuta aku hoko pko diroko , kru ara God ko a dinkrai ko begema domsori .
61003008	Hamo no kire gyoke , kronam trusa ko gyo nononkromoe . Yomkra ya hine brenkra ko aku trusa o ma ambum wan tausen hamo ko bryokosa . Ma yo dima haepki ko drike trusa .
61003009	Ma Yomkra ya swagumin ko yo kumin hominkmaepu . Ma wike gwin ka hine bren ko yo kuminsa hominkra dinkrai . Howa wirin , yo gyo dima hine bra huminkra , tenam yo kru ara trusa domsorin ko yo a dinkra . Yo hoda wike butmin ka hweke ko hro naedraida .
61003010	Hamo yomkra ya pkikrako udin wike ka pkinkrai ko bryoko pki . Aku hokeko wyaen hyena buru kwoe ko wirinki . Ma kwoe kom hokan gryo butmin ko deia dua domsora naedi . Ma to hyenu me ya gryogryo butmin ko wirinki .
61003011	Ma tenam gryogryo butmin ko hamike domsoryeiki , hakina kren gyo haekin dinaeka hureikike . Gua huwekraiko waenu yaeyosa hakina hwyenina , ma butmin ko God dima daena .
61003012	Ma gyo God ya pkra aku ho huma pakadi , hoko katma pknada taetepminknai . Hokeko kwoe pkuri ya ki hoa kwoe kom gryogryo ko disiru dua domka waiki .
61003013	Ma kua humrai ko ya swagumite ko kwoe nin homa mate to hyenu kesu nin homa hami ko dite humrai . Ma hokan ko kronam dukin hoasa ae pen braema .
61003014	Hakina kren , kire gyoke , gyo aku ho huma paka God yo gitma kronam waenukinsa homo God ya gyo diwadi , gyo hweke dumkina din braema . Homake yo dima ganeswama pnai .
61003015	Ma gyo Yomkra ya hminsa huma tmaeki penkra ho dima hine brenknai . Yo hoda gyo gwemkin ko yo a dinkra . Ma kua kire Por ya kesu gyo dima harike kimite . God ya braemkin yo dima daen home kimite .
61003016	Ma Kwonam butmin ya swa hi kimako , yo kesu harike kikima . Ma swa gwin ya kimin ko tukina . Hamo wike gwin ko nononka swa ate ate daera dumahaki diskinkrai . Hamo ko ya swa me mate Kwonam kimin gwin ya drike nononma riaegiminkrai . Ko hamike hominkrai kren kae ko domsoryeiki .
61003017	No kire , gyoke , gyo hiko sem braemkewi . Hakina kren gua braeme , pako koma swa daerinaemkin wike ko ten kweroma to , gyoke ten ho diwa troko , aekwa ri waenukin gua penkrai ko hro msyemeda .
61003018	Hamo kua Yomkra me kua ware daenin kru Yesu Keriso ya proeki hamaha din kronam me mate ya braemkin ho ko gyo braemkinina . Ma braemkin ho ko hyenminina . Hamo kae waenukin aekwa me dyaen dyaen yae hamo yo dima aenada . Haminina .
62001001	Kyo Ware Swa ko gyo dima hi kimraiha . Ma swa hiko to hominaemkina , yae yatumki hamo hete . Hamo Swa ho ko tyo , kyo daeriti . Ma kyo kua kron me diwa , mate kua krite me yo guriti .
62001002	Ma ware Swa hoko pko kyo dyeti . Yo ko God minki yae hamo henkra . Ma yo ware dyaen dyaen swa hoko kyo dima naegimite .
62001003	Ma kua diwa daera homiti hoko kyo gyo dima twyerakrai . Ma gyo kesu kyo hmene hine trusa bra God me ya kya Yesu Keriso minki swa tyenkwe .
62001004	Hamo kyo swa hi ko kima neaendroko kua yoyomkin ko bryoko ae .
62001005	Ma swa kua daeriti ko kwasu gyo dima twyerakraiha . God ko kae . Ma yo ko hunam true aemaepu .
62001006	Hakina krenku , kudi kyo haryoko , God me no me ki ko hin trusa harioko , ma kyo hunam dinaekin penkrai , hamo kyo kraekraema tyenkrai .
62001007	Hamo kudi kyo ya kae hokan huroko , kyo yominki swa tyaka kire droko , ya kya Yesu ya kapoe ho psyo diwa yo kua hweke sora naendu waenukreiki .
62001008	Ma kutadi kyo hweke hrenkmaepu droko , kuae kyo rwyo ho kraeraiha .
62001009	Ma kudi kua hweke ko God dima wainsaeroko , ya swa gumite hoko yo dumasa hamikraha . Yo kua hweke dware ko begema , dore a dae , mate kua hin ko kronam swokin homwera hine brenkrai ko ya homa naendinkra .
62001010	Ma kudi kyo harioko kyo hweke hrenkmaepu droko , ya swa ko kua kunam aemaepuha , hamo kyo God yo ko kraekraemin kru draiha .
62002001	Ekum gyoke , nokwa swa hi kimra ko gyo hweke hrimeda . Ma kutadi kru trua hweke hraeroko , kru trua kua swa taetaepma tyenkra , kru hoko Yesu Keriso . Yo ko hweke dumkina .
62002002	Ma Yesu Keriso ya homite krenku , kua hweke ko sora hamaha dite . Ma kua hweke sa wirin , wike butmin ka hweke kesu .
62002003	Ma kudi kyo ya trya ho daera homroko , hamroko , kyo yo braemaha .
62002004	Ma kru ara dika harioko kyo yo braema dano , ma ya tyo daera hominaemkroko , ko kraekraema tyenkraiha .
62002005	Ma kru ara dika ya tyo daera homroko , ko drinu God dima proeka hine pya brenkraiha . Ma kyo naemike braemki kyo yominki huraike . Kyo himike braemkrai .
62002006	Kru ara kyo God yominki hurai droko , ko ko Yesu Keriso ya hote haminina .
62002007	Kire gyoke , swa nokwa hi kimra ko nin wirin . Hiko sem uminki tyete ho .
62002008	Ma nokwa hi kimirakra ko nin , ya drike ko kyo Keriso ma gyo diwa braemkin braema . Tenam hunam dinaekin ko wirinkirakra , hamo kae nu ko kaekra .
62002009	Ma kru diya yo harioko , no kaegite henkra duro , ya goe gmore ko yo a duro yo hunam sa penkra .
62002010	Ma kru dika ka goe gmore dima proeka hine pya bruroko , ko kaegite troko wike gwin ko kae ho diroko , hweke hro toten braema wirin .
62002011	Ma kru dika ka goe gmore ko a droko , ko hunam sa penkrai . Ko hunam sa troko , ma ten ka trai ko ko braema wirin , tenam hunam hoa ka kron duduminkrai .
62002012	No kya kuku gyoke , no gyo dima kimra , tenam Yesu yo me kren gua hweke ko sora hamaha dina .
62002013	No kwo hi wike yomkra gyo dima kimra , tenam gyto braema kru sem yatumki yae hamo hena . Ma no kwaten kru gyo dima kimra , tenam gyo Hweke Yanai ko dimkiti kren No kya kuku , no gyo dima kimra , tenam Kuai ko gyo braema hoa .
62002014	Ma wike yomkra gyo dima kimra ko , tenam kru yatumki hete ko gyo braema hoa . Ma no kwaten kru gyo dima kimra ko , tenam gyo ko aia , ma God ya swa ko gua kunam aerura , ma gyo sem Hweke Yanai ko dimki naenditi .
62002015	Ma gyo to hyenu kronam dima hine braka mate to hyenu gryogryo dima hine pya braka haminina wirin . Ma kudi kru trua yo to hyenu dima proeka hine pya brenkmaepuha .
62002016	Ma to hyenu kronam hoko diwa kuae kua hina swoka gryo kua hodrai hoda , mate gryo kua irinkrai hoko , teinam ko Kuai ya wirin , hoko to hyenu hi yana .
62002017	Ma to hyenu kronam me gryo wike ka hoda dinkrai ko wirinkirakra . Hamo wike dika God ya hodra ho homroko , ko aepesu yae hamo huwekraiha .
62002018	No kya kuku gyoke , to hyenu ya hoe yen ko sem kurya . No sem gyo dima tyete , Keriso ya totetyen kru ko pki . Ma Keriso ya totetyen wike pya sem taenkewi . Hamo kyo braema to hia hoe yen ko kurya .
62002019	Ma wike hoko sem kyominki gaemaewi , ma kyo hine trusa brumaepu . Hakina kren ko kyo kworewi . Ma kudi kyo hin trusa bruroko , ko aekwa kyominki gaema swa tryai . Ma ko kyo kworewi kren , kyo braema ko ko gire trusa wirin .
62002020	Ma gyo ko , God ya Dure gyo dima pkete kren , drinu swa hiko gyo butmin braema .
62002021	Ma no gyo dima kimrako , tenam gyo drnu swa hiko braemkinaemkin dware wirin . Tenam gyo braema . Hamo hi kesu gyo braema , swa kraekraema tyen ko drinu swa tyenkrai hakina pkin braema wirin .
62002022	ma kru di ko kraekraemin kru ne . Kru diya harike tryoko , Yesu ko Keriso wirin droko yo howa .
62002023	Tenam wike dika ya kya dima ko a droko , yai kesu ko a dinkrai .
62002024	Swa yatumki gyo daeriti hoko gua kunam hren yae hamo aenina . Ma swa hoko yae hamo aeroko , gyo Kuai me ya kya kominki hwyen braema .
62002025	Ma Keriso yae kyo dima swa gumite ko , yo ware aepesu hamo henin ko daera dite .
62002026	No swa hi gyo dima kimra ko wike wa gyo dima kro tyenkrai ka swa ho tyera .
62002027	Ma Keriso ya Dure ko gyo dima pkete . Hamo yo gyominki hra , hamo kru gwin ka kumta gyo dima swa gwin naegimin ko bryoko wirin . Dure ya gyo butmin naegiminkra . Ma ya naegiminkra ko kraekraemin me wirin , drinusa . Ma yo gyo dima naegiminkra ko daera homaka Keriso yominki hwyenina .
62002028	Drinu , no kya kuku gyoke , gyo yominki hwyenkrnai hamo ya pkikra aku hoko , kyo hukwae a direiki .
62002029	Ma gyo braema Keriso ko waenukina hamo hi kesu gyo braemknai , wike dika kronam waenukin homroko , ko ko God ya kya .
62003001	Ma swa hi ko hine pya brunai . Kuai yo kyo dima proeka hine pya braka kyo ko ya kya dinkra . Hamo kyo ko yana . Ma to hyenu ko kyo braema wirin , tenam ko yo braema wirin .
62003002	Kire gyoke , aekwa kyo ko God ya kya . Ma kyo hamosu naekikra hoko kyo braema wirin . Hi sa kyo braema . Hamosu Keriso ya rwyo pkosu , kyo yo dinaekreiki . Hamo kyo yo tuma dyenu direiki .
62003003	Hamo wike dika ko ya rwyo pkikra ho huma paka , kronam swokin hro naendinkrai . Tenam Yesu yo kronam swokin ko wirinsa krenku .
62003004	Ma wike dika ko hweke turoko , God ya koma ho kiraiha . Tenam hweke ko koma kyenkrai .
62003005	Gyo braema Keriso ya pkite ko hweke ho taera trada pkite . Ma yo dima ko hweke tru wirin sa .
62003006	Hamo wike dika ko Keriso yominki huroko , ko hweke twen braema wirin .
62003007	Ai gyoke , kru trua kumta gyo dima kraeme . Wike di kronam dukin homroko , kru hoko waenukina . Yo ko Keriso dinaekina .
62003008	Sem uminki Saiten yo hweke hrete , hakina kren , hweke twenkrai ko ko Saiten ya kyaha . Ma God ya kya yo kumta Saiten ya hominkra ho domsirira pkite .
62003009	Ma kru diya yo ko God ya kya kroko , yo hweke hren hin a bre . Tenam God ya kronam ko kru hoa ya hinara aenku .
62003010	God ya kya ko tei tru ma Saiten ya kya ko tei tru . Hamo kru ara dika ko kronam dukin hominaemka , mate ka goe gmore ko dima proeka hine pya brenaemka hamroko ko ko God ya kya wirin .
62003011	Ma swa hiko gyo yatumki daerite , gyo matum proeku matum proeku haminina .
62003012	Hamakano gyo Kein dinaekromoe . Yo ko Hweke yanai ya kya , hamo yo ya gmore Abor yete . Ma yo naemo diwa yo yeteke . Tenam ya homite ko swoku , ma ya gmore ya homite ko waenukite kren .
62003013	Kire gyoke , to hyenu wike ka gyo dima a du gyo girmnomoe .
62003014	Tenam kyo kua goe gmore dima proeka hine pya braenmkrai kren , hamo kyo braema kyo pwen ko hro ware dyaen dyaen sena .
62003015	Kru diya yo ya goe gmore a droko , yo ko wike yenin kru ho bryoko . Ma gyo braema wike yenin kru yo ware dyaen dyaen ko yo sen braema wirin .
62003016	Ma proeka hine pya bren kronam ko naekinane . Ho ko hiwa . Keriso ya ware kyo dima hrete . Hakina kren kyo kesu kua ware kua goe gmore ko dima hrenina .
62003017	Ma kudi kru diya yo gryo pya ae , ma ya goe gmore ko diwa no bute taetaepmin mgakwen tru aemaepu droko , braemane .
62003018	No kya kuku gyoke , kua kire ko dima proeka hine pya brenkrai din ko ti twomsa tyenina wirin . Ko dima drinu proeka hime pya braka ko dima kronam waenukin hominknai .
62003019	Hamo kyo braemkrai kyo ko Drinu swa tyen wike . Hamo kyo God ya kinaete gite huroko , kyo a hukwaekreiki .
62003020	Ma kudi , kua hina harioko , gu ko God yana wirin droko , kyo braema , God ko hyena , ma kua hine ko hyena wirin . Ma God yo butmin braema .
62003021	Hakina krenku , kua hina gyo ko God ya wike wirin harinaemkroko , kyo God ya kron ti waenuma pen braema .
62003022	Kyo ya trya daera homroko , kua hoda kentryai ko sen braema .
62003023	Ma ya homniada tyen ko hiwa . Kyo ya kya Yesu Keriso ko drinu , God ya kya da ma wike gwin ko dima kesu proeka hine pya brenina . Hi ko Keriso ya kyo dima harike tyete .
62003024	Ma wike dika God ya tyo daera homroko ko God yominki ho huraiha . Ma God yo kesu kominki ho hraha . Kyo himike braemkrai tenam God yo Dure kyo dima daete kren .
62004001	Kire gyoke , wike dika ko God ya Dure kominki henkra drai ko bryoko dyenina . Ma Dure kominki hra ko God ya pra hwya pkrake ma wirinne . Ma kraekraema tyenkrai wike pya ko to hoegite hoegite tamaewi .
62004002	Ma gyo naemike braemkmawe dure hoko God yana di ate di . Kru dika hirike tryoko , Yesu Keriso yo kumta wikma hamtete droko , kru hoko God ya Dure yo minki hraha .
62004003	Ma kru dika Yesu ko hmaepu droko , dure kominki hra ko God yana wirin . Dure ya sen ko Keriso yo dima wasiha . Ma Dure hoko pki ko du gyo daerewiha . Hamo yo sem to hikan dima pke .
62004004	No kya kuku , gyoke , gyo ko God yana . Ma wike kraekraema tyadaeminkrai ko gua dimki naendewi . Tenam Dure gyominki hra ko aiya . Ma dure , wike to hyenu wike kana kominki hra ko aiya wirin .
62004005	Ma wike to hyenu wike ko ka swa daerinkrai , tenam ko ko to hyenu yana kren .
62004006	Ma kyo ko God yana . Hamop kru dika God ko ko braema kroko , kua swa ko daerin braema . Ma God ko braemkinaemkroko , kua swa ko ko daerinkmaepu . Hamo Dure di ko drinu tyenkra ma dure di ko kraekratyenkra ho kyo braemkin braema .
62004007	Kire , kyo matum proeku , matum proeku hamwe . Proeka hine pya bren kronam teinam ko God . Wike dika wike gwin ko dima proeka hine pya brenkrai ko , God ko ko braema . Hamo ko ko God ya kya .
62004008	Ko haminaemkroko , God ko ko braema wirin , tenam yo ko proekin yanai .
62004009	Ma God yo proeka hine pya bren kronam kyo dima naegimite , tenam ya kya ko trusa , hamo yo to hyenu dima pru psyete kren . Hakina krenkuy kyo ware dyaen dyaen hamo hwyen braema .
62004010	Hi ko proekin kronam nu . Kyo God dima hine brumaepu , ma yo kyo dima proeka hine pya bra ya kya kyo dima pru psyete . Hamo ya pkinku kua hweke ko sora hamaha dite .
62004011	Kire gyoke , God yo kyo dima himike hine brete , hamo kyo kesu wike gwin ko dima hamike hine brtenina .
62004012	Ma kru truato God dimaepu . Ma kyo wike gwin ko dima proeka hine pya bruroko , kyo God yominki pen braema , ma ya proekin kyo dima ko hyena .
62004013	Kyo braema , kyo God yominki hwyenkrai , ma yo kyominki henkra , ya Dure kyo dima daenkuy .
62004014	Ma kyo dyeti God ya kya pru kumta to hyenu wike butmin kua hweke hoe sera pkite ko . Hamo kyo swa hiko wike gwin ko dima tyadaeminknai .
62004015	Wike dika ko Yesu ko God ya kya droko , ko God yominki hwyenkrai , ma God ko yominki henkra .
62004016	Ma kyo braema hiko drinu , God yo kyo dima proeka hine pya brenkra .
62004017	Proekin ko kyo dima aera , hamo Begemin Aku ho pko diroko kyo a tempureiki , tenam kyo sem ware dyaen dyaen sena kren .
62004018	Kyo wike dima proeka hine pya bruroko , kyo a tempureiki . Proekin kronam hoa tempwen kronam ko krurinkra . Hamo wike dika ko tempuroko ka proekin kronam ko hyena wirin . Ma kyo hine himike brenkrai hweke hoe no dima daemau dini da tempwenkrai .
62004019	Kyo ko preokin wike , tenam God yo yatumki kyo dima proeka hine pya brete kren .
62004020	Ma kru trua harike tryoko , no God dima hine pya brenkra , ma no goe gmore ko dima ko no a droko , yo ko kraekraemin kruha . Ma kudi yo ya gmore yo diwa , hine brenaemkroko ya naemike God dyenaemkin ko yo dima hine bren braema din braemane .
62004021	Keriso ya kyo dima koma hro tyen ko hiwa , kru dika God dima hine bruroko wike gwin ko dima kesu hine brenina .
62005001	Ma kru ara dika ko Yesu ko God ya pru pkin droko , ko ko God ya kya . Ma wike dika ko yai dima hine pya brenkroko , ko ya kya dima kesu hine brenkraiha .
62005002	Kyo hine bra braemki kyo God ya kya kuku ko dima hine pya brenkrai , tenam kyo God dima hine braka ya komaa trya ho hominkrai kren .
62005003	God dima hine bren ya drike ko ya trya daera hominina . Ma ya koma trya ko tuwa wirin , kyo homin braema .
62005004	Ma God ya kya ka to hyenu ka kronam swokin butmin ko ka dimkin braema . Kua God ko drinu dinkrai hoa kua ho dimkraiha .
62005005	Ma wike dika ko to hyenu dimkin braemane . Wike wa Yesu ko God ya kya dinkrai ka sa .
62005006	Yesu Keriso yo pko diroko , yo baptais wai me ya pwen kapoe me pkite . Yo wai mesa pkmaepu , wai me kapoe me hamo pkete . Ma Dure ya tyenkra hi ko drinu . Ma Dure ko drinu swa tyenin yanai .
62005007	Diwa tyo tyenin ko haepki trumo hamo .
62005008	Ma Dure me wai me kapoe me hamo . Ma ko butmin swa trusa tyenkrai .
62005009	Ma kyo wike ka diwa tyoro kyo daera drinu dinkrai . Ma God ya tyenkra ko drike hyena , hamo ya kya ho kyo dima naegite .
62005010	Hamo wike diya God ya kya ko drinu dra , ya drinu din ko ya kunam ae ko yo braema . Ma wike dika ko God ya swa ko drinu dinaemkroko , ko God ko kraekraemin kru dinkrai , God ya kya swa ya tyete hoko drinu dinkmaepu kren .
62005011	Ya swa ko hiwa . God yo ware dyaen dyaen ho kyo dima daete . Ma ware hiya ya teinam ko , ya kya dima aera .
62005012	Hamo wike dika ko God ya kya sena kroko , ko ware hi saewiha . Ma wike dika ko God ya kya simaepu kroko , ko ware ko simaepu .
62005013	No swa hiko wike dika God ya kya ko drinu hra drai gyo dima kimra , gyo ware dyaen dyaen sem sen hoko gyo braemkrnaida .
62005014	Hamo kyo God ya kinaetegite huroko , kyo tempureiki . Tenam kyo yo dima kentryoko , kua kentrya hoko kyo dima daemaekroko , kyo braema yo daeryaha .
62005015	Kua dikan kentinakroko , yo daerinkra . Ma kyo braema yo drinu daerinkra ma kyo braema , kyo nakoe yo dima kentryoko , hoko kyo dima daenkra .
62005016	Ma kudi gua kire ya hweke hrae dirai ko , ma hweke ho ko pwen hweke wirin kroko , gyo God dima tryoko , God yo ware yo dima dae . Pwenaemkin hweke sa haminina . Ma hweke tru ko ya hoe ko pwenina , ma no gyo God dima swa ho harike trnya hweke ho dware dmaepu .
62005017	Ma kronam swokin butmin ko hweke . Ma hweke gwin ka hoe ko pwenina wirin .
62005018	Kyo braema God ya kya kuku ko kronam swokin hamosa homin braema wirin . Tenam God ya kya ya ko tikminkra . Ma Hweke Yanai ya ko domsorin braema wirin .
62005019	Kyo braema kyo ko God yana . Ma Swokin Yanai yo to hyenu tikminkra .
62005020	God ya kya yo kumta kyo dima naegimo God nu ko kyo braema . Hamo kyo God ya kya kominki hwyenkrai . Yo ko God nu . Ma hi ko ware dyaendyaen .
62005021	No kya gyo kraekraemin god ko dima hine brenkromoe .
63001001	No ko Sos tikmin kru hamo nokwa kwo hi kimira . Kwo hiko , ara nokwa yo dima hine pya brenkra ma hote ya kya kuku butmin hamo gyo dima kimira . Ma nokwasa wirin , wike swanu braemkrai butmin ko kesu gu dima drinu proekinkrai .
63001002	Tenam swanu ko kua tyonam henku . Huka trya yae hamosa kyominki henina .
63001003	Ma kuai God me Yesu Keriso , kuai ya kya , gi kyo dima waenuma pen kronam da mate hamaha din kronam me mate ganeswamin kronam butmin hamo kyo dima daena . Dae kyo drinusa proekin me tuma sen hoda .
63001004	Ma no gwa kya kuku gwin ko dirako , ko ten duma yomasa tamo no diwa , yoyomkin hyenkra . Tenam Kuai God ya kyo dima tyete hosa hominknai da dinku .
63001005	Hamo no ara gu dima tyera . Kua kire ko dima matum proeku matum proeku haminina . Koma hi gu dima kimra ko nin wirin . Koma hiko brunai , sem uminki kyo dima kimina .
63001006	Ma proekin kronam nokwa hi trya drike ko , kyo God ya tyen swa ho daera hominina . Koma swa sem twya hren gyo butmin daeriti ko hiwa , gua matum proeku matum proeku hamnai dina .
63001007	Hamo kraekraema naegimin wike pya ko to hyenu hoe hoe butmin hamo hrya siwekraiha . Ma wike wa ko harinkmaen Yesu Keriso ko wikema hamtena dinkmaepu . Hamo wike hoko dumasa kraekraema tyen wike ma ko ko Yesu Keriso ya totetyen wikesa .
63001008	Gua braeme , pako tmoe kua homiti hoko kwerma gua hoe senaemkmeda . Ma tmoe gua homiti ya hoe ko butmin hamo senina .
63001009	Ma kru diya yo Keriso ya naegimamite hoko daerinaemka yae ya hine bren o ya braemkin hosa atma naegimroko , kru hoko God ya ware ko yo sena wirin howa . Kru diya swa hiko yoma daerina kroko yo Yesu me Yai ta tyonam hen braema .
63001010	Ma kudi kru trua ya swa waenukin hi sa kumta naegiminaem kroko kru hi dima duwa da hipya gwa aewe dima tromoe . Ma gu yo dima haryome gu wyaen dumka waenuma henkna haryomoe .
63001011	Kru diya wyaen dumka hna droko ya kire dinaeka tmoe swokin ya hominkra yo kesu taetaepminkra .
63001012	No swa gyo dima pya tmyaekina aera , Ma no pensore me kwonam kimin ko bryoko wirin . Ma no hine ko naesa kuta gyominki paka swa tyo tyo , yoyomkinina .
63001013	Gwa syom ya kya ka yoyomkin swa gyo dima hre traiha .
64001001	No ko Sos tikmin kru . Kire Gaies , no gu dima kwo hi kimira . No gu dima drinu hine pya brenkra .
64001002	Kire no God dima kentinkra ko gu tren dumka waenuma pnada . Ma no braema gua dure ko aiya .
64001003	Ma Krwistin kru gwin sem pkewi ka gwa swa no dima tyaewi ko , gu God ya swa ko drinu da penkra du , no daera yoyomke .
64001004	Ma no kya kuku ko swanu drinu tyen ko daera drinu dinkrai no daera yoyomkinkra .
64001005	Kire , gu Krwistin wike taetaepminkra ko , hoko waenumasa hominkra . Ma wike gwin ko gwa koesen wirin ma gu ko taetaepminkra .
64001006	Hamo ko Krwistin wike hikan gaeminkrai ko dima gwa proekin kronam ho tyaewi . Hakina kren , ko gwa to dima troko gu hote ko taetaepmna . Hamike taetaepmin ko God ya diwa duwa din braema .
64001007	Ko Keriso ya tmoe homi tenkrai . Ma Krwistin dinaemkin wike ko dima daemae hakin ko simaepu .
64001008	Hakina kren , Krwistin wike kyo wike hakin ko taetaepmwe . Ma ko drinu swa naegimo kyo ko taetaepma hominkrai .
64001009	No sem kwo kima Krwistin wike ko dima hre ta . Ma Diotrepa yo hoda yo ko ka aiipe dinknaida , hamo yo no swa daerinkmaepu .
64001010	Hamo nokwa kumtasu ya hominkra ho me mate kua swa ya tyenkra me mate ya kraekraema tyenkra ho nokwa taen tye . Ma yo hosa hominkmaepu . Yo Krwistin wike ko pko diroko yo ko a dinkra . Ma wike gwin ko hoda ko taetaepmwera duro , yo ko garinkra . Ma ko Krwistin wike gwin kominki gaemwerakekano yo ko pru tenkra .
64001011	No kire , gu kronam swokin diwa , ho bryoko homrome . Dukinsa diwa ho bryoko hominkna . Tenam wike dika kronam dukin hominkrai ko ko God yana . Ma wike dika kronam swokin hominkrai ko ko God dimaekina wirin .
64001012	Ma wike butmin ko Demitria ya swa tyakano , yo ko kru waenukin dinkrai . Ma Drinu yo kesu yo ko duwa dinkra . Ma kyo kesu hote ho bryoko harinkrai . Ma gyo braema kua tyenkrai ko drinusa tyenkrai .
64001013	No swa pya gyo dima tyera , ma no pensore me inka me a kimi .
64001014	Ma nokwa kumta gu dimae ko kurya . Hokansu kyo hmene swa tyo tyo hamwe .
64001015	Waenuma pen kronam gu dima aenknada .
65001001	No hi ko Jud , hamo kwo hiko nokwa kimira . Ma no ko Yesu Keriso ya tmoe homin kru . Ma no ko Jeims yagmore .
65001002	God ya proekin kronam da mate ya waenuma pen kronam da mate ya hine pya bren kronam gyo dima hyenma aenada .
65001003	Kire gyoke , no gyo dima ware dyaendyaen sen swa , kua sene ho , gyo dima kimira de . Ma no hine ko , swa tru hi gyo dima dumasa kimira de . No hoda gyo aiki , God ya swa , wike ko dima daen ko tuma daera braemki , yoma naegimnaida .
65001004	Ma wike gwin God ya swa a daeryeiki ko dinkrai ko gwemki kyo hmene gaeminkrai . Ma God ya kyo dima proeki hamaha dite swa hoko , ko atma tyenkrai . Ko harinkrai , tenam kronam swokin ka hominkrai ko bryoko dinkrai . Hamake ko Yesu Keriso yasa ko kua ware daenin kru din ko ko a dinkrai . Ma sem soge Kwonam kima tyen ko , dore ka sem sen ho ko begemasu sireiki dina .
65001005	Ma swa butmin hiko gyo braema , ma no hoda gyo hote hine bra braemknaida . Ma , Isrwaeo wike ko to Ijep hokan po , Yomkra ya ko gyori taka , wike gwin , ya swa daerinaemkrai , ko butmin domsorite .
65001006	Ma wike God ya po penkrai gwin ko , Yomkra ya swa daerinaemka ka to hro teti . Hamo aekwako , ko sen me pupuma to hunamkin hokan wogitmina penkrai . Ma God ya ko tikminkra . Ma aku hyenu ho pko diroko , yo ko begema hoe swokin dae .
65001007	Ma to Sodom , me mate to Gomora me mate to gwin hawyo peti ko dima hine brunai . Wike hi ka homiti ko God ya po penkrai ka homiti ho bryoko homiti . Kru kae ko aeng tyaka kore tyaka hamamiti . Hakina kren ko dei dyaen dyaen duen henkra hokan dore drimi hurai . Ho ko naegu wike gwin ko braemknaida .
65001008	Hote ho bryoko , wike hiko ko ripe krogoekeka , kronam ate diwa , kae ka bute domsorinkrai . Ma ko God ya swa aikin hoko a deka , wike kine waenukin kome penkrai , ko dima ikareminkrai .
65001009	Ma kru hya God ya po penkrai , ya hi ko Maiko , yo hamike homaepu . Yo Saiten yominki grwin brake prite , diya Moses ya bute ko simawe da grwin braka , Maiko yo Saiten dima tempwa ikarema tmyaepu . Ya tyeskite , Yomkra ya gu dima tyenina dite .
65001010	Ma wike hiko , kronam diko ko braemkinaemkrai hokan dima ikareminkrai . Ma ko ko ware gryogryo tona dinaekina . Ma kronam wiko braemkiskrai hoa ko domsorinkrai .
65001011	Aenuwe ko kru Kein ya homite ho bryoko hominkrai . Ma sere dware ko , ko Beirem ya hwekma homite ho bryoko hominkrai . Ma Kora ya yomkra dima a dite ko kesu hominkrai . Ma ka yo yeti kren ko kesu kuryeiki .
65001012	Ma gyo hmene gaema wai me kudin deka ko riorema hukwae dumka ku diskinkrai . Ma ko ko tupe mina dinaekina . Ma ko kaesa ko tikminkrai . Ma ko ko kwoe u dinaekina . Hamo hworea ya u sapko wai surinaemkinkrai hakina . Ma ko ko dei dinaekina . Hamo ka ke yen aku ho pko diroko , ko ke yen braema wirin . Dei droke ko hmoru , dei bute ko pwenku .
65001013	Ma ko ko wai dawara ya takurinkra hakina . Ma kronam ka hukwae dumka hominkrai ko wai dawara ya takuru maho minkinkrai hakina . Ma ko ko pute kwoe ti hamasa kwehwyenkrai ho dinaekina . God ya ka ri ko , hunam hokan hrera homina .
65001014	Ma Adam ya kyankya kumta tu ko Inok . Ka swa ya sem tyeteko , Yomkra me wike ya po penkrai ko pya yo me pkreiki .
65001015	Hamo ya kumtasu wike butmin ka hoko begemi . Tmoe swokin ka homiti , da mate swa swokin ka yo dima tyeti hoa dware dore ko dima daemi .
65001016	Ma wike hiko aku butmin ka hweke ko prikma harinkrai no ko wirin , wike gwin ka hwekesa , harinkrai . Ma ko hoda kronam swokinsa homaka , irika , wike gwin ko dima kraekraema tyaka gu ko duwa deka harinkrai , tenam kae ka hoda draisa siwera da .
65001017	No kire gyoke , kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya tmoe homin wike pru tamaka ka gyo dima tyeti ko nononkromoe .
65001018	Ka gyo dima tyetiko , to hyenu hiya hoe yekra hokeko , wike gwin , dika God ko , ko a da , kae ka hoda draisa homaka , gyo dima ikaremreiki .
65001019	Ma wike hikemin ko , gyo dima tyo , gyo ridwa penina . Ka buta hoda drai ho hominkrai . Ma Dure yato ka hine bren tikmaepu .
65001020	Ma no kire gyoke , gyo god ya Dure ya swa daerinknai . Hamake Dure ya ai me God dima tyenknai .
65001021	God ya proekin me gua tikminkrai . Hamake gyo Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya proekin me huminina . Yo gyo dima ware dyaendyaen hamo hwyen daemi .
65001022	Ma wike dika ko dumahaki din ko bubutkroko ko dima proekinknai .
65001023	Ma wike dika dei duen dima sywerakraiko , ko taentaema samtnai . Hamake wike gwin ko dima tempwa kyomkromoe . Hamake kronam swokin ka hominkrai ko gyo a dinknai .
65001024	Ma God ya gyo tikmo gyo totin braema wirin . Ma gyo kronam swokin homroko , ya gua hine homa , ya hin bren hweke dumkin ho gyo dima hre diroko , gyo ri ya pra waenukin dima gyori pko , yoyomkin me pkin braema .
65001025	God yasa ko God , yo ko kua ware daenin kru . Ma yo kua Yomkra Yesu Keriso pru , ya homo , kyo ware dyaendyaen senkrai . Kyo yo dima tyenkwe , gwasa ko yomkra hya henina . Ma kine waenukin me ma ai butmin gu dima aenkra . Ya aku butmin hakina sa aenina . Drinu haminina .
66001001	Sem uminki swa hiko gwemki aete . Hamo Yesu Keriso ya naegite . God ya hamosu homwerakrai ko , Yesu dima naegimosu , Yesu ya ya tmoe homin wike ko dima naegu braemknaida . Hamo ya po penkrai kru tru pru ya tmoe homin kru Jon dima pkite .
66001002	Hamo naegu , Jon ya dya butmin ko kwonam kimite . Hamo kwo hi ko God me Yesu Keriso ta naegiti .
66001003	Ma kru dika ko kwo kimin hi hyaeku ma wike dika ko hamosu pkikra swa hi daera tuma daeryoko , God ya ko hagurma , swa tyo ko pitma pen braema . Tenam swa hi kimra ko sem taenkirakra .
66001004	Kwo hi ko Jon nokwa , Keriso ya wike tonesu dehraensin hamo to Asia hokan penkrai , gyo dima kimra . Ma God yo aekwa me sem uminki yae hamo heten kru yo me , ma dure dehraensin ko kesu king hyenu ya pen ri kinaegite hurai ko me , ma Yesu Keriso yo ko God ya swa tyo dumasa tyen kru , yo ko to gyenam aerwa durkyo asin kru hya , hamo yo ko to hyenu wike ka king ka yomkra , waenuma pen kronam gyo dima pru pknada .
66001005	
66001006	Ya kyo homu kyo ko yai God ya tmoe homin wikkiti . Yesu yo ko waenu yae yosa hakina , ma ya ai ko dyaendyaen aepesu yae hamo aenina hoe yen braema wirin .
66001007	Dinai yo u nam pkira . Hamo wike butmin ka kron me yo direiki . Kru yo baku me tukweti , ko kesu yo direiki . Hamo wike butmin ko yo pko diwa byen drimreiki . Maren hoko hamreiki .
66001008	No ko andu me mare me hakin kru . Hamo God yo ai butmin sena . Yo hamosa hra , ma yo sem uminki kesu hena , hamo marensu yo pki .
66001009	No hi ko Jon . Kyo ko Keriso yana hakina krenku , no ko gua goe hamo no pyenkin hi diwa huma pa dyenkra . Ko no hipya kumta to dupi Patmos hikan hro pke , tenam no God ya swa me Yesu ya naegimite ho tyadaeminku .
66001010	Ma Yomkra ya aku hokeko , Dure waenukina kumta no tranmo diroko , swa tru no taugite tyo daerire ko widoke wyaen dinaekina .
66001011	Hamo swa gwa dira ko kwonam kimna . Hamo Keriso ya wike to 7 hamo gaemina hokan dima two tamna . To ka gaemrai hi ko Epeses da Smena da Pegamon me Tairataira da ma Sadis me Piadepia da ma Reodisia hamo ko dima two tamnai .
66001012	Ma no krwyo , kru swa no dima trya ho dyera di , twan 7 hamo , gor me homina tyena ho dyere .
66001013	Ma twan 7 hamo dure hokan ko kru tru ho me dyere . Hamo yo bai gawekin me katutaka ya karike woe butmin hamo ruwori bereti gor me ya kmaeke dwaena .
66001014	Ya ku binmten ko dmekiskina . Mine sip mtene o yemka gudraen hakina . Ya kron ko dei trupe byau kaekinkrai hakina .
66001015	Ma ya karike ko auri disiru dei tin dinaekinkrai hakina dyere . Ma no ya kepronam wyaen daeryako wai rurin dinaekina .
66001016	Hamo ya krite dunaegite ko pute 7 hamosa hro ho dyere . Ma krarang tru ya rire ko suke urina dinaekina , ma ya rire ko yae yo sa hakina , ya mgatram hokan mto dyere . Ma ya tokram ko tei , ua guorinaemku hrenkrai hakina dyere .
66001017	Ma no hoko dyaka , kiri taka ya karike tkyo durino pwena dinaeka aere . Hamo diroko , ya krite dunaete home no guori pri gu tempurome dire . No sem natumki hena . Ma wike gwin ko tosuru naedu no hamosa heskraha .
66001018	No ware hamosa hi heskinkraha , no sem pwa naedite . Ma aekwa no ware dyaen dyaen hamosa hra . Ma pwen me dure ka tonae ko nokwa tikminkra .
66001019	Hamo gwa dyenkra ko butmin kimna . Kronam aekwa hi aera da mate hamosu pkikra hokesu kimna .
66001020	Gu pute no krite dunaetegite pro dira da ma twan 7 hamo hoko gor me sa hro ho dira ya drike ko hiwa . Pute 7 hamo hoko God ya po penkrai wike ka no wike ka gaemo ko tikminkrai . Ma twan 7 hamo ko hote hamo no wike no swa tyenkrai 7 hamo ho bryoko .
66002001	Gu God ya po penkrai kru tru Keriso ya wike to Epeses hokan paka tikminkra yo dima swa hi kimna . Kru tru ya krite dunaete ko pute 7 hamo sa hro hra , hamo yo twan 7 hamo gor me homina hokan kwenkra ya trya ko hiwa .
66002002	Kronam gwa homra butmin ko no braemki naedra . Ma gwa tmoe idima homaka huma pa dyenkra ko no braema . Ma kru kronam swokin hominkrai ko gu a diskinkra . Ma kru hoka gu dima harike tyaewi , kyo kesu tmoe homraida pru ten wike dewi . Ma ko ko wirin , ma gu ka swa begema kraekraemin wike sa dya .
66002003	Ma gu ko nana krenku wike gwin ko gu dima kronam swokin homrai ko , gu totoka no kwormaepu .
66002004	Ma no swa tru gu dima tyerakra . Gu sem uminki no dima hine pya bramite hakin ko aekwa gu haminkmepu .
66002005	Sem uminki gwa homi pkete kronam ko waenukina , ma aekwa gwa homra ko kwori sryaha . Hakina krenku , gwa hweke ko hra naedna , tmoe sem uminki gwae homite hoko hote homna . Ma kudi gwa hweke hro naedinaemkroko , no kumta gwa twan ko sa ti .
66002006	Ma kronam hiko gu dima aeraha . Ma kronam Nekorai wike ka hominkrai ho ko no a , gu kesu a dinkra .
66002007	Ma kudi gyo kehenamina kroko , Dura Keriso ya wike ko dima trya ho ko daernyai . Ma kru ara dika aika dimkroko , nokwa tyo , ko dei ke ware daenkra God ya sanam hokan hra , ko ko din braema .
66002008	Kwasu gu kwo God ya po penkrai kru tru Keriso ya wike to Smena hokan paka tikminkra yo dima kimna . Swa hi ko kru yo andu me ma mare me hakin kru yo sem pwa asite ,
66002009	ya trya ko gwa hine pyenkra ko no braema . No braema gwa sere me gryo ko pya aemaepu . Ma gwa senkra ko hyena . Kru gwin ka gu dima ikarema tyenkraiko , no braema , ma ko harinkrai kyo ko Ju wike dinkrai . Ma ko ko drinu Ju wike nu wirin . Ko butmin ko Saiten ya wikesa .
66002010	Mare gwa pyenkin diwa tempurome . Daenyai , maren Saiten yo kru gwin gyo bryoko diwa aku bekesin hamo wogitmi . Hamo gu nokwa ko drinu da , hamosa troko , ko gu myaudi , ma gwa hoe ko ware dyaen dyaen to waenukin hokan henina .
66002011	Ma kudi gyo kehenamina kuro daernyai , Dura Keriso ya wike ko dima trya hoko . Kru dika dimkroko ko hote a pureiki .
66002012	Ma God ya po penkra kru ya Keriso ya wike to Pegamon hokan paka tikminkra yo dima kimna .
66002013	Swa hi ko kru krarang rire ko braekraekme kyomekin ho sen ya trya ko , no braema to gwa pra ko Saiten ya yomkraka penkra . Ma no swa tyadaemin kru Aentipa ka yo diroko , gu no kwormaepu .
66002014	Ma no swa gwin gu dima tyerakra . Gua wike gwin ko Beirem ya naegite ho bryoko hominkrai . Yo uminki Berek naegimo yo Isrwaeo wike ko saio tona swokin ko dima daemo , ko kore aeng tya hweke hamike homiti .
66002015	Hote ho bryoko wike gwin guminki hurai ko kesu Nikorai wike ka swama tyo daera hominkrai .
66002016	Hakina krenku gwa hweke ko hro naedna . Ma kudi gu hominaemkroko , aku tru no kumta gyominki grwin bra , krarang no mgatramgite mtra ho me tye .
66002017	Ma kehenamin gyo daenyai , Dure ya Keriso ya wike ko dima trya ko . Ma wike dika Saiten minki grwin braka dimkroko , no kudin maena gwemin ko gwin ko dima dae . Mate ike dmekin kae ka hi nin ko ike ho ti kimin ko dima trusa trusa ma daemi . Ma ike dmekin ko dima daemikrako , kru ho taerwekrai ka sa hi hokan kimin ko ka sa braemkreiki .
66002018	God ya po penkrai kru tru yo Keriso ya wike to Taiataira hokan paka tikminkra yo dima kimna . God ya kya ya kron ko trupe byauwo kae hyenkinkrai hakina , ma ya karike kesu auri disiru dei tinkikrai hakina .
66002019	Ya harya , no braema , kronam gwa hominkra butmin ko . Ma gwa hine pya bra drinuhaki deka gwa tmoe homin da ma gwa huma penkra ko no braema . Uminki gu tmoe kukumasa homite , ma aekwa ko gu hyena hominkra .
66002020	Ma no swa tru gu dima tyera . Ma gu ara Jesebe yo swokin hominkra ko gu diwa naediskinkra . Hamo yaesa harinkra , no ko God ya tyo tyen ara no dinkra . Hamake yo no wike naegimo ko kore aeng tyaka kraekraemin tona ko dima kudin daeminkrai .
66002021	Ma no ya hweke hro naedirnada huma penkra , hamo ya kore tyen kronam hro naedin ko yo a de .
66002022	Hamo no yo sa bedi ti hatomgu yominki kore tyeti ko tren hyena direiki .
66002023	Ma wike ya kronam diwa hominkrai ko , nokwa kuyosu , Keriso ya wike ko braemkreiki , wike butmin ka hine brenkrai ko no braema . Hamo nokwa gua hominkrai dware gyo dima hoe trusa trusama daemikraha .
66002024	Ma Taiataira wike gwin gyo kronam hoko hominkmaepu . Gyo Saiten ya gwemkin nu ho dinkrai hoko a braemkreiki dinkrai . Hamo no gyo dima swa tru a tye .
66002025	Hamo gyo naekin senakroko hosa tumasa senina . Hamosa sa hroko no pki .
66002026	Ma wike dika Saiten yominki grwin bra dimkroko , nokwa ko dima wike gwin tikmin tmoe hyenu ko dima daekraha . Nai ya no dima daete ho bryoko . Hamosu yo auri sasu , wike wa to dinaekin ko pkrapkrasi kukuma tkutkureiki . Ma no ko dima dwarin gye tru daekraha .

66002028	
66002029	Hamo wike dika kehenamena kroko , Dura Keriso ya wike ko dima trya hoko daenyai .
66003001	God ya po penkrai kru tru Keriso ya wike to Sadis hokan paka tikminkra yoko dima kimna . Ma hiko kru dure 7 hamo sa mate pute 7 hamo sa haminten kru hoa swa . Gwa hominkra ko no braema . Wike ko harinkrai gu aiki henkra . Ma gu ko pwene ho bryoko .
66003002	Hamo gu pwena dinaekin aera ko grwyori asi dudumna . Gwa homo no God ya dira ko kukuma dukmaepu .
66003003	Uminki sa gwa daerite hoko hote hine bra hominkna . Ma hweke ko hro naedna . Ma kudi gu krogoe aerwa grwyori asinaemkroko nokwa pkikra tei kron ko gua braemki .
66003004	Ma Sadis hokan penkrai wike gwin gua bai ko tupe wirin . Hamo gyo bai dmekin draeka no me kwe hureiki . Ko ko bryokaena krenku .
66003005	Ma kru ara dika Saiten yominki grwin bra dimkroko , ko bai dmekin hikin draekreiki . Hamo no ka hi ware kwonam hokan kimina aera ko no a sori . Hamo no ko nai ya kinaegite da ma nai ya po penkrai wike ka kinaegite haka no ko naegi ko ko no wike dikraha .
66003006	Hamo gyo kehenamina kroko Dura Keriso ya wike ko dima trya hi ko daernyai .
66003007	God ya po penkrai kru tru yo Keriso wike to Piradepia hokan paka tikminkra yo dima kimna . Kru dumasa tyenin kru , yae yo sa hakina , yo Debid ya ki ko ya senano dinkra . Ma yo inam tyaeroko , kru trua timin braema wirin , ma yo inam timroko , kru trua tyaen braema wirin . Hamo swa hiko ya gu dima tyerakra .
66003008	Ma kronam gwa hominkra ko no braema . Ma ai kukiskin gwa sen hoko no braema . Gu no dima , no yo braema wirin dmaepu .
66003009	Daernya , wike wa Saiten yana harike tyenkrai kyo ko Ju wike dinkrai . Ma hoko drinu wirin , ko ko Junu wirin . Hamosu nokwa ko pru kumta gwa karike tkyo tama drima prako , ko braemkwekraiha nokwa gu dima hine pya brenkra .
66003010	Tenam gu ko , nokwa tyo , pyen gu dima pkra swa ko gu daera aiki heskra krenku , aku , wike butmin bryoko diwekrai aku ho pko diroko , nokwa gu tikmi .
66003011	No katmasa taenkikraha . Ma gu nakoe sena kroko hoko gu pitma tikmna , pako Saiten yominki grwin bra dimkire hoe ko kru trua simeda .
66003012	Ma kru diya Saiten yominki grwin bra dimkroko , no yo sa , no God ya aewe hrukma hmyo tukroko , yo ko no God yankikraha , hamo aewe hoko hote graegite a sye . Hamo no ya buti no God ya hi kimi . Ma no God ya tonae hi nin hoko Jerusraem nin no God ya to Hewen hokan hwya msyekraha . Hamo no ya buti no hi nin kimi .
66003013	Ma dika gyo kehenamena kroko , Dure ya Keriso ya wike ko dima trya ho daernyai .
66003014	God ya po penkrai kru tru yo Keriso ya wike to Reodesia hokan paka tikminkra yo ko dima kimna . Kru tru yo drinu swa sa tyenkra , ma God ya homite su teinam ko yo .
66003015	Hamo ya trya ko , gwa homra ko no braema . Ma gu ko kiokinkmaepu ma gu ko kikinkmaepu . No hoda gu ko ki me hrada o kio me hnada .
66003016	Tenam gu ko kio wirin , me ki wirin ma dru sa kroko , no mgatram gite no gu dima weri .
66003017	Ma gwa trya ko , no ko gryogryo namin kru dra . Ma gryo no dima ko wirinkmaekina wirin dra . Ma gu braema wirin , gu ko kron duka mgyore dinaeka kriskom sa hra .
66003018	Hakina krenku , nokwa hine brenkra hi ko gu dima tyera . No gor ko disiru gwa siroko maren gu sernamin kru kikraha . Hamo bai dmekin hro sa dwae , gwa kriskomkin ko hukwae wirinkrnada . Ma muramura kesu hro sa gwa kron ti hriroko gu dyen braema .
66003019	Ma no kru ara diko nokwa ko dima hine pya brenkrako , hweke hriroko no ko naegimasu dore daenkra . Hakina kren gu hine yoma bra God ya tmoe aiki hominina . Hamake gwa hweke hro naedna .
66003020	Daenya , no inam dwen tkyo haka gwagwarinkra . Hamo kru diya nokwa urya , daera , inam tyaeroko , no ya aewe ta kudin din braema , ma yo kesu nominki kudin din braema .
66003021	Hamo wike dika Saiten yominki grwin bra dimkroko nokwa pru ko ri waenukin dae king ya penkra hokan nominki penina . Nokwa Saiten yominki grwin bra dimki ri naia penkra ko nokwa penkra gyo ke haminina .
66003022	Ma kudi gyo kehenamina kroko Dure yo Keriso ya wike ko dima trya hoko daernyai .
66004001	Swa hiko twya wirinku diroko , no kukmakadi , kwoe komgite inam tru tyaena ho dyere . Ma swa begor wyaen dinaekina sem daere hoa hote tyo daerire . Hamo ya tyere gu mto swa hamosu homwekrai ho gu dima naegimira dire .
66004002	Haru diroko , dumasa Dure waenukin ya no tranmo Hewen hokan kru trua king ya ri hokan po dyere .
66004003	No ya kae ko ike jaspa kinkinkin hakina dyere . Ma king ya ri hawyo ko wai surin sasawe dinaeka dwodwoekina haguri yaepmina dyere .
66004004	Ma hote hamo King ya ri ya penin hawyo ri ko 24 hamo , ma hote hamo wike yomkra 24 hamo ko king ya ri hokan pro dyere . Ma wike yomkra hokan preri ka bai ko dmekinsa brena . Ma ko gor tukin sa ka ku ti brena pro dyere .
66004005	Ma king ya penkra ri hoa kma kimkimki tyo daerire . Ma king ya ri kinaegite ko twan 7 hamo . Hamo hoko God ya dure 7 hamo .
66004006	Ma king ya penkra kinaegite hokan ko gryo tru ae dyere ko wai dawara dinaeka kaenai yae yo sa hakina . Ma ya penkra ri hawyo hokan ware gryogryo 4 hamo hawyo dyere .
66004007	Ma ware gryogryo hyenu hoko psaen raion dinaekina . Ma msya hoko mine boromakau dinaekina . Ma msya tru hoa tikram ko wike ka tokram dinaekina . Ma msya tru ko smire kadama huri pi ka tenkrai hakina dyere .
66004008	Ma ware gryogryo 4 hamo hoka pi butmin ko 6 hamo . Ma ka bute kron ko pya graegite me dure hokan kesu . Ma hune me aku butmin ko harike tyenkrai , Ai butmin ko God gu dima aera . Gu ko waenuka yae yo sa hakina . Gu sem song hena ma aekwa kesu gwae hamo heskra .
66004009	Ma ko kru ware dyaendyaen aepesu henin kru yo ri ya penkra hokan poro ma ware gryogryo itkoesin hamo ko yo dima gu ko duwa da ya hi hya yoyomkin me yoke giri .
66004010	Hamako ma wike yomkra 24 hamo ko kru ware aepesu henin kru yo dima hyawohyawonku dyere . Ma ko gor ka ku ti bren ho hmura hatyo taka kru ya sea ti pra ya kinaegite duduru tyo daerire ko Yomkra , gu ko kua God gu ko waenukina .
66004011	Wike pya ko gu dima yoyomkinkrai . Tenam gryo butmin ko gwasa homite krenku . Gwae gwa hodra hokan sa homa hre mta aenkra .
66005001	Ma no dyere ko kru tru yo king ya sea ti penkra hokan ya krite dunaegite hokan kwo tru ae dyere . Ma kwo hoko tyonamgite me tigite hamo kimena dyere . Ma kwarin ko 7 hamo kwarina dyere .
66005002	Ma God ya po penkrai kru tru ya ai ko hyena , hamo ya aima harike tyere , ma kru diya yo ko duwa , ma kwo hi kwarin ko ya kia draen braemane .
66005003	Ma kwo ho drae kru tru Hewen hokan hmaepu . Ma to hyenu hokan kesu hmaepu , ma to kupram kesu hmaepu .
66005004	Ma drura di kru hakin truato hokan ho dimaepu . Haku diku no idima byere .
66005005	Hamo diroko , ma yomkra trua no dima tyere , gu bryome no dire . Gu daernya , raion tru Juda me Debid ta kyankya , yo yaesa Saiten yominki grwin bra dimkite kren , kwo prima kwarin ho ko ya sa kiya dro dyen braema .
66005006	Ma no mine sip bi ko asi king ya sea ti ho dyere . Ma ware gryogryo 4 hamo ka wike yomkra ka prai dure hokan hwyo dyere . Ma min sip bi hoko yeha dinaekina dyere . Ma ya ku ko ikoke ko 7 hamo , ma ya kron kesu 7 hamo . Ma hoko God ya Dure 7 hamo . Hamo God ya pru ko to hoe hoe taminkrai .
66005007	Ma mine sipbi hoko kuta ya penkra hokan kwo ya krite ti aera ho sera tere .
66005008	Ma ya hamo diroko , ware gryogryo 4 hamo ma yomkra 24 hamo ko mine sipbi dima hyawonhyawonkiri . Ma butmin ko gita me dis gor me homin ho taerina . Hamo dis hoko pauda torina . Ma hoko disiru pom ko dei tuka kwoe dima sa tenina , kru ara ka God dima swa tyenkrai ka swa ko pom waenukin ho bryoko .
66005009	Ma ko yoke nin giri . Hamo kwo kwarin hiko gwasa kiya draen braema . Ka gu yo pwa gwa kapoe me wike swa ate ate butmin ko hro sa kumta God dima daete .
66005010	Hamo gwa hamike homite ko , ko ko God ya prist tmoe homrnaida hamite . Hamo ka king hyenu ko gu . Hamo maren ko ko to hyenu kingkitreiki .
66005011	Ma no hote diwa daera hamire ko God ya po penkrai wike pya ka swa daerire . Ma ware gryogryo 4 hamo ho ka ma wike yomkra ko king ya sea hawyo hwyeri .
66005012	Hamo ko yoke aima giri . Ma mine sipe bi sem yeti yo ko ai me braemkin me yo dima daen ko bryoko .
66005013	Ma ware gryogryo tei ate ate God ya homina Hewen hokan penkrai da ma to hyenu hikan penkrai da ma wai dawaranam penkrai da ma to kupram penkrai da hamo ko kesu yoke giri . Ma kyo , king ya sea ti penkra me mine sip bi ai butmin ti dima aenkra ta hi hiwe .
66005014	Haru diroko ware gryogryo 4 hamo hoka priri , hoko drinuno diri . Ma wike yomkra ko sya tama drima praka God me Yesu ti dima priri , gu su ko duwa diri .
66006001	Ma no dyere ko God ya kya , min sip bi dinkrai hoa kwo kwakwarin dehraensin hamo hoko kiyo dyere . Ma ware gryogryo butmin itkoesin hamo hokan trua aima tyere , gu pkna du , min hos konkina pko dyere .
66006002	Hamo kru tru hokan po dyere ko dimin aepin me taera ta hro po dyere . Ma kru trua king ka maka ka ku kusinkrai tru yo dima daere . Yo ko totetyen dirakin kru dinaeka wike gwin ko dima totetyaka dimkire to dyere .
66006003	Ma mine sip bi dinkrai hoa kwo kwarin tru hoko kiya drae dyere . Hamo diroko , ware gryogryo rasya trua tyere gu pkna no dire .
66006004	Haru diroko , mine hos tru pkire ko kapoekina . Ma kru hos ti po sa tra yo dima ai dae to hyenu hikan dima pkosu totetyen pki , hamo wike ka kum yo yo hamreiki . Hamo yo dima krarang hyenu daere .
66006005	Hamo diroko , mine sipbi dinkrai hoa kwo kwarin tru ko kiyere . Ma ware gryo gryo msya trua tyere , gu kesu pkna dire . Haru no kukmaka di , min hos tru ko hukina pko dyere . Ma kru mine hos ti hokan po tra ya krite ko skeri hmigu dyere .
66006006	Ma no swa tru daerire ko ware gryogryo itkokesin ka hurai hoke tyo daerire . Ma ya tyere , kru trua yo aku tru tmoe homroko , ya hoe sasu , ya da hro sen ko kukiskina , ike dinaekina . Ma aku tru , kesu tmoe homroko , ya hoe sasu , dma beke skauwin trusa hro sen braema . Hamo dei orib me tike byen grep hoko domsoriomoe .
66006007	Ma God ya kya min sip bi dinkrai , hoa kwo kwarin itkoe kiya , drae no dyere . Ma ware gryogryo itkoe hoa tyere gu pkna no dire .
66006008	Haru no kukmakadi , mine hos skukina pko dyere . Ma kru min hos sapkra ya hi ko pwene . Ma ya mare pkire ya hi ko Hero . Ko to hoegite sya wike kuyaka , tren dae tosureka , mate gehmen dae , ware gryogryo tona , kuyaka hamwekraiha .
66006009	Ma hokeko , God ya kya , min sipbi dinkrai , yokwo kwarin yaem ko kiya drae diroko , no ware gryogryo yenkrai kyorin tukram hokan ko wike pro dyere . Ko ko God ya swa ko drinu da naegimin krenku , wike ka ko yaewi .
66006010	Ko aima tyaka priri , O God , gu ko duwa , waenukiskina , hariri . Ma gu aku naemo kru ara kyo kuyaewi ho ko begema dore a daeke diri .
66006011	Hamo yo ko dima bai dmekin daema pri , gyo kriki prasuno dire . Gyo tmaekisknai wike gwin ko kuwya wirinmasu .
66006012	Ma min sip bi yo kwo kwarin tu ho ko kiyo diroko , mimi hyena mta . Hamo diroko , tei ko kriseku , dwarin ko kapoeku hake .
66006013	Hamo diroko , pute ko kwoe hokan hwya totembra hamako hwore mtaka , dei ke dwo msyenkrai hama .
66006014	Ma kwoe ko kasuke primakugwemkinkrai hama . Hamo diroko , dubi me aengu me ko psya ri ate saewi .
66006015	Hokeko , to hyenu yomkra da , mate tmoe homin wike da , tmoe hominaemkin wike da , gryogryonamin wike butmin ko kuta dei sunam o inam o sonam dikan ko hokan gwemkwerada tamewi .
66006016	Aengu me dite gyo kumta kyo sa gwemnano harewi .
66006017	King me ya kya ko kyomka kyo dimeni dewi . Ko kyomku kru tru homin braema wirin .
66007001	Maresu dyere ko , God ya po penkrai wike itkoesin , ka to hyenu krigwotnam hwyaka hwore itkoesin hamo ka sa taetaema hwyo dya . Ma hwore mtaka dei tkwya mate wai dawara takureka hamaka ka ten dwaewi .
66007002	Ma no dira ko God ya po penkrai kru trua yo teia hwirinkragite hwya to dya . Yo ko God yae hamo henkra ya kwarin trusa sa pko dya . Ma ya God ya po pen kru wike gwin itkoesin hamo wike domsorinkrai ko dima ura pri , gyo to me dei me wai dawara katma domsoryomoe de .
66007003	Kyo kua God ya wike ka ku ti maka hrosu no de .
66007004	Hamo ka tyo no daere ko , wike aripe ho taerwekrai ko wan handred end poti po tausen ( 144,000 ) hamo .
66007005	Ka tonesu ko Isrwaeo tweb tausen ( 12,000 ) hamo tonesu trusa trusama taerewi . Tonesu ko Juda me Ruben da ma Gad me Asa da ma Napari me Manasa da ma Simiyon me Ribai da ma Isika me Seburon me Josep me Bensamin hamo .

66007009	Marensu no dyere ko tonesu ate ate da ma swa ate ate da mate kate ate ate hamo pro dya . Hamo wike hoko kuta God me ya kya min sipbi dinkrai ta kinaegite hwyo dya . Ko bai dmekin bra mate dei gryau tkua ka kriteme taera wawarmi hwyo dya .
66007010	Ka tyaewi , gu me gwa kya gi ko taetaepmin tenam nai .
66007011	Ma God ya po penkrai wike butmin wike yomkra me ware gryogryo itkoesin hamo ya pra hawyo hwaewi .
66007012	Ma ko God dima tama drima paka priwi , drinu gu ko duwa gu ko ai me ma gu ko yae hamo hen God harike tyaewi .
66007013	Kru yomkra trua hare , kru bai dmekina breri ko ko dikan hwya pkerike de .
66007014	Haru diroko , nokwa pri , no braema wirin , gu su braema . Ya tya wike hi ko pyenkin hyenu dyeti . Ko God ya kya , min sip dinkrai ka bai ko ya kapoe me sora naedu , dmeki teri .
66007015	Hakina krenku ko kumta God ya kinaegite hokan hurai . Ko hune me aku me God ya aewe hokan tmoe hominkrai . Hamo God ya ko tikminkra .
66007016	Hamo ko gehmen tyaka mate wai tyaka me wai garin mate tei ki tyaka a hamreiki .
66007017	Tenam God ya kya ko tikminkra krenku , yo ware wai sunam hokan dima gyori ta . Hamosu ka kron wai ko God yasa sori .
66008001	God ya kya , min sipbi dinkrai ya kwo kwarin hyaeki dehraen hoko kiyo diroko , wike ko swa tmyaepu . Ki krikrika hwya dyeskewi .
66008002	Ma no God ya po penkrai wike dehraensin hamo dya ko aku butmin God ya pra hokansa hwyenkrai , hamo diroko , kru tru kibi dehraensin ko dima daema .
66008003	Ma God ya po penkrai kru trua kumta pauda pomkin disirinkrai hokan kuri ha .
66008004	Pauda pya ko yo dima dae yo sa disnam disiru , pom me tuke me wike ka God dima swa tryai ho sa ta .
66008005	Marensu yo dei tin ko disnam bra to hoegite ko dripma . Yo dei tin ko dripmo diroko , kma kimkimki kiyaka mimi mtaka hama .
66008006	God ya po penkrai wike butmin 7 hamo , ka kibi kesu 7 hamo , ko kibi urwera huma hwyaewi .
66008007	Ma God ya po pen kru hya hoa ya kibi uru diroko , aisi me dei me kapoe me butko to ti dima msya . Hamo diroko , to hoegite deia duwa . To gwin mate dei gwin mate kose butmin ko deia duwa .
66008008	Ma msya God ya po penkrai kru trua kibi uru diroko dite hyena , deia duwaka kiyori take wai dawara ture .
66008009	Hamo diroko , wai dawara ko kapoea sa ruwore . Hamako wai dawara hoegite ko bun me yokingai da ma mosore me kno kesu domsore .
66008010	Ma God ya po penkrai kru tru msya hoa kibi ure . Hamo dirokoy kwoe kom hokan pute tru ya kae to hyenu toti pkeka hokan dure .
66008011	Ma pute ho ya hi ko gyenkina . Ya toti pkeka wai tu henum hokan kesu dure ko , wike ko wai hoko dua tosurewi .
66008012	Ma God ya po penkrai kru itkoe hoa , ya kibi uru diroko , tei me dwarine me pute ko hunamke . Ma aku braeke me hune braeke ko hunamke .
66008013	Ma no kukmakadi , smire kunoia harike tyo daere , o aenuwe to hokan penkrai wike gyo , hamosu God ya po penkrai kru haepki trumo mta kibi urwerakrai ko de .
66009001	Hokeko , God ya po penkrai kru trua ya kibi uru diroko , pute tru , wike dinaekina kwoe kom hokan hwya hwosori to dima syo dya . Hamo kru trua inam gawekin ho tyaenada ki yo dima daea .
66009002	Ma yo inam hoko tyae diroko , dei tuke hyena mta . Kwoe kae ko tuke hoa mta sa ko , hunamke .
66009003	Ma dei tuke hoa pkyori mta ko , ikusrim dinaekin ho me sa mtamaka kake dinaekin ka sum ho me wike tukwaewi .
66009004	Hamo diroko , kru trua tya , gyo kose , dei yokingai ho me domsorome hare . Gyo kuta kru diya yo ko God ya aripe ya ku dure ti hokan aenaemku diroko , wike hoko sa domsornyano de .
66009005	Hamo ko kuta dwarin yaemsin hamo tukwo diroko tren dyenina . Kake ka sum me hmyo tren dyenkrai hakina .
66009006	Ma ko tren hamo dyakano tosura naedwerakraiha dewi . Ma ko tosurmaepu .
66009007	Ma ikusrim hoko mine hos dinaekina dya . Hamo mine hos hoko totetye naete tweraku dya . Hamo ka totetyen gryogryo taera kunam bra to dya . Ma ka tokram ko wike ka tokram dinaekina .
66009008	Ma ka binmten ko ara ka binmten dinaekina . Ka pete ko raion ka pete dinaekina .
66009009	Ma ka ko ko , bun tete dinaekina arnma buti hokan draekina dya . Ma pi wyaen ko traka hyenma tenkrai wyaen hakina .
66009010	Ma ka sum ko kake sum dinaekin hoa wike kuyewi .
66009011	Ma ka king ko inam gawekin ho tikminkra . Hamo kru ho ya hi , Hibru ka swama hyaewi ko Abadon , ma Grwik ka swama hyaewi ko Aporon . Ma hi hoa ya drike ko domsorin kru .
66009012	Tren hoko wirinkra , ma tren tei hakin ko hote haepki dwerakrai .
66009013	Ma hokeko , God ya po penkrai kru msya hoa , kibi uru , daere . Ma God ya pra kinaegite hokan ko depkyon pauda pomkin disirinkrai hoegite hokan swa tru daere .
66009014	Swa tru hoa God ya po penkrai kru msya tru yo dima tya gu kusya wai Yupreitis hokan kru tona itkoesin hamo tike me pupuma twena aerurai ho ko knora two tamnai de .
66009015	Ka pupumin me hamo pro , aku hi ko pkosu ko tamwekraiha hare . Ma ko wike pya kuwyera de .
66009016	Tona hoka ka totetyen wike ko tu handred miryen hamo ( 200,000,000 ) .
66009017	Ma no ripe krogoekeka di , kru hos taera tenkrai ka ko kutekin ko kapoekapoekina da dowoedowoekina da , sasarkin da hakemin drimo dya . Ma ka min hose ku ko hote psaen raion ku dinaeka . Ma ka mgatramgite hokeko , dei ti dinaekina ruri hwyo dya .
66009018	Hamo dei ti hoa wike pya kuya .
66009019	Ma hos ka ai ko mgatramgite ma sumgite hakina . Ka sum ko sine ku ho bryoko hoa wike tren daea .
66009020	Ma wike kuyenaemkrako ka homina dima hine bren ko naendmaepu . Ko tona dima swa tyaka mate kae ka kriteaie gor me siba me kopa me ike me dei me homin ko ko daereka dyaka mate ten braema wirin hakemin ko dima swa tyaka , sere me kudin daemo , ko taetaemnada haminkrai ko hro naedmaepu .
66009021	Ma ko wike kuwyaka , kae tei atma homaka ara kortyaka , o aengtyaka , wataremaka haminkrai ho ko hro naedmaepu .
66010001	Ma no God ya po penkrai kru tru yo ko ai hyenu hoa kwoe kom hwya msyo dya . Hamo yo ua ruworu wai surin sasawa kome ya ku ti wyaen ho dya . Ma ya tokram ko tei kae dinaekina . Ma ya karike ko dei kae dinaekina .
66010002	Ma ya kritnam ko kwo dro hrena ae dya . Ma ya karike dunaete ko wai dawara tima , ma karike weknaete ko to ti tima hamo ho dya .
66010003	Ma yo aima ure wyen ho ko psaen raion wyaen dinekina .
66010004	Uru diroko , hamo rwyo kyo daere . Ma no ka tryai ho kimirake ko , kru tru kome hokan paka pri , wirin , kimromeno de .

66011003	Hamosu nokwa tyotyenin kru haepki ti pru kumta bai domka krekresiten ho draeka no swa tyadaemra ko aku wan tausen tu handred end siksti hamo ( 1,260 ) .
66011004	Ma ti ko twan haepki dinaeka ma deike haepki dineka God to hyenu homite ya kinaegite hokan hwyenkrai hakina .

66011007	Ma ko God ya swa naegiminkrai ko wirinku diroko , ware gryogryo inam gontegnam prai kumta kominki grwin braka kuryeiki .

66011009	Ma ko kuwya tweti ko aku haepki trumo wirinku kae hamo hokan aerwo wike swa ate ate ko kumta ko hnanemreiki . Ma ko ti a giwa bruki .
66011010	Ma wike ko yoyomkreiki tenam kru haepki ho ti pwenku . Hamo ka kum gryo matum dae matum dae hamreiki , tenam kru haepki ta wike ko dima pyenkin daen krenku .

66013001	Ma tyere hoko wai gunae hokan ha . Ma hoko wirinku diroko , ware gryogryo tru wai dawara nam gite mto dya . Ma ya ikoke ko bekesin hamo . Ma ya ku ko deihraensin dya . Ma ya kutekin ko ikoke hokan draekina aerwo dya . Ma ya ku hokan kimin ko God ya hi su tyen kimina dya .
66013002	Ware gryogryo hoko psaen lepod dinaekina . Ma ya karike ko psaen bea karike dinaekina . Ma ya mgatram ko psaen raion mgatram dinaekina . Ma tyere hoa ware gryogryo ho dima tya , gu no ri sa nokwa yomkra tmoe hominkra ko gwa homra no hare .
66013003	Ma ya ku tru ko mgakwena hama yena pumaekina hamo ae dya , ma yenam hoko gaikina dya .
66013004	Hamo wike ko ware gryogryo hoa homa ho diwa , tyere dima hine bra ya tyo daera hoinaewi . Tenam tmoe ya hominkra ai ko ware gyrogryo ho dima daenku . 66013009	Hamo kru diya yo kehenam mena kroko , daerinina .
66013010	Ma God ya kru diko wogitmira droko ko dumasa yo wogitmin braema . Ma kudi kru tru nyai droko , ko kuta kru ho yen braema . Hamo God ya wike ko God ko drinu pra dinina .
66013011	Hamakadi , ware gryogryo tru tonamgite mto dya . Ma ho ko min sip bi dinaekina . Ma ya ikoke ko haepki , ma ya swa ko tyere swa dinaekina .
66013012	Hamo yo ware gryogryo sem mtere ya ku ti wonam pra grwyorina ho ya kron ti hokan ma ya hinam tya to hyenu wike butmin gyo ware gryogryo sem mta yo dima gu ko duwa dinina de .
66013013	Hamo wike ko hwya dya ko ware gryogryo maresu pke ko yo tei ate ate homa yo dei pru komgite hwyamsya .
66013014	Yo hamike wike ko dima kraekraema homa . Ma ware gryogryo tonam hwya mta hoa wike ko dima tya , ware gryogryo ya ku ti wonam pra grwyorin ya bute ho bryoko homnai de .
66013015	Ma ware gryogryo mare pke hoa ware gryogryo hya krite me homin ho sa huhuru yo swa tyen braema . Ma kru ara dika yo dima gu ko duwa dinaemkroko , ko kuyenina .
66013016	Hamo ware gryogryo ya wike butmin , hyenu me kukin , sere min da mate sere dumkin , da ma hro sen da ma hro senaemkin hamo ko maka ka krite dunaetegite o ka dwe hokan kikimnai de .
66013017	Ma wike dika maka ho ko wirinkuro gryo twa taerin braema wirin . Ma maka hoko ware gryogryo ya hi o ya hi ya namba .
66013018	Ma wike dika ko ko braemnai kroko gyo ware gryogryo ho ya namba hyaeka diwa braemkinina . Namba hoko wike ka hi namba . Ma ya namba ko sik handred end siksti siks hamo ( 666 ) .
66014001	Ma no kukmakadi , mine sip bi dinkrai ko aengu Saion hokan ho dya . Ma wike yominki hwyaewi ka ku ti hokan ya hi me yai ya hi me kimina ho dya . Wike butmin hamo ko wan handred end potipo tausen hamo ( 144,000 ) .
66014002	Ma Hewen hokan wike ka swa tyo no daere ko , kma wyaen dinaeka , mate wai rurin wyaen dinaeka mate wike ka gita yenkrai wyen hakina daere .
66014003	Ma wike 144,000 ko God ya pra da mate ware gryogryo itkoesin mate wike yomkra hokan hwyo dya . Hamo ko yoke nin giwi . Ma yoke hoko ka sa braema .
66014004	Wike hiko ara kominki kronam swokin hominaemka kraekraeminaemka , mate min sip bi yo dike to ko me tenkrai . Hamo to hyenu wike hi ko God ya ko ko hya hro sete .

66014007	Hamo yo aima uri tyaka pri , gyo God dima tempwaka , yo ko hyena yo ko aiya dinkrnai . Hamaka ya kwoe homite da mate to hyenu homite da mate wai homa mate wai sura bra tu henum hwya komdwa bra pkinin da hamo homite . Hamo yo dima , gu ko duwa dinina . Ma aekwa hi ko God ya begemin aku .

66015001	Ma kronam tru kwoe kom hokan no dya ko a braemkmaekina . God ya po penkrai kru dehraensin hamo diwa , mate ka kritme tren dehraensin hamo taera hwyo dya . Hoko daemroko , God ya kyom ko wirinki .

66016001	Hamo kru tru aewe Tempo hokan ha , ya God ya po penkrai wike ko dima uri tyo tlo daere . Ya tya ko kuta God ya kyom dis dehraensin hamo hokan aera ho taera togite dridripma no de .
66016002	Haru diroko , God ya po penkrai kru tru yo yatumki kuta dis tru yana ko dripma . Ma wike dika ko ware gryogryo ya maka sena o yo bryoko kritme homin ho dima gu ko aiya duwa dewi ka bute ko wonama ruwore .

66016013	Ma tyere ya mgatramgite da mate ware gryogryo ya mgatramgite da mate kraekraema tyadaemin kru ya mgatramgite da dure swokin ko ka mgatramgite pkyore dinaekemena pkemo dya .
66016014	Hamo dure ho kumta kronam tei atma homaewi . Ko kuta tonaesu ate ate ka yomkra ko dima tyaewi , gyo gaema God dima totetinai dewi .

66016017	Ma God ya po penkrai kru tru dehraen hoa ya dis ko sa , dure hwyaepe hokan dripma . Ma kru trua God ya sea ti paka tya , kwasu wirinkirakrako de .

66017013	Hamo yomkra gwin ka yo dima harieki gu ko kua yomkra duwe dreki .

66019010	Hamako no sya ya karike tkyo paka pri , no gu duwa dira de . Haru ya pri , wirin , gu hamromoe . Gu me no me ki ko God ya tmoe homin wikesa de . Kyo God dimasa gu ko duwa dwe . 66020001	Hamo hokeko , no God ya po penkrai kru tru ko kwoe kom hokan hwya syo dya . Ma yo inam gaweka hoe dyenaemkina hoa ya ko me sen me hamosa msyo dya .

66020004	Hamo no dya ko wike king ka sea ti pro dya . God ya begemin tmoe ko dima dae hamo dya . Hamo no God ya swa tyadaemin wike ka ku gwaewi ka dure dya . Ma ko ware gryogryo wa krite me homaewi ho ya dure dima ko hine brumaepu . Hamake , ma ko ya hi ka ku ti hokan kimaepu . Hamo ko durkyo warki asino Keriso yominki 1000 yeas hamo hwyo dya . Ma ko katumki durkyo asi , 1000 yeas hamo hwyosu .
66020005	
66020006	Wike hoko hote pwen aku ho pko diroko ko a tempureki . Ko God me Keriso timinki hamosa yoyomki hwenku .
66020007	Ma ambum 1000 yeas hoko wirinku diroko , Saiten yo wogitmiti ko hma hrireki .
66020008	Yo hma hre mta no yo to hoegite hoegite kwe haka wike Gog me Magog ko dima kraekraema tye kwe . Hamo ko hapke gaemo totetiwera . Ko ko hyaeka kwarmaekina wirin . Atyon ptenamin hirinkrai hakina .
66020009	Hamo ko kumta to Jerusraem hagewi . Ma God ya wike ko to Jerusraem hokan paewi . Hamako God ya dei ko kom Hewen hokan hwya msya ko dua .
66020010	Hamo diroko , Saiten ya ko dima kraekraemite kren ka yo sa dei sryesryekina duwe henkra hokan hasirewi . Ma hokan ko ware gryogryo me kraekraema tyadaemin kru ho ti sem hokan hatyewi ko hokan hurai . Ma ka tren dyenkrai ko dyaen dyaen hoe yen braema wirin .
66020011	Hamo diroko , no God ya sea tru dmekina hyena dya . Ma kru tru ko hokan po dya . Ma kwoe me to me ko yo diwa , hwara taewi . Ma ho ko to hote dimaepu .
66020012	Ma hoko diwa wirinku diroko , wike tosurewi wike yomkra da kya kuku hamo ko king ya sea kinaegite hoke hwyo dya . Ko hokan hwyako God ya wike ko kwo ko draedraemewi . Ma kwo trusa ko ware kwo . Hamo kwo hoko tosurin wike ka naemike homiti ho kimin ho hyaeka begemaewi .
66020013	Hamo wike waia yen da mate ya to hre aeka domkin da ko akwasi begemewi .
66020014	Hamosu pwen me Her me ko dei duwen tonae hasirewi . ( Ka hote tosurwekrai ko dei duwen tonae hokan dima treki . )
66020015	Hamo kru ara dika ka hi ko ware kwonam hokan kiminaekin ko taera dei duen tonae dima hatyaewi .
66021001	Ma no tru dya ko kwoe nin mate to nin hamo dya . Ma wai dawara ko dimaepu . Tenam to me kwoe me ko gwemkinku .
66021002	Hamo no hote kukmakadi , to Jerusraem nin ko Hewen hokan hwya msyo dya . Hamo yo ara semwera kutekin nin waenukinsa driminkra hakina , drima msyo dya .
66021003	Ma swa tru tyo pko daere ko , hamosu God yo kumta ya wike kominki hi ko du , daere . Hamo ko ko ya wike nu du daere .
66021004	Hamo yo kumta kominki ho diroko , ka byen kron wai da mate ka tren da mate yoyomkinaemkin da mate kronam ate hakin ko hote a direki .
66021005	Ma kru God ya sea ti pra hoa tya , no kronam butmin ko nin homirakra de . Nokwa trya ko drinu . Hamo gu drinu da kimna .
66021006	No hosu gryogryo ko maresu mtamena . Hamo gryogryo butmin ko wirinka naedu no hamo hi . Ma kru ara dika ko ware dyaendyaen ho dima wai garin tiroko , no ko dima ware wai hoko sumsa daemi .
66021007	Ma Saiten yominki grwin bruroko , hamo no ko ka God ku , mate ko ko no kya ku hami .
66021008	Ma wike dika ko no kwika , kronam ate ate homake kaesa gryogryo kriteme homa hro , hoko ka god nu no da , ma God nu ko sa kuta magite hro , hamake wike gwin kraekraemaka haminkrai wike hoko ko marensu taera dei sryesryekina ruri henkra hokan hatireki . Hokan ko hote pwenina .
66021009	Hamo God ya po penkrai kru trua yo no dima tya , gu hike pko min sip bi dinaekina ara yo dima semwekra ho naegira de .
66021010	Hamo hokeko Dura no trnama God ya po pen kru trua no sa kuta aengu ti hokan hrea . Hamo diroko , God ya to waenukin Jerusraem ko kome hokan hwya msyo dya .
66021011	Ma to hoko God ya kae mena . Ma kae hoko tei daea dri o to ti dikan hmyo , yokingai kukukemena hokan aerwaka kikimki arwenkrai hakina . Ma grare hoko gawa hyena .
66021012	Hamo grare hokan inam ko kosin hamo ma God ya po penkrai ko kesu kosin hamo . Hamo ko grare inam hyaekin titikma hwyaewi . Ma Isrwaeo wike ka tei dudute hi ko kosin hamo ko grare inam dwen ti hokan kinkimaewi .
66021013	Hamo tei dima gite ko inam haepki trumo , mate tute hoegite ko haepki trumo , mate tute hoegite kesu haepki trumo .
66021014	Hamo hruke ti hokan ko min sip dinaekina ya pru ten ka hi kosin hokan kimina .
66021015	Ma God ya po pen kru tru yo to ho ya auri rula me bryokaebryokaema ko , ya gau me ya hyen hoko tu tausen po handred kirometes ( 2400Km ) hamo .
66021016	
66021017	Ma kru hoa yo hote grare ho bryokaebryokaema , ya gauwe ko 60 mites hamo . Mate ya dmurekin ko bryokaebryokaema , wan handred end potipo mites hamo ( 144m ) . Ma God ya po penkrai kru bryokae-bryokaeminkrai ho bryoko homa .
66021018	Ma to hoa ya grare ko ike tru ya hi ko Jaespa , kine ko waenukina , hamo home hrena . Ma ike hosa wirin , ike yae tei ate ate krisekin da mate dwoedwoekin da , hukin da , ike tei ate ate waenukina pkemin home hrena . Hamo to hoa ya aew me ya togoe me ko gor me homa naedu wai gin dyen dinaekina .
66021019	
66021020	
66021021	Ma to hoa ya grare inam timin ko sunoi wai dawara hokan taerinkrai hakin home timina .
66021022	Hamo to hoko Tempo aewe ko wirin . Tenam God ya kya ti hokan hwyenku .
66021023	Ma to hokan ko kae ate ko wiriri , tei kae , ma dwarin kae ko wirin . God ya kya Yesu ta kae sa kaema aea .
66021024	Hamo kae hoasa to hoe hoe butmin hamo kaema ae diroko kae hoa to hyenu wike yomkra hoegite hoegite ko ka sere me ka kutekin sa sampkreki .
66021025	Hamo diroko , inam ko a timreki , hamake , ma a hunamki .
66021026	Hamo diroko , kru ara to ate ate ka gryogryo me ka sere ko taera to hyenu hokan dima treki .
66021027	Ma gryogryo ka drimiri hoko tupminka mate kraekraemaka , wike kornam hakemen ko a mtreki . Hamo kru ara ka hi God ya ware kwonam kimin hokesa mtreki .
66022001	Hamo God ya po penkrai kru hoa ware wai ko God ya kya ta sea ti prai , hokan aeka msyenkra ho naegi .
66022002	Ma wai hoko tupe dumka kaenai waenu yae yosa hakina psya . Ma wai hoko to ya ten dure hokan dumasa bra hatomgu tenkra . Hamo wai di gunae braeke breke hokan ko ware dei ko hokan hwyo dya . Ma ka ke yenkrai ko dwarin hyaekinsa . Hamo ka woe ko wike tren min ko homu gaikinkrai .
66022003	Ma to hokan ko kronam swokin tru ko wirin , tenam to hokan ko God ya kya ti penku . Hakina krenku ya wike ko yo dima hine pya brureki .
66022004	Ma ko ya tokram diwekraiha . Hamo ya hi ko dwe ti hokan kimreki .
66022005	Ma hokeko a hunamki . Ma twan kae wirin me tei kae kesu wirin , tenam Yomkra God yo ko ka kae . Hamo wike hokan pwekrai ko yomkra tmoe aepesu dyaen dyaen homreki .
66022006	Ma no swa hi ko drinu trya . Hamo gyo yoma hine brenina . Ma God yo ya Dure ko ya tyo tyen wike ko dima daenkra , hamo ya po penkrai kru pru msya kronam naekin hamosu taenkira kurya ho hi naegimraha .
66022007	Hamo Yesu ya tya daernyai , nokwa pmae ko sem kurya . Hamo kru ara dika ko kronam hamosu taenkirakra swa hi kwo nam kimina aera hi hyaeka hine pya homroko ko yoyomkwekraiha .
66022008	Ma no ko Jon , hamo nokwa kronam hi ko butmin diwa daere . Ma nokwa daera diwa hamra wirinku diroko , God ya po penkrai kru kronam hi no dima naegimo sya ya karike tkyo tama drima paka gu ko duwa dirakeka , ya hare , wirin , gu hamromeno hare .
66022009	No kesu tmoe homin krusa . Gu me Yesu ya wike gyo me wike ka kwonam kimin ho hyaeka diwa hominkrai ma ko kesu ko tmoe homin wikesa . Hamo gyo God dima gu ko duwa dinina .
66022010	Hamo ya no dima tya , kronam hamosu taenkirakra kwonam hi kimina aera ko gu kwari gwema hriome no hare . Kronam hi taenkirakra ko sem kurya ko de .
66022011	Hamo kru ara dika ko kronam swokin homrai ko ko ho sa homi treki . Ma kru ara dika ko kronam waenukin homrai ko ko ho sa homi treki .
66022012	Yesu ya tya ko nokwa pkmae ko sem kurya , ma no no wike ka naemike hominkrai ka hoe kesu taera pki . Ma tmoe ka naemike homiti ka hoe ko no trusa trusa ko dima prnye .
66022013	No ko natumki hena , hamo no nae hamo hen kra . Kronam butmin nokwa sa dmyaena ma noko kru hya . Mate gryogryo butmin yanai ko nokwasa .
66022014	Ma kru ara dika ka bai ko sosoma tupe dumka ko kuta to hyenu waenukin ho ya grare inam ho tasu , ware dei ke hoko droko ko yoyomkreki .
66022015	Ma kru ara dika ko psaen dinaeka , ko God ya swa ko daerinaemka , kore aengtyaka , wike sa yaka , mate to snaem sa krika hamake , ma tona ate dimasa hine braka mate kraekraema tyaka , kronam hakin hominkrai ko God ya tonae ko ko graegitesa preki .
66022016	Ma no ko Yesu , hamo no popenkrai kru tru pru sya no tmoe homin wike gyo dima swa trnyada . Ma no wikema hamteti ko Debid ko no kingwamha . Hamo no ko pute dwarin gye hyenu ukan kaekinkra howa .
66022017	Ma Dure Waenukin yo me mate ara God ya kya ya sekra ta tryai , gu pkna . Hamo wike dika swa hi daeryai gua kesu gu pkna dnai . Hamo kru ara dika ko ware wai ho dwera garin tiroko , gyo kumta sumsa dinina .
66022018	Ma no ko Jon , hamo no swa tru hi tyerakra , gyo daera braemknai . Ma kru ara dika ko hamosu homwekrai swa kwonam hikan kimin ho daera , swa gwin kimroko , God yo tren kwonam hikan tyen hoko ko dima dae .
66022019	Hamo kru ara dika hamosu homwekai swa kwonam kimin gwin ko tigi wama hatiroko , God ya to waenukin hokan paka ware dei ke ko ko a dreki .
66022020	Hamo kru swa hi trya ko drinu . Nokwa pkmae ko sem kurya . Hene Yomkra Yesu gu pkna .
66022021	Yomkra Yesu Keriso ya proekin waenukin ho ko kumta gyo dima yae hamo aenada .
